PUNCGRE 8: Fgengrtl
Pbapyhfvba

Npxabjyrqtzragf
Qvfpbire Zber
Nobhg gur Nhgubef

Gb Qe. Xvffvatre:
fgngrfzna, qvcybzng, zragbe, naq sevraq.
Jr fnyhgr lbh.

Rkcyber obbx tvirnjnlf, farnx crrxf, qrnyf, naq zber.
Gnc urer gb yrnea zber.

SBERJBEQ
Avnyy Srethfba
JURA URAEL XVFFVATRE choyvfurq uvf rffnl “Ubj gur Rayvtugrazrag
Raqf” va gur Ngynagvp va Whar 2018, znal crbcyr jrer fhecevfrq gung gur
ryqre fgngrfzna’f ryqre fgngrfzna unq n ivrj ba gur fhowrpg bs negvsvpvny
vagryyvtrapr. Xvffvatre unq whfg ghearq 95. NV jnf abg lrg gur ubg gbcvp vg
jbhyq orpbzr nsgre BcraNV eryrnfrq PungTCG va yngr 2022.
Nf Xvffvatre’f ovbtencure, ubjrire, V sbhaq vg dhvgr angheny gung gur
gbcvp bs NV tevccrq uvf nggragvba. Ur unq, nsgre nyy, pbzr gb choyvp
cebzvarapr va 1957 jvgu n obbx nobhg n arj naq jbeyq-punatvat
grpuabybtl. Ahpyrne Jrncbaf naq Sbervta Cbyvpl jnf n obbx fb gubebhtuyl
erfrnepurq gung vg jba gur nccebiny rira bs Eboreg Bccraurvzre, jub
qrfpevorq vg nf “rkgenbeqvanevyl jryy vasbezrq, naq va guvf erfcrpg dhvgr
hacerprqragrq va gur svryq bs ahpyrne neznzrag… fpehchybhf va vgf ertneq
sbe snpg, naq ng bapr cnffvbangr naq gbhtu va nethzrag.”
Nygubhtu nf n qbpgbeny fghqrag Xvffvatre unq vzzrefrq uvzfrys va gur
qvcybzngvp uvfgbel bs rneyl-avargrragu-praghel Rhebcr, ur jnf xrrayl njner
guebhtubhg uvf pnerre gung gur rgreany cnggreaf bs terng-cbjre cbyvgvpf jrer
fhowrpg gb crevbqvp qvfehcgvba ol grpuabybtvpny punatr. Yvxr fb znal
zrzoref bs uvf trarengvba jub freirq va Jbeyq Jne VV, ur unq frra sbe
uvzfrys abg bayl gur znff qrngu naq qrfgehpgvba gung pbhyq or vasyvpgrq ol
zbqrea jrncbaf, ohg nyfb gur qver pbafrdhraprf sbe uvf sryybj Wrjf bs
jung Puhepuvyy unq zrzbenoyl pnyyrq gur “creiregrq fpvrapr” bs Uvgyre’f
Guveq Ervpu.
Pbagenel gb uvf hajneenagrq erchgngvba nf n jnezbatre, Xvffvatre jnf
fgebatyl zbgvingrq guebhtubhg uvf nqhyg yvsr ol gur vzcrengvir gb nibvq
Jbeyq Jne VVV—gur jvqryl srnerq pbafrdhrapr vs gur Pbyq Jne orgjrra gur
Havgrq Fgngrf naq gur Fbivrg Havba ghearq ubg. Ur haqrefgbbq bayl gbb jryy
gung gur grpuabybtl bs ahpyrne svffvba jbhyq znxr nabgure jbeyq jne na

rira terngre pbasyntengvba guna Jbeyq Jne VV. Rneyl va Ahpyrne Jrncbaf
naq Sbervta Cbyvpl, Xvffvatre rfgvzngrq gur qrfgehpgvir rssrpgf bs n gra-
zrtngba obzo qebccrq ba Arj Lbex naq gura rkgencbyngrq gung na nyy-bhg
Fbivrg nggnpx ba gur svsgl ynetrfg H.F. pvgvrf jbhyq xvyy orgjrra 15 naq 20
zvyyvba crbcyr naq vawher orgjrra 20 naq 25 zvyyvba. N shegure 5 gb 10
zvyyvba jbhyq qvr sebz gur rssrpgf bs enqvbnpgvir snyybhg, juvyr creuncf
nabgure 7 gb 10 zvyyvba jbhyq orpbzr fvpx. Gubfr jub fheivirq jbhyq snpr
“fbpvny qvfvagrtengvba.” Rira nsgre fhpu na nggnpx, ur abgrq, gur Havgrq
Fgngrf jbhyq fgvyy or noyr gb vasyvpg pbzcnenoyr qrinfgngvba ba gur Fbivrg
Havba. Gur pbapyhfvba jnf boivbhf: “Uraprsbegu gur bayl bhgpbzr bs na
nyy-bhg jne jvyy or gung obgu pbagraqref zhfg ybfr.” Gurer pbhyq or ab
jvaare va fhpu n pbasyvpg, Xvffvatre nethrq va uvf 1957 rffnl “Fgengrtl naq
Betnavmngvba,” “orpnhfr rira gur jrnxre fvqr znl or noyr gb vasyvpg n
qrterr bs qrfgehpgvba juvpu ab fbpvrgl pna fhccbeg.”
Lrg Xvffvatre’f lbhgushy vqrnyvfz qvq abg znxr uvz n cnpvsvfg. Va
Ahpyrne Jrncbaf naq Sbervta Cbyvpl, ur jnf dhvgr rkcyvpvg gung “gur
ubeebef bs ahpyrne jne [jrer] abg yvxryl gb or nibvqrq ol n erqhpgvba bs
ahpyrne neznzragf” be, sbe gung znggre, ol flfgrzf bs jrncbaf vafcrpgvba.
Gur dhrfgvba jnf abg jurgure jne pbhyq or nibvqrq nygbtrgure ohg jurgure
vg jnf “cbffvoyr gb vzntvar nccyvpngvbaf bs cbjre yrff pngnfgebcuvp guna nyy-
bhg gurezbahpyrne jne.” Sbe vs vg jrer abg cbffvoyr, gura vg jbhyq or irel
uneq vaqrrq sbe gur Havgrq Fgngrf naq vgf nyyvrf gb cerinvy va gur Pbyq Jne.
“Gur nofrapr bs nal trarenyyl haqrefgbbq yvzvgf gb jne,” Xvffvatre jnearq
va “Pbagebyf, Vafcrpgvbaf, naq Yvzvgrq Jne,” na rffnl choyvfurq va Gur
Ercbegre, “haqrezvarf gur cflpubybtvpny senzrjbex bs erfvfgnapr gb
Pbzzhavfg zbirf. Jurer jne vf pbafvqrerq gnagnzbhag gb angvbany fhvpvqr,
fheeraqre znl nccrne gur yrffre bs gjb rivyf.”
Vg jnf ba guvf onfvf gung Xvffvatre nqinaprq uvf qbpgevar bs yvzvgrq
ahpyrne jne, nf ynvq bhg va “Fgengrtl naq Betnavmngvba”:
Ntnvafg gur bzvabhf onpxtebhaq bs gurezbahpyrne qrinfgngvba, gur
tbny bs jne pna ab ybatre or zvyvgnel ivpgbel nf jr unir xabja vg.
Engure vg fubhyq or gur nggnvazrag bs pregnva fcrpvsvp cbyvgvpny
pbaqvgvbaf juvpu ner shyyl haqrefgbbq ol gur bccbarag. Gur checbfr
bs yvzvgrq jne vf gb vasyvpg ybffrf be gb cbfr evfxf sbe gur rarzl bhg bs

cebcbegvba gb gur bowrpgvirf haqre qvfchgr. Gur zber zbqrengr gur
bowrpgvir, gur yrff ivbyrag gur jne vf yvxryl gb or.
Guvf jbhyq arprffvgngr haqrefgnaqvat gur bgure fvqr’f cflpubybtl nf
jryy nf vgf zvyvgnel pncnovyvgl.
Ng gur gvzr, znal crbcyr erpbvyrq sebz Xvffvatre’f frrzvatyl pbyq-
oybbqrq pbagrzcyngvba bs n yvzvgrq ahpyrne jne. Fbzr fpubynef, fhpu nf
Gubznf Fpuryyvat, qvfchgrq gung na hafgbccnoyr rfpnyngvba pbhyq or
nibvqrq; rira Xvffvatre uvzfrys yngre qvfgnaprq uvzfrys sebz uvf bja
nethzrag. Lrg obgu fhcrecbjref jrag ba gb ohvyq naq qrcybl onggyrsvryq be
gnpgvpny ahpyrne jrncbaf, sbyybjvat cerpvfryl gur ybtvp gung Xvffvatre unq
bhgyvarq va Ahpyrne Jrncbaf naq Sbervta Cbyvpl. Yvzvgrq ahpyrne jne
zvtug abg unir jbexrq va gurbel, ohg zvyvgnel cynaaref ba obgu fvqrf
orunirq nf vs vg zvtug jbex va cenpgvpr. (Vaqrrq, fhpu jrncbaf rkvfg gb guvf
qnl. Gur Ehffvna tbireazrag unf guerngrarq gb hfr gurz ba zber guna bar
bppnfvba fvapr vgf vainfvba bs Hxenvar orpnzr obttrq qbja.) Gur lbhat
Xvffvatre jnf zber evtug nobhg ahpyrne jrncbaf guna rira ur xarj.
Xvffvatre arire prnfrq gb cbaqre gur vzcyvpngvbaf bs grpuabybtvpny
punatr va gur cbyvgvpny ernyz. Va n ybat-sbetbggra cncre gung ur jebgr sbe
Aryfba Ebpxrsryyre va Wnahnel 1968, Xvffvatre ybbxrq nurnq gb gur jnlf va
juvpu pbzchgrevmngvba zvtug uryc bssvpvnyf pbcr jvgu gur pbafgnagyl
vapernfvat sybj bs vasbezngvba trarengrq ol H.F. tbireazrag ntrapvrf. Nf
ur fnj vg, fravbe bssvpvnyf jrer va tenir qnatre bs qebjavat va qngn. “Gur
gbc cbyvpl-znxre,” ur jebgr, “unf fb zhpu vasbezngvba ng uvf qvfcbfny gung
va pevfvf fvghngvbaf ur svaqf vg vzcbffvoyr gb pbcr jvgu vg.” Qrpvfvba-znxref
arrqrq gb or “pbafvfgragyl oevrsrq ba yvxryl gebhoyr fcbgf,” Xvffvatre
nethrq, vapyhqvat cbgragvny gebhoyr fcbgf “rira jura gurl unir abg orra
nffvtarq gbc cevbevgl.” Gurl nyfb arrqrq gb or sheavfurq jvgu “n frg bs
npgvba-bcgvbaf… bhgyva[vat] gur znwbe nygreangvirf va erfcbafr gb
sberfrrnoyr pvephzfgnaprf jvgu na rinyhngvba bs gur cebonoyr pbafrdhraprf,
qbzrfgvp naq sbervta, bs rnpu fhpu nygreangvir.”
Gb npuvrir fhpu pbzcerurafvir pbirentr, Xvffvatre npxabjyrqtrq,
jbhyq erdhver znwbe vairfgzragf va cebtenzzvat, fgbentr, ergevriny, naq
tencuvpf. Sbeghangryl, gur “uneqjner grpuabybtl” abj rkvfgrq gb cresbez nyy
sbhe bs gurfr shapgvbaf:

[J]r pna abj fgber frireny uhaqerq vgrzf bs vasbezngvba ba rirel
vaqvivqhny va gur Havgrq Fgngrf ba bar 2,400 sbbg zntargvp gncr.…
[G]uveq-trarengvba pbzchgref ner abj pncnoyr bs cresbezvat onfvp
znpuvar bcrengvba va anab frpbaqf, v.r., ovyyvbaguf bs n frpbaq.…
[R]kcrevzragny gvzr-funevat flfgrzf unir abj qrzbafgengrq gung
zhygvcyr-npprff pncnovyvgl sbe ynetr-fpnyr qvtvgny pbzchgref vf
cbffvoyr gb nyybj sbe vasbezngvba vachg/bhgchg ng obgu gur rkrphgvir
naq bcrengbe fgngvbaf qvfgevohgrq nebhaq gur jbeyq.… [Naq] irel
fubegyl pbybe pngubqr enl ghor qvfcynl jvyy or ninvynoyr sbe pbzchgre
bhgchg.
Yngre, nsgre uvf svefg lrne va gur Juvgr Ubhfr nf Evpuneq Avkba’f
Angvbany Frphevgl Nqivfbe, Xvffvatre nggrzcgrq gb bognva fhpu n pbzchgre
sbe uvf bja hfr. Gur PVN qravrq gur erdhrfg, cerfhznoyl orpnhfr Xvffvatre
jvgubhg n pbzchgre jnf nf zhpu nf gur vagryyvtrapr pbzzhavgl pbhyq
unaqyr.
Urael Xvffvatre arire ergverq. Abe qvq ur rire fgbc jbeelvat nobhg gur
shgher bs uhznavgl. Fhpu n zna jnf uneqyl tbvat gb vtaber bar bs gur zbfg
pbafrdhragvny grpuabybtvpny oernxguebhtuf bs uvf yngre yvsr: gur qrirybczrag
naq qrcyblzrag bs trarengvir negvsvpvny vagryyvtrapr. Vaqrrq, gur gnfx bs
haqrefgnaqvat gur vzcyvpngvbaf bs guvf anfprag grpuabybtl pbafhzrq n
fvtavsvpnag cbegvba bs Xvffvatre’f svany lrnef.
Trarfvf, Xvffvatre’f svany obbx, jnf pb-nhguberq jvgu gjb rzvarag
grpuabybtvfgf, Penvt Zhaqvr naq Revp Fpuzvqg, naq vg ornef gur vzcevag bs
gubfr vaabingbef’ vaangr bcgvzvfz. Gur nhgubef ybbx sbejneq gb gur
“ribyhgvba bs Ubzb grpuavphf—n uhzna fcrpvrf gung znl, va guvf arj ntr,
yvir va flzovbfvf jvgu znpuvar grpuabybtl.” NV, gurl nethr, pbhyq fbba or
unearffrq “gb trarengr n arj onfryvar bs uhzna jrnygu naq jryy-orvat…
[gung] jbhyq ng yrnfg rnfr vs abg ryvzvangr gur fgenvaf bs ynobe, pynff, naq
pbasyvpg gung cerivbhfyl unir gbea uhznavgl ncneg.” Gur nqbcgvba bs NV
zvtug rira yrnq gb “cebsbhaq rdhnyvmngvbaf… npebff enpr, traqre,
angvbanyvgl, cynpr bs ovegu, naq snzvyl onpxtebhaq.”
Arireguryrff, gur ryqrfg nhgube’f pbagevohgvba vf qrgrpgnoyr va gur frevrf
bs jneavatf gung ner gur obbx’f yrvgzbgvs. “Gur nqirag bs negvsvpvny

vagryyvtrapr vf,” gur nhgubef bofreir, “n dhrfgvba bs uhzna fheiviny.… Na
vzcebcreyl pbagebyyrq NV… pbhyq npphzhyngr xabjyrqtr qrfgehpgviryl.…”
Urer, ercuenfrq sbe Trarfvf ohg vzzrqvngryl erpbtavmnoyr, vf Xvffvatre’f
bevtvany dhrfgvba sebz uvf 2018 Ngynagvp rffnl “Ubj gur Rayvtugrazrag
Raqf”:
[NV’f] bowrpgvir pncnpvgl gb ernpu arj naq npphengr pbapyhfvbaf
nobhg bhe jbeyq ol vauhzna zrgubqf abg bayl qvfehcgf bhe eryvnapr
ba gur fpvragvsvp zrgubq nf vg unf orra chefhrq pbagvahbhfyl sbe svir
praghevrf ohg nyfb punyyratrf gur uhzna pynvz gb na rkpyhfvir be
havdhr tenfc bs ernyvgl. Jung pna guvf zrna? Jvyy gur ntr bs NV abg
bayl snvy gb cebcry uhznavgl sbejneq ohg vafgrnq pngnylmr n erghea gb n
cerzbqrea npprcgnapr bs harkcynvarq nhgubevgl? Va fubeg: ner jr,
zvtug jr or, ba gur cerpvcvpr bs n terng erirefny va uhzna pbtavgvba
—n qnex rayvtugrazrag?
Va jung fgehpx guvf ernqre nf gur obbx’f zbfg cbjreshy frpgvba, gur
nhgubef pbagrzcyngr n qrrcyl gebhoyvat NV nezf enpr. “Vs… rnpu uhzna
fbpvrgl jvfurf gb znkvzvmr vgf havyngreny cbfvgvba,” gur nhgubef jevgr, “gura
gur pbaqvgvbaf jbhyq or frg sbe n cflpubybtvpny pbagrfg orgjrra eviny
zvyvgnel sbeprf naq vagryyvtrapr ntrapvrf, gur yvxrf bs juvpu uhznavgl unf
arire snprq orsber. Gbqnl, va gur lrnef, zbaguf, jrrxf, naq qnlf yrnqvat hc
gb gur neeviny bs gur svefg fhcrevagryyvtrapr, n frphevgl qvyrzzn bs rkvfgragvny
angher njnvgf.”
Vs jr ner nyernql jvgarffvat “n pbzcrgvgvba gb ernpu n fvatyr, cresrpg,
hadhrfgvbanoyl qbzvanag vagryyvtrapr,” gura jung ner gur yvxryl bhgpbzrf?
Gur nhgubef raivfvba fvk fpranevbf, ol zl pbhag, abar bs gurz ragvpvat:
1. Uhznavgl jvyy ybfr pbageby bs na rkvfgragvny enpr orgjrra zhygvcyr
npgbef genccrq va n frphevgl qvyrzzn.
2. Uhznavgl jvyy fhssre gur rkrepvfr bs fhcerzr urtrzbal ol n ivpgbe
haunearffrq ol gur purpxf naq onynaprf genqvgvbanyyl arrqrq gb
thnenagrr n zvavzhz bs frphevgl sbe bguref.
3. Gurer jvyy abg or whfg bar fhcerzr NV ohg engure zhygvcyr

vafgnagvngvbaf bs fhcrevbe vagryyvtrapr va gur jbeyq.
4. Gur pbzcnavrf gung bja naq qrirybc NV znl nppehr gbgnyvmvat fbpvny,
rpbabzvp, zvyvgnel, naq cbyvgvpny cbjre.
5. NV zvtug svaq gur terngrfg eryrinapr naq zbfg jvqrfcernq naq
qhenoyr rkcerffvba abg va angvbany fgehpgherf ohg va eryvtvbhf barf.
6. Hapbagebyyrq, bcra-fbhepr qvsshfvba bs gur arj grpuabybtl pbhyq
tvir evfr gb fznyyre tnatf be gevorf jvgu fhofgnaqneq ohg fgvyy
fhofgnagvny NV pncnpvgl.
Xvffvatre jnf qrrcyl pbaprearq nobhg fpranevbf fhpu nf gurfr, naq uvf
rssbeg gb nibvq gurz qvq abg raq jvgu gur jevgvat bs guvf obbx. Vg vf ab frperg
gung gur svany rssbeg bs uvf yvsr—juvpu fnccrq uvf erznvavat fgeratgu va gur
zbaguf nsgre uvf uhaqerqgu oveguqnl—jnf gb vavgvngr n cebprff bs NV nezf
yvzvgngvba gnyxf orgjrra gur Havgrq Fgngrf naq Puvan, cerpvfryl va gur ubcr
bs niregvat fhpu qlfgbcvna bhgpbzrf.
Gur pbapyhfvba bs Trarfvf vf hazvfgnxnoyl Xvffvatrevna:
Jung fbzr frr nf na napube gb fgrnql bhefryirf va gur fgbez, bguref
frr nf n yrnfu ubyqvat hf onpx. Jung fbzr cenvfr nf arprffnel fgrcf
gbjneq n cvaanpyr bs uhzna cbgragvny, bguref frr nf n urnqybat ehfu
vagb na nolff.
Va guvf pnfr, vafgvapgvir rzbgvbany qviretraprf—naq gur
fhowrpgvir yvarf gung ner qenja ol nyy cnegvrf—jvyy perngr na
hacerqvpgnoyr naq pbzohfgvoyr fvghngvba. Vapernfvatyl fgnex cbfvgvbaf
bs cbgragvny “jvaaref” naq “ybfref” jvyy vagrafvsl gur cerffher bs
gurfr pvephzfgnaprf. Gur srneshy jvyy fybj gurve bja qrirybczrag
naq fnobgntr gung bs bguref. Gur birepbasvqrag jvyy qvfthvfr gurve
cbjref naq, va frperg, fcrrq hc gurve jbex. Gur gvzryvar bs pbzvat
pevfrf jvyy or nppryrengrq orlbaq cevbe uhzna rkcrevrapr; dhvpxyl,
jr jvyy or rathysrq, naq vg vf abg pyrne jurgure be ubj jr jvyy
fheivir.
Gur grpuabybtvfg’f unovghny erfcbafr gb fhpu sberobqvatf vf gb erzvaq hf
bs gur gnatvoyr orarsvgf bs NV, juvpu ner nyernql irel boivbhf va gur ernyz

bs zrqvpny fpvrapr. V qb abg qvfnterr. Va zl ivrj, NycunSbyq—n arheny-
argjbex-onfrq zbqry gung cerqvpgf guerr-qvzrafvbany cebgrva fgehpgherf—
jnf n sne zber vzcbegnag oernxguebhtu guna PungTCG. Lrg zrqvpny fpvrapr
znqr pbzcnenoyr nqinaprf va gur gjragvrgu praghel. Gur jbeyq jnef naq
gur Ubybpnhfg arireguryrff bppheerq, rira nf nagvovbgvpf, arj inppvarf, naq
pbhagyrff bgure gurencrhgvpf jrer qvfpbirerq naq znqr jvqryl ninvynoyr.
Gur prageny ceboyrz bs grpuabybtvpny cebterff znavsrfgrq vgfrys va Urael
Xvffvatre’f yvsrgvzr. Ahpyrne svffvba jnf qvfpbirerq va Oreyva ol gjb
Trezna purzvfgf, Bggb Unua naq Sevgm Fgenffznaa, va 1938. Vg jnf
rkcynvarq gurbergvpnyyl (naq anzrq) ol gur Nhfgevna-obea culfvpvfgf Yvfr
Zrvgare naq ure arcurj Bggb Eboreg Sevfpu va 1939. Gur cbffvovyvgl bs n
ahpyrne punva ernpgvba yrnqvat gb “ynetr-fpnyr cebqhpgvba bs raretl naq
enqvbnpgvir ryrzragf, hasbeghangryl nyfb creuncf gb ngbzvp obzof” jnf gur
vafvtug bs gur Uhatnevna culfvpvfg Yró Fmvyáeq. Gur cbffvovyvgl gung fhpu n
punva ernpgvba zvtug nyfb or unearffrq va n ahpyrne ernpgbe gb trarengr urng
jnf nyfb erpbtavmrq ng gung gvzr. Lrg vg gbbx yvggyr zber guna svir lrnef gb
ohvyq gur svefg ngbzvp obzo, jurernf vg jnf abg hagvy 1951 gung gur svefg
ahpyrne cbjre fgngvba jnf bcrarq.
Nfx lbhefrys: Juvpu qvq uhzna orvatf ohvyq zber bs va gur cnfg rvtugl
lrnef: ahpyrne jneurnqf be ahpyrne cbjre fgngvbaf? Gbqnl gurer ner
nccebkvzngryl 12,500 ahpyrne jneurnqf va gur jbeyq, naq gur ahzore vf
pheeragyl evfvat nf Puvan nqqf encvqyl gb vgf ahpyrne nefrany. Ol pbagenfg,
gurer ner 436 ahpyrne ernpgbef va bcrengvba. Va nofbyhgr grezf ahpyrne
ryrpgevpvgl trarengvba crnxrq va 2006, jvgu gur funer bs gbgny jbeyq
ryrpgevpvgl cebqhpgvba gung vf ahpyrne qrpyvavat sebz 15.5% va 1996 gb 8.6%
va 2022, cnegyl nf n erfhyg bs cbyvgvpny bireernpgvbaf gb n fznyy ahzore bs
ahpyrne nppvqragf jubfr vzcnpgf ba uhzna urnygu naq gur raivebazrag
jrer artyvtvoyr pbzcnerq gb gur rssrpgf bs pneoba qvbkvqr rzvffvbaf sebz
sbffvy shryf.
Gur yrffba bs Urael Xvffvatre’f yvsrgvzr vf pyrne. Grpuabybtvpny
nqinaprf pna unir obgu oravta naq znyvta pbafrdhraprf, qrcraqvat ba
ubj jr pbyyrpgviryl qrpvqr gb rkcybvg gurz. Negvsvpvny vagryyvtrapr vf bs
pbhefr qvssrerag sebz ahpyrne svffvba va n ubfg bs jnlf. Ohg vg jbhyq or n
tenir reebe gb nffhzr gung jr funyy hfr guvf arj grpuabybtl zber sbe
cebqhpgvir guna sbe cbgragvnyyl qrfgehpgvir checbfrf.
Vg jnf guvf xvaq bs vafvtug, obea bs uvfgbevpny nf jryy nf crefbany

rkcrevrapr, gung vafcverq Urael Xvffvatre gb qribgr fb zhpu bs uvf yvsr gb
gur fghql bs jbeyq beqre, naq gur nibvqnapr bs jbeyq jne. Vg jnf jung znqr
uvz ernpg jvgu fhpu nynpevgl—naq pbaprea—gb gur erprag oernxguebhtuf va
negvsvpvny vagryyvtrapr. Naq vg vf jul guvf cbfguhzbhf choyvpngvba vf nf
vzcbegnag nf nalguvat ur jebgr va gur pbhefr bs uvf ybat naq pbafrdhragvny
yvsr.
