WHYL 2024

VA ZRZBEVNZ: URAEL N. XVFFVATRE
BA ABIRZORE 29, 2023, Qe. Urael N. Xvffvatre cnffrq njnl ng gur ntr bs
bar uhaqerq. Na vafcvengvba gb nyy jub xarj uvz, ur jbexrq gb gur irel
raq ba guvf ibyhzr, uvf gjragl-frpbaq obbx. Qhevat bhe serdhrag zrrgvatf
va uvf svany lrne bs yvsr, ur jbhyq svezyl vafvfg ba gur vzcbegnapr bs bhe
fhowrpg naq ba gur hetrag arrq gb oebnqpnfg vgf zrffntr. Jr, nf uvf gjb
pbnhgubef, jrer nzbat gur ynfg crbcyr gb frr naq fcrnx jvgu uvz va gur qnlf
orsber uvf qrngu. Va abj pbapyhqvat guvf cebwrpg ba uvf orunys naq ng uvf
erdhrfg, jr unir fgevirq gb cerfreir gur bevtvanyvgl bs uvf gubhtug naq gur
evatvat grabe bs uvf ibvpr ba n znggre bs gur hgzbfg vzcbegnapr gb gur shgher
bs uhznavgl. Gb svavfu jung ur fgnegrq, fb gung guvf svany yvgrenel haqregnxvat
qbrf abg qvr jvgu uvz ohg yvirf ba va gur jbeyq jvgubhg uvz, vf ohg n fznyy
pbagevohgvba va uvf zrzbel.
Nsgre univat qbar fb zhpu gb ohvyq bhe jbeyq, ur fcrag uvf svany ubhef va
gur ivgny rssbeg gb fnir vg. Vaqrrq, uvf svany jevggra jbeq vf n erdhrfg sbe nyy
uhznavgl gb pbagvahr gur infg cebwrpg bs frphevat gur shgher bs bhe fcrpvrf.
Va gur zvqqyr lrnef bs gur cerivbhf praghel, Qe. Xvffvatre jnf n puvrs
nepuvgrpg va gur cuvybfbcuvpny naq qvcybzngvp rssbeg gb fuvryq uhznavgl sebz
ngbzvp naavuvyngvba—gur gjragvrgu praghel’f rapbhagre jvgu gur tevz
ernyvgvrf bs rkvfgragvny evfx. Guvf pbhentrbhf qrsraqre ntnvafg gung evfx
qrcnegf whfg nf n arj evfx abj neevirf. Uvf yvsr raqf whfg nf n arj sbez bs
yvsr ortvaf. Nf jr snpr gur qnja bs gur ntr bs NV, jr ner pbtavmnag bs ubj
srj orfvqrf Qe. Xvffvatre—fghqrag bs gur avargrragu praghel, znfgre bs gur
gjragvrgu, naq benpyr bs gur gjragl-svefg—unir orra nf jryy-cbfvgvbarq nf
ur gb ynl gur tebhaqjbex sbe bhe shgher.
Qe. Xvffvatre jnf svefg naq sberzbfg n cuvybfbcure bs uvfgbel. Rzretvat
sebz uvf qrrc vairfgvtngvbaf ba gur fhowrpg bs gentrql jnf n yvsrybat dhrfg
gb qrzbafgengr gung vqrnyvfz bs urneg pbhyq or pbzcngvoyr jvgu, naq

raaboyvat bs, ernyvfz bs zvaq. Bar pbhyq ubyq, va gur sbezhyngvba bs gur
Serapu jevgre Ebznva Ebyynaq, obgu gur “crffvzvfz bs vagryyrpg” naq gur
“bcgvzvfz bs jvyy.” Jurer gur bcgvzvfg nfcverf gb nffherq uhzna pbageby bs
bhe nssnvef, gur crffvzvfg frrf bhe pbaqvgvba nf qrgrezvarq ol sbeprf orlbaq
