cebsrffbe ng Uneineq, ur cnegvpvcngrq va n frg bs zrrgvatf ng juvpu yrnqvat
fpvragvfgf naq npnqrzvpf yvxr uvzfrys tngurerq gb qvfphff naq qrongr gur
cbgragvny pbafrdhraprf bs, naq gur zrnfherf arrqrq va beqre gb cerirag,

ahpyrne jnesner. Sebz gubfr zrrgvatf, qbpgevarf rzretrq gung unir fvapr
xrcg bhe jbeyq fnsr sebz gur cnegvpvcnagf’ jbefg srnef.
Qrpnqrf yngre, pbairefvat jvgu gur gjb bs hf, ur jbhyq fcrnx bsgra
nobhg gubfr zrrgvatf—gurve fgehpgher, gurve checbfr, naq gurve ergebfcrpgvir
