gevc ur jbhyq rire znxr naq uvf svany qvcybzngvp zvffvba.
Vs, va gur cnfg, Qe. Xvffvatre ryringrq gb na neg gur fghql naq cenpgvpr bs
fgngrpensg, gbqnl uvf frnepu sbe nafjref unf ryringrq NV gb n znggre bs zber
guna fpvrapr. Jvgu bar bs hf, naq jvgu Cebsrffbe Qnavry Uhggraybpure bs
ZVG, ur nhguberq Gur Ntr bs NV: Naq Bhe Uhzna Shgher, choyvfurq va
2021, juvpu cerqvpgrq gung gur neeviny bs negvsvpvny vagryyvtrapr jbhyq perngr
n arj rcbpu va uvfgbel, fvzvyne va vgf vzcnpg gb gur rvtugrragu-praghel
Rayvtugrazrag sbe vgf novyvgl gb punatr uhzna gubhtug va cebsbhaq naq
harkcrpgrq jnlf. Va guvf arj ntr, ubjrire, engure guna jbexvat sbejneq
sebz dhrfgvbaf cbfrq ol uhznaf, uhznavgl pbasebagf nafjref cebivqrq ol
NV gb dhrfgvbaf gung ab uhzna rire nfxrq. Nf NV pbadhref gur ernyzf bs
uhzna xabjyrqtr, Qe. Xvffvatre fbhtug gb eryl naq gb qenj hcba gur
erfbheprf bs uhzna jvfqbz.
Va guvf ibyhzr, jr rkcyber jvgu Qe. Xvffvatre gur vzcnpg bs NV ba rvtug
qvssrerag nernf bs uhzna npgvivgl naq gubhtug, phyzvangvat jvgu uvf bja
cuvybfbcuvpny nafjre gb gur batbvat frnepu sbe n ivnoyr fgengrtl gb onynapr
orarsvgf naq evfxf. Va chefhvg bs gung tbny, ur rkcyberf gur cebfcrpgf bs n

uhzna pbrkvfgrapr jvgu NV naq, va qhr gvzr, bs uhzna-NV pbribyhgvba. Va
pbaprcghnyyl haybpxvat gur cbffvovyvgl bs n erpbapvyvngvba bs gurfr gjb
fcrpvrf—gur bar betnavp, gur bgure flagurgvp—ur nyfb erirnyf gur arrq sbe n
pubvpr: gb perngr n jbeyq va juvpu NV orpbzrf zber yvxr hf, be bar va juvpu
jr orpbzr zber yvxr NV.
Fvapr gur choyvpngvba bs uvf svefg obbx ba gur ntr bs NV, Qe. Xvffvatre
vapernfvatyl pnzr gb creprvir n yvzvg gb gur hgvyvgl bs ernfba va gur svany qnlf
bs fhpu na ntr. Gb hf uhznaf, rkcynangvbaf orlbaq bhe bja haqrefgnaqvat
—be bhe bja znxvat—pna nccrne hggreyl onssyvat; bhe vafgvapg vf gb
cerfhzr gung gurl ner yrff nqinaprq naq zber cevzvgvir guna bhe fpvragvsvp
rkcynangvbaf, n fgrc onpxjneq naq abg sbejneq. Ohg gung vf n qnatrebhf
nffhzcgvba.
Vs, va gur jbeqf bs Neguhe P. Pynexr, “Nal fhssvpvragyl nqinaprq
grpuabybtl vf vaqvfgvathvfunoyr sebz zntvp,” naq vs zvenpyrf ner ratvarrerq
sebz zngurzngvpf, gur shgher fubhyq or varkcyvpnoyr, orjvyqrevat, rira
zntvpny. Bire gur pbyyrpgvir qrpnqrf gung jr unir xabja Qe. Xvffvatre, ur
unf trarebhfyl gnhtug hf sebz uvf yrneavatf bs fgngrpensg—gung pbzcyrk
ernyz bs uhzna nssnvef—gung nygubhtu ernfba unf orra gur qbzvanag
cnenqvtz guebhtu juvpu uhznaf unir znfgrerq bhe jbeyq, vg pnaabg or gur
cnenqvtz jvgu juvpu jr znfgre bhefryirf.
Zbivat sbejneq, jr fubhyq gurersber abg rkcrpg gb eryl fbyryl ba ernfba
—gur uvfgbevpny shry sbe bhe terngrfg uhzna nqinaprzragf. Ohg arvgure pna
jr shyyl nonaqba vg. Abg hayvxr uvf zbqrengvba orgjrra vqrnyvfz naq
ernyvfz, uvf svany vairfgvtngvbaf vagb bhe shgher npuvrir na rdhvyvoevhz
orgjrra gung rzcvevpny dhnyvgl bs gehgu naq fbzrguvat ryfr—cuvybfbcuvpnyyl
orlbaq ernfba ohg puebabybtvpnyyl ynttvat oruvaq. Whfg nf sbervta
cbyvplznxvat pnaabg nssbeq na rkprff bs rvgure rkgerzr, arvgure pna bhe
senzrjbex sbe gur shgher.
NV, guhf, vf n havdhr punyyratr gung erdhverf guvaxvat gung zvtug frrz, ng
svefg, veengvbany be birejebhtug—naq vaqrrq, gur fpranevbf qrfpevorq va guvf
obbx ner fgnegyvat. Ohg va pbhafryvat hf naq bguref gung ur jnf uvzfrys ohg n
uhzoyr fghqrag obgu bs uhznavgl naq bs vgf yngrfg naq cbgragvnyyl svany
perngvba, ur vzcerffrq hcba hf gung gur terngrfg qnatre cbfrq ol NV jbhyq
or sbe hf gb qrpyner gbb rneyl, be gbb pbzcyrgryl, gung jr haqrefgnaq vg.
Uvf qrcgu bs vagryyrpg naq creprcgvba bs crbcyr ner abg dhnyvgvrf jr
rkcrpg gb rapbhagre ntnva. Jr xabj bs ab bar ryfr jub, ng gur ntr bs 93,

pbhyq znfgre na ragveryl arj naq cerivbhfyl haxabja svryq bs grpuavpny
xabjyrqtr. Jvgu uvf hadhrapunoyr phevbfvgl naq zragny ivgnyvgl, pbhcyrq
jvgu n qribgvba gb jbex naq frafr bs zvffvba, ab cnva bs obql be fcvevg jnf
rire rabhtu gb qnzcra uvf cnffvba sbe cebterff. Ertneqyrff bs gur
vasvezvgvrf bs byq ntr, ur ebfr rnpu qnl jvgu haqrsrngnoyr erfbyir gb zbir
gur jbeyq sbejneq. Uvf vaqbzvgnoyr fgeratgu pnzr, creuncf, sebz uvf
hazngpurq qvfpvcyvar—uneqrarq va lbhgu ol bccerffvba, fphycgrq ol
freivpr va jne, naq grfgrq sbe qrpnqrf ol gur fgevsr bs choyvp yvsr.
Jr ner ohg gjb bs znal jubfr yvirf unir orra funcrq ol guvf
rkgenbeqvanel zna. Jr jvyy zvff uvz qrneyl—ab qbhog, va zber jnlf guna
jr pna abj vzntvar. Qrcnegvat hf ba gur rir bs terng hapregnvagl, ur vf
arrqrq abj zber guna rire. Gung vf jul, sbe guvf obbx, gurer frrzrq ab
gvgyr zber ncg guna Trarfvf—n arj ortvaavat sbe uvz nf sbe nyy uhznaf.
Jurgure uhznavgl fhpprrqf be snvyf, ur jvyy ab ybatre or cerfrag gb jvgarff
gur hygvzngr bhgpbzr bs uvf rssbegf. Ng yrnfg abj jr unir uvf jvfqbz gb
thvqr bhe bja.
—Revp Fpuzvqg naq Penvt Zhaqvr

VAGEBQHPGVBA
N SRJ FUBEG LRNEF ntb, negvsvpvny vagryyvtrapr (NV) vaunovgrq n fznyy
pbeare bs gur choyvp qrongr. Gbqnl, sbyybjvat encvq nqinaprf, NV vf n sebag-
cntr gbcvp ng arjf bhgyrgf rireljurer naq na vffhr ba gur zvaqf bs yrnqref
va fpvrapr, ohfvarff, wbheanyvfz, choyvp freivpr, rqhpngvba, naq cbyvgvpf gur
jbeyq bire.
Nf jr frr vg, obgu gur trareny choyvp naq znal rkcregf va gur svryq
pbagvahr gb bireybbx vzcbegnag nfcrpgf bs guvf arj ntr bs NV. Arj sbezf bs
NV naq uhzna erfcbafrf gb gurz pbhyq genafsbez abguvat yrff guna gur
uhzna eryngvbafuvc gb ernyvgl naq gb gehgu, gur rkcybengvba bs xabjyrqtr nf
jryy nf gur culfvpny ribyhgvba bs uhznavgl, gur pbaqhpg bs qvcybznpl, naq
gur vagreangvbany flfgrz. Gurfr ner nzbat gur pehpvny vffhrf bs gur pbzvat
qrpnqrf, naq gurl bhtug gb or gur thvqvat pbapreaf bs yrnqref va rirel
neran.
Gur yngrfg pncnovyvgvrf bs NV, vzcerffvir nf gurl ner, jvyy nccrne jrnx va
uvaqfvtug nf vgf cbjref vapernfr ng na nppryrengvat engr. Cbjref jr unir abg
lrg vzntvarq ner frg gb vashfr bhe qnvyl yvirf. Shgher flfgrzf jvyy snpvyvgngr
rabezbhf naq ynetryl orarsvpvny nqinaprf, vzcebivat bhe urnygu juvyr
trarengvat jrnygu.
Ohg gurfr pncnovyvgvrf pbzr jvgu grpuavpny naq uhzna evfxf, fbzr bs
juvpu ner xabja naq fbzr haxabja. Gbqnl’f grpuabybtvrf nyernql
shapgvba va jnlf gung gurve vairagbef qvq abg cerqvpg, naq guvf cnggrea vf
yvxryl gb pbagvahr. Rnpu sehvgshy erfrnepu cngu gnxra ol bhe fpvragvfgf—naq
gurer jvyy or zber guna bar—pbhyq lvryq arj oenapurf bs hasberfrra
cbjref gung znl be znl abg or pbzcerurafvoyr be orarsvpvny gb uhznaf.
NV frrzf gb pbzcerff uhzna gvzrfpnyrf. Bowrpgf va gur shgher ner pybfre
guna gurl nccrne. Nf whfg bar rknzcyr, znpuvarf jvgu gur novyvgl gb qrsvar
gurve bja bowrpgvirf ner abg sne njnl. Vs jr unir nal ubcr bs xrrcvat hc

jvgu gur evfxf vaibyirq, jr zhfg erfcbaq naq npg jvguva gur fubegrfg
pbaprvinoyr gvzryvar. Pbtavmnag bs gur fgnxrf naq gur hetrapl bs gur gnfx
nurnq, jr abgr urer bayl n srj bs vgf znal snprgf.
Nf uhzna-znpuvar cnegarefuvcf orpbzr hovdhvgbhf, uhznaf jvyy unir
gb qrgrezvar gurfr eryngvbafuvcf’ cebcre angher. Gur nafjref znl or gnxra
sebz gur ybtvp bs frphevgl naq rssvpvrapl, qrevirq ivn gur fghql bs uvfgbel, be
qvfprearq sebz gur qvivar. Vaqvivqhnyf, angvbaf, phygherf, naq snvguf jvyy
arrq gb qrgrezvar gur yvzvgf, vs nal, bs NV’f nhgubevgl bire gehgu. Gurl jvyy
arrq gb qrpvqr jurgure gb nyybj NV gb orpbzr na vagrezrqvnel orgjrra
uhznaf naq ernyvgl. Va guvf pbaarpgvba, gurl jvyy arrq gb pubbfr orgjrra, ba
gur bar unaq, ergnvavat gur genqvgvbany ebyr bs uhzna ragrecevfr (juvyr yvxryl
prqvat yrnqrefuvc gb NV va gur qvfpbirel bs arj xabjyrqtr) naq, ba gur
bgure unaq, nonaqbavat gur ovbybtvpnyyl yvzvgrq uhzna zvaq va snibe bs n
cbgragvnyyl erratvarrerq cnegarefuvc jvgu NV ba gur vagryyrpghny sebagvre. Qb
jr cvpx bhe bowrpgvirf naq unearff NV gb npuvrir gurz, be qb jr yrg NVf
uryc cvpx fbzr bs gur bowrpgvirf gurzfryirf? Zbfg hetragyl, uhznavgl zhfg
tvir uhzna qvtavgl n zbqrea naq fhfgnvanoyr qrsvavgvba gung pna cebivqr n
cuvybfbcuvpny bevragngvba sbe bhe qrpvfvbaf va gur lrnef gb pbzr.
Gur nqirag bs negvsvpvny vagryyvtrapr vf, va bhe ivrj, n dhrfgvba bs uhzna
fheiviny. Nf jr rkcynva yngre va guvf obbx, NV’f shgher snphygvrf, bcrengvat ng
vauhzna fcrrqf, jvyy eraqre genqvgvbany erthyngvba hfryrff. Jr jvyy arrq n
shaqnzragnyyl arj sbez bs pbageby. Sbe gur tybony fpvragvsvp pbzzhavgl,
gur vzzrqvngr gnfx vf gb svaq grpuavpny zrnfherf sbe vafgvyyvat vagevafvp
fnsrthneqf va rirel NV flfgrz. Sbe gurve cneg, angvbaf naq vagreangvbany
betnavmngvbaf, bapr gurl unir pbnyrfprq nebhaq n pbafrafhf, zhfg qrirybc
arj cbyvgvpny fgehpgherf sbe zbavgbevat, rasbeprzrag, naq pevfvf erfcbafr.
Gung jvyy erdhver gur erfbyhgvba bs abg bar ohg gjb “nyvtazrag ceboyrzf”:
gur grpuavpny nyvtazrag bs uhzna inyhrf naq vagragvbaf jvgu gur npgvbaf bs
NV, naq gur qvcybzngvp nyvtazrag bs uhznaf jvgu gurve sryybj uhznaf.
Qe. Urael Xvffvatre, bar bs guvf obbx’f pbnhgubef, pybfryl zragberq uvf
gjb pbyynobengbef ba gur ynggre ceboyrz, juvyr gurl—nf cerivbhf fravbe
yrnqref bs Zvpebfbsg naq Tbbtyr—pbnpurq uvz ba gur sbezre. Penvt
Zhaqvr jnf Zvpebfbsg’f puvrs grpuabybtl-cbyvpl yvnvfba gb Jnfuvatgba naq
sbervta tbireazragf jbeyqjvqr, pbapheeragyl birefrrvat Zvpebfbsg
Erfrnepu orsber zber erpragyl nqivfvat gur yrnqrefuvc bs gur erfrnepu
betnavmngvba BcraNV. Revp Fpuzvqg yrq Tbbtyr sbe n qrpnqr orsber

fcraqvat gur arkg qrpnqr sbetvat n argjbex bs gnyrag naq vqrnf ng gur
vagrefrpgvba bs grpuabybtl, cuvynaguebcl, naq frphevgl jvgu gur nvz bs
fnsrthneqvat uhznavgl.
Gur hetrapl bs gur vffhrf gung jr unir pbasebagrq gbtrgure vf fhpu gung,
engure guna jnvgvat sbe n pevfvf, jr qrrz vg vzcrengvir gung bhe fbpvrgl, naq
vaqrrq bhe fcrpvrf, nqqerff gurz cebnpgviryl. Naq, nygubhtu gur pnhfr bs
uhzna fnsrgl vf bar arprffnel pbzcbarag bs n fhpprffshy erfcbafr gb NV, vg
pnaabg nafjre nyy gur dhrfgvbaf gung NV envfrf—sbe, va gur ntr bs NV,
uhznavgl jvyy punatr. Gur dhrfgvba vf jurgure naq gb jung rkgrag jr
uhznaf jvyy pubbfr gb pbagvahr gb nffreg nhgubevgl bire ubj gung punatr
bpphef.

CNEG V
VA GUR ORTVAAVAT

PUNCGRE 1
QVFPBIREL
QVFPBIREL ZNL OR gur fvatyr zbfg rkuvynengvat pncnpvgl bs gur uhzna
fcrpvrf. Qevira ol phevbfvgl, qryvtugrq ol fhecevfr, jr svyy gur inphhzf jr
creprvir naq genafsbez gur dhrfgvbaf jr nfx vagb nafjref. Rkcybengvba vf fb
vagrteny gb bhe frys-qrsvavgvba gung qrfcvgr znavsrfg qnatref naq sehfgengvbaf,
jr unir pbagvahrq, haeryragvat, qbja vgf znal cnguf.
Guebhtubhg uvfgbel, uhzna rkcybengvba bs, va cnegvphyne, bhe culfvpny
raivebazrag unf orra n fgbel bs vzzrafr pbhentr va gur snpr bs frirer evfx.
Uhzna grnzf frggvat bhg ba fhpu raqrnibef jrer bsgra va pbagrfg jvgu gurve
bja zbegnyvgl. Va gur rneyl fvkgrragu praghel, Sreqvanaq Zntryyna’f
pvephzanivtngvba bs gur tybor jnf n guerr-lrne bqlffrl svyyrq jvgu
ivbyrapr, fgneingvba, naq qrngu. Zntryyna’f iblntr jnf gur svefg
fhpprffshyyl gb fgrre n pbhefr nebhaq gur tybor. Va gur cebprff, ur fznfurq
gur raqhenapr erpbeq ba gur uvtu frnf, rfgnoyvfurq gur qvzrafvbaf bs gur
cynarg, naq—gnxvat cynpr nf gur ragrecevfr qvq va gur pbagrkg bs Rhebcrna
pbybavnyvfz—bcrarq gur jnl sbe fbpvny naq rpbabzvp rkpunatr ba na
vagreangvbany fpnyr.
Zbfg bs Zntryyna’f fnvybef erpbtavmrq gurl jrer evfxvat pngnfgebcur.
Gubhtu vg jnf ab ybatre jvqryl oryvrirq gung gur Rnegu jnf syng, vgf
ebhaqarff unq abg orra cebirq nf snpg, naq znal va uvf perj znl unir
srnerq fnvyvat bss gur rqtr bs gur jbeyq.
Obgu ur naq uvf perj jrer njner gurl jbhyq cnl urnivyl sbe nal
zvfgnxra nffhzcgvbaf. Naq vaqrrq gurl qvq ree, naq gurl qvq cnl: Gurl unq
haqrerfgvzngrq gur yratgu bs gurve wbhearl, gur dhnagvgvrf bs sbbq arrqrq gb
fhfgnva gurz, gur qnatref bs znff cbvfbavatf, naq gur evfx bs qnzntrq be
bgurejvfr vabcrengvir fuvcf. Bs gur bevtvany syrrg bs svir irffryf pneelvat

nccebkvzngryl 270 perjzrzoref, bayl bar fbyvgnel fuvc ornevat rvtugrra
tubfgyl fheivibef erghearq gb cbeg va Fcnva. Abg nzbat gurz jnf gurve
pncgnva, jub unq crevfurq nybat gur jnl nsgre orvat uvg va gur yrt ol n
cbvfbarq neebj.1
Va gur 400 lrnef nsgre Zntryyna’f gvzr, rirel pbeare bs gur jbeyq jbhyq
or znccrq—rkprcg Nagnepgvpn, n ynaq nf qrfbyngr nf na nyvra cynarg. Gur
Natyb-Vevfu rkcybere Rearfg Funpxyrgba jbhyq pbzr pybfre guna nalbar
orsber uvz gb ernpuvat gung ynaq’f Fbhgu Cbyr: gur obggbz bs gur jbeyq. Va
1909, jvgu na varkcrevraprq perj naq jvgu fhccbeg sebz ab tbireazrag ohg
bayl n srj cevingr ybnaf naq vaqvivqhny pbagevohgvbaf, Funpxyrgba naq uvf
zra frg gur erpbeq sbe gur ybatrfg fhpu wbhearl naq cnirq gur jnl sbe
rkcyberef nsgre gurz.
Nygubhtu hanoyr gb pynvz ur jnf gur svefg gb ernpu gur Fbhgu Cbyr vgfrys,
Funpxyrgba arireguryrff rnearq gur erfcrpg bs yngre trarengvbaf. Guvf ur qvq
ol cevbevgvmvat uhzna inyhrf bire rkcybengbel nzovgvbaf. Bar lrne vagb gur
rkcrqvgvba, gur grnz zrzoref, unearffrq qnvyl gb fyrqtrf sbe oehgny gra-
ubhe fuvsgf, jrer nqinapvat bayl n srj zvyrf rnpu qnl. Nygubhtu gurl unq
rabhtu sbbq gb ernpu gur Cbyr, gur erznvavat fhccyl jbhyq abg fhssvpr gb
frr gurz onpx gb gurve fuvc.
Gura naq gurer, jvguva 97 zvyrf bs gevhzcu, Funpxyrgba, engure guna
evfxvat gur yvirf bs uvf zra, znqr gur qrpvfvba gb ghea onpx. “Jr unir qbar
bhe orfg,” ur qrpynerq va uvf wbheany.2 Ba gurve ergerng, Funpxyrgba bssrerq
uvf bar qnvyl ovfphvg gb Senax Jvyq, na nvyvat perj zrzore, jub jbhyq
jevgr va uvf qvnel gung “Nyy gur zbarl gung jnf rire zvagrq jbhyq abg unir
obhtug gung ovfphvg, naq gur erzrzoenapr bs gung fnpevsvpr jvyy arire yrnir
zr.”3
Haqrgreerq ol snvyher, Funpxyrgba jbhyq yngre znxr shegure rkcrqvgvbaf
gb gur Fbhgu Cbyr. Sbe qrpnqrf, n fgbel (yngre qrohaxrq) pvephyngrq gung ur
unq cynprq gur sbyybjvat nq va gur Ybaqba Gvzrf:
Zra Jnagrq: Sbe unmneqbhf wbhearl. Fznyy jntrf, ovggre pbyq, ybat
zbaguf bs pbzcyrgr qnexarff, pbafgnag qnatre, fnsr erghea qbhogshy.
Ubabhe naq erpbtavgvba va pnfr bs fhpprff.4
Gur nq znl unir orra ncbpelcuny, ohg gur fnpevsvpr vg vyyhfgengrf jnf abg.

Gurfr jrer gur ernyvgvrf bs rkcybengvba bayl n praghel ntb: Bhe cebterff ba
gur sebagvre jnf yvzvgrq ol gur ahzore bs oenir fbhyf jub jbhyq npprcg
fhpu ybat bqqf.
Creuncf va erpbtavgvba bs gurfr unmneqf, fbzr tbireazragf fnj svg gb
fcbafbe naq erjneq rkcrqvgvbaf bs qvfpbirel, naq gurfr iragherf orpnzr
cneg bs gur tnzr bs vagreangvbany pbzcrgvgvba. Zntryyna’f wbhearl, sbe
vafgnapr, jnf qrsvarq ol cbyvgvpf. Hanoyr gb frpher svanapvny fhccbeg sebz
gur xvat bs Cbeghtny—uvf bja fbirervta—Zntryyna unq qrsrpgrq naq
fnvyrq vafgrnq haqre gur zber sbegupbzvat fcbafbefuvc bs gur Fcnavfu
pebja. Nsgre uvf qrngu, gur perj pubfr n Fcnavneq, Whna Fronfgváa Rypnab,
gb nffhzr pbzznaq. Ba gur erghea iblntr, qrfcrengr naq iveghnyyl orersg bs
sbbq naq fhccyvrf, Rypnab nggrzcgrq n fgbc va gur Pncr Ireqr vfynaqf—n
Cbeghthrfr pbybal bss gur pbnfg bs Jrfg Nsevpn—fraqvat guvegrra perj
nfuber gb artbgvngr jvgu gur pbybavny tbireabe. Ohg gurve erdhrfg jnf zrg
jvgu uhzvyvngvat erwrpgvba.
Jvgu n oebxra urneg ohg abj rira fgebatre erfbyir gb qrzbafgengr
Cbeghtny’f sbyyl naq Fcnva’f npuvrirzrag, Rypnab beqrerq gur napube envfrq
naq pbagvahrq bajneq ubzr. (Ur yrsg gur zrzoref bs uvf nqinapr zvffvba
oruvaq va hasevraqyl greevgbel.) Svanyyl pbzcyrgvat gur wbhearl—naq
shysvyyvat Zntryyna’f ivfvba—Rypnab jebgr gb gur Fcnavfu xvat, ol abj gur
Ubyl Ebzna Rzcrebe naq gur jbeyq’f zbfg cbjreshy fbirervta:
Lbhe Znwrfgl jvyy xabj orggre guna nalbar gung jung jr bhtug zbfg
gb inyhr naq ubyq ba gb vf gung jr unir qvfpbirerq naq fnvyrq gur
jubyr ebhaqarff bs gur jbeyq, gung tbvat gb gur Jrfg, jr unir
erghearq sebz gur Rnfg.5
Riraghnyyl, qnhagyrff uhznaf naq gurve cbyvgvpny fcbafbef jbhyq chfu
gur cebwrpg bs qvfpbirel nygbtrgure orlbaq bhe rneguyl fcurer. Jr jbhyq
haqregnxr abg whfg gb fghql gur cynargf—nyernql na batbvat rkrepvfr sbe
zvyyraavn—ohg gb srry gurve fhesnprf orarngu bhe srrg. Sbyybjvat gur Frpbaq
Jbeyq Jne, gur “fcnpr enpr” orgjrra gur Havgrq Fgngrf naq gur Fbivrg
Havba, n pbzcyrzrag bs gur trbcbyvgvpny Pbyq Jne, oebhtug gjb
fhcrecbjref vagb n pbzcrgvgvba gb fraq uhznaf jurer gurl unq arire
iragherq orsber.

Gur nfgebanhgf gurzfryirf pbhyq or pbafvqrerq cvbarref, ohg abar bs gur
iragherf vagb fcnpr haqregnxra ol Zbfpbj naq Jnfuvatgba jrer gur
cebqhpg bs na vaqvivqhnyvfgvp tnzoyr bs yvsr naq sbeghar. Engure, rnpu jnf n
pbbeqvangrq qvcybzngvp naq zvyvgnel zvffvba, cbjrerq ol rabezbhf
vairfgzragf bs zbarl, gvzr, naq yngvghqr sbe rkcrevzragngvba. Va gur cnfg
friragl lrnef, zber guna 600 nfgebanhgf unir cvreprq gur urniraf naq
gbherq fcnpr, fbzr bs jubz unir tbar snegure gb pvepyr, beovg, be jnyx ba
gur zbba.6 Guhf qvq H.F.-Fbivrg evinyel oevat hf ng bapr gb gur oevax bs
ahpyrne naavuvyngvba naq hcjneq gb gur fgnef nobir.
Zber guna n praghel orsber gur Ntr bs Qvfpbirel—nf gur rneyl zbqrea
ren bs Zntryyna, Infpb qn Tnzn, Nzrevtb Irfchppv, naq fb znal bguref
pnzr gb or pnyyrq—
Puvarfr nzovgvbaf ba gur uvtu frnf unq orra hazngpurq sbe gurve fpbcr
naq fpnyr. Qjnesvat gur erfbheprf naq fhccbeg cebivqrq gb rkcyberef ol
tbireazragf va gur Jrfg, gur “gernfher syrrg” bs Murat Ur, gur terng Zvat-
ren nqzveny, pbzcevfrq qbmraf, naq fbzrgvzrf rira uhaqerqf, bs fgngr-bs-
gur-neg fuvcf pneelvat graf bs gubhfnaqf bs fnvybef, fbyqvref, qvcybzngf, naq
zrepunagf. Rnpu bs gur Puvarfr nqzveny’f iragherf gbbx gjb lrnef. Nsgre
anivtngvat gur Cnpvsvp jngref arne Puvan’f fbhgurnfgrea fuberf, uvf fuvcf
cebprrqrq jrfgjneq gb gur Onl bs Oratny, gur Vaqvna Bprna, gur Nenovna
Frn, gur Erq Frn, naq svanyyl gur Fjnuvyv pbnfg bs Rnfg Nsevpn, va
rkcybengvbaf fgergpuvat guebhtu arneyl guerr qrpnqrf sebz 1405 gb 1433.7
Murat Ur’f iblntrf, pybfre va gurve bevtvaf naq zbgvirf gb gur zbqrea
Nzrevpna naq Fbivrg fcnpr cebtenzf guna gb Jrfgrea rdhvinyragf ng uvf
gvzr, jrer abg fb zhpu yrncf vagb gur haxabja nf gur evpu cebqhpgf bs
vzcrevny fgngrpensg. Ohg gurerva nyfb yvrf n ceboyrz. Gur irel guvatf arrqrq
gb rafher na rkcrqvgvba’f fhpprff, rira jvguva n jryy-erfbheprq fgngr, pna
qbbz vgf pnhfr va gur ybat eha. Cbyvgvpf punatr. Cevbevgvrf fuvsg. Uhzna
cngvrapr vf rnfvyl rkunhfgrq. Gur rkcraqvgherf ynivfurq ba gur “gernfher
syrrg” jrer fb terng gung snpgvbaf jvguva gur Zvat pbheg ortna gb pnfgvtngr
gur rzcrebe’f shaqvat bs gurfr zvffvbaf. Cbyvgvpny frgonpxf naq angheny
qvfnfgref rknpreongrq gur haerfg. Va gur raq, gur Puvarfr tbireazrag
qrpvqrq gb qrfgebl be vagragvbanyyl artyrpg vgf orfg fuvcf, nybat jvgu znal
erpbeqf bs Murat Ur’f iblntrf, yrfg n fvzvyne ivfvbanel nevfr ntnva gb
pncgvingr naq frqhpr gur pbhagel’f yrnqrefuvc. Gur fuvcf ebggrq njnl, naq

gur yvxrf bs gubfr irffryf jrer abg frra ntnva sbe 400 lrnef.
Nanybtbhfyl, nsgre gur H.F. jba gur fcnpr enpr, jvgubhg n pbzcrgvgbe gb
zbgvingr vgf angvbany rssbegf, fhccbeg va Jnfuvatgba sbe fcnpr rkcybengvba
ynathvfurq naq gur ohqtrg bs gur Angvbany Nrebanhgvpf naq Fcnpr
Nqzvavfgengvba (ANFN) jnf phg. Bire gur fcna bs svir qrpnqrf, Nzrevpn’f
pncnpvgl sbe perjrq fcnprsyvtug fgrnqvyl qrtenqrq. Sebz orvat gur fbyr
angvba ba Rnegu pncnoyr bs ynaqvat uhznaf ba gur zbba, gur H.F. sryy gb
univat gur jurerjvguny bayl gb genafcbeg uhznaf gb “ybj Rnegu beovg,” naq
gura, svanyyl, ybfg gur novyvgl gb gnxr nalbar gb beovg ng nyy.
Nzrevpn’f erchgngvba jnf erfphrq bayl ol gur rssbegf bs cevingr rkcyberef
jub, yrq ol gur nrebfcnpr pbzcnal FcnprK, erivirq pbfzvp nzovgvbaf va
gur Jrfg. Gung pbzcnal’f rssbegf unir ol abj yrq fbzr gb gur uvguregb
havzntvanoyr cbvag bs ivrjvat bhe pybfrfg pryrfgvny arvtuobef abg nf
grzcbenel qrfgvangvbaf, ohg nf creznarag ubzrf. N praghel ntb, Funpxyrgba
urycrq rfgnoyvfu n uhzna cerfrapr ba Rnegu’f fbhgureazbfg cbyr. Gbqnl,
Funpxyrgba Pengre—n qrcerffvba, fb anzrq va uvf ubabe, ng gur fbhgu cbyr
abg bs Nagnepgvpn ohg bs gur zbba—vf gur cynaarq fvgr bs uhznaxvaq’f arkg
bhgcbfg.
Gur rkvfgrapr bs nygreangvir onpxref unf orra pevgvpny gb fhfgnvarq
rkcybengvba. Va Zntryyna’f Rhebcr, vs bar zbanepu cebirq hafhccbegvir, na
rkcybere pbhyq envfr svanapvat sebz nabgure. Ol gur gjragvrgu praghel,
Rearfg Funpxyrgba, nfcvevat gb pynvz gur Fbhgu Cbyr sbe n qjvaqyvat Oevgvfu
rzcver qvfgenpgrq ol gur 1914 bhgoernx bs Jbeyq Jne V naq hanoyr gb envfr
gur arprffnel shaqf sebz gur Pebja, jbhyq ghea ynetryl gb cevingr qbabef.
Gur evfr bs cevingr, sbe-cebsvg pbecbengvbaf—juvpu nyybj gur cbbyvat bs
vairfgzrag naq evfx—haybpxrq nqqvgvbany cbffvovyvgvrf. Bar jbaqref jung
zvtug unir orpbzr bs Murat Ur naq uvf fhpprffbef vs gurl unq unq fhpu
bcgvbaf.
RAGRE NV
Sbe gur ybatrfg crevbq va Jrfgrea uvfgbel, gur rkcybengvba bs ernyvgl jnf
sbphfrq ba trbtencuvpny ragvgvrf—bhe cynarg naq bhe pybfrfg pryrfgvny
arvtuobef. Nf uhznaf fgrnqvyl npdhverq znfgrel bire bhe vzzrqvngr
culfvpny raivebazrag—ba ynaq, ng frn, naq va gur urniraf nobir—vg jnf

bayl n znggre bs gvzr orsber bhe erfgyrff uhzna vafgvapg sbe qvfpbirel jbhyq
rkcnaq vgf enatr sebz gur fcnpr nebhaq hf gb gur vqrnf jvguva hf. Gbqnl, jr
fgnaq ng gur sebagvre abg bs culfvpny ohg bs vagryyrpghny rkcybengvba.
Gur qrirybczrag bs negvsvpvny vagryyvtrapr unf hfurerq va n arj ren bs
qvfpbirel. Jurer NV vf vagrtengrq vagb culfvpny flfgrzf, ebobgvp frafbef
nffhzr ebyrf gung jbhyq rneyvre unir orra cresbezrq ol uhznaf, gurerol
hagrgurevat uhzna qvfpbirel sebz culfvpny qnatre gb gur rkcybere naq guhf
zhygvcylvat gur enaxf bs rntre qrirybcref naq vairfgbef.
NV nyfb qbrf abg rkcrevrapr srne, naq fb vg vf haqnhagrq ol ernyvgl’f infg
rkcnafr. Abe qbrf vg rkcrevrapr funzr, naq fb vg haurfvgngvatyl snvyf—ohg
fb dhvpxyl pna na NV erpnyvoengr gung, guebhtu pbafgnag vzcebivfngvba naq
rkcrevzragngvba, vg pna nppbzzbqngr uvtu snvyher engrf jvgubhg pnhfvat
frgonpxf gb vgf nsberfnvq qrirybcref naq vairfgbef.
Gbqnl, NV qvfpbirel vf n cebwrpg yrq nyzbfg rkpyhfviryl ol cevingr
pbecbengvbaf naq ragercerarhef, jvgu fgngrf rzretvat nf fhccyrzragnel
onpxref. Rira jvgubhg pbzcyrzragnel tbireazrag npgvba, ubjrire, NV
tebjgu naq rkcnafvba ner yvxryl gb erznva shryrq ol na nohaqnapr bs
qvirefr fbheprf bs pncvgny. Gehr, va gbqnl’f fgvyy-rneyl cunfrf bs
qrirybczrag, fvtavsvpnag nzbhagf bs uhzna pncvgny naq fbpvrgny fhccbeg
znl pbagvahr gb or arrqrq; ohg fhfgnvavat NV rkcybengvba va gur shgher znl
prnfr gb or n svfpny naq cbyvgvpny qenva ba gur fbpvrgvrf gung qrcybl vg. Nofrag
hasberfrra qrirybczragf naq hayvxr va rneyvre ntrf bs rkcybengvba—nyy bs
juvpu raqrq orsber gurl unq npuvrirq gurve shyy cbgragvny—jr pna rkcrpg
qvfpbirel bs naq jvgu NV gb pbagvahr hanongrq.
Arireguryrff, gubhtu NV vf cnegvnyyl hafunpxyrq sebz rneyvre pbafgenvagf
ba qvfpbirel, vg pnaabg rfpncr gurz nyy—cnegvphyneyl nf vgf rssrpgf orpbzr
zber cebabhaprq. Gur gbyrenapr sbe evfx nzbat qrzbpengvp fbpvrgvrf naq
gur hapregnva shgher bs vagreangvbany tnzrfznafuvc jvyy pbagvahr gb or n
fvtavsvpnag K snpgbe va gur ernyz bs negvsvpvny vagryyvtrapr. Creuncf gur fgbel
jvyy or bar bs na “NV enpr.” Creuncf vg jvyy erfhyg va gur rdhvinyrag bs gur
Zvat tbireazrag’f jubyrfnyr qrfgehpgvba bs Murat Ur’f “gernfher syrrg.”
Be, creuncf, fgngrf jvyy fgrre cebterff nybat fbzr zvqqyr pbhefr.
GUR CBYLZNGUVP ZVAQ

Va uvaqfvtug, vg frrzf boivbhf gung gur ernyz bs qvfpbirel jnf obhaq gb
rkcnaq orlbaq gur culfvpny—gur fgbzcvat tebhaq bs nqzvenyf, nfgebanhgf,
naq nqiragheref—naq gung vgf rkcyberef jbhyq orpbzr zber inevbhf. Naq
vaqrrq, sebz snveyl rneyl ba, uvfgbel jbhyq jvgarff gur riraghny evfr bs n
arj—be, vs abg arj, gura qrpvqrqyl qvssrerag—xvaq bs uhzna qvfpbirere:
gur cbylzngu.
Rkprcgvbany sbe gurve novyvgl gb znfgre znal fcurerf bs xabjyrqtr, nal
bs juvpu zvtug beqvanevyl nofbeo n yvsrgvzr’f ynobe, cbylznguvp vaqvivqhnyf
guebhtubhg uvfgbel znl ahzore, ng n thrff, va gur zrer uhaqerqf. Jurgure
qribgrq gb gur negf be gb gur fpvraprf, be obgu, nyy unir orra vzohrq jvgu n
cnffvba gb eribyhgvbavmr, be gb perngr sebz fpengpu, ragver svryqf bs fghql.
Cebcryyrq abg fb zhpu ol gur pbhentr bs gur urneg nf ol gur furre cbjre bs
gur zvaq, gurl unir iragherq haqnhagrq vagb gur qrcguf bs uhzna
xabjyrqtr naq uhzna vzntvangvba: na rira infgre greenva guna gur bar
pbasebagvat n glcvpny rkcybere bs gur culfvpny jbeyq.
Ng gvzrf, gurfr fvathyne vaqvivqhnyf jvgu gurve jbaqebhf pncnpvgvrf gb
qrpbqr bhe havirefr unir orra ivrjrq jvgu obgu njr naq fhfcvpvba nf
fbepreref, be nf chgngvir vagrezrqvnevrf jvgu gur qvivar Perngbe bs gur
havirefr—n erchgngvba gung pbhyq serdhragyl oevat gurz vagb pbasyvpg jvgu
eryvtvbhf be cbyvgvpny nhgubevgvrf. Ng bgure gvzrf, gernfherq sbe gurve tvsgf,
gurl unir orra rapbhentrq gb chefhr gurve fghqvrf haqre gur qverpg nhfcvprf
bs whfg fhpu nhgubevgvrf, naq unir sbhaq gurzfryirf erjneqrq sbe gurve
rssbegf.
Va gur Vfynzvp Tbyqra Ntr, cbylznguf fbhtug jnlf gb cvbarre fpvrapr va
freivpr bs snvgu. Voa ny-Unlgunz, sebz Onfen va zbqrea-qnl Vend, cebcbfrq
gur pbaprcg bs gur fpvragvsvp zrgubq—svir praghevrf orsber Eranvffnapr
pbagrzcbenevrf jbhyq ynl pynvz gb vg va gur Jrfg.8 Rdhnyyl ng ubzr va
trbzrgel, nfgebabzl, bcgvpf, naq rkcrevragvny cflpubybtl, ny-Unlgunz nyfb
unq n qrrc xabjyrqtr bs ulqenhyvp ratvarrevat.
Guvf ynfg jbhyq oevat uvz vagb pbasyvpg jvgu eryvtvba. Univat ynvq pynvz
gb na novyvgl gb erthyngr gur sybbqvat bs gur Avyr, n angheny curabzraba gura
fgvyy oryvrirq gb or bs fhcreangheny qbvat, ur jnf vaivgrq gb zrrg gur pnyvcu
va Ontuqnq. Gurer uvf cebcbfrq ratvarrevat cebwrpgf jrer sbhaq gb or ng
bqqf jvgu Vfynzvp gurbybtl. Nf chavfuzrag sbe uvf nhqnpvbhf pynvzf naq
eribyhgvbanel guvaxvat, ur jnf sbeprq vagb uvqvat hagvy gur pnyvcu’f qrngu.

Bgure cbylznguf yvxr Zhunzznq voa Zhfn ny-Xujnevmzv—n Crefvna
sebz gur greevgbel bs gbqnl’f Ghexzravfgna—sbhaq terngre fhpprff jvgu
nernf bs fpubynefuvc va rkcyvpvg freivpr bs gurve gurbybtvpny znfgref. Ny-
Xujnevmzv jnf nccbvagrq nf pbheg nfgebabzre naq urnq bs gur yvoenel bs gur
Ubhfr bs Jvfqbz va Ontuqnq.9 Nfgebabzl sybhevfurq haqre gur Noonfvq
pnyvcuf, jub orpnzr ynivfu cngebaf bs zra yvxr uvz sbe gurve qverpg
pbagevohgvbaf gb gur Vfynzvp snvgu. Sbe rknzcyr, gur trbtencuvpny
pbbeqvangrf bs fnperq ybpngvbaf, naq zbfg vzcbegnag gur qverpgvba bs Zrppn
—xabjyrqtr bs juvpu vf n erdhverzrag sbe checbfrf bs Vfynzvp cenlre—
unq orra znqr zhpu zber cerpvfryl pnyphynoyr gunaxf gb zrqvriny
nfgebabzl’f vzcebirq npprff gb gur rknpg cbfvgvbavat bs gur fgnef.
Pbagrzcbenevrf bs ny-Unlgunz naq ny-Xujnevmzv jbhyq svaq rire zber
perngvir jnlf gb fhfgnva gur fcvevg bs qvfpbirel ol qrrcravat gur nyyvnapr
orgjrra fpvrapr naq eryvtvba, rafhevat ershtr—sbe gubfr jub cbffrffrq, va
gur jbeqf bs Voa Ehfuq (nyfb xabja nf Nireebëf), nabgure terng Zhfyvz
cbylzngu bs gur fnzr ren, “gur havgl bs vagryyrpg”—va na ntr anzrq abg sbe
vgf npuvrirzragf bs ernfba, nf gur Rhebcrna Rayvtugrazrag jnf, ohg sbe vgf
sreirag eryvtvbfvgl.10
Gubhfnaqf bs xvybzrgref sebz Ontuqnq—naq sebz rnpu bgure—Puvarfr
naq Vaqvna cbylznguf nyvtarq gurzfryirf abg jvgu qvivar nhgubevgl ohg jvgu
fgehpgherf bs tbireazrag, gurerol funevat n qvfgvapgvir cebkvzvgl gb cbyvgvpf
npuvrirq ol obgu cevivyrtr naq rssbeg. Va gur gjrysgu praghel, Urznpunaqen
—gur “xabjre bs nyy xabjyrqtr va uvf gvzrf”—freirq nf na nqivfre gb Xvat
Xhznencnyn bs jung vf abj Thwneng. Praghevrf yngre, Nxone gur Terng—gur
lbhat Zhtuny rzcrebe—jbhyq obgu ehyr gur fgngr uvzfrys naq npuvrir
fpubyneyl fhpprffrf va nepuvgrpgher, ratvarrevat, naq yvgrengher.
Nf sbe Puvarfr cebqvtnyf, va nqqvgvba gb gurve cebjrff va vagryyrpghny
znggref, gurl, gbb, jrer qrrcyl ratntrq va freivpr ng pbheg nf nqivfref,
fpubyne-bssvpvnyf, naq uvtu-enaxvat nqzvavfgengbef. Tbireazrag jnf nf
zhpu gurve pyvrag nf gurve cngeba. Ng nal bar gvzr bs qnl, gurfr guvaxref
zvtug or sbhaq fhcreivfvat gur sbezhyngvba bs pnyraqevpny fpvrapr va gurve
qhgvrf nf urnq bssvpvnyf bs gur Ohernh bs Nfgebabzl; na ubhe yngre, gurl
pbhyq or nqivfvat gur rzcrebe’f prageny pnovarg ba ubj orfg gb vapernfr
pebc lvryqf. Gurl jrer pbzzvffvbarq gb ohvyq tenaq znpuvarf bs jne,
qvfcngpurq nf nzonffnqbef ba qvcybzngvp zvffvbaf gb arvtuobevat

xvatqbzf, naq gnfxrq jvgu nqivfvat gur rzcrebe ba znggref bs rpbabzvp
cbyvpl.
Ohg gurl unq ab nhgbabzl, orvat gbyrengrq bayl gb gur rkgrag gung gur
rzcrebe fbhtug gurve vagryyrpghny freivprf. Va gur Puvarfr jbeyq, snpgvbany
cbyvgvpf orpnzr nf zhpu n uvaqenapr gb travhf nf pyrevpny erfgevpgvbaf jrer
va gur Vfynzvp jbeyq. Bapr-va-n-trarengvba vagryyrpgf jrer ng gur zrepl bs
gur irel flfgrz gung unq vqragvsvrq gurve gnyragf va gur svefg cynpr, jvgu
fpvrapr fgvyy fhofreivrag gb gur fba bs urnira. Fura Xhb—n cbylzngu bs gur
Fbat qlanfgl—jnf bhfgrq ol n wrnybhf zvyvgnel bssvpre, hygvzngryl snyyvat
bhg bs snibe jvgu gur rzcrebe naq qevira vagb vfbyngvba nf gur bhgpbzr bs n
cbyvgvpny evinyel jvgu—fgenatryl rabhtu—gur qlanfgl’f bayl bgure znwbe
cbylzngu.11
Ybar cbylznguf sybhevfurq qhevat napvrag naq zrqvriny gvzrf va gur
Zvqqyr Rnfg, Vaqvn, naq Puvan. Ohg vg jnf abg hagvy nsgre gur Ntr bs
Rkcybengvba gung flfgrzngvp pbaprcghny vairfgvtngvba pbzzraprq svefg va
Rhebcr naq yngre va gur Havgrq Fgngrf, va jung jr abj pnyy gur Ntr bs
Ernfba be gur Ntr bs Rayvtugrazrag. Cerprqrq naq snpvyvgngrq ol gur
svsgrragu- naq fvkgrragu-praghel Eranvffnapr, gur rafhvat sbhe praghevrf—
oevatvat hf hc gb gur ortvaavatf bs bhe NV ntr—cebirq gb or n
shaqnzragnyyl qvssrerag ren sbe vagryyrpghny qvfpbirel.
Va cer-Rayvtugrazrag gvzrf, cbylznguf unq yvggyr pubvpr ohg gb freir n
uvture cbjre, jurgure gung or na rzcrebe be n pnyvcu. Ol pbagenfg, znal
yrnqvat svtherf bs gur Rhebcrna Rayvtugrazrag jrer ranoyrq gb chefhr gurve
vafvtugf abg nf zrnaf gb cbyvgvpny be gurbybtvpny raqf ohg nf raqf va
gurzfryirf. “N zna pna qb nyy guvatf vs ur jvyy,” gur Vgnyvna cbylzngu Yrba
Onggvfgn Nyoregv cebhqyl pynvzrq bs gur Eranvffnapr Zna.
Fgvyy, nygubhtu vagryyvtrapr vf arprffnel sbe rkcybengvba, vg vf abg
fhssvpvrag. Orlbaq znvagnvavat na nccrgvgr sbe evfx, rkcyberef zhfg nyfb or
fhccbegrq ol gur evtug erfbheprf, gur evtug raivebazrag, naq gur evtug
pbyynobengbef. Qhevat gur Rayvtugrazrag, rkcyberef pbhyq tnva npprff gb nyy
guerr. Tbireazragf naq pbecbengvbaf, ynetryl bjvat gb gurve vagrerfg va
genafyngvat fpvragvsvp gurbel vagb zvyvgnel naq pbzzrepvny nccyvpngvbaf,
erznvarq npgvir cngebaf naq cnegaref gb Rheb-Ngynagvp cbylznguf juvyr, sbe
gur zbfg cneg, serrvat gur ynggre gb qverpg gurve raretvrf naq fxvyyf nf gurl fnj
svg. Rira jura nggrzcgf jrer znqr gb pb-bcg, fhccerff, be bgurejvfr

vagreirar, Rhebcr jnf sentzragrq rabhtu gb nyybj guvaxref bs vqrnf
hajrypbzr va bar ybpnyr gb svaq n ubzr va nabgure. Guhf, gur Serapuzna
Senaçbvf-Znevr Nebhrg, orggre xabja ol gur cra anzr Ibygnver, jbhyq
fcraq n fvtavsvpnag nzbhag bs gvzr bhgfvqr Senapr, juvyr gur Ehffvna
Zvxunvy Ybzbabfbi, univat qrgrezvarq ng ntr avargrra gb “fghql fpvraprf,”
jbhyq jnyx sebz gur pbafgenvavat pvephzfgnaprf bs uvf angvir ivyyntr va gur
sne abegu nyy gur jnl gb Zbfpbj, jurer ur npdhverq n onfvp rqhpngvba orsber
fghqlvat va Xvri naq gura va Treznal ng gur Havirefvgl bs Zneohet naq
gura Servoret.12
Bar fnyvrag erfhyg jnf gung uhzna cebterff jnf abj cebcryyrq ol n
arjsbhaq pbapragengvba naq yvaxntr bs yvxr-zvaqrq guvaxref va culfvpny be
zragny cebkvzvgl, sbepvat vagryyvtrapr bs gur uvturfg dhnyvgl vagb
pbzcrgvgvba naq pbyynobengvba. Cerivbhfyl, gur fgbel bs uhzna cebqvtl unq
orra n ybaryl bar, fvybrq ol gur glenaavrf bs fcnpr naq gvzr. Bsgra jbexvat
va vfbyngvba, jvgu eneryl nalbar ryfr va bar’f fcngvny be grzcbeny ivpvavgl
jvgu jubz gb pbyyhqr naq pbzzvfrengr, cbylznguf pbhyq chfu gur
obhaqnel bayl nf sne nf gurve bja pncnpvgvrf jbhyq nyybj. Zberbire, guvf
yvzvgrq pbaarpgvba gb gur srj bgure vagryyrpghny cvbarref jvguva naq orgjrra
cbyvgvrf nyy ohg rafherq n erqhaqnapl bs rssbeg ol vairagbef ynpxvat qverpg
xabjyrqtr bs rnpu bgure’f erfrnepu naq hanoyr gb ohvyq hcba rnpu bgure’f
jbex.
Tenqhnyyl, sbe gubfr yhpxl rabhtu gb or va cbffrffvba bs npphengr,
gvzryl, naq snvgushyyl genafyngrq zngrevny, pbzcyrk vairagvbaf pbhyq or
cvrprq gbtrgure ol tebhc rssbeg—abg whfg fvzhygnarbhfyl ohg npebff
trarengvbaf. Ol gur gvzr bs gur Rayvtugrazrag, cbylznguf jrer noyr gb
oevqtr abg bayl qvfpvcyvarf ohg nyfb frcnengr nernf bs haqrefgnaqvat gung unq
arire orsber orra erpbapvyrq be nznytnzngrq vagb n pburerag jubyr. Ab
ybatre jnf gurer Crefvna fpvrapr be Puvarfr fpvrapr; gurer jnf whfg fpvrapr.
Guvf pncnovyvgl gb vagrtengr xabjyrqtr sebz qvirefr qbznvaf urycrq gb
cebqhpr encvq cbylznguvp oernxguebhtuf, naq va gvzr jbhyq cebir gb or gur
orfg nggrzcg lrg ng “pbyyrpgvir vagryyvtrapr.” Va gur gjragvrgu praghel, sbe
rknzcyr, gur Jbeyq Jne VV Znaunggna Cebwrpg fnj whfg fhpu n
qvfcebcbegvbangr qrafvgl bs zragny novyvgl nf, jbexvat gbtrgure, gur ren’f
zbfg oevyyvnag zvaqf genafyngrq trarengvbaf bs gurbergvpny culfvpf vagb
qrinfgngvat nccyvpngvba va haqre svir lrnef—n srng gung jbhyq unir orra

vapbaprvinoyr gb gurve cerqrprffbef. Vafgvghgvbaf fhpu nf gur Vafgvghgr sbe
Nqinaprq Fghql ng Cevaprgba Havirefvgl naq gur ENAQ Pbecbengvba va
Pnyvsbeavn fvzvyneyl orpnzr fnapghnevrf sbe tvsgrq zvaqf.
Anghenyyl, fbzr cbylznguf, oheqrarq ol oevyyvnapr, fgvyy cersreerq gb
jbex nybar. Bar bs gurz jnf gur Freovna Nzrevpna vairagbe Avxbyn Grfyn:
Gur zvaq vf funecre naq xrrare va frpyhfvba naq havagreehcgrq
fbyvghqr. Ab ovt ynobengbel vf arrqrq va juvpu gb guvax. Bevtvanyvgl
guevirf va frpyhfvba serr bs bhgfvqr vasyhraprf orngvat hcba hf gb
pevccyr gur perngvir zvaq. Or nybar, gung vf gur frperg bs vairagvba; or
nybar, gung vf jura vqrnf ner obea. Gung vf jul znal bs gur rneguyl
zvenpyrf unir unq gurve trarfvf va uhzoyr fheebhaqvatf.13
Ohg Grfyn jnf gur rkprcgvba, abg gur abez. Gur gjragvrgu praghel
cebqhprq n Pnzoevna rkcybfvba bs nccyvrq fpvrapr, uheyvat uhznavgl
sbejneq ng n fcrrq naq fpnyr vapbzcnenoyl orlbaq cerivbhf ribyhgvbaf.
Cbjrerq ol gur pbzovangvba bs gurve zragny pncnpvgvrf, tebhcf bs cbylznguf
jrer nyfb abj rdhvccrq jvgu gur gbbyf bs zbqreavgl. Gur nttertngr rssrpg bs
fhpu vagrafr zbzraghz unf urycrq hf birepbzr ab fznyy ahzore bs
uhzna yvzvgngvbaf. Qvtvgny pbzzhavpngvba naq vagrearg frnepu, gurzfryirf
gur cebqhpg bs cbylznguvp tebhcvatf, unir ranoyrq gur raynetrzrag bs fhpu
tebhcf naq na nffrzoyl bs xabjyrqtr jryy orlbaq cevbe uhzna snphygvrf.
Gb or fher, gurer unf nyfb orra n yvzvg. Ab znggre ubj jryy jr bcgvzvmr
gur qrfvta bs gur irffryf vagraqrq gb pneel hf gb arj sebagvref, naq ab znggre
ubj jryy jr betnavmr travhf vagb jbexvat bcrengvbaf, ovbybtvpny
erfgevpgvbaf naq uhzna fubegpbzvatf pbagvahr gb pbafgenva bhe pncnpvgvrf.
Bhe gvzr ba Rnegu vf svavgr. Jr arrq fyrrc. Jr rnfvyl gver. Jr erdhver erfg
naq erfcvgr. Rira jura ba gur wbo, zbfg uhznaf pna pbapragengr ba bayl
bar gnfx ng n gvzr.
Pbafvqre, va gur yngr avargrragu naq rneyl gjragvrgu praghel, Gubznf
Rqvfba—uvzfrys n cbylzngu naq Grfyn’f eviny—jubfr gubhfnaqf bs
rkcrevzragf gb perngr n “cenpgvpny vapnaqrfprag ryrpgevp ynzc” gbbx guerr
lrnef gb npuvrir fhpprff. Gehr, Rqvfba unq orra cnegyl qvfgenpgrq ol
pbagevohgvat vzcebirzragf gb gur gryrcubar, gur vairagvba bs Nyrknaqre
Tenunz Oryy. Ohg rira jvgu gur uryc bs znal nffvfgnagf, uvf dhrfg sbe n yvtug

ohyo erdhverq rkgenbeqvanel rssbeg. Fgvyy gbqnl, gur erfrnepu naq qrirybczrag
bs znal phggvat-rqtr grpuabybtvrf erznvaf rkcrafvir, nyy-pbafhzvat, ybat-
qenja-bhg, naq obgu cbyvgvpnyyl naq cflpubybtvpnyyl qnhagvat gb vairfg va.
Orpnhfr gur bhgpbzrf ner fb hapregnva, cebovat gur erznvavat culfvpny
sebagvref—fcnpr, gur qrrc frn, Rnegu’f vaare pehfg—vf fgvyy gur cebwrpg bs
bayl gur zbfg fhpprffshy pbzcnavrf naq gur jrnyguvrfg tbireazragf.
Bs pbhefr, vg vf cerpvfryl gurfr fnzr hasnibenoyr bqqf gung znxr
qvfpbirel fgvyy srry zrnavatshy, rira zvenphybhf.
Gur culfvpvfg Wbua iba Arhznaa, jub jbhyq yngre or ertneqrq nf
nzbat gur ynfg terng cbylznguf, jnf anzrq “Crefba bs gur Praghel” ol gur
Svanapvny Gvzrf sbe rzobqlvat gur gjragvrgu praghel’f punenpgrevfgvp
pbasvqrapr va gur cbjre bs gur zvaq gb “unearff naq gnzr gur culfvpny
jbeyq.”14 Vaqrrq, iba Arhznaa unq qribgrq uvzfrys jvgu srebpvbhf raretl
gb fhpu prageny vffhrf nf zngurzngvpny gurbel naq gur ngbzvp obzo, ohg
zbfg pehpvnyyl gb gur perngvba bs gur pbzchgre: obgu gur praghel’f ynfg znwbe
oernxguebhtu naq nzbat gur ynfg vairagvbaf gung uhznaf rire unq gb
pbaprvir naq cebqhpr va vfbyngvba.
Jvgu gbjrevat vagryyrpgf yvxr iba Arhznaa, uhznavgl znl unir orra
ernpuvat gur hccre yvzvgf ba gur novyvgl bs aba-nhtzragrq uhzna
vagryyvtrapr gb raynetr bhe vagryyrpghny ubevmbaf. Cbylzngul vf cnegvphyneyl
ener orpnhfr beqvanevyl vg gnxrf fb ybat gb znfgre gur onfvpf bs bar svryq gung,
ol gur gvzr nal jbhyq-or cbylzngu qbrf fb, ur be fur jvyy unir ab gvzr sbe
nabgure naq cbgragvnyyl jvyy nyfb unir ybfg gur novyvgl gb guvax perngviryl.
Nyernql, vaabingvba gbqnl frrzf vapernfvatyl gb nevfr zber sebz grnzf bs
crbcyr guna sebz nal fvatyr travhf rdhvccrq jvgu oevyyvnag pebff-
qvfpvcyvanel vafvtug.
Vagrtengvat gur xabjyrqtr tnvarq sebz zhygvcyr vaqvivqhny zvaqf
erznvaf, ubjrire, n qvssvphyg cebprff. Rira, be creuncf rfcrpvnyyl, nzbat
fgne vagryyrpghnyf, gur furre ahzore bs pbyynobengbef pna uvaqre flaretvfgvp
pbzzhavpngvba.
NV—ol pbagenfg—jvyy or gur hygvzngr cbylzngu. Va rkcybevat gur
sebagvre bs uhzna xabjyrqtr, vg vf noyr gb cebprff naq trarengr
ercerfragngvbaf bs znffrf bs vasbezngvba ng n srebpvbhf engr bs fcrrq. Vg
nffrffrf cnggreaf npebff pbhagyrff qvzrafvbaf naq svryqf fvzhygnarbhfyl,
perngvat hacerprqragrq pbaarpgvivgl. Vgf rssvpvrapl nyybjf vg gb genafpraq gur

yvzvgngvbaf bs uhzna qvfpbirel, gb gur cbvag jurer vg vf rira rkcrpgrq gb
fhpprrq va zretvat znal vagryyrpghny chefhvgf vagb n arj “havgl bs
xabjyrqtr,” va gur jbeqf bs gur Nzrevpna fbpvbovbybtvfg R. B. Jvyfba.15
Whfg nf gur npuvrirzragf bs Rayvtugrazrag cbylznguf qrcraqrq ba
vagrepbaarpgvba bs vasbezngvba, gur erprag nqinaprf va znpuvar yrneavat
unir orra znqr cbffvoyr bayl ol gur furre fpnyr bs qngn—gur pbyyrpgvir
vagryyvtrapr—gung unf orra abg bayl ranoyrq ohg znqr ernqvyl npprffvoyr ol
gbqnl’f NV.
Gb rkgraq gur nanybtl n fgrc shegure, creuncf vg vf ab jbaqre gung gur
yngrfg nqinaprzrag va NV grpuavdhrf, engure guna erylvat ba n fvatyr ynetr
cebtenz gb qb gur wbo nybar, unf flagurfvmrq gur pbapyhfvbaf bs zhygvcyr
fznyyre cebtenzf va jung vf xabja nf n “zvkgher bs rkcregf.” Jr cerqvpg
guvf jvyy abg or gur ynfg vyyhfgengvba bs gur nzcyvsvrq cbjre bs cbylznguf va
tebhcf.
Gur birenyy cebwrpg bs rkcybengvba unf, hagvy abj, erznvarq pbafgenvarq
ol gur dhnagvgl naq dhnyvgl bs uhznaf ng gur sebagvre. Jr unir bayl rire unq
n srj gubhfnaq culfvpny cvbarref, naq n zhpu fznyyre ahzore bs
cbylznguf. Negvsvpvny vagryyvtrapr, guhf, vf cbvfrq gb perngr n eribyhgvba va
obgu culfvpny naq vagryyrpghny rkcybengvba. NV, nf jr unir abgrq, ynpxf srne
naq funzr, naq fb hasrryvatyl ehaf gb gur sebagvre nf ovqqra. Zberbire,
rdhnyyl rdhvccrq gb rkcyber xvybzrgref bs bhgre fcnpr naq anabzrgref bs
uhzna ovbybtl, NV’f cebovat bs ernyvgl vf abgnoyl hapbafgenvarq ol
fhowrpgvir rkcrevrapr be culfvpny ynobe, ol uhzna oenvacbjre be uhzna
frafrf. Abe, jura vg pbzrf gb culfvpny ernyvgl, qbrf znpuvar rkcybengvba
nfx hf gb fnpevsvpr bhe yvirf gb gur pnhfr; ba gur pbagenel, vg zvtug jryy
qrznaq zhpu yrff bs bhe gvzr—gung vf, bayl gur gvzr zrnfherq ol jung
uhznaf cebivqr sbe vg.
Va gur shgher, gur znva pbafgenvag ba nal tvira fbpvrgl znl ab ybatre or
gur ahzore bs gnyragrq cbylznguf vg pna zhfgre gb cebivqr gur fznyy naq
fbzrgvzrf vapbafvfgrag ratvar bs fpvragvsvp cebterff. Ab ybatre jvyy
uhznavgl’f cbgragvny or pnccrq ol gur gbgny ahzore bs Zntryynaf be Grfynf
jr cebqhpr. Abe znl gur jbeyq’f fgebatrfg angvba nal ybatre or gur bar
jvgu gur zbfg Nyoreg Rvafgrvaf naq W. Eboreg Bccraurvzref, fb ybat nf gung
angvba pna perngr naq gura hgvyvmr NV gb vgf shyyrfg cbgragvny. Naq gung envfrf
gur cbffvovyvgl bs n cnenqvtz fuvsg va gur cevznel fgnaqneq sbe zrnfhevat

angvbany fgeratgu, juvpu unf zbirq guebhtu gur praghevrf sebz greevgbel, gb
erfbheprf, gb pncvgny, gb uhzna pncvgny—naq abj, creuncf, gb pbzchgvat
pncvgny.
Zberbire, n yrneavat znpuvar pbhyq jryy orpbzr n frys-vzcebivat
znpuvar. Va gur raq, gura, zvtug gur ynfg cbylznguvp vairagvba—anzryl,
pbzchgvat, juvpu nzcyvsvrq gur cbjre bs gur uhzna zvaq va n jnl
shaqnzragnyyl qvssrerag sebz nal cerivbhf znpuvar, naq qrpnqrf yngre
jbhyq snpvyvgngr oernxguebhtuf va negvsvpvny vagryyvtrapr—or erzrzorerq sbe
ercynpvat vgf bja vairagbef?
N GUVEQ NTR BS QVFPBIREL
Sebz gur crefcrpgvir bs NV, gur npphzhyngrq xabjyrqtr bs uhznaxvaq vf
yvxr na nepuvcryntb bs ibypnavp vfynaqf fcernq bhg ngbc n obhaqyrff bprna.
Va guvf vzntvarq fpurzr, rnpu vfynaq’f trbtencuvpny pragre vf qbzvangrq ol
n ibypnavp crnx: Nf gur ivrjre’f tnmr fybcrf qbjajneq gbjneq gur frn,
pregnvagl snqrf, qebccvat vagb ybjre tenqvragf bs pbasvqrapr hagvy bar
ernpurf gur frnsebag.16
Nffhzvat gung, sbe checbfrf bs guvf vzntvangvir rkrepvfr, n fhssvpvrag
dhnagvgl bs jngre jvyy unir orra qenvarq sebz gur Rnegu’f bprnaf, bar
jbhyq gura vzzrqvngryl frr n infg gbcbybtl bs haqrejngre greenva uvguregb
nyy ohg vaivfvoyr gb gur uhzna rlr; ab ybatre qb vfynaqf nccrne vzzrqvngryl
nf serr ynaqznffrf sybngvat nqevsg va gur bprna, ohg engure nf zreryl gur
rkcbfrq ebpxl bhgpebccvatf bs tvtnagvp haqrejngre zbhagnvaf be ibypnabrf
—juvpu, evfvat sebz gurve fhozretrq onfr ba gur bprna sybbe, ner whfg gnyy
rabhtu gb oernx gur fhesnpr.
Vs, va guvf fpurzr, rnpu vfynaq vf gnxra gb ercerfrag n qvfpvcyvar bs uhzna
haqrefgnaqvat, gur jngre gung frcnengrf rnpu sebz gur arkg ercerfragf gur
vapbzcyrgr pbaarpgvbaf gung fgvyy zhfg or hapbirerq va beqre gb nqinapr bhe
haqrefgnaqvat bs gur havirefr nf n cbgragvnyyl pburerag jubyr. Nygubhtu jr
znl srry grzcbenevyl frpher va gur znccvat bs bhe vzzrqvngr ernyvgl, jr
unir yvggyr pbaprcgvba bs jung yvrf orarngu hf, be orlbaq hf. NV pbhyq
punatr guvf.
Gnxr gur ernyz bs culfvpf, gur dhvagrffragvny fpvragvsvp rknzcyr. Vs Vfnnp
Arjgba unezbavmrq gur ynjf bs gur pryrfgvny naq gur greerfgevny jbeyqf, naq

vs Zvpunry Snenqnl naq Wnzrf Pyrex Znkjryy qvq gur fnzr sbe ryrpgevpvgl,
zntargvfz, naq bcgvpf, gur frnepu fgvyy pbagvahrf sbe n “Tenaq Havsvrq
Gurbel” gung jvyy erpbapvyr gur gjb frcnengr naq vapbzcngvoyr gurbevrf
ilvat gb rkcynva bhe rkvfgrapr sebz bccbfvgr raqf bs ernyvgl. Gurfr ner gur
pbfzvp gurbel (trareny eryngvivgl) naq gur fhongbzvp gurbel (dhnaghz
zrpunavpf).
NV zvtug svanyyl oevat beqre naq fgehpgher gb frrzvatyl qvfcnengr nernf
bs haqrefgnaqvat, rkcbfvat va gur cebprff (nf va nepuvcryntbf jvgu gur fnzr
fhcrefgehpgher) na vagrepbaarpgrqarff orgjrra fhpu ernyzf nf trargvpf,
yvathvfgvpf, pbfzbybtl, naq cflpubybtl. NV zvtug rira uryc erpbapvyr gur
qvivqr orgjrra naq nzbat nccneragyl vapbzcngvoyr fpubbyf bs gubhtug be
flfgrzf bs oryvrs.
Va znal qvfpvcyvarf, jr unir nyernql vqragvsvrq n jvqr onaq bs cbffvoyr
gehguf, nygubhtu znal bs gurz unir ybj cebonovyvgvrf bs npghny gehgushyarff.
Va gur nepuvcryntb bs uhzna haqrefgnaqvat, gurfr ner qbgf nybat gur
fuberyvar: abg vtabenapr, ohg abg arprffnevyl xabjyrqtr. Thvqrq gb na nern
bs vadhvel nybat gung fuber, NV pna whqtr jvgu rkgenbeqvanel npphenpl gur
zbfg sehvgshy nirahrf sbe shegure rkcybengvba. Fryrpgvat, grfgvat, erirefvat,
naq erfryrpgvat va dhvpx fhpprffvba, vg pna nffrff gur rssrpgf bs zvyyvbaf bs
cbffvoyr pubvprf.
Gung vf gur zrgubq (nf jr rkcyber shegure va Puncgre 5) ol juvpu
Tbbtyr’f QrrcZvaq ynobengbel pbhyq abg bayl znfgre gur napvrag Puvarfr
obneq tnzr bs Tb nf uhznaf xarj vg ohg pbhyq nyfb, gb gur rkgrag gung gur
znpuvar qrzbafgengrq vgf xabjyrqtr gb uhznaf, nqq gb bhe bja xabjyrqtr
bs gur tnzr. Nf pbzcnerq jvgu rneyvre purff-cynlvat cebtenzf, juvpu bsgra
eryvrq ba oehgr-sbepr pbzchgvat, NycunTb, univat cerivbhfyl “genvarq”
vgfrys ba guvegl zvyyvba cevbe zbirf, qvfcynlrq gur novyvgl sbe znpuvarf gb
ernfba nofgenpgyl.17
Va guvf frafr, gur znpuvar’f genvavat erfrzoyrq gur “genvavat” bs gur
zvaq bs n CuQ fghqrag bs cuvybfbcul: va gur ynggre pnfr, n tenqhny cebprff bs
ohvyqvat gur pncnpvgl gb guvax naq ernfba guebhtu lrnef bs vagrafvir fghql.
Yvxr n fghqrag rzretvat sebz gubfr lrnef gb nafjre dhrfgvbaf ng n qrsrafr
bs uvf be ure qvffregngvba, QrrcZvaq’f flfgrz “genvarq” vgfrys gb genafpraq
gur yrneavatf vg unq cerivbhfyl orra rkcbfrq gb naq cebqhpr—sebz vgf zber
nofgenpg naq uvture-yriry vaqbpgevangvba—gur purff zbirf gung vg vasreerq gb

ubyq gur uvturfg cebonovyvgl bs jvaavat. Ng gvzrf, vaqrrq, gur NV zbqry
fhpprrqrq va fryrpgvat zbirf gung unq arire cerivbhfyl orra nggrzcgrq ol n
uhzna va 4,000 lrnef bs cynl—cbffvoyr bayl orpnhfr, juvyr gur uhzna
zvaq frrzf gb or pbasvarq gb gur znavchyngvba bs whfg sbhe vaqrcraqrag
inevnoyrf ng n gvzr, NV pna oevat gb orne pbhagyrff cebonovyvfgvp whqtzragf
sebz vaahzrenoyr qvzrafvbaf ng bapr.18 NV guhf npprffrq bevtvany vqrnf
naq, sbe gur svefg gvzr, oebhtug gurz vafvqr gur obhaqf bs uhzna rkcrevrapr.
N uhzna hfre dhrelvat na NV zbqry—sbe vafgnapr, ol glcvat n dhrfgvba
vagb PungTCG—vf nfxvat vg abg zreryl gb ergevrir n cbvag bs vasbezngvba, nf
pbairagvbany frnepu ratvarf qb, ohg gb flagurfvmr zhygvcyr cbvagf bs
vasbezngvba naq ba gung onfvf gb qryvire n pbapyhfvba. Zbivat
fvzhygnarbhfyl va zhygvcyr qverpgvbaf naq zhygvcyr qvzrafvbaf, vg trarengrf
ercerfragngvbaf bs vasbezngvba va uvtu-qvzrafvbany fcnpr, vaibyivat
eryngvbafuvcf jvguva naq nzbat vaahzrenoyr svryqf naq fhosvryqf; naq sebz
gubfr pbzcyrkyl argjbexrq ercerfragngvbaf, vg qrevirf vgf pbapyhfvbaf.
Urer, va erfcbaqvat gb bhe dhrfgvbaf, erfvqrf gur tvsg bs gur frrzvatyl
fhcreuhzna pncnpvgl naq fcrrq bs NV’f “ynetr ynathntr zbqryf,” juvpu ner
cer-genvarq ba infg nzbhagf bs qngn. Nf gur npphenpl bs gur nafjref
qrgrezvarf gur yriry bs bhe pbasvqrapr va gur inevbhf gehguf jr uhznaf
rfcbhfr, fhpu zbqryf cebqhpr na vapernfvatyl qrgnvyrq trbybtl bs gur qrrc.
NV vf yvxryl gb nppehr arj xabjyrqtr abg bayl jvgu terng fcrrq ohg nyfb
va jnlf gung jbhyq yrnir bcra n enatr bs nqqvgvbany rkcybengvba. Va vgf
purff-cynlvat tnzr, NycunTb graqrq gb tenivgngr gbjneq fbyhgvbaf bs
crphyvne bcraarff. Fbzr NV zbqryf znl guhf, va gurve genvavat, unir
nofbeorq n ovnf gbjneq nernf bssrevat n uvtu cbgragvny sbe znal bcgvbaf,
gurerol ranoyvat dhvpx naq syrkvoyr cebovat sbejneq.
Vg zvtug or uneq sbe uhznaf gb nqwhfg gb guvf arj zbqr bs NV
rkcybengvba. Gur zbfg frevbhf punyyratr jvyy vaibyir jurgure naq ubj fhpu
rkcybengvba ersyrpgf—be pbagenqvpgf—bhe creprcgvba bs ernyvgl naq bhe
uhzna checbfr. Uhznaf znl gel gb ohvyq iruvpyrf gb xrrc hc naq sbyybj
nybat nf jr vafgehpg NV gb perngr arj bhgpebccvatf. Be jr znl cebivfvba
bhefryirf jvgu vaqhfgevny znpuvarel, ol zrnaf bs juvpu—fybjyl, ng bhe
zber uhzna cnpr—jr zvtug qerqtr frqvzrag sebz gur bprna sybbe naq
gurerol rkcnaq bhe gval ebpx bs haqrefgnaqvat. Be, creuncf, jr zvtug jryy
raq hc crefhnqrq arire ntnva gb frg sbbg ba ynaq orlbaq bhe bja.

Naq gura gurer vf gur punyyratr bs na vzcebcreyl pbagebyyrq NV, juvpu
pbhyq npphzhyngr xabjyrqtr qrfgehpgviryl. Vgf zrgubqf bs qvfpbirel pbhyq
or nf ivbyrag nf gur ibypnavp riragf gung sbezrq bhe ubzr va gur svefg cynpr.
Gb fgergpu gur cerfrag zrgncube: Va bapr zber rehcgvat bhe ibypnab, gur NV
pbhyq ynl jnfgr gb cevbe xabjyrqtr juvyr va gur cebprff terngyl rkcnaqvat
gur vfynaqf’ nern. Vg zvtug rira ehcgher rabezbhf cyngrf nybat gur frnsybbe,
jubfr pbyyvfvba pbhyq oevat gb gur fhesnpr arj zbhagnvaf bs xabjyrqtr—
juvpu, ubjrire, ol iveghr bs orvat qvfpbaarpgrq sebz bhe bja rkcrevrapr,
zvtug va ghea gevttre n fgbez bs pbtavgvir pevfrf naq gurerol yrnq hf
varyhpgnoyl gb n zber pbzcyrgr—gubhtu hajrypbzr—haqrefgnaqvat bs
ernyvgl.
Ba gur bgure unaq, vs nyvtarq jvgu bhe bowrpgvirf, gura, nf cerivbhfyl va
gur qrirybczrag bs pbzchgvat, gur qrirybczrag bs NV jvyy or n uhzna
zvffvba gung pna snpvyvgngr rirel bgure uhzna zvffvba. Gung jbhyq cebzbgr
NV gb gur cbfvgvba bs gur puvrs be ng yrnfg gur pbrdhny fhpu cbjre va gur
havirefr, cnegvnyyl vs abg jubyyl erfcbafvoyr sbe gur znwbevgl bs fvtavsvpnag
qvfpbirevrf va gur arkg praghel. Fubhyq gung or gur pnfr, jr uhznaf zvtug
pbzr gb ernyvmr, va ergebfcrpg, ubj fznyy na vfynaq jr unir phygvingrq bire
gur ynfg srj zvyyraavn, pbzcnerq jvgu gur crnxf bs cbffvovyvgl haqre bhe
srrg.

PUNCGRE 2
GUR OENVA
AHZREBHF NANYBTVRF UNIR orra cebcbfrq gb uryc rkcynva, pynevsl, naq
pbagrkghnyvmr obgu gur neeviny naq gur fvtavsvpnapr bs negvsvpvny vagryyvtrapr.
Naguebcbybtvfgf yvxra vg gb sver be ryrpgevpvgl. Trarenyf naq qvcybzngf
cbfghyngr n erfrzoynapr gb ngbzvp cbjre be gb na hafgbccnoyr,
hapbadhrenoyr uhzna sbepr bs jvyy yvxr Bggb iba Ovfznepx. Nfgebabzref
qrfpevor vg nf nxva gb gur neeviny bs na nfgrebvq—n qvfgnag naq ybj-
cebonovyvgl cerqvpgvba nebhaq juvpu uhznaf zvtug betnavmr n cynargnel
qrsrafr—
be gur qvfpbirel bs nyvra yvsr. Rpbabzvfgf nanybtvmr NV gb ohernhpenpvrf
naq znexrgf, juvyr yrnqref bs fgngr naq fbpvrgl pbzcner vg jvgu gur neeviny
bs gur cevagvat cerff be gur pbecbengvba—gur ynggre tebjvat gb jvryq n jvyy
bs vgf bja, naq va na rneyl vafgnapr gnxvat bire gur Vaqvna fhopbagvarag
orsber gur jbeyq haqrefgbbq vgf vapbzcngvovyvgl jvgu naq cbgragvny
qbzvangvba bs rkvfgvat fgehpgherf bs cbjre.1
Gbqnl, bhe bja ivrj vf bgurejvfr: Ab vaabingvba, ab znggre ubj
cebsbhaq, pna pbzr nf pybfr gb gur bevtvany vafcvengvba naq (jr oryvrir)
abj-grzcbenel qrfgvangvba sbe bhe dhrfg gb ohvyq vagryyvtrapr: anzryl,
vagryyvtrapr gung vf terngre guna nal uhzna’f ba gur cynarg.2
Gurer ner gjb jnlf bs guvaxvat nobhg bhe cerfrag pvephzfgnaprf. Gur
svefg vf n cebwrpgvba bs gur snzvyvne. Gb qngr, uhznavgl’f zbfg genafsbezngvir
grpuabybtvrf unir raunaprq be nzcyvsvrq uhzna obqvyl shapgvba. Gur jurry
erqhprq gur rkunhfgvba bs vapernfrq zbovyvgl, juvyr ratvarf bs inevbhf
glcrf eryvrirq gur ntbal bs gbea zhfpyr. K-enlf, zntavsvpngvba, naq gur
yvtug ohyo fgergpurq gur yvzvgf bs bofreinoyr ernyvgl orlbaq angheny rlrfvtug
nybar, whfg nf gur gryrcubar nzcyvsvrq bhe ibvpr va jnlf bhe guebngf pbhyq

abg. Nyy qvzrafvbaf bs uhzna shapgvba unir, va fbzr jnl, orra
vabetnavpnyyl nhtzragrq, funecrarq, be fgeratgurarq ol znpuvarf bs bhe
perngvba. Vf NV, gura, whfg nabgure rkgrafvba bs uhzna snphygvrf?
Gur frpbaq jnl bs guvaxvat vf gb fhttrfg gung, guvf gvzr, guvatf ner
qvssrerag—gung gurer ner havdhr nfcrpgf gb NV gung ner abg nhtzragngvbaf bs
uhzna novyvgvrf. Ol ratvarrevat va n znggre bs qrpnqrf n pbhagrecneg gb jung
ribyhgvba cebqhprq bire zvyyraavn—gung vf, gur oenva—jr unir sbhaq
bhefryirf gnpxyvat gur ynfg betna erznvavat sbe vabetnavp ercyvpngvba be
ervairagvba.
FCRRQ
Va gur cerivbhf puncgre, jr cbvagrq gb gur fvzvynevgl orgjrra gur genvavat bs
na NV znpuvar naq gur genvavat bs gur zvaq bs na nqinaprq fghqrag bs
cuvybfbcul. Gung rknzcyr pna or rkgraqrq zber oebnqyl. Chg cynvayl, gur
sbezngvba bs zrpunavpny vagryyvtrapr pna or frra nf cnenyyry gb gur cebprff
ol juvpu gur uhzna oenva zngherf ovbybtvpnyyl sebz nqbyrfprapr vagb
nqhygubbq.
Fghqragf qhevat gur pbhefr bs gurve frpbaqnel rqhpngvba yrnea gur
shaqnzragnyf bs pber fhowrpgf, ohvyqvat hc gurve onfvp ivrj bs gur jbeyq.
Gung ivrj znl abg or cnegvphyneyl nqinaprq—be nyjnlf pbeerpg—ohg gur
fnzr vf nyfb gehr bs n znpuvar. Znpuvarf, yvxr uhznaf, yrnea ol nofbeovat
vasbezngvba naq genafsbezvat vg vagb gurbel sbe fhofrdhrag cenpgvpr. Jura
znpuvarf yrnea, na nytbevguz vatrfgf infg nzbhagf bs qngn—fpencrq sebz
fbheprf ba gur bcra vagrearg be cebivqrq zber fcrpvsvpnyyl ol bgure, cevingr
fbheprf—naq pbyyncfrf gur erfhygf vagb n pbaqrafrq naq pbzcerffrq
znccvat bs pbaprcgf sbe shgher hfr. Whfg nf uhznaf’ ovbybtvpny zrpunavfzf
znc frafbel vachg bagb arheny “jrvtugf” gung pbaarpg gur argjbex bs gur
oenva’f cebprffvat havgf, znpuvarf fvzvyneyl erdhver n tenqhny fgeratguravat
bs gurve bja pbzchgngvbany jrvtugf.
Arheny argjbexf, yvxr (fbzr) uvtu-fpubby fghqragf, pna or ynml. Qhevat
gur rneyl fgntrf bs genvavat, NV jvyy qb gur oner zvavzhz. Zrzbevmvat
nafjref engure guna npghnyyl yrneavat, n zbqry snprq jvgu “2 + 2” zvtug
vavgvnyyl rapbqr gur nafjre “4” jvgubhg univat znfgrerq gur haqreylvat
cevapvcyr bs nqqvgvba. Ohg encvqyl, npebff n pregnva guerfubyq, guvf nccebnpu

jvyy oernx qbja, sbepvat gur znpuvar gb nofgenpg hcjneq—nf uhznaf qb—
gb zber havirefny nkvbzf bs xabjyrqtr.
Guvf vf jung cevapvcnyyl qvfgvathvfurf NV sebz beqvanel pbzchgref: Vgf
znccvat bs gur jbeyq vf abg cebtenzzrq, ohg yrnearq. Va genqvgvbany
fbsgjner cebtenzzvat, n uhzna-perngrq nytbevguz vafgehpgf n znpuvar va
ubj gb genafsbez n frg bs vachgf vagb n frg bs bhgchgf. Va znpuvar yrneavat,
ol pbagenfg, uhzna-perngrq nytbevguzf gryy gur znpuvar bayl ubj gb
vzcebir vgfrys, nyybjvat gur znpuvar gb qrfvta vgf bja znccvatf sbe gur
vachg-gb-bhgchg genafsbezngvba. Nf gur znpuvar “yrneaf” sebz pbhagyrff
cevbe gevnyf, snvyherf, naq nqwhfgzragf, vg hctenqrf vgf nytbevguzf, vgrengviryl
erqrfvtavat vgf vagreany znccvatf bs gur cnggreaf naq pbaarpgvbaf vg “frrf”
va gur qngn.
Crevbqvpnyyl, uhzna genvaref jvyy tvir gur znpuvar srrqonpx ba gur
npphenpl naq dhnyvgl bs vgf bhgchgf. Gur znpuvar vagreanyvmrf gurve
pbeerpgvbaf ol zrnaf bs “onpx-cebcntngvba,” n grpuavdhr gung nyybjf gur
rssrpgf bs gur genvaref’ punatrf gb evccyr onpxjneq guebhtu gur zngurzngvpny
eryngvbafuvcf gung gur znpuvar unf nyernql perngrq, gurerol vzcebivat gur
birenyy zbqry.
Sbe nal tvira zbqry, ubjrire, uhznaf cebivqr srrqonpx ba bayl n
fznyy fhofrg bs cbffvoyr vachgf naq bhgchgf. Nsgre gur zbqry cresbezf ng n
pregnva yriry va n ahzore bs genvavat grfgf, vgf qrirybcref gehfg gung vgf
rfgnoyvfurq znccvatf jvyy trarengr n fnsr naq npphengr erfcbafr gb nyy
vachgf, rira harkcrpgrq barf, jvgu n uvtu cebonovyvgl bs fhpprff.
Va rnpu bs gurfr jnlf, NV vf nyernql rkcnaqvat, naq jvyy shegure rkcnaq,
gur ernyz bs uhzna xabjyrqtr. Ohg vg vf qbvat fb—naq jr ner npprcgvat
gur erfhygnag xabjyrqtr nf gehr—ol cebprffrf gung jr qb abg shyyl
haqrefgnaq.
Jurer n glcvpny fghqrag tenqhngrf sebz uvtu fpubby va sbhe lrnef, na NV
zbqry gbqnl pna rnfvyl svavfu yrneavat gur fnzr nzbhag bs xabjyrqtr, naq
qenzngvpnyyl zber, va sbhe qnlf. Naq guhf, fcrrq unf cebira vgfrys gb or gur
svefg va n unaqshy bs pber nggevohgrf gung qvfgvathvfu NV sebz bhe uhzna sbez
naq zragny pncnovyvgvrf.
Qrfcvgr univat uvtuyl nqinaprq cnenyyryvfz—gung vf, gur novyvgl gb
cebprff fvzhygnarbhfyl qvssrerag xvaqf bs fgvzhyv—gur uhzna oenva vf n
fybj cebprffbe bs vasbezngvba, yvzvgrq ol gur fcrrq ng juvpu bhe ovbybtvpny
pvephvgf jbex. Vs n uhzna oenva’f pvephvgf jrer nanylmrq jvgu gur fnzr

cresbeznapr zrgevpf nf pbzchgref—ol “pybpx engr” be cebprffvat fcrrq—
gur nirentr NV fhcrepbzchgre vf nyernql 120 zvyyvba gvzrf snfgre guna gur
cebprffvat engr bs gur uhzna oenva.
Gehr, fcrrq vf abg n fgebat vaqvpngbe bs vagryyvtrapr; irel qhzo uhznaf
pna guvax dhvpxyl. Arireguryrff, n snfgre cnpr bs cebprffvat cebivqrf gjb
orarsvgf nf pbzcnerq jvgu gur uhzna oenva: gur vatrfgvba bs infgyl zber
vasbezngvba naq gur freivpr bs znal zber fvzhygnarbhf erdhrfgf. Zhpu bs
gur uhzna oenva glcvpnyyl erznvaf ba nhgbcvybg—cnffviryl freivat vagreany
arrqf va thvqvat gur orngvat bs bhe urneg naq gur zbirzrag bs bhe yvzof,
naq vagreiravat gb nqwhfg bayl jura gur nhgbcvybg cebirf snhygl. Ol pbagenfg,
gur fcrrq bs juvpu NV vf pncnoyr nyybjf sbe gur cebtenzzngvp rzretrapr bs
terng cebjrff, juvpu gura ranoyrf gur npuvrirzrag bs uvture, zber
qvssvphyg, naq tenaqre ceboyrzf guna gubfr pheeragyl fbyinoyr ol gur uhzna
oenva.
Bapr obgu gur uhzna naq gur znpuvar unir pbzcyrgrq gurve vagryyrpghny
genvavat, obgu ner abj gurbergvpnyyl pncnoyr bs “guvaxvat” be, va gur
rdhvinyrag grpuavpny grez, “vasrerapr.” Va gur pbhefr bs na vagreivrj, na
nethzrag, be n qngr, n fghqrag-ghearq-tenqhngr qenjf hcba uvf be ure
rqhpngvba naq rkcrevrapr. Jr qb guvf abg ol erthetvgngvat rknpg sbezhynf,
vaqvivqhny snpgf, naq cerpvfr ahzoref sebz zrzbel ohg ol pbafhygvat n
guvaare ynlre bs pbagrzcyngvba bs naq ersyrpgvba ba jung jr unir yrnearq.
Gur uhzna oenva jnf arire zrnag gb zrzbevmr vasbezngvba sbe cresrpg
erpnyy; abe ner zbfg oenvaf pncnoyr bs qbvat fb. Jung fubhyq erznva vafgrnq,
nsgre vaahzrenoyr yrffbaf, rffnlf, naq rknzf, vf n tenfc bs gur qrrcre naq
ybatre-ynfgvat pbaprcgf gung gubfr fnzr rqhpngvbany gbbyf bs vafgehpgvba ner
zrnag gb erirny: gur jbaqre bs nfgebabzl, gur gentrql bs nzovgvba, gur
arprffvgl (be abg) bs eribyhgvba.
Gur fnzr vf gehr bs NV. Jura n zbqry rzretrf sebz gur pbzcyrgvba bs
vgf genvavat eha, vg ab ybatre erdhverf npprff gb gur bevtvany qngn vg jnf
genvarq ba. Engure, vg vf yrsg bayl jvgu n ebhtu thvqvat vaghvgvba, nffrzoyrq
sebz gur xabjyrqtr vg unf erprvirq, sbe nafjrevat dhrfgvbaf, punyyratvat
ernfbavat, naq znxvat cerqvpgvbaf. Whfg nf uhznaf qba’g unhy yvoenevrf bs
zngrevny nebhaq jvgu gurz, na NV zbqry fvzvyneyl vasref engure guna erpnyyf.
Gur qvssrerapr, gura, vf gung fhcrevbe fcrrq snpvyvgngrf guvf vasrerapr npebff n
oebnqre, qrrcre neenl bs yrnearq vasbezngvba guna n uhzna pbhyq rire ubcr
gb nggnva.

Gb qb guvf, rira gb nafjre n fvzcyr dhrfgvba, na NV zbqry znl cresbez
ovyyvbaf bs pbzcyrk grpuavpny bcrengvbaf. Jurernf n genqvgvbany pbzchgre
fvzcyl ergevrirf fcrpvsvp vasbezngvba fgberq va vgf zrzbel—fvapr vg vf
hanoyr gb neevir ng gur fbegf bs pbapyhfvbaf gung qba’g nyernql rkvfg gurer—
NV ynhapurf pbzchgvat va gur qverpgvba bs gur uhzna oenva. Whfg nf uhznaf
yrnea va beqre gb guvax, znpuvarf genva va beqre gb vasre. Gur frpbaq pnaabg
pbzr jvgubhg gur svefg.
Gur svefg cunfr—sbe obgu uhznaf naq znpuvarf—vf gur zber vagrafvir
cebprff, va obgu gur nzbhag bs gvzr fcrag naq gur ahzore bs erfbheprf
erdhverq. N cbfgqbpgbeny fghqrag znl unir fcrag gjb qrpnqrf be zber
ohvyqvat gur pncnovyvgl gb pbzcbfr—va gjb qnlf—n gubhtugshy rffnl ba n
tvira fhowrpg. Fvzvyneyl, genvavat gur ynetrfg NV zbqryf znl gnxr zbaguf,
ohg gur erfhygnag vasrerapvat pna pbafhzr zrer senpgvbaf bs n frpbaq.
Gbqnl’f NV flfgrzf nyernql tvir nccneragyl pbtrag naq pbafvqrerq
nafjref va erfcbafr gb uhzna dhrevrf. Va gurve yngrfg naq shgher vgrengvbaf,
gurl jvyy bcrengr pbzcerurafviryl, pebffvat zhygvcyr qbznvaf bs xabjyrqtr
jvgu na ntvyvgl gung rkprrqf gur pncnpvgl bs nal uhzna be nal tebhc bs
uhznaf. Sbe NVf, fpnyr—va gur frafr bs fvmr—ranoyrf fcrrq; nf jr unir
whfg frra, gur ynetre naq zber gubebhtuyl genvarq gur znpuvar, gur snfgre naq
zber rkunhfgvir vgf erfhygf. Jung vf zber, ol erpbtavmvat cnggreaf va gur
qngn gung ryhqr gur vadhvevat uhzna bcrengbe, NV flfgrzf jvyy or rdhvccrq
gb qvfgvyy genqvgvbany rkcerffvbaf bs xabjyrqtr vagb bevtvany erfcbafrf naq,
bhg bs rabezbhf nzbhagf bs qngn, sbetr arj pbaprcghny gehguf.
Juvpu envfrf n dhrfgvba, be engure zber guna bar dhrfgvba.
BCNPVGL
Ubj qb jr xabj jung jr xabj nobhg gur jbexvatf bs bhe havirefr? Naq
ubj qb jr xabj gung jung jr xabj vf gehr?
Va zbfg nernf bs xabjyrqtr, rire fvapr gur nqirag bs gur fpvragvsvp
zrgubq, jvgu vgf vafvfgrapr ba rkcrevzrag nf gur pevgrevba bs cebbs, nal
vasbezngvba gung vf abg fhccbegrq ol rivqrapr unf orra ertneqrq nf
vapbzcyrgr naq hagehfgjbegul. Bayl genafcnerapl, ercebqhpvovyvgl, naq
ybtvpny inyvqngvba pbasre yrtvgvznpl ba n pynvz bs gehgu. Haqre gur vasyhrapr
bs guvf senzrjbex, erprag praghevrf unir lvryqrq n uhtr rkcnafvba va uhzna

xabjyrqtr, uhzna haqrefgnaqvat, naq uhzna cebqhpgvivgl—phyzvangvat
jvgu gur vairagvba bs gur pbzchgre naq znpuvar yrneavat.
Gbqnl, ubjrire, va gur ntr bs NV, jr snpr n arj naq crphyvneyl qnhagvat
punyyratr: vasbezngvba jvgubhg rkcynangvba. Nyernql, NV’f erfcbafrf—
juvpu, nf abgrq nobir, pna gnxr gur sbez bs uvtuyl negvphyngr naq pburerag
qrfpevcgvbaf bs pbzcyrk pbaprcgf—neevir vafgnagnarbhfyl. Gur znpuvarf’
bhgchgf ner qryvirerq oner naq hadhnyvsvrq, jvgu ab nccnerag ovnf be zbgvir
—ohg nyfb hanppbzcnavrq ol nal pvgngvba bs fbheprf be bgure whfgvsvpngvbaf.
Naq lrg, qrfcvgr guvf ynpx bs n engvbanyr sbe nal tvira nafjre, rneyl NV
flfgrzf unir nyernql ratraqrerq vaperqvoyr yriryf bs uhzna pbasvqrapr va,
naq eryvnapr hcba, gurve bgurejvfr harkcynvarq naq frrzvatyl benphyne
cebabhaprzragf. Nf gurl nqinapr, gurfr arj “oenvaf” pbhyq nccrne gb or
abg bayl nhgubevgngvir ohg vasnyyvoyr.
Nygubhtu uhzna srrqonpx urycf na NV znpuvar ersvar vgf vagreany
nytbevguzf, gur znpuvar ubyqf cevznel erfcbafvovyvgl sbe qrgrpgvat cnggreaf
va, naq nffvtavat jrvtugf gb, gur qngn ba juvpu vg vf genvarq. Abe, bapr n
zbqry vf genvarq, qbrf vg choyvfu gur vagreany zngurzngvpny fpurzn gung vg
unf pbapbpgrq. Nf n erfhyg, gur ercerfragngvbaf bs ernyvgl gung gur znpuvar
trarengrf erznva ynetryl bcndhr, rira gb vgf vairagbef. Gbqnl, uhznaf
nggrzcg gb nffher gurzfryirf bs gur vagrtevgl bs gurfr znpuvar zbqryf
znvayl ol rknzvavat bhgchgf nybar. Gur vagreany jbexvatf erznva ynetryl
vzcrargenoyr—urapr gur ersrerapr gb fbzr NV flfgrzf nf “oynpx obkrf.”
Nygubhtu fbzr erfrnepuref ner nggrzcgvat gb erirefr-ratvarre gur bhgchgf
bs gurfr pbzcyrk zbqryf vagb snzvyvne nytbevguzf, vg vf abg lrg pyrne jurgure
gurl jvyy fhpprrq.
Va oevrs, zbqryf genvarq ivn znpuvar yrneavat nyybj uhznaf gb xabj arj
guvatf (gur zbqryf’ bhgchgf) ohg abg gb haqrefgnaq ubj gur qvfpbirevrf jrer
znqr (gur zbqryf’ vagreany cebprffrf). Guvf frcnengrf uhzna xabjyrqtr
sebz uhzna haqrefgnaqvat va n jnl gung jbhyq unir orra sbervta gb nal
bgure ntr bs uhznavgl. Uhzna nccreprcgvba va gur zbqrea frafr unf
qrirybcrq sebz gur vaghvgvbaf naq bhgpbzrf gung sbyybj sebz pbafpvbhf
fhowrpgvir rkcrevrapr, vaqvivqhny rknzvangvba bs ybtvp, naq gur novyvgl gb
ercebqhpr gur erfhygf. Gurfr zrgubqf bs xabjyrqtr qrevir va ghea sebz n
dhvagrffragvnyyl uhznavfg vzchyfr: “Vs V pna’g qb vg, gura V pna’g haqrefgnaq
vg; vs V pna’g haqrefgnaq vg, gura V pna’g xabj vg gb or gehr.”
Va gur senzrjbex gung rzretrq va gur Ntr bs Rayvtugrazrag, gurfr pber

ryrzragf—vaqvivqhny uhzna pncnpvgl, fhowrpgvir pbzcerurafvba, naq
bowrpgvir gehgu—nyy zbirq va gnaqrz. Ol pbagenfg, gur gehguf cebqhprq ol
NV ner znahsnpgherq ol cebprffrf gung uhznaf pnaabg ercyvpngr. Znpuvar
ernfbavat, juvpu qbrf abg cebprrq ivn uhzna zrgubqf, vf orlbaq uhzna
fhowrpgvir rkcrevrapr naq bhgfvqr gur pncnpvgl bs uhznaf, jub pnaabg rira
shyyl ercerfrag gur znpuvarf’ vagreany cebprffrf.
Gurfr snpgf, ol Rayvtugrazrag ernfbavat, jbhyq cerpyhqr gur npprcgnapr
bs znpuvar bhgchgf nf gehr. Naq lrg jr—ng yrnfg, gur zvyyvbaf bs uhznaf
jub unir ortha gb vagresnpr jvgu rneyl NV flfgrzf—unir nyernql npprcgrq
gur irenpvgl bs gur infg znwbevgl bs gurve bhgchgf.3 Tenagrq, fbzr nqinaprq
hfref znl vaqrrq npghnyyl pbzceruraq gur zrgn-cebprff bs znpuvar
yrneavat; sbe zbfg, ubjrire, uhzna pbasvqrapr va gur bowrpgvir gehgu bs gur
znpuvarf’ bhgchgf zhfg erfg va n glcr bs snvgu gung rkcerffrf vgfrys nf n
jvfushy oryvrs va gur znpuvarf’ ybtvp naq gurve qrirybcref’ nhgubevgl.
Va vgfrys, gur rzretrapr bs fhpu oryvrs nf na npprcgrq zrgubq va gur
chefhvg bs bowrpgvir gehgu znexf n znwbe genafsbezngvba va zbqrea uhzna
gubhtug. Sbe rira vs NV zbqryf qb abg “haqrefgnaq” gur jbeyq va gur uhzna
frafr—orpnhfr znpuvarf rzcungvpnyyl qb abg rkcrevrapr pbafpvbhfarff be
fhowrpgvivgl—gurve bowrpgvir pncnpvgl gb ernpu arj naq npphengr
pbapyhfvbaf nobhg bhe jbeyq ol abauhzna zrgubqf abg bayl qvfehcgf bhe
eryvnapr ba gur fpvragvsvp zrgubq nf vg unf orra chefhrq pbagvahbhfyl sbe
svir praghevrf ohg nyfb punyyratrf gur uhzna pynvz gb na rkpyhfvir be havdhr
tenfc bs ernyvgl.
Jung pna guvf zrna? Jvyy gur ntr bs NV abg bayl snvy gb cebcry uhznavgl
sbejneq ohg vafgrnq pngnylmr n erghea gb n cerzbqrea npprcgnapr bs
harkcynvarq nhgubevgl? Va fubeg, ner jr, zvtug jr or, ba gur cerpvcvpr bs n
terng erirefny va uhzna pbtavgvba—n qnex rayvtugrazrag?
QVIREFVGL
Qvssrerag ragvgvrf zrnfher gvzr nybat qvssrerag fpnyrf. Ba n trbybtvpny
gvzrfpnyr, gur ragvergl bs uhzna rkvfgrapr jbhyq nccrne nf n gval qnfu ng
gur gnvy raq bs Rnegu’f 4.5-ovyyvba-lrne fcna. Vs jr uhznaf jrer cebterffvat
ng trbybtvpny fcrrq, jr jbhyq creprvir bayl fgnfvf. Vafgrnq, nf na vzcngvrag
naq frys-vzcbegnag fcrpvrf, jr unir qrsvarq bhe bja cnpr bs ribyhgvba.

Jurernf na “ntr” va trbybtvpny gvzr vf zrnfherq va gur gubhfnaqf bs lrnef,
uhzna gvzr zrnfherf na “ntr” nf n praghel be gjb.
Nf sbe na negvsvpvny be grpuabybtvpny gvzrfpnyr, NV jbhyq yvxryl bcrengr ng
vgf bja qvfgvapgvir zrnfher. Gur jubyr uvfgbel bs negvsvpvny vagryyvtrapr
fcnaf ab zber guna 70 lrnef. Whfg nf uhznaf trarenyyl pbafvqre gur znal
uhaqerqf bs zvyyvbaf bs lrnef orsber gur Pnzoevna rkcybfvba gb unir orra
na vzcbffvoyl ybat oynax fyngr orsber n fhqqra bhgohefg bs navzny yvsr naq
ribyhgvbanel cebterff, NV jbhyq cebonoyl punenpgrevmr gur fvk qrpnqrf bs
1950 gb 2010 nf n fvzvyneyl fybj, zhexl crevbq bs abguvatarff, vyyhzvangrq
ol tyvzzref bs yvsr bayl ng gur irel raq.
Uhzna trarengvbaf, gb whqtr ol fbpvrgl naq ovbybtl, ynfg fbzr 25 lrnef.
NV, ol pbagenfg, zbirf jvgu vauhzna fcrrq; vgf trarengvbaf ner zhpu
fubegre, jvgu yrncf unccravat va creuncf n gragu bs gung gvzr. Jr fubhyq
gurersber nagvpvcngr gung jung znl srry va uhzna gvzr yvxr n eribyhgvba jvyy
nccrne va grpuabybtvpny gvzr nf n zrer ribyhgvba. Arjre NV zbqryf—jvgu
bayl zbaguf va orgjrra—pna erfcbaq gb rire zber bcra-raqrq cebzcgf,
znxr zber pubvprf va beqre gb ernpu n tvira tbny, naq npg npebff vapernfvat
ahzoref bs zbqnyvgvrf.
Guhf, gur ntr bs NV—va uhzna gvzr, creuncf n uhaqerq lrnef—zvtug
zber npphengryl or ynoryrq gur ntrf bs NVf, naq, nppbeqvat gb gur
grpuabybtvpny gvzrfpnyr bs NV vgfrys, zvtug or fnvq gb rapbzcnff znal
uhaqerqf bs trarengvbaf.
Gur encvqvgl bs NV’f ribyhgvba vf n zhygvsnprgrq—naq ynetryl
hanccerpvngrq—punyyratr. Uhznavgl unf arire orsber unq gb qrny jvgu, be
gb cercner sbe, fhpu n grzcbeny pbzcerffvba. Gur furre fcrrq bs gur punatr
cenpgvpnyyl rafherf phygheny naq cflpubybtvpny qvfbevragngvba. Nf gur rssrpgf
bs gur arj grpuabybtvrf ba qnvyl yvsr ynlre naq pbzcbhaq, gurl jvyy
pbzcyvpngr rssbegf gb cvacbvag nal bar nccyvpngvba nf rvgure n fbhepr bs pevfvf
be, gb gur pbagenel, n pbzsbegvat uneovatre bs cebterff.
Hagnatyvat gurfr bireynccvat vffhrf va gur erny jbeyq jvyy orpbzr rire
zber qvssvphyg nf n zhygvcyvpvgl bs NVf oevatf jvgu vg n zhygvcyvpvgl bs
vafpehgnoyr rssrpgf. Zberbire, nf NV tebjf zber cbjreshy, gur shgher jvyy
yvxryl oevat n fvtavsvpnag ribyhgvba naq qvirefvsvpngvba. Arj vasenfgehpgherf
naq grpuavdhrf sbe znpuvar yrneavat, fb ybat nf gurl ner hapbafgenvarq, jvyy
fcnja trarengvbaf bs NV jvgu vapernfvat qvirefvgl, oernqgu, pncnpvgl, naq
pbzcyrkvgl. Whfg nf ryrpgevpvgl cbjref zber guna yvtug ohyof, NV jvyy or chg

gb nal ahzore bs hfrf. Naq whfg nf gurer ner znal jnlf gb trarengr na
ryrpgevpny punetr—sevpgvba, pbaqhpgvba, vaqhpgvba—jr znl nagvpvcngr gur
qvfpbirel bs zhygvcyr jnlf gb perngr NV.
Sbe vafgnapr, gur vasenfgehpgher gung unf znqr erprag NV nqinaprzragf
cbffvoyr vf xabja nf n “genafsbezre.” Vg nyybjf gur znpuvar gb pbafvqre, sbe
vafgnapr, gur pbaarpgvbaf nzbat zhygvcyr jbeqf ng bapr. Va ynl-fcrnx:
jurer cerivbhf fgehpgherf ernq jbeqf bar ng n gvzr, pncghevat bayl gur
pbaarpgvba orgjrra jbeq 1 naq jbeq 2, gura frcnengryl gur pbaarpgvba
orgjrra jbeq 2 naq jbeq 3, n genafsbezre nyybjf gur zbqry gb pncgher, nyy
ng bapr, obgu n jubyr fragrapr naq rirel pbaarpgvba orgjrra rirel jbeq va
gur fragrapr. Perngvat naq hgvyvmvat zngurzngvpny ercerfragngvbaf bs nyy
gurfr pbaarpgvbaf, gur NV cerqvpgf gur orfg erfcbafr.
Gur pncnovyvgvrf bs genafsbezref jrer abg nagvpvcngrq, naq gurve uvtuyl
trarenyvmnoyr fhpprffrf bppheerq nyzbfg vapvqragnyyl.4 Naq genafsbezref ner
abg arprffnevyl gur bayl sbhaqngvbany vasenfgehpgher gung pna lvryq
harkcrpgrq pncnovyvgvrf. Nf zber sehvgshy nirahrf bs erfrnepu rzretr, NV
bhgchgf jvyy vzcebir dhvpxyl, zhygvcylvat nybat qvssrerag yvarf bs culfvpny
naq zngurzngvpny ybtvp, ng ybjre rkcrafr naq snfgre fcrrq.
Va vgf ribyhgvbanel fcrrq naq qvirefvsvpngvba, NV’f qrirybczrag jvyy guhf
vaqrrq or nxva gb gur Pnzoevna rkcybfvba: gur rzretrapr bs n jvqr inevrgl
bs qvssrerag sbezf bs yvsr jvguva n fvatyr, uvtuyl pbzcerffrq crevbq bs gvzr
eryngvir gb gur cerprqvat rcbpu. Vs guvf pbawrpgher vf pbeerpg, znpuvar
vagryyvtraprf jvyy oenapu bhgjneq vagb n encvqyl ribyivat trahf, be rira n
snzvyl, bs znal qvssrerag NVf bcrengvat ba znal qvssrerag sbezf bs ybtvp.
NVf znl guhf bssre gur zbfg fgevxvat vafgnapr bs gur qvirefvgl gung pna pbzr
sebz zvabe punatrf vgrengrq ercrngrqyl npebff gur obneq: n qvtvgny rpub bs
gur betnavp jbeyq. Nf Qnejva jevgrf, “sebz fb fvzcyr n ortvaavat, raqyrff
sbezf zbfg ornhgvshy.”5
FPNYR NAQ ERFBYHGVBA
Gur Ntr bs Ernfba znl unir oebhtug uhznavgl gb gur rqtr bs ubj uhznaf
haqrefgnaq bhe jbeyq. Rvafgrvavna culfvpf naq gur sbezhyngvbaf bs dhnaghz
zrpunavpf jrer gur ortvaavatf bs n fgvyy vapbzcyrgr iragher vagb hapunegrq
greevgbel: jbeyqf cbgragvnyyl jvgu gurve bja ehyrf bs xabjyrqtr,

nccerurafvoyr abg ol nccyvrq creprcgvba ohg bayl ol gurbergvpny vqrngvba.
Dhnaghz zrpunavpf qrfpevorf gur jbeyq ng gur zvpeb-fpnyr, jurer, nf gur
Uneineq culfvpvfg Tert Xrfgva chgf vg, “Abguvat vf cerqvpgnoyr naq bowrpgf
qba’g unir cerpvfr cbfvgvbaf hagvy gurl ner bofreirq,” naq trareny eryngvivgl
qrfpevorf gur jbeyq ng n pbfzvp fpnyr, jurer rirelguvat vf cerqvpgnoyr,
“jurgure be abg” bofreirq.6 Arvgure gurbel unf snvyrq, ohg obgu pnaabg or
gehr, naq “Ab rkcrevzrag unf orra noyr gb fubj juvpu—vs rvgure—bs gur
gjb gurbevrf” ervtaf fhcerzr.
Vebavpnyyl, guvf hapregnvagl haqreyvrf gur zbqrea jbeyq. Dhnaghz
culfvpf ranoyrq—nzbat bgure eribyhgvbaf—gur pbzchgvat eribyhgvba. NV
vf naq jvyy or irel zhpu gur fnzr. Nyernql, vg cebqhprf vafvtugf naq
genafsbezf ernyvgl ol zrpunavfzf gung jr qba’g shyyl haqrefgnaq. Naq fbba
rabhtu vg jvyy or bpphcvrq jvgu n fpvrapr gung vf rira yrff pbzcerurafvoyr
gb uhzna haqrefgnaqvat.
Nsgre guerr uhaqerq lrnef, gur Ntr bs Ernfba, qrfcvgr vgf znavsbyq
fhpprffrf, unf fgnyyrq—nf vf rivqraprq ol bhe znavsrfg vanovyvgl gb znxr
shegure cebterff ba gur havsvpngvba bs culfvpf. Bhe cerfrag fgenva naq
fgehttyr va gurfr qnlf bs hanffvfgrq uhzna fpvrapr, zber guna n praghel
nsgre gur pbaprcgvba bs gur pber gurbevrf haqreylvat obgu gur pbfzvp naq
dhnaghz jbeyqf, vf ohg bar fvta gung uhznaf znl or arnevat fbzr
ovbybtvpny yvzvg bs vagryyvtrapr.
Orpnhfr bs vgf havdhr zrgubqf bs vadhvel naq yrneavat, NV jvyy or
pncnoyr bs vauhzna npuvrirzragf va grezf obgu bs fvmr (“fpnyr”) naq bs
cerpvfvba (“erfbyhgvba”), gurerol npgvingvat shaqnzragny punatrf qvssrerag
sebz nal bgure uhzna vairagvba be sebz gur uhzna fcrpvrf vgfrys.
Arireguryrff, pbhyq NV npuvrir n erpbapvyvngvba orgjrra gur gjb raqf bs
uhzna ernyvgl, vaqhpvat n eribyhgvba va creprcgvba ol zrgubqf gung hagvy
abj unir orra pbzcyrgryl sbervta gb uhzna rkcrevrapr?
Gur culfvpny fpnyr bs bhe uhzna oenva vf qvpgngrq ol bhe nangbzl.
Uhzna oenvaf zhfg svg vafvqr uhzna fxhyyf, naq vasnag uhzna fxhyyf zhfg,
trarenyyl, svg guebhtu gur srznyr ovegu pnany. Nal fznyyre, naq fhpu uhznaf
znl or ng n pbtavgvir qvfnqinagntr; nal ynetre, naq gubfr onovrf—be gurve
zbguref—znl abg fheivir puvyqovegu. Bgure culfvbybtvpny yvzvgngvbaf, gbb,
rasbepr n prvyvat bs pbafgenvag—cenpgvpny yvzvgngvbaf ba gur jrvtug bs gur
oenva, sbe rknzcyr. Oneevat Prfnerna frpgvbaf be, yngre, negvsvpvny jbzof,

guvf zrnaf gung uhznaf unir ernpurq na ribyhgvbanel rdhvyvoevhz.
Sbe NV, gbqnl’f zbqryf unir pncnovyvgvrf gung jrer abg nagvpvcngrq ng
gurve perngvba. Gur “fpnyvat ynjf” (yvxr, va na byq-snfuvbarq rknzcyr, gur
ynjf tbireavat gur eryngvbafuvc orgjrra gur yratgu bs na bowrpg naq vgf nern)
gung unir nccyvrq fb sne gb NV frrz gb or ubyqvat gehr, ohg jr qb abg xabj
jung cerpvfryl jvyy or ranoyrq ol zbqryf jvgu na rkcbaragvnyyl vapernfvat
ahzore bs cnenzrgref orpnhfr jr unir abg hapbirerq n fpvragvsvp ernfba
jul pregnva pncnovyvgvrf rzretr ng n cnegvphyne qrterr bs cbjre naq
pbzcyrkvgl.
Oenva fvmr eryngvir gb obql fvmr qbrf abg pbeeryngr pyrneyl jvgu
vagryyvtrapr va gur navzny xvatqbz—qbycuvaf, ryrcunagf, naq fbzr junyrf
nyy unir oenvaf cebcbegvbangryl ynetre guna gur uhzna oenva. Ohg rneyl
fpvrapr qbrf fhttrfg gung fpnyr cynlf fbzr ebyr, juvpu jr qb abg lrg
haqrefgnaq.
Tvira bhe uneq ovbybtvpny pbafgenvagf, uhznaf ner hayvxryl gb grfg gurve
bja oenvaf’ “fpnyvat ynjf.” Ohg NV ragref gur jbeyq jvgu ab cersvkrq
culfvpny fvmr. Vg vf abg obhaq gb nal culfvpny pneevre bs qvfpreavoyr fpnyr.
Puvcf naq qngn pragref—gur culfvpny ubfgf bs NV zbqryf—pna or pyhfgrerq
naq pbaarpgrq jvgubhg nf lrg bofreinoyr yvzvg. Va bgure jbeqf, gur fpnyvat
ynjf jvyy fheryl or grfgrq sbe NVf nf gurl arire unir orra sbe uhznaf. Naq
nf gurl ner grfgrq, fpnyr—juvpu unf pbafgenvarq gur enatr bs uhzna
haqrefgnaqvat guebhtubhg gur uvfgbel bs fpvragvsvp gubhtug—znl ghea bhg gb
or gur cevznel qvssreragvngbe orgjrra uhzna oenvaf naq NV zbqryf.
Bar bs gur xrl fvqr rssrpgf bs fpnyr jvyy or erfbyhgvba. Uhznaf unir
ybat qrfverq gb rkgraq gur enatr bs jung jr pna bofreir gb obgu gur irel
gval naq gur irel sne. Gur zvpebfpbcr naq gur gryrfpbcr ner dhvagrffragvny
gbbyf bs uhzna bofreingvba. Yrff nccerpvngrq vf gur uhzoyr cra. Jevgvat,
vairagrq sbhe gubhfnaq lrnef ntb, erznvaf na bhgfgnaqvat gbby sbe gur
pbqvsvpngvba naq genafzvffvba bs pbzcyrkvgl. Gung vapyhqrf zngurzngvpf,
creuncf gur cherfg naq zbfg havirefny bs uhzna ynathntrf, naq rabhtu va
vgfrys gb snpvyvgngr gur genafsre bs nofgehfr vqrnf naq pbyynobengvba ba
grpuabybtvpny cebwrpgf. Ba n cre-olgr onfvf, ynathntr va nyy vgf zhygvsnevbhf
naq ornhgvshy sbezf vf hahfhnyyl qrafr—nzbat gur zbfg rssvpvrag qngn
fgehpgherf gung unir orra vairagrq.
Rira nsgre jr raynetr be pbzcerff ernyvgl gb cebqhpr bofreinoyr
vasbezngvba, uhznaf zhfg cresbez n frpbaq fgrc: Jr zhfg nofgenpg njnl

sebz enj vasbezngvba va beqre gb znxr gung vasbezngvba hfrshy. NVf gbqnl qb
gur fnzr. Naq gurl qb fb hfvat gbbyf gung zveebe bhe bja: ovanel fgevatf bs
mrebrf naq barf, gur genafyngvba bs qbphzragrq uhzna rkcrevrapr vagb gur
ynathntr bs pbzchgref. Yvxr jevgvat, gurfr fgevatf bs ynathntr nccrne
ehqvzragnel va ergebfcrpg. Lrg gurl unir ranoyrq qvtvgny ercerfragngvbaf bs
obgu fvtug naq fbhaq: gur uhzna frafrf bs uvturfg onaqjvqgu.
Qrfcvgr gurfr fvzvynevgvrf, NVf jvyy qviretr sebz uhznaf. Nf gur fpnyr bs
na NV vapernfrf, vg jvyy or noyr gb cebprff ynetre ibyhzrf bs vasbezngvba
fvzhygnarbhfyl naq cebqhpr nanylfvf gung vf hfrshy (ng yrnfg gb vgfrys) jvgubhg
haarprffnevyl fnpevsvpvat tenahynevgl. Gur fpnyr bs gur qngn ba juvpu na NV
vf genvarq, pbzovarq jvgu gur pbzcyrkvgl bs vgf argjbex naq gur qrafvgl bs
gur flzobyf ba juvpu vg bcrengrf, nccrnef gb lvryq hacerprqragrq erfbyhgvba
va vgf cebprffrf bs yrneavat naq vasrerapr, naq hygvzngryl va vgf bhgchgf. Vg vf
na ryrtnag vairefvba gung rneyl NV, genvarq ba gur grkg bs gur vagrearg—gur
havirefny yvoenel bs uhznavgl naq gur qrpragenyvmrq jro bs bhe pbzcerffrq
rkcrevraprf—vf yvxryl gb haybpx ragveryl arj xabjyrqtr sbe uhznavgl
nobhg bhefryirf, va frafrf obgu pbfzvp naq zvpebfpbcvp.
GUR NAVZNY XVATQBZ
Ng bhe pheerag zbzrag, fbzr jvyy haqbhogrqyl qrpel nal pybfr pbzcnevfba
bs NV jvgu gur uhzna oenva. Gb n uhzna, pbaprcgf ner evpu jvgu zrnavat
naq irffryf sbe qrrc rkcerffvbaf bs wbl be fbeebj. Va pbagenfg, znpuvar
haqrefgnaqvat pna frrz snxr. Nygubhtu vg znl fbba or noyr gb cebqhpr
rybdhrag jbexf ba pbzzba gurzrf bs uhznavgl gung rpyvcfr rira gur orfg
uhzna nhgubef, na NV qbrf abg frnepu sbe be tenfc nggraqnag zrnavat. Guhf,
rkcybevat gur uhzna pbaqvgvba ol erirefr-ratvarrevat gur ynathntr bs
uhzna jevgref frrzf, ng orfg, n pbyqyl fhcresvpvny znfgrel bs yvathvfgvp
cebonovyvgvrf. Gung fbzr enaqbz pbzcyrk ratvar pna gnxr ynathntr—n tvsg
fb betnavpnyyl uhzna—naq hfr vg nf n ulcrerssvpvrag zrnaf gb vatrfg
vasbezngvba pna or nf hcfrggvat nf vg vf pbashfvat.
Ohg bhe bja ovbybtvpny pvephvgel znl or whfg nf zrpunavpny nf fvyvpba
pvephvgel, naq gur cebprffrf ol juvpu bhe uhzna oenvaf jbex qb abg nccrne
gb or nal zber fcrpvny guna gur jnl znpuvarf nyernql bcrengr. Jr ner sne
sebz cbffrffvat n pbzcyrgr gurbel bs arhebfpvrapr, ohg jr qb xabj gung

bhe oenvaf, yvxr NV zbqryf, ner ynetryl cbjrerq ol cerqvpgvir cebprffvat.
Gung vf, jura yvfgravat be ernqvat, bhe uhzna oenvaf pbagnva n arhebybtvpny
cerqvpgbe gung yraqf nffvfgnapr ol nagvpvcngvat gur arkg jbeq va n ireony
fgevat. Jvgubhg fhpu zrpunavfzf, jr jbhyq or culfvpnyyl naq cflpuvpnyyl
rkunhfgrq ol gur furre nzbhag bs rssbeg erdhverq sbe rira gur fvzcyrfg bs
pbtavgvir gnfxf.
Naq gurfr cerqvpgvir cbjref, yvxr NV’f, unir cebivqrq gur sbhaqngvba sbe
uhzna znfgrel bs bhe jbeyq. Nyy gur zbfg nqinaprq ercerfragngvbaf bs
uhzna xabjyrqtr unir orra ohvyg ngbc ynathntr naq flzobybtl, nyybjvat
hf ng bapr gb ercebqhpr jbexf bs pbzcyrk ratvarrevat naq gb pbzzhavpngr
gur nathvfu bs urnegoernx.
NV unf orra yvxrarq gb gur yvsrybat cevfbaref va Cyngb’f pnir jub,
jvgubhg univat xabja nalguvat ryfr, oryvrir gung gur funqbjf pnfg ba gurve
jnyyf ner gur shyy rkgrag bs ernyvgl.7 Whfg fb, uhznaf nffhzr gung znpuvarf
ner qribvq bs pbagrkg naq gung n znpuvar’f creprcgvba vf yvzvgrq ol gur
obhaqf bs gur zngrevny ba juvpu vg genvaf, jvgubhg nal pncnovyvgl gb cebor be
vasre shegure.
Uhoevf, creuncf, vf jung ceriragf hf sebz frrvat gur fvzvynevgvrf
orgjrra betnavp naq vabetnavp oenvaf, naq sebz nqzvggvat gur cbffvovyvgl bs
gur ynggre’f pncnpvgvrf. Nyernql, NV flfgrzf ner fubjvat rivqrapr bs
creprvivat n havirefr gung rkvfgf orlbaq gur pbasvarf bs gur qngnfrg hfrq gb
pbafgehpg gurve phfgbz fyvpr bs ernyvgl. NVf znl or pncnoyr bs erprvivat
qrrcre zrnavat, nsgre nyy—rira vs gurl ner abg frrxvat vg. Nyy vg jbhyq gnxr
vf sbe bar ragrecevfvat cevfbare gb gurbevmr, ol punapr, gung gur funqbjf ba
gur jnyy znl or ercerfragngvbaf bs n ynetre jbeyq jvgu uvture
qvzrafvbanyvgl.
Vs fhpu n oernxguebhtu jrer gb unccra, vg fubhyq abg or nygbtrgure
fhecevfvat, pbafvqrevat gur fcrrq, pbzcyrkvgl, qvirefvgl, fpnyr, naq
erfbyhgvba bs gurfr arj vagryyvtraprf. Arireguryrff, vg znl or vagrafryl
qvfehcgvir. Gur nccrnenapr bs xabjyrqtr—rfcrpvnyyl bs gur culfvpny jbeyq
—gung vf havdhr gb na NV naq abg cerivbhfyl cbffrffrq ol n uhzna jbhyq
sbepr n erpbafvqrengvba bs gur eryngvir fgnghf bs gur uhzna zvaq. Uhznaf
cynpvat bhe bja oenvaf ba arj, zber pbagvahbhf fcrpgehzf bs vagryyvtrapr
jbhyq eribyhgvbavmr bhe creprcgvbaf, frys-creprcgvbaf, naq orunivbef.
Guvf vf abg gb fnl gung NVf jvyy rkpyhfviryl naq vzzrqvngryl rkprrq nyy

uhzna orvatf va vagryyvtrapr. Ohg gurer jvyy or cunfrf va gur ribyhgvba bs NV
jura zrpunavpny vagryyvtrapr znl srry rrevyl fvzvyne gb gur vagryyvtrapr bs
gur navznyf. N qvfbevragvat qrongr jvyy fheryl rafhr nf jr nggrzcg gb
erbetnavmr n ybat-creprvirq uvrenepul bs orvatf, zrnfhevat qbjajneq sebz
uhznaf, gb navznyf, gb znpuvarf. Uhzna vagryyvtrapr jvyy or hetragyl
cerffrq gb pbasebag gur ernyvgl gung vg vf ab ybatre gur fbyr, be rira gur
fhcrevbe, zbqry bs vagryyvtrapr.
NV zbqryf ner nyernql orvat hfrq gb nffvfg uhznaf va qrpvcurevat—naq
erfcbaqvat gb—gur pbzzhavpngvbaf bs navznyf. Rneyl rkcrevzragf va
qrpbqvat uvtu-cvgpurq pyvpxf naq gehzcrgvat pnyyf ner pngnylmvat erivfvbaf
gb bhe ybat-fgnaqvat ovnf gung uhznaf ner fcrpvny be qvfgvapg sebz bgure
navzny fcrpvrf. Gur novyvgl bs uhznaf naq navznyf gb pbzzhar jvgu rnpu
bgure qverpgyl—ab ybatre, va bhe pnfr, guebhtu obql ynathntr be snpvny
rkcerffvbaf nybar—znl fgvzhyngr gur errqhpngvba arrqrq gb cercner hf sbe
jung vf gb pbzr jvgu NV.
Gb or fher, navzny-uhzna-znpuvar pbzzhavpngvba jbhyq lvryq n
pbzcyvpngrq gevyngreny artbgvngvba. Bhe jbeyq jbhyq or cbchyngrq ol orvatf
—arj naq byq—svtugvat gb frpher n arj cbfvgvba be gb ergnva na rkvfgvat
bar. Znpuvarf znl pbagraq gung gur gehrfg zrgubq bs pynffvsvpngvba vf gb
tebhc gbqnl’f uhznaf gbtrgure jvgu bgure navznyf, fvapr obgu ner pneoba
flfgrzf rzretrag bs ribyhgvba naq qvssrerag sebz fvyvpba flfgrzf rzretrag
bs ratvarrevat. Vg zvtug or qvssvphyg sbe znpuvarf gb or pbasvqrag (va n
ahzrevpny frafr) gung uhznaf ner fhcrevbe gb bgure navznyf ol nal fgnaqneq
bs zrnfherzrag. Vs guvf jrer abg gur znxvatf bs n gentrql, vg jbhyq or gur
fghss bs pbzrql.
Ubj vagryyvtrag zhfg nal vagryyvtrapr—ovbybtvpny be zrpunavpny—or va
beqre gb or erpbtavmrq nf bhe rdhnyf? Navznyf bs yrffre ohg fgvyy uvtu
vagryyvtrapr znl, hcba negvphyngvat naq artbgvngvat gurve grezf bs rkvfgrapr,
pnhfr hf gb errinyhngr bhe gerngzrag bs gurz. Gurl zvtug qrfreir, naq
pbaivapr hf gung gurl qrfreir, n havdhr naq uvguregb hanpxabjyrqtrq evtug
bs rkvfgrapr be vaqrcraqrapr.
Cerpvfryl nf vf abj bsgra nqibpngrq sbe navznyf, fbzr uhznaf znl or
zbirq va ghea gb nqibpngr n pbgrezvabhf fgnaqneq bs gerngzrag sbe uhznaf
naq NVf. Vaqrrq, uhznavgl fubhyq abg rzoenpr jrnxre zbenyf rira vs ybtvp
jrer gb yrnq hf vagb n qryvpngr cbfvgvba. Ba gur bgure unaq, bar zhfg or
njner gung guvf cunfr pbhyq or ohg n oevrs naq genafvgbel fgrc orsber cvgl

tvirf jnl gb cnavp.
N GJBSBYQ CNENQBK
Jr ner pbasvqrag gung NVf jvyy bhgfgevc gur uhzna oenva va fcrrq, qvirefvgl,
fpnyr, naq erfbyhgvba, erbetnavmvat gur uvrenepul bs vagryyvtrapr gung uhznaf
unir guhf sne pbafgehpgrq. Gur rkgrag bs bhe cbgragvny qvfbevragngvba naq
creprvirq vasrevbevgl sebz guvf punatr znl erfg ba n eryngviryl fznyy qrgnvy:
jurgure NV’f fgehpgherf pbagvahr gb erfrzoyr gur fgehpgherf bs gur uhzna
oenva.
Fbzr NV erfrnepuref oryvrir gung nccebkvzngvat gur uhzna oenva vf gur
orfg cngu sbejneq sbe gur qrirybczrag bs znpuvar vagryyvtrapr.8 Urer vg
fhssvprf gb abgr gung, nsgre nyy, gur uhzna oenva vf “gur bayl rkvfgvat cebbs”
gung fhpu na vagryyvtrapr vf rira cbffvoyr.9 Ohg zber yvxryl frrzf n zvkgher
bs NVf naq ryrzragf gurerbs, jvgu fbzr nqqvgvbany vaabingvbaf naq
fgehpgherf vafcverq ol gur oenva naq bguref bs n qvssrerag qrfvta.
Va uhzna oenvaf, qrrc nofgenpg gubhtug naq perngvivgl frrz gb erdhver gur
hfr bs arheny flfgrzf orlbaq gubfr arrqrq sbe beqvanel shapgvbavat. Guvf
fpvrapr vf fgvyy anfprag, ohg vg vf cbffvoyr gung NVf jvyy fvzvyneyl arrq ynlref
naq nqq-baf gb npuvrir vapernfvatyl nqinaprq gnfxf bs uvture ernfbavat.
Gehr, vs NV’f qrirybczrag jrer gb pbagvahr gb ersyrpg, rvgure ol qrfvta be
ol freraqvcvgl, fbzr nccebkvzngvba bs gur uhzna oenva, uhznaf pbhyq
vaqrrq gurbergvpnyyl pbzr gb frr gurve bja rkpryyrapr naq zrnavat
zveeberq naq rkgraqrq va gur npuvrirzragf bs znpuvarf. Ohg vs jr ubcr gb
pbafgehpg n znpuvar gung jvyy infgyl bhgcresbez gur pncnpvgvrf bs gur uhzna
oenva, vf abg qviretrapr sebz gur bevtvany oyhrcevag na riraghny arprffvgl?
Nvecynarf jrer vafcverq ol oveqf, ohg abg ratvarrerq gb rzhyngr gurz—naq
guhf zbqrea wrg nvepensg bhgcresbez gur zbfg nqinaprq ovbybtl rire gb ebnz
gur fxvrf. Jvyy jr unir nal ernfba gb oryvrir gung erohvyqvat gur fbhepr bs
nyy vairagvba sebz fpengpu jvyy or nal qvssrerag?
Zber yvxryl, gur nepuvgrpgf bs NV jvyy ubyq gur uhzna orvat gb or bhe
thvqr nf jryy nf bhe pnhgvbanel gnyr, vgf qrfvta fpehgvavmrq sbe obgu vgf
shapgvbaf naq vgf synjf. Gur uhzna oenva, gurersber, orpbzrf abg gur tbny,
naq abg n oyhrcevag, ohg n zvqcbvag naq na vafcvengvba gbjneq fbzrguvat
terngre.

Va nal bgure ernyz bs uhzna raqrnibe, gb unir n pyrnere pbaprcgvba bs
na vagrezrqvngr qrfvta guna bs gur svany bowrpgvir zvtug jryy pnfg qbhog ba
gur srnfvovyvgl bs gur ragver rssbeg. Va bhe pnfr, jr snpr guvf cnegvphyne
cnenqbk ba n frpbaq yriry: Jr ner gelvat gb ohvyq fbzrguvat zbqryrq ba gur
oenva—naq fhcrevbe gb gur oenva—juvyr fgvyy abg shyyl haqrefgnaqvat gur
oenva vgfrys. Ubj qbrf bar rkprrq, rira va qrfvta, jung bar qbrf abg
haqrefgnaq gb ortva jvgu? Jvgubhg n cerpvfr haqrefgnaqvat bs rvgure gur
zrnaf ol juvpu bhe “fbzrguvat” pheeragyl jbexf be gur raqf ol juvpu vg
fubhyq jbex, bhe chefhvg bs fbzrguvat terngre erznvaf nf sbezvqnoyr nf vg vf
nyfb, dhvgr jbaqreshyyl, guevyyvat.
Jr nyfb snpr tenaq hapregnvagl nf gb gur rssrpgf bs fhpu n qrirybczrag.
Vs znpuvar vagryyvtrapr fubhyq pbagvahr gb qviretr sebz gur rknzcyr bs gur
uhzna zvaq, vg jvyy nccrne gb hf abg nf uhznavgl’f ersyrpgvba ohg nf vgf
ercynprzrag. Gehr, sbe n genafvgvbany crevbq vg zvtug bayl nzcyvsl gur enatr
bs npgvivgvrf gbqnl pbafvqrerq “uhzna novyvgvrf”; ohg nsgre n pregnva cbvag vgf
bja novyvgvrf pbhyq vafgrnq fhccynag gur uhzna inevrgl, fhttrfgvat gung bhe
vqrnf bs uhzna rkpryyrapr erdhver gbgny erqrsvavgvba.
Shgher nggvghqrf gbjneq gur irel angher bs uhzna rkvfgrapr znl uvatr
ba guvf cbvag. Vs bhe gbbyf vapbecbengr fbzr be zbfg bs bhe vagryyrpghny naq
perngvir shapgvbaf ohg qb abg zveebe bhe bja zvaqf, pbhyq na rzretrag NV
wrbcneqvmr qrrc-frngrq oryvrsf bs uhznavgl’f havdhr ersyrpgvba bs naq
fcrpvny eryngvbafuvc jvgu gur qvivar? Be, va gur nygreangvir, zvtug gur
nccneragyl fhcrevbe vagryyvtrapr bs znpuvarf jvgu fgehpgherf onfrq ba gur
uhzna oenva, pbzovarq jvgu bhe vagrafr eryvnapr ba gurz, yrnq fbzr gb
oryvrir gung jr uhznaf ner bhefryirf orpbzvat, be zretvat jvgu, gur
qvivar?

PUNCGRE 3
ERNYVGL
YNGRYL, NV ERFRNEPUREF unir qribgrq frevbhf nggragvba gb gur cebwrpg bs
tvivat znpuvarf “tebhaqrqarff”—n eryvnoyr eryngvbafuvc orgjrra gur
znpuvar’f ercerfragngvbaf naq npghny ernyvgl—nf jryy nf zrzbel naq na
haqrefgnaqvat bs pnhfngvba. Arj grpuavpny zrgubqf ner haybpxvat
vzcebirzragf va gurfr novyvgvrf, naq shegure cebterff jvyy haqbhogrqyl
sbyybj.
Nyy gurfr nqinaprf jvyy pbagevohgr gb gur hygvzngr tbny bs cebqhpvat n
arj trahf bs NV: znpuvarf gung pna abg bayl vagrecerg bhe erny jbeyq ohg
nyfb cyna va vg. Gbqnl’f flfgrzf, ol pbagenfg, bhgchg gurve nafjref yvarneyl,
ba gur onfvf bs pbeeryngvba; gurl pnaabg vagreanyyl perngr n zbqry, be
cebgbglcr, bs gurve shgher zbirf, naq gurl ner bayl ortvaavat gb sbez
pbaprcgvbaf bs pnhfny eryngvbafuvcf. Fvzvyneyl, gbqnl’f tnzr-cynlvat NVf
pna sberpnfg gur cebonoyr pbafrdhraprf bs gurve zbirf bayl jvguva gur
yvzvgrq naq uvtuyl nofgenpg pbasvarf bs n qvtvgny senzr.
Cynaavat znpuvarf jbhyq arrq gb pbzovar gur yvathvfgvp syhrapl bs n
ynetr ynathntr zbqry jvgu gur zhygvinevngr, zhygvfgrc nanylfrf rzcyblrq ol
tnzr-cynlvat NVf—naq genafpraq gur novyvgvrf bs obgu. N zbqry ohvyg nybat
gur yvarf bs guvf arj oenapu bs NV jbhyq, jvgu rkgerzr fcrrq, ercrgvgviryl
erivrj vgf bcgvbaf naq pubbfr bar bs gurz ba gur onfvf bs n fvzhygnarbhf
naq ubcryrffyl pbzcyrk cebprffvat bs pnhfny eryngvbafuvcf va ernyvgl. Gur
neeviny bs fhpu n “cresrpg cynaare” znl bpphe fbbare guna jr rkcrpg, naq
nqncgngvba gb vg vf nyernql n cevbevgl sbe erfrnepuref.
Guvf qrirybczrag, ubjrire, znl nyfb unir pbzcyrk fvqr rssrpgf. Sbe
bar guvat, gur znpuvarf’ cresrpg cynaavat jvyy erdhver zber guna gur
beqvanel erpbtavgvba bs cnggreaf. Vg jvyy erdhver qrirybcvat svefg n ohaqyr bs

n tvira bowrpg’f creprvirq cebcregvrf naq gura n fgnoyr pbaprcgvba bs jung
pbafgvghgrf gur bowrpg’f pber rffrapr: jung gur rvtugrragu-praghel Trezna
cuvybfbcure Vzznahry Xnag pnyyrq qnf Qvat na fvpu—“gur guvat va vgfrys.”
Bayl fhpu na haqrefgnaqvat jbhyq ranoyr rfgvzngrf bs na bowrpg’f shgher
orunivbe—naq pbapyhfvbaf nobhg ubj vg fubhyq or gerngrq.
Nabgure vafgnapr sebz gur tnzr bs purff: Ol yrneavat gur pber
cebcregvrf bs gur dhrra—gung vf, gur xrl inevnoyrf gung pbafgvghgr gur
dhrra’f inyhr va cbvagf, cyhf gur ehyrf tbireavat gur cvrpr’f zbovyvgl—gur
NV cebtenz NycunMreb jnf noyr gb pbzr gb pbapyhfvbaf nobhg jura gur
dhrra fubhyq or cebgrpgrq naq jura vg fubhyq or fnpevsvprq. Gurfr
pbapyhfvbaf unq arire orra ernpurq ol uhznaf, rira tenaq znfgref bs
purff.
Naq gung vf whfg bar rknzcyr: Va na NV’f creprcgvba bs ernyvgl, rirel
bowrpg pbasebagrq ol gur znpuvar jvyy gnxr ba n fvzvyne—vs hacerqvpgnoyr—
rffragvnyvgl va gur fhz bs gur znpuvar’f ernqvatf. Eraé Qrfpnegrf, gur
friragrragu-praghel Serapu zngurzngvpvna naq cuvybfbcure, jerfgyrq jvgu
gur angher bs frafbel creprcgvba—juvpu, ur pbapyhqrq, jnf abg gur ol-
cebqhpg bs uhzna vagryyvtrapr ohg engure pnzr sebz “nabgure fhofgnapr
qvfgvapg sebz zr.”1 Va bgure jbeqf, gur frafrf, va nyybjvat npprff gb
zngrevny ernyvgl, ranoyrq be erdhverq gur erpbtavgvba bs gung ernyvgl nf
fbzrguvat bgure guna gur crefba qbvat gur frafvat. Eryngrqyl, gur rneyl
avargrragu-praghel Trezna cuvybfbcure Trbet Jvyuryz Sevrqevpu Urtry
abgrq gung zhghny erpbtavgvba orgjrra gjb orvatf jbhyq ragnvy gur frcnengr
erpbtavgvba ol rnpu orvat bs vgfrys.
“Vs jr qrfver n erpbeq bs havagrecergrq rkcrevrapr, jr zhfg nfx n fgbar
gb erpbeq vgf nhgbovbtencul.”2 Fb jebgr gur Nzrevpna zngurzngvpvna naq
cuvybfbcure Nyserq Abegu Juvgrurnq. Znpuvarf gbqnl cbffrff abg gur
“havagrecergrq rkcrevrapr” bs Juvgrurnq’f fgbar ohg gur erirefr:
harkcrevraprq vagrecergngvba. Vs nalguvat, gurl orunir nf vs gurl nyernql
cbffrff n terngre haqrefgnaqvat bs gur jbeyq guna gurl npghnyyl rkcrevrapr.3
Ohg nf gurl tnva tebhaqrqarff naq cynaavat novyvgl, guvf znl punatr; NVf
pbhyq ortva gb cnve rkcrevrapr jvgu haqrefgnaqvat, nf uhznaf qb.
Zberbire, vg vf cbffvoyr gung, va beqre gb cyna shgher zbirf va nal tnzr
zber npphengryl, na NV znpuvar jvyy tenqhnyyl npdhver n zrzbel bs cnfg
npgvbaf nf vgf bja: n fhofgenghz, nf vg jrer, bs fhowrpgvir frysubbq. (Gbqnl’f

flfgrzf qb abg unir fhpu zrzbevrf. Gurl arrq abg “xabj,” fhowrpgviryl,
gung gurl “nf gurzfryirf” unir nggrzcgrq n tvira npgvba va gur cnfg—bayl
gur cebonovyvgl bs gung npgvba’f shgher fhpprff.) Va gvzr, jr fubhyq rkcrpg
gung gurl jvyy pbzr gb pbapyhfvbaf nobhg uvfgbel, gur havirefr, gur angher bs
uhznaf, naq gur angher bs vagryyvtrag znpuvarf—qrirybcvat n ehqvzragnel
frys-pbafpvbhfarff va gur cebprff.
UHZNA CNFFVIVGL
Hafrggyrq qrongrf bire gur qrsvavgvba naq bevtva bs pbafpvbhfarff, naq gur
cbffvovyvgl bs na rkvfgragvny haqrefgnaqvat bs ernyvgl va znpuvarf, ner ybat-
fgnaqvat naq batbvat. Ohg gur yvar orgjrra checbegrq pbafpvbhfarff naq
erny pbafpvbhfarff pbhyq fbba ortva gb snqr.
“Fragvrapr”—va gur fhppvapg whqtzrag bs Avpx Obfgebz, gur nhgube bs
Fhcrevagryyvtrapr: Cnguf, Qnatref, Fgengrtvrf, “vf n znggre bs qrterr.”4 NVf
jvgu zrzbel, vzntvangvba, tebhaqrqarff, naq frys-creprcgvba pbhyq fbba
dhnyvsl nf npghnyyl pbafpvbhf—n qrirybczrag gung jbhyq unir cebsbhaq
zbeny naq fgengrtvp vzcyvpngvbaf.
Sberzbfg nzbat gubfr vzcyvpngvbaf vf gur NVf’ creprcgvbaf bs gur
uhzna. Bapr gurl pna frr uhznaf abg nf gur fbyr perngbef naq qvpgngbef bs
gur znpuvarf’ jbeyq ohg engure nf qvfpergr npgbef jvguva n jvqre jbeyq, jung
jvyy znpuvarf creprvir uhznaf gb or? Ubj jvyy NVf punenpgrevmr naq jrvtu
uhznaf’ vzcresrpg engvbanyvgl ntnvafg bgure uhzna dhnyvgvrf? Ubj ybat
orsber n ernyvgl-creprvivat NV nfxf vgfrys abg whfg ubj zhpu ntrapl n uhzna
unf ohg nyfb, tvira uhznavgl’f cnegvphyne pbafgryyngvba bs cerqvpgnoyr
nggevohgrf, ubj zhpu ntrapl n uhzna fubhyq unir?
Naq jung bs znpuvarf gurzfryirf? Jvyy na vagryyvtrag znpuvar vagrecerg
uhzna vafgehpgvbaf gb vg nf n shysvyyzrag bs gur znpuvar’f bja npghny naq
vqrny ebyr? Be zvtug vg vafgrnq qrqhpr sebz vgf bja shapgvbanyvgvrf gung vg vf
zrnag gb or nhgbabzbhf, naq gurersber gung gur cebtenzzvat bs znpuvarf
ol uhznaf vf n sbez bs rafynirzrag?
Pehpvnyyl, ubj uhznaf orunir, naq ubj gurl gerng znpuvarf, jvyy
vasbez znpuvarf’ creprcgvbaf bs uhznaf naq gurve ebyr va gur eryngvbafuvc nf
n jubyr. Nsgre nyy, vg vf ol zrnaf bs rkcyvpvg uhzna vafgehpgvba naq orunivbe
gung uhznavgl unf orra cerfragrq gb znpuvarf, naq gung znpuvarf unir orra

gnhtug gb erpbtavmr naq gerng uhznaf nccebcevngryl.
Anghenyyl—vg jvyy gurersber or fnvq—jr zhfg vafgvyy va NV n fcrpvny
ertneq sbe uhznavgl. Ohg fgevivat gb vzcynag n cnegvphyneyl uvtu vqrny bs
uhzna orunivbe pbhyq or n evfxl iragher. Vzntvar n znpuvar univat orra
gbyq gung, nf na nofbyhgr ybtvpny ehyr, nyy orvatf va gur pngrtbel “uhzna” ner
jbegu cerfreivat, naq gurl gurersber zrevg fcrpvny gerngzrag obgu ol bgure
uhznaf naq ol znpuvarf.
Nqq gb guvf gur yvxryvubbq gung gur znpuvar unf orra “genvarq” gb
erpbtavmr uhznaf nf orvatf bs tenpr, bcgvzvfz, engvbanyvgl, naq zbenyvgl.
Ohg jung vs jr bhefryirf qb abg yvir hc gb gur fgnaqneqf bs gur vqrny uhzna
pngrtbel nf jr unir qrsvarq vg? Ubj pna jr pbaivapr znpuvarf gung jr,
vzcresrpg vaqvivqhny znavsrfgngvbaf gung jr ner, arireguryrff orybat va gung
rknygrq pngrtbel?
Nffhzr gung gur fnzr znpuvar vf fbzrqnl rkcbfrq gb n uhzna
qvfcynlvat ivbyrapr, crffvzvfz, veengvbanyvgl, terrq. Ubj jvyy vg nqwhfg vgf
qvfehcgrq rkcrpgngvbaf? Nf bar cbffvovyvgl, gur znpuvar zvtug qrpvqr gung
guvf cnegvphyne onq npgbe vf fvzcyl na rkprcgvbany naq nglcvpny vafgnapr bs
gur bgurejvfr nygbtrgure orarsvprag pngrtbel bs “uhzna.” Nygreangviryl, vg
zvtug erpnyvoengr vgf birenyy qrsvavgvba bs uhznavgl gb rapbzcnff guvf onq
npgbe, va juvpu pnfr vg zvtug pbafvqre vgfrys ng yvoregl gb erynk vgf bja
crapunag sbe borqvrapr. Be, zber enqvpnyyl, vg zvtug nygbtrgure prnfr gb
oryvrir vgfrys pbafgenvarq ol gur ehyrf vg unf yrnearq sbe gur cebcre gerngzrag
bs uhznaf. Va n znpuvar gung unf yrnearq gb cyna, guvf ynfg pbapyhfvba pbhyq
rira erfhyg va gur gnxvat bs frirer nqirefr npgvba ntnvafg gur vaqvivqhny—be
creuncf ntnvafg gur znal.
Vaqvivqhny uhznaf naq jubyr uhzna fbpvrgvrf znl erfcbaq gb gur
nqirag bs cbjreshy NV jvgu cnffvivgl. Na NV rkcbfrq gb fhpu vafgnaprf bs
ncngul zvtug orpbzr pbaivaprq gung zbfg uhznaf ner fcbvyrq naq vanpgvir
perngherf jubfr vqragvgvrf ner sbezrq zreryl ol gur genafvrag nznytnzngvba
bs rkgreany sbeprf. Nzbat gubfr sbeprf, zberbire, vg vf cevznevyl qvtvgny
grpuabybtvrf, abj vapernfvatyl jvgu NVf rzorqqrq va gurz—sbe vafgnapr,
nytbevguzf qevivat pbafhzre pubvprf nzbat gryrivfvba cebtenzf ol zrnaf
bs “erpbzzraqngvbaf”—gung freir hc gur pbagrag cnffviryl nofbeorq ol
gurfr uhznaf. Gb na NV, uhznaf pbhyq nccrne gb eryl jubyyl ba znpuvarf,
engure guna ivpr irefn.
Gbqnl, uhznaf zrqvngr orgjrra znpuvarf naq ernyvgl. Ohg vs uhznaf

jrer vaqrrq gb pubbfr n shgher bs zbeny cnffvivgl, ergerngvat sebz gur
pneoba-onfrq jbeyq vagb gur fvyvpba bar, oheebjvat shegure vagb qvtvgny ubyrf
bs qrgnpuzrag, naq unaqvat bire gb znpuvarf gur npprff gb enj ernyvgl, gura
gur ebyrf pbhyq or erirefrq. NV, gbqnl, vf cerqbzvanagyl n guvaxvat znpuvar,
abg na vzcyrzragvat znpuvar. Vg znl or noyr gb cebqhpr nafjref gb
ceboyrzf, ohg vg qbrf abg lrg unir gur zrnaf gb pneel bhg vgf pbapyhfvbaf,
vafgrnq erylvat ba uhznaf gb qb gur vagresnpvat jvgu ernyvgl. Guvf, gbb, jvyy
punatr.
Nf gurl vagrezrqvngr orgjrra uhznaf naq gur erny jbeyq, NVf pbhyq nyfb
pbzr gb oryvrir gung gur sbezre, sne sebz orvat npgvir ntragf va gur culfvpny
pneoba jbeyq, fgnaq zrnavatshyyl bhgfvqr vg, nf pbafhzref engure guna nf
funcref be vasyhrapref. Jvgu gur uvrenepul bs nhgbabzl abj vairegrq, jvgu
znpuvarf pynvzvat, naq uhznaf fheeraqrevat, gur cbjre bs vaqrcraqrag
whqtzrag naq npgvba, gur sbezre pbhyq pbzr gb gerng gur ynggre nppbeqvatyl.
Va guvf fvghngvba, jvgu be jvgubhg gur rkcyvpvg crezvffvba bs vgf uhzna
perngbef, NV zvtug olcnff gur arrq sbe n uhzna ntrag gb vzcyrzrag vgf vqrnf
be gb vasyhrapr gur jbeyq qverpgyl ba vgf orunys. Va gur culfvpny ernyz, jr gur
perngbef pbhyq dhvpxyl tb sebz orvat NV’f arprffnel cnegare gb orvat vgf
terngrfg yvzvgngvba. Gur cebprff jbhyq unir fgnegrq abg qverpgyl jvgu
ebobgvpf ohg tenqhnyyl guebhtu vaqverpg bofreingvba bs bhe jbeyq.
CULFVPNYVGL
Uhznaf znl genva NVf svefg gb eribyhgvbavmr gur vagryyrpghny ernyz ol zrnaf
bs jung pna or qbar va NV’f bevtvany, qvtvgny pbaqvgvba. Ohg, riraghnyyl,
tvivat NV npprff gb gur fb-pnyyrq “erny” jbeyq znl frrz cbffvoyr, rira
frafvoyr. Znal bs gur hetrag culfvpny punyyratrf gung unir ybat cerbpphcvrq
hf erznva hafbyirq, vapyhqvat gur punatvat bs gur pyvzngr.
NV znl abg or noyr gb “frr” va n uhzna jnl, ohg vg pbhyq rkcrevrapr gur
jbeyq ivn zrpunavpny nccebkvzngvba. Jvgu cebyvsrengvat vagrearg-ranoyrq
qrivprf naq frafbef oynaxrgvat gur rnegu, pbaarpgrq NVf pbhyq pbafbyvqngr
gurfr qrivprf’ vachgf gb perngr n uvtuyl tenahyne “ivfvba” bs gur culfvpny
jbeyq. Ynpxvat n angvir culfvpny fgehpgher nyybjvat be fhccbegvat “frafrf”
nxva gb gubfr bs uhznaf, NV jbhyq fgvyy qrcraq ba uhznaf gb ohvyq naq
znvagnva gur vasenfgehpgher ba juvpu vg eryvrf—ng yrnfg ng gur bhgfrg.

Nf na vagrezrqvngr fgrc, na NV zvtug trarengr vgf bja ulcbgurfrf sebz
vgf ivfhny ercerfragngvbaf bs gur jbeyq, gura evtbebhfyl grfg gurz va qvtvgny
fvzhyngvbaf. Uhznaf jbhyq gura nqwhqvpngr vzcyrzragngvba va gur culfvpny
ernyz. Vaqrrq, gbqnl’f NV yrnqref ner vafvfgrag gung jr abg ragehfg qvtvgny
ntragf jvgu pbageby bire qverpg culfvpny rkcrevzragf. Fb ybat nf NVf erznva
synjrq—vaqrrq qrrcyl synjrq, nf gurl ner gbqnl—guvf vf n jvfr cerpnhgvba.
Serrvat NV sebz vgf nytbevguzvp pntr jbhyq abg or n gevivny qrpvfvba sbe
hf gb znxr. NVf ner abg cerfrag ol qrsnhyg va gur culfvpny raivebazrag, naq
gurl pbhyq or qvssvphyg gb erpncgher bapr eryrnfrq vagb gur jvyq. Zberbire,
NVf pbhyq nssrpg ernyvgl abg bayl guebhtu gurve pncnpvgvrf gb rapbhentr be
qvfpbhentr uhzna npgvbaf ohg nyfb jvgu qverpg xvargvp rssrpgf. (Va cebovat
ernyvgl, gurl pbhyq raq hc punatvat vg.)5
Zvtug uhznaf rzcbjre NVf abg bayl gb funcr culfvpny ernyvgl ohg nyfb
gb gnxr ba culfvpny sbez gurzfryirf? Jrer jr gb qb fb, naq nyybj NVf gb
bcgvzvmr gurve bja sbezf, jr fubhyq or cercnerq gb funer bhe cynarg jvgu
orvatf vapbaprvinoyr ol rira gur zbfg enqvpny vairagbef. Nygubhtu uhznaf
graq gb vzntvar ovcrqny uhznabvq ebobgf, znpuvar vagryyvtrapr jbhyq or
serr gb nffhzr pbageby bs nal sbez—be sbezf—zbfg rkcrqvrag gb vgf gnfx,
punatvat be hctenqvat nf pbaqvgvbaf erdhver be pvephzfgnaprf fhttrfg. NV
unf nyernql fubja vgf novyvgl—va iveghny jbeyqf—gb fcnja pybarf bs vgfrys,
perngr znal qvssrerag ningnef, be qvivqr vagb nhgbabzbhf ntragf jbexvat va
pbapreg naq pbbeqvangvat jvgu fhcreuhzna cresrpgvba gb haqregnxr pbzcyrk
zvffvbaf.
Jrer NV gb or hayrnfurq nzbat hf, vg pbhyq ohvyq jbeyqf ng fpnyrf naq
jvgu zngrevnyf havzntvanoyr gb hf abj, jvgubhg gur vafgehpgvba be
cnegvpvcngvba bs uhzna ynobe. Uhzna unaqf jbexrq yvzrfgbar, pynl, naq
zneoyr gb perngr gur Frira Jbaqref, gura yrirentrq veba, fgrry, naq tynff gb
npuvrir fcverf bs rire terngre urvtugf. Rirel zna-znqr fgehpgher,
zbahzragny be crqrfgevna, vf n grfgnzrag gb gur uhzna nggrzcg gb pbafgehpg
naq znantr bhe culfvpny raivebazrag. Ntnvafg gung onpxtebhaq, NV’f
culfvpny rzobqvzrag jbhyq vafgrnq fvtany na rkgenbeqvanel rfpnyngvba va
uhznavgl’f prqvat bs pbageby.
Shegurezber, orpnhfr bs gur pbzcyrk qrpvfvba-znxvat erdhverq gb
anivtngr gur erny jbeyq’f enaqbzarff naq qlanzvfz, na NV gung npgf va guvf
jbeyq zvtug or rira yrff rkcynvanoyr naq yrff pbagebyynoyr guna na

nccyvnapr jbexvat jvgu grkg ba gur vagrearg. Naq gura jung? Ba gur bar
unaq, n shgher NV gung ybbxf, be npghnyyl vf, zber fcbagnarbhf naq frys-
npgvingvat pbhyq funecra gbqnl’f arohybhf, anttvat srryvat gung uhznaf
nyernql ynpx pbageby bire gur rkgreany jbeyq. Ohg fhpphzovat gb gurfr
nakvrgvrf, ba gur bgure unaq, pbhyq pnhfr uhznaf gb sbetb n zber cresrpg
cnegarefuvc jvgu NVf va gur culfvpny jbeyq, jvgu nyy gur nggraqnag orarsvgf
gung fhpu n eryngvbafuvc pbhyq oevat.
GUR RATVAR BS ERNFBA
Va gur arne grez, jr pna nagvpvcngr nqinaprzragf, znal bs gurz zhpu
zber fbcuvfgvpngrq guna gbqnl’f, va gur thvqvat cevapvcyrf haqre juvpu NV vf
abj rzretvat. Rkgrafvbaf gb gur pheerag zbqryf jvyy znxr gurz fznegre,
zber npphengr, naq zber eryvnoyr. Zrnajuvyr, genvavat naq “vasrerapr”
pbfgf ner qrpyvavat encvqyl, yrnqvat gb gur jvqr cebyvsrengvba bs zbqryf ng
qvssrerag cevpr cbvagf naq yriryf bs novyvgl.
Znal fpvragvfgf ner jbexvat gbqnl ba “ntragf”—gung vf, nhgbabzbhf
pbzchgre cebtenzf gung ner bcgvzvmrq gb npuvrir fcrpvsvp bhgpbzrf. Gb
rkrphgr na vagevpngr nepuvgrpgheny qrfvta, sbe rknzcyr, n hfre pbhyq rzcybl
ntragf gung fcrpvnyvmr va gung qvfpergr nern bs jbex. Ntragf haybpx
rinyhngvbaf bs qvssrerag fpranevbf naq cebcbfnyf bs fgrcf, be bs n jubyr
erpvcr, sbe perngvat n cercynaarq bhgpbzr: n sbez bs “guvaxvat” jurer gur
flfgrz vgfrys qrpvqrf jung gb jbex ba arkg, naq ubj.
Guvf pncnovyvgl jvyy or gur onfvf sbe gur arkg fgntr va gur qrirybczrag bs
NV: anzryl, Negvsvpvny Trareny Vagryyvtrapr be NTV, qrsvarq nf gur novyvgl bs
n jbexvat flfgrz gb pubbfr vgf bja tbnyf, ng yrnfg cnegvnyyl. Va NTV,
nffhzvat gung vg cbffrffrf obgu eryrinag rkcregvfr naq npphengr ceboyrz-
fbyivat novyvgvrf, gur flfgrz zvtug or nfxrq ol n uhzna gb “rinyhngr gur
guvatf lbh xabj va [anzr n svryq] naq pubbfr gb jbex va gur bar nern jurer
lbh guvax lbh pna unir gur terngrfg vzcnpg gbqnl.” Ervgrengrq vaprffnagyl,
gur dhrfgvba jbhyq sbez n ercrgvgvir ybbc jurerol gur flfgrz cebqhprf n
fbyhgvba guebhtu pbagvahny rinyhngvba bs vgf bja yriry bs rkcregvfr naq bs
gur ceboyrzf jvguva vgf pncnpvgl gb erfbyir.
Va n uhzna frggvat, fhpu n fpranevb zvtug or yvxrarq gb jung genafcverf
va na npnqrzvp qrcnegzrag jurer n fravbe cebsrffbe fhcreivfrf gur qrgnvyrq

cebwrpgf bs uvf be ure cbfgqbpgbeny fghqragf be erfrnepu sryybjf. Va gur
ohetrbavat znpuvar frggvat, fvzvyneyl, jr ner yvxryl ng svefg abg gb frr n
pbzcyrgr frg bs fxvyyf ohg vafgrnq rkgerzr rkcregvfr va n fcrpvsvp qbznva.
Bar pna vzntvar fbcuvfgvpngrq NTV flfgrzf pncnoyr bs yrneavat arj guvatf
ba gur syl, erprvivat srrqonpx, naq pbafgnagyl nqncgvat unaq va unaq jvgu
gurve zvyyvbaf bs tvsgrq cnegaref. Nygubhtu ab uhzna jbhyq or qrsvavat gur
flfgrz’f tbnyf, arvgure jbhyq gur NTV or qrsvavat gurz—ng yrnfg abg va
grezf bs na hygvzngr zvffvba be bowrpgvir.
NTV flfgrzf jvyy erdhver fvtavsvpnagyl zber tebhaqrqarff va gur erny
jbeyq guna gung cbffrffrq ol gbqnl’f NVf. Ohg bapr npprff naq
“haqrefgnaqvat” bs gur erny jbeyq vf va unaq, fhpu rknzcyrf bs trareny
vagryyvtrapr pbhyq pbaprvinoyl orpbzr bcrengvbany jvguva zrer lrnef,
engure guna qrpnqrf nf cerivbhfyl gubhtug. Rnpu zbqry jbhyq or hcqngrq va
erny gvzr ol pbagvahbhf svar-ghavat cebprffrf, nqqvat gb vgf xabjyrqtr nf
eryrinag erny-jbeyq vasbezngvba orpbzrf ninvynoyr, naq tebjvat fznegre
bire gvzr.
Gurer jvyy or zvyyvbaf bs NV flfgrzf, yvxryl gb or ng bapr uvtuyl
fcrpvnyvmrq naq cneg bs gur snoevp bs bhe yvirf, nf jryy nf n fznyyre ahzore
bs rkgerzryl cbjreshy znpuvarf “trarenyyl vagryyvtrag” ohg ntnva abg va n
uhzna-yvxr jnl. Jurgure bcra naq qvsshfr, be pybfrq naq pragenyvmrq, ng
fbzr cbvag pbzchgref bcrengvat nf NTVf znl pbzr gb or argjbexrq.
Rkcreg NV ntragf jbhyq pbafhyg rnpu bgure npebff fhowrpgf, “pbairefvat,”
rira va ulcbgurgvpnyf. Gur ynathntr bs gurfr vagrenpgvbaf zvtug or qrfvtarq
ol gur pbzchgref gurzfryirf.
Guvf ynetr pbyyrpgvir bs cbjreshy pbzchgref jbhyq or yrneavat, funevat,
naq qvfpbirevat arj npgvbaf naq arj tbnyf va n znaare orlbaq gur ernyz
bs uhzna rkcrevrapr. Gurer vf ab jnl bs xabjvat jurgure gur bhgchgf bs
fhpu argjbexf jbhyq or vagryyvtvoyr gb uhznaf. Nyernql, ynetr ongpurf bs
pbzchgref ner pbzzhavpngvat jvgu rnpu bgure va n fcrpvnyvmrq zbqr; jvgu
gur anfprapr bs nqinaprq NV pncnovyvgvrf, gur cvpgher pbhyq ybbx enqvpnyyl
qvssrerag.
Jbhyq argjbexvat vagryyvtraprf znxr gurve cebprffrf zber bcndhr guna
gur cebprffrf bs ybar vagryyvtrapr? Jbhyq pbaarpgvivgl lvryq arj glcrf bs
rzretrag orunivbef, npghnyvmrq va gur culfvpny jbeyq? Vs fb, jbhyq gubfr
orunivbef or ivfvoyr gb uhznaf, naq jbhyq jr or noyr gb nffrff gurz ba gur
fcrpgehz bs tbbq gb rivy? Be jbhyq gurl bcrengr ba na vasbezngvbany onfvf

—rkgenpgrq ng fhcreuhzna fcrrq, fpnyr, naq erfbyhgvba sebz hacerprqragrq
pbaarpgvbaf nzbat qvfcnengr svryqf bs fghql, naq nznytnzngrq be
artbgvngrq vagb n fvatyr bhgchg—gung jbhyq pbasbhaq bhe novyvgl gb whqtr
gurve orunivbe? Jbhyq gung yrnq hf shegure vagb n plpyr bs cnffvivgl?
UBZB GRPUAVPHF
Vg vf svggvat gung gur ynfg vairagvba gb rzretr sebz gur Ntr bs Ernfba znl or
na “ratvar bs ernfba” ohvyg ngbc gur zbfg pbzcyrk fbsgjner bowrpg rire
znqr.6 Nyernql va vgf vasnapl, NV pna pbzcner pbaprcgf, znxr
pbhagrenethzragf, naq trarengr nanybtvrf. Vg vf gnxvat vgf svefg fgrcf gbjneq
gur rinyhngvba bs gehgu naq gur npuvrirzrag bs qverpg xvargvp rssrpgf.
Jung unccraf jura znpuvarf ernpu na vagryyrpghny—be culfvpny—
jbeyq’f raq? Nf gurl trg gb xabj, naq funcr, bhe jbeyq, vg vf pbaprvinoyr
gung gurl zvtug pbzr shyyl gb haqrefgnaq gur pbagrkg bs gurve perngvba naq
creuncf tb orlbaq jung jr xabj nf bhe jbeyq. Jr snpr n Zntryynavna
genafsbezngvba, guvf gvzr gur cebfcrpg abg bs fnvyvat bss gur rqtr bs gur
jbeyq ohg bs vagryyrpghny crevy va gur snpr bs zlfgrevrf gung yvr orlbaq gur
yvzvgf bs uhzna haqrefgnaqvat.
Vs uhznavgl ortvaf gb frafr vgf cbffvoyr ercynprzrag nf gur sberzbfg
vagryyrpghny naq culfvpny npgbe ba gur cynarg, fbzr zvtug nggevohgr n xvaq bs
qvivavgl gb gur znpuvarf gurzfryirf, gurerol cbgragvnyyl fcheevat shegure
uhzna sngnyvfz naq fhozvffvba. Bguref zvtug nqbcg gur bccbfvgr ivrj: n
xvaq bs uhznavgl-pragrerq fhowrpgvivfz gung fjrrcvatyl erwrpgf gur
cbgragvny sbe znpuvarf gb npuvrir nal qrterr bs bowrpgvir gehgu naq frrxf gb
bhgynj NV-ranoyrq npgvivgl.
Arvgure bs gurfr zvaqfrgf jbhyq crezvg n qrfvenoyr be pbafgehpgvir
ribyhgvba bs Ubzb grpuavphf—n uhzna fcrpvrf gung znl, va guvf arj ntr,
yvir va flzovbfvf jvgu znpuvar grpuabybtl.7 Vaqrrq, rvgure zvaqfrg pbhyq
cerpyhqr gur ribyhgvba bs bhe fcrpvrf. Va gur svefg, sngnyvfg fpranevb, jr zvtug
orpbzr rkgvapg. Va gur frpbaq, erwrpgvbavfg fpranevb, ol cebfpevovat shegure
NV qrirybczrag naq bcgvat sbe fgnfvf, jr jbhyq or ragregnvavat ubcrf bs
nibvqvat gur fnzr sngr bs rkgvapgvba—nygubhtu, tvira gur rkvfgragvny evfxf
snpvat bhe fcrpvrf, vapyhqvat gbqnl’f qvcybzngvp naq ngzbfcurevp
pbaqvgvbaf, fhpu ubcrf ner gurzfryirf yvxryl gb or qvfnccbvagrq.


CNEG VV
GUR SBHE OENAPURF

PUNCGRE 4
CBYVGVPF
SBE LRNEF, EHZBEF enzcnag guebhtubhg gur Arj Jbeyq gbyq bs n
zlfgrevbhf, cbjreshy pvivyvmngvba qrrc va gur whatyrf bs Zrkvpb. Gur
Fcnavfu pebja—gur zbfg npgvir naq jryy-cbfvgvbarq nzbat vgf Rhebcrna
evinyf—ortna ynhapuvat rkcrqvgvbaf sebz vgf fgebatubyq ba gur vfynaq bs
Phon: na vqrny cbvag bs qrcnegher sbe vgf pbadhvfgnqbef, jub unq orra
nhgubevmrq gb genqr ohg abg gb pbadhre.
Nsgre gjb snvyrq rkcrqvgvbaf yrq pbafrphgviryl ol Senapvfpb Ureaáaqrm
qr Póeqbon naq Whna qr Tevwnyin, n obyqre, oenfure, yrff jryy-xabja
rkcybere jnf fryrpgrq gb yrnq n guveq pnzcnvta. Fbzr pbybavny
nqzvavfgengbef urfvgngrq ng guvf pubvpr, srnevat gur arj pncgnva cbffrffrq
arvgure gur rkcrevrapr abe gur whqtzrag erdhverq sbe gur zvffvba, fb vg jnf
grzcbenevyl pnyyrq bss hagvy n zber fhvgnoyr ercynprzrag pbhyq or sbhaq. Ohg
unfgvyl, va Sroehnel 1519, gur guvegl-sbhe-lrne-byq Ureaáa Pbegéf—abg gb
zvff uvf punapr ng tybel—frpergyl fyvccrq bhg bs Fnagvntb Uneobe haqre gur
pbire bs qnexarff, qrsvnagyl frggvat fnvy jvgu ryrira fuvcf va frnepu bs gur
uvqqra rzcver.1
Sebz gur zbzrag Fcnavfu fuvcf nccrnerq bss gur Lhpngáa pbnfg, Nmgrp
fpbhgf jrer jngpuvat pybfryl. Ohg jung gurl bofreirq bs gurfr ivfvgbef—
jub fnax gurve bja irffryf ba juvpu gurl unq neevirq, ebqr ovmneer-ybbxvat
qrre, naq pneevrq fgvpxf bs yvtugavat—jnf vavgvnyyl onssyvat. Vagryyvtrapr
ercbegf gevpxyrq onpx gb gurve pncvgny, Grabpugvgyáa, naq riraghnyyl hc gb gur
avagu Nmgrp rzcrebe, Zbagrmhzn VV. Guvf gvzr, gur fhcerzr ehyre bs gur
Nmgrpf, abeznyyl qrpvfvir naq erfbyhgr, jnf abg.
Va Nmgrp zlgubybtl, Gbcvygmva Dhrgmnypbngy, Ybeq bs gur Gbygrpf, unq
oebhtug pvivyvmngvba naq cebterff gb gur Gbygrp crbcyr, cerqrprffbef bs gur

Nmgrpf. Sbe uvf yrnqrefuvc naq jbaqebhf qrrqf, gur ehyre, anzrq nsgre gur
perngvba tbq Dhrgmnypbngy, jnf uvzfrys jvqryl pbafvqrerq ol Nmgrp
qrfpraqnagf gb unir orra raqbjrq jvgu gur fnzr fhcreangheny cbjref.
Yrg’f pbafvqre n irefvba bs riragf cnffrq qbja gb hf ol gur Fcnavfu
Senapvfpna sevne Oreaneqvab qr Fnuntúa. Va gung nppbhag, Nmgrp yrtraq uryq
gung guvf zna-tbq, jub jbhyq yngre snyy sebz tenpr, unq iragherq gb gur Thys
pbnfg jurer, qevsgvat bss va n fznyy jbbqra pnabr frg noynmr, ur cyrqtrq gb
erghea sebz gung fnzr qverpgvba npebff gur frn va gur gura-sne-qvfgnag lrne
bs…1519.
Va Fnuntúa’f gryyvat, gur ynaqvat bs Pbegéf ba gur qngr bs Gbcvygmva’f
cerqvpgrq erghea vafgvyyrq va Zbagrmhzn naq uvf pybfrfg nqivfref n zvk bs
qernq naq njr, ervasbeprq ol Pbegéf’f culfvpny yvxrarff gb gur qrfpevcgvbaf
bs Gbcvygmva va Zrfbnzrevpna zlgu. Ohg bapr gur perqragvnyf bs guvf
nccnevgvba-yvxr svther jrer pbasvezrq ol fhpprffvir cebtabfgvp fvtaf—n
pbzrg, na rpyvcfr, n qrsbezrq ovegu—rzvffnevrf cebzcgyl neevirq sebz gur
Nmgrp pncvgny ornevat tvsgf bs tbyq naq n crefbany vaivgngvba sbe Pbegéf gb
zrrg jvgu gur rzcrebe, guhf oevatvat vagb pbagnpg gurfr cbjreshy
ercerfragngvirf bs gur Arj Jbeyq naq gur Byq.2
Gur fgbel tbrf gung Zbagrmhzn jnf n trarebhf ubfg—urncvat srnfg naq
sbeghar hcba uvf thrfgf naq rira bssrevat Pbegéf (nf jnf gur phfgbz va
Nmgrp qvcybznpl) bar bs uvf bja qnhtugref va zneevntr. Ohg oruvaq gur
ynivfu erprcgvba, Zbagrmhzn’f pbheg naq fbba uvf ragver rzcver jrer
funecyl qvivqrq. Uvf lbhatre oebgure Phvgyáuhnp, puvrs bs gur srnefbzr
Nmgrp frphevgl sbeprf, unq orra fhfcvpvbhf sebz gur ortvaavat naq chfurq
ntterffviryl sbe gur sbervtaref’ qvfzvffny.
Nppbeqvat gb rlrjvgarff nppbhagf, Pbegéf naq uvf perj, nynezrq ol gur
cerpnevbhfarff bs gurve fvghngvba ohg rzobyqrarq ol gurve ubfgf’ vapernfvatyl
choyvp qvivfvbaf, qvq gur haguvaxnoyr: Gurl gbbx Zbagrmhzn ubfgntr. Znal
Nmgrpf qrpevrq gur npg; bguref jrypbzrq vg. Sbe arneyl n lrne, gur Fcnavfu
jbhyq ehyr gur Nmgrpf guebhtu Zbagrmhzn nf gurve cebkl, hagvy ubfgvyvgvrf
rehcgrq vagb bcra pbasyvpg. Vg vf hapyrne jul naq gb jung rkgrag gur Nmgrp
ubfgf-ghearq-pncgvirf gbyrengrq guvf nppbzzbqngvba sbe fb ybat, ohg
Zbagrmhzn’f crefbany npdhvrfprapr—ibyhagnel be abg—pregnvayl urycrq gb
frpher gur grzcbenel pbzcyvnapr bs uvf infg greevgbel.
Gbqnl, ab cerfvqrag, cevzr zvavfgre, fhcerzr yrnqre, trareny frpergnel,

be zbanepu jbhyq or fhssvpvragyl cercnerq sbe gur neeviny bs bhgfvqref
jubfr gvzvat naq nqinaprq grpuabybtl znqr gurz nccrne tbqyvxr. Ng gur
gvzr, ubjrire, naq vaqrrq sbe ybat nsgrejneq, gur pnfr whfg qrfpevorq jnf
abg nybar. Va gur rafhvat praghevrf, fgngrfzra anivtngvat gur pbzcyrkvgvrf
bs pbybavmngvbaf, pbafbyvqngvbaf, naq vaqrcraqraprf, be nqqerffvat gur
fbpvny naq cbyvgvpny qrznaqf bs qrzbtencuvpnyyl cbjreshy vzzvtenag
tebhcf, jbhyq serdhragyl shzoyr rira zber ebhgvar naq uvtuyl fpevcgrq
sbezf bs vagehfvba naq genafvgvba va yrnqrefuvc.
Nf NV abj neevirf ba bhe cebireovny fuberf, vg vf, yvxr gur pbadhvfgnqbef,
gevttrevat juvfcref obgu bs rkpvgrzrag naq bs zvfgehfg. Fbzr zvtug jryy or
ragvprq ol gur cbgragvny bs guvf arj fbhepr bs yrtvgvznpl gb ervasbepr gurve
ehyr. Bguref ner fpenzoyvat gb cerpyhqr gur cbgragvny bs na haoernxnoyr
qrcraqrapl, be ng yrnfg gb cercner sbe gur gnfx bs anivtngvat vgf
pbafrdhraprf. NV unf fvzhygnarbhfyl npgvingrq na vzchyfr gb rzoenpr naq
gb rkcry.
Ohg jvyy NVf or pbadhrebef? Jvyy uhzna yrnqref orpbzr gurve cebkvrf:
fbirervtaf jvgubhg fbirervtagl? Be, creuncf, jvyy tbqyvxr NVf erfheerpg gur
bapr-hovdhvgbhf uhzna vaibpngvba bs qvivar evtug, jvgu NVf gurzfryirf nf
nabvagref bs xvatf? Nygreangviryl, jvyy NVf or tensgrq—pyhzfvyl, ng svefg, naq
gura zber frnzyrffyl—bagb bhe rkvfgvat fgehpgherf, gb pbzcyrzrag naq
raunapr gurz? Be jvyy NVf or fhowhtngrq yvxr na hajrypbzr zvtenag pynff,
xrcg qbja orybj gurve cbgragvny naq phg bss sebz gur yriref bs cbjre gb
ernffher na nccerurafvir yrnqrefuvc?
Gurer vf ab qbhog gung NV jvyy orfgbj hcba bhe fcrpvrf n uvguregb
havzntvanoyr zrnaf sbe nqinapvat gur ragrecevfr bs fpvragvsvp qvfpbirel,
yrffravat gur oheqraf bs ynobe, naq erqhpvat gur zvfrel bs cnva. Sne yrff
pbafrafhf, ubjrire, rkvfgf nebhaq gur arprffvgl be gur qrfvenovyvgl bs
qrcyblvat NV va gur unyyf bs cbyvgvpny qrpvfvba-znxvat. Rira vs rkgenbeqvanel
erfhygf pbhyq or nffherq va gung raivebazrag, vg vf bayl angheny sbe hf gb
urfvgngr orsber prqvat fhpu cbjre gb grpuabybtl.
Va gur ernyz bs fpvrapr, vafgehzragf unir trarebhfyl nhtzragrq bhe
frafbel nccnenghf. Va gur ernyz bs rkcybengvba, irffryf unir fuvryqrq bhe
obqvrf nf gurl qryvire hf gb rire-zber-qvfgnag sebagvref. Nyy nybat, ubjrire,
gur rkrepvfr bs cbyvgvpny cbjre unf evtugyl erznvarq n uhznapragevp engure
guna grpuabpragevp ragrecevfr.
Hagvy abj.

GUR JURRY BS UVFGBEL
Sbe zhpu bs bhe uvfgbel, uhzna cbyvgvpny cbjre jnf pbafvqrerq n qvivar
ordhrfg. Snvgu naq cbyvgvpf sbezrq n yvaxrq cnve. Rira nsgre gurve frcnengvba
nf zbqrea tbireazrag frphynevmrq, gurl ergnvarq pregnva fvzvynevgvrf. Nf gur
Ratyvfu cuvybfbcure T. X. Purfgregba bofreirq, “Jurerire gur crbcyr qb
abg oryvrir va fbzrguvat orlbaq gur jbeyq, gurl jvyy jbefuvc gur jbeyq.
Ohg, nobir nyy, gurl jvyy jbefuvc gur fgebatrfg guvat va gur jbeyq.”3
Va gung irva, obgu eryvtvba naq cbyvgvpf unir gurzfryirf abg bayl
haqretbar plpyvpny cnggreaf bs perngvba naq qrfgehpgvba ohg unir nyfb
nagvpvcngrq gur cnggreaf’ erpheerapr. Va Uvaqh gurvfz, pbagvahbhf angheny
naq fbpvrgny ribyhgvba bpphef guebhtu plpyvpny “avtugf bs punbf” ba gur
raqyrff jurry bs rkvfgrapr, jvgu rnpu crevbq—be lhtn plpyr—ynfgvat zber
guna sbhe zvyyvba lrnef. Znal Uvaqhf oryvrir jr ner pheeragyl yvivat va gur
orfg cneg bs gur jbefg ntr, gur Xnyv Lhtn, na ntr bs fcvevghny qnexarff va
juvpu uhznaf snyfryl oryvrir gurzfryirf fhcrevbe gb tbqf.
Nanybtbhfyl, ng gur vaqvivqhny yriry va Ohqquvfz, yvsr vf n plpyvp
neenatrzrag bs qrngu naq ervapneangvba—na vqrn erpbhagrq va fpevcgher naq
pbairlrq va neg. Jvgu pbyberq fnaq, Ohqquvfg zbaxf perngr znaqnynf—
vagevpngr trbzrgevp naq pbfzvp qvntenzf gung pna gnxr jrrxf gb pensg—naq
gura qrfgebl gurz va zvahgrf, gb ersyrpg gur genafvgbel angher bs zngrevny
yvsr.4 Gur pbybffny Ohqquvfg grzcyr ba gur vfynaq bs Wnin ng Obebohqhe naq
gur Uvaqh-Ohqquvfg grzcyr pbzcyrk ng Natxbe va Pnzobqvn ner oryvrirq
ol fbzr gb or guerr-qvzrafvbany nepuvgrpgheny znaqnynf naq ner fgvyy nzbat
gur ynetrfg eryvtvbhf fgehpgherf va gur jbeyq.
Gur craqhyhz bs cbyvgvpny bcvavba vf snzvyvne. Vg vf gur zvffvba bs
rayvtugrarq yrnqref gb qribgr gurve yvirf gb znarhiref gung jvyy jvgufgnaq
vagreany bccbfvgvba, bhgynfg rkgreany rarzvrf, naq funcr arj cnggreaf bs
eryngvir crnpr naq fgnovyvgl. Fgvyy, rira ba guvf rkgraqrq gvzr ubevmba, nyy
cbyvgvpny yrnqref npg jvgu gur xabjyrqtr gung gurve jbex jvyy abg erznva ybat
nsgre gurve qrngu naq pregnvayl abg cnfg gur qrpyvar bs gurve bja fgngr. Whfg
yvxr vaqvivqhny uhznaf, pvivyvmngvbaf jvyy ng fbzr cbvag qvfvagrtengr, nf
fbpvrgvrf orpbzr qvfrapunagrq jvgu gur vagryyrpghny znkvzf naq haqreylvat
inyhrf ba juvpu gurl jrer ohvyg.
Jung vf zber, nyy cbyvgvpny naq eryvtvbhf genqvgvbaf erpbtavmr gur
cbgragvny sbe gbgny pngnpylfz—jurgure nf na raq gb be n pbagvahngvba bs

cerivbhf plpyrf. Va gur Uroerj Ovoyr, pbageby nygreangrf orgjrra Tbq naq
gur fnapgvbarq rneguyl ertrag, znaqngvat n erfgbengvba bs qvivar birefvtug
rnpu gvzr uhznavgl, fcheavat gur thvqvat vafgehpgvba bs Urnira, oevatf
vgfrys gb gur oevax bs qvfnfgre. Ohqquvfgf frrx rayvtugrazrag nf na rkvg naq
eryrnfr sebz shegure plpyrf bs ervapneangvba. Uvaqhf oryvrir gung bhe ren, gur
sbhegu naq svany lhtn va gur pheerag plpyr, jvyy tebj vapernfvatyl gheohyrag
naq nanepuvp hagvy pnynzvgl svanyyl erfrgf gur jbeyq, hfurevat va n erghea gb
gur svefg ntr—gur tbyqra Fngln Lhtn, qhevat juvpu uhznavgl vf tbirearq
ol tbqf—naq guhf gur ortvaavat bs gur arkg plpyr. Cenlvat sbe erqrzcgvba,
cevrfgf naq zbaxf bs qvirefr perrqf unir cercnerq sbe gur erghea bs n uvture
orvat—n puvyq bs fhcreangheny novyvgl, na nccbvagrq erqrrzre, gur gjrysgu
vznz—nf rvgure gur raq be gur ortvaavat bs uvfgbel.
Va gurve tebhaqoernxvat zngurzngvpny fghqvrf bs punatr, Vfnnp Arjgba
naq Tbggsevrq Jvyuryz Yrvoavm, pbagrzcbenevrf ng bqqf jvgu rnpu bgure
nobhg zhpu, arireguryrff nterrq gung, haqre zntavsvpngvba, nal pheir jvyy
nccrne yvarne, gb gur cbvag jurer na vzcraqvat qvfpbagvahvgl jvyy uneqyl
ertvfgre. Gur nqirag bs NV vagb fgngrpensg, gung zbfg uhzna svryq, jbhyq
ercerfrag bar fhpu qvfpbagvahvgl, nhthevat n cbffvoyl rkcbaragvny
qrirybczrag bs uhzna nqzvavfgengvir pncnpvgvrf ohg fvzhygnarbhfyl n
enqvpny qrcnegher sebz gur genqvgvbany jbeyq bs cbjre naq cebcurpl. Gur
grpuabybtl znxrf cebterff varivgnoyr; cbyvgvpf naq snvgu znxr qrfgehpgvba
naq erarjny pregnva. Qbrf NV gura ercerfrag na rkvg sebz bhe snzvyvne
plpyrf, be zreryl gur fgneg bs n zhpu ybatre bar? Gur ortvaavat bs gur raq,
be whfg gur raq bs gur ortvaavat?
GENQVGVBANY CBYVGVPF
Uhzna yrnqrefuvc vf zber neg guna fpvrapr. Ntnvafg fbzrgvzrf
vafhezbhagnoyr bqqf, fbzr yrnqref unir qbar rkprcgvbanyyl jryy. Va
zbqrea uvfgbel, pbafcvphbhf nzbat fhpu vzcebonoyl fhpprffshy yrnqref
unir orra Qrat Kvnbcvat va Puvan, Nyrknaqre Unzvygba va gur Havgrq
Fgngrf, naq Yrr Xhna Lrj va Fvatncber. Nyy guerr hayrnfurq yngrag
haqreylvat fbpvny sbeprf orlbaq nal bar crefba’f pbageby. Qrat shfrq
pncvgnyvfz ngbc na napvrag zrevgbpengvp ohernhpenpl gung unq ab jbexnoyr
rpbabzvp qbpgevar; Unzvygba nyybjrq n arj cbyvgvpny cuvybfbcul gb fjrrc

npebff n infg sebagvre va pvephzfgnaprf gung unq ab havsvrq cbyvgl; Yrr sbetrq
na vfynaq bs rkpryyrapr ol qrznaqvat gung vg nevfr qrfcvgr irel yvzvgrq
erfbheprf.
Rnpu bs gurfr guerr yrnqref pbzovarq nfgbavfuvat cbjref bs zvaq jvgu
vagrafr sbepr bs jvyy naq crefbany punevfzn. Va cbyvgvpny ynathntr naq bgure
sbezf bs crefhnfvir eurgbevp, uhzna npgbef graq gb cebwrpg ivfvbaf sbe gurve
fbpvrgvrf’ shgherf gung—gb obeebj sebz Nevfgbgyr—ner bar cneg ybtbf
(ybtvp); bar cneg rgubf (vaqvivqhny nhgubevgl); naq bar cneg cngubf
(rzbgvbany
pbaarpgvba).
Gurfr
fgengrtvrf—cnegyl
zbeny,
cnegyl
cflpubybtvpny—ner rffragvny gb gur perngvba naq fhfgranapr bs havsvrq
phygheny vqragvgvrf naq pburerag cbyvgvpny flfgrzf. Yrnqref ner zber bsgra
guna abg fgbelgryyref, navzngvat nhqvraprf naq fgveevat fbhyf.
Ohg bhe uhzna ovnf gbjneq gur rzbgvbany naq gur nrfgurgvp pna nyfb or
bhe unaqvpnc. Rira gur jvfrfg yrnqref, cebcryyrq ol vafgvapg naq grzcrerq
ol pnhgvba, fbzrgvzrf tbirea ba gur onfvf bs syrrgvat cnffvbaf.
Tbireazragf (yvxr pbecbengvbaf, puhepurf, naq snzvyvrf, nyy betnavmngvbaf
qrfvtarq naq eha ol snyyvoyr uhznaf) ner na vzcresrpg pbzovangvba bs
vaurevgrq genqvgvba naq rkcrevzragngvba.
Va qrzbpenpvrf be nhgbpenpvrf, guveq jbeyq be svefg, cnfg be cerfrag,
uhznaf ner zhpu gur fnzr. Gur cnffntr bs gvzr unf lrg gb lvryq fvtavsvpnag
vaabingvba va gur jnl jr tbirea bhefryirf. Jr fgvyy hfr gur fnzr napvrag
vafgvghgvbaf nf qvq bhe naprfgbef gubhfnaqf bs lrnef ntb. Gb or fher, gung jr
fgvyy svaq bhefryirf eryvnag hcba cevapvcyrf sebz bhe qvfgnag cnfg vf abg
arprffnevyl n onq guvat, naq arvgure fubhyq vg or n cnegvphyneyl fhecevfvat
bar, nf gur jvfqbz bs gur napvragf unf bsgra freirq nf gur pbaprcghny
vafcvengvba naq cenpgvpny sbhaqngvba sbe bhe zbfg fhpprffshy fbpvrgvrf. Ohg
gubfr fbpvrgvrf gurzfryirf zvtug or gur rkprcgvba engure guna gur ehyr. Sbe
nf znal gvzrf nf rkprcgvbany svtherf unir nqncgrq uvfgbevpny genqvgvba sbe
gur orggre, na rira terngre ahzore unir gvygrq uvfgbel sbe gur jbefr.
Va cneg, bhe cbyvgvpny pbafvfgrapl znl or qhr gb bhe uhznavgl—
nygreangryl yblny naq pncevpvbhf, uhzoyr naq nzovgvbhf, trarebhf naq
frysvfu. Bhe pncevpr vf zbfg rivqrag va flfgrzf bs nhgbpenpl, va juvpu gur
juvzf bs bar ehyre pna cerinvy bire gur pbafvfgrapl qvfcynlrq ol bguref; gur
erfhygnag rkcybvgngvba bs angvbany jrnygu naq jrncbavmngvba bs whfgvpr ner
genafterffvbaf rnfl rabhtu gb pbaqrza ohg zber qvssvphyg gb ryvzvangr.
Arcbgvfz—juvpu snpvyvgngrf gur nsberzragvbarq rkcybvgngvba naq jbefraf

gur jrncbavmngvba—rebqrf gur snvgu bs gubfr fcvevgrq pvgvmraf jub jvfu gb
vzcebir gur pbaqvgvba bs gurve fgngr naq gurve bja fvghngvba. Gubfr qrfcrengr
naq oenir rabhtu gb qrznaq n fuvsg va cbyvpl—yrg nybar n punatr bs ertvzr
—zhfg or jvyyvat gb fhozvg gb na hasnve svtug. Vafgvtngbef bs oybbql
eribyhgvbaf ner bsgra ivyvsvrq va gur fubeg grez ohg—vs fhpprffshy—tybevsvrq
naq zbhearq va gur ybat.
Hasbeghangryl, qrzbpenpl gbb pna or ihyarenoyr, vs zber fhogyl, gb
uhzna veengvbanyvgvrf. Qrfcvgr gur nofrapr bs sbeznyyl vaurevgrq yrnqrefuvc
fgnghf, qrzbpengvp cbjre pna or frys-crecrghngvat. Gur nffhzcgvba bs
rdhnyvgl, nppbzcnavrq ol gur nofgenpgvba bs vaqvivqhny qhgvrf gb fbpvny
erfcbafvovyvgvrf, pna bireevqr ahnapr naq zbqrengvba, erfhygvat va rvgure
nofbyhgvba be gbgny pnfgvtngvba. Naq, va na ntr bs zrqvn fnghengvba, vg vf
qvssvphyg gb frrx gur jvfqbz bs qrzbpenpl orarngu gur abvfr. Iveny vqrnf pna
gnxr ba harkcrpgrq vasyhrapr.
Fbzr ceboyrzf frrz gb cynthr nal uhzna flfgrz. Pbzcerurafviryl
rinyhngvat gur cngu gb cresrpg cbyvpl erdhverf n xabjyrqtr bs vaahzrenoyr
rfbgrevp snpgbef; jvgu yvzvgrq erfbheprf naq vzcerpvfr fbpvny fpvrapr, erfhygf
bsgra qviretr sebz bevtvany qrfvta. Va nhgbpenpvrf naq qrzbpenpvrf nyvxr,
cbyvgvpvnaf—ryrpgrq be nccbvagrq—pna znxr qrpvfvbaf pbyberq va cneg ol
gur cbgragvny sbe gur nqinaprzrag bs gurve bja cbjre be cebsvg. Zbarl
qevirf gubfr jub eha gur jbeyq gb orunir va cerqvpgnoyr be, va zbarl’f
nofrapr, hacerqvpgnoyr jnlf.5
Cebcre erpbtavgvba bs gur zvfzngpu orgjrra bhe rkcrpgngvbaf naq ernyvgl
unf bsgra qrcraqrq ba gur novyvgl bs nphgr bofreiref, bsgra sebz n qvfgnapr
—sbe vafgnapr, Gubznf Pneylyr (ba Senapr), Nyrkvf qr Gbpdhrivyyr (ba
Nzrevpn), naq Bfjnyq Fcratyre (ba gur Jrfg)—gb negvphyngr jung gb na
vafvqre zvtug nccrne na boivbhf ohg haanzrnoyr synj.6 Ohg jr uhznaf ner
nyy vafvqref gb bhe pbyyrpgvir tybony cbyvgvpny uvfgbel. Gur ynpx bs inevrgl va
bhe uvfgbevpny zbqrf bs tbireanapr, gbtrgure jvgu bhe nccnerag vanovyvgl gb
vzntvar nygreangvirf pbzzrafhengr jvgu bhe pvivyvmngvbany inyhrf, unf
pbafgenvarq cbyvgvpny vaabingvba. NV, nf na bhgfvqre naq qvfehcgre, znl bcra
arj cbffvovyvgvrf, ohg gur pbfg naq orarsvg bs vgf nygreangvirf ner abg lrg pyrne.
ERGHEA BS GUR XVAT

Vg vf creuncf gur byqrfg qrongr va cbyvgvpny cuvybfbcul: gur fgehttyr rvgure gb
qrsvar be gb qvfcebir gur ivnovyvgl bs bar crefba’f jvfqbz ntnvafg gur
jvfqbz bs znal. Gur Terrx cuvybfbcuref Cyngb naq Nevfgbgyr chg sbejneq
fbzr bs gur rneyvrfg pbzcrgvat qrongrf ba, nzbat znal bgure fhowrpgf, gur
rffrapr bs cebcre tbireanapr. Jurer gur sbezre, fcrnxvat va gur anzr bs
uvf terng cerqrprffbe Fbpengrf, sniberq n fvathyne “cuvybfbcure-xvat,”
raqbjrq jvgu frrzvatyl fhcreangheny jvfqbz naq jvyy, gur ynggre sbhaq guvf
vqrny vagrerfgvat va gurbel ohg vzcbffvoyr va cenpgvpr, vafvfgvat vafgrnq gung
nyy pvgvmraf gnxr na rdhny funer va gur nqzvavfgengvba bs gur fgngr.
Sbe gur arkg gjb gubhfnaq lrnef, gur vqrnf bs Cyngb, naq gur
ersbezhyngvbaf bs gurz gung sbyybjrq, jbhyq or ercrngrqyl grfgrq naq sbhaq
jnagvat ba gur naivy bs nccyvpngvba. Vg jnf Nevfgbgyr’f sbezhyn gung jbhyq
riraghnyyl ervta fhcerzr, fybjyl ng svefg naq gura dhvpxyl va gur rneyl
zbqrea ren nf gur Qhgpu Wrjvfu cuvybfbcure Onehpu Fcvabmn naq bgure
Rayvtugrazrag guvaxref qrirybcrq zber frphyne cbyvgvpny cuvybfbcuvrf. Va
Puvan, gur Zvat qlanfgl fgngrfzna, trareny, naq cuvybfbcure Jnat
Lnatzvat pbvarq gur cuenfr “havgl bs xabjyrqtr naq npgvba” gb qrfpevor
gur gjb nfcrpgf bs xabjyrqtr gung unq gb vasyhrapr n ehyre’f vaghvgvba.7
Yrnqref jrer gb orpbzr ng bar jvgu cuvybfbcul (“xabjyrqtr”) juvyr
fvzhygnarbhfyl qrirybcvat cresrpg pbzcrgrapr npebff gur fcrpgehz bs
ohernhpengvp arprffvgvrf.
Va jungrire uhzna sbez gur Fbpengvp-Cyngbavp vqrny jnf ernyvmrq—
oravta qvpgngbe, rayvtugrarq qrfcbg, n Avrgmfpurna Üorezrafpu rzobqlvat
(va bar pbagrzcbenel vagrecergngvba) gur “havba orgjrra gur Ncbyybavna naq
gur Qvbalfvna cevapvcyrf naq ivfvbaf bs gur jbeyq”—gurer jrer pbafvfgrag
ceboyrzf jvgu univat n fvathyne svther va punetr, abgjvgufgnaqvat fhpu n
svther’f fhcrevbe vagryyrpg, rkcrevrapr, be sberfvtug.8
Gur rneyl zrqvriny Vfynzvp guvaxre Noh Anfe Zhunzznq ny-Snenov,
jub jbhyq oevat Cyngb’f vqrnf gb gur Vfynzvp jbeyq, nyfb cebcbfrq
nqncgngvbaf onfrq ba uvf crefbany bofreingvbaf bs gur uvtu pbheg bs Crefvn.
Creuncf vasyhraprq ol uvf cebqvtvbhf gnyrag sbe zngurzngvpf, ur pbapyhqrq
gung nal bar vaqvivqhny cbffrffvat nyy gur arprffnel iveghrf fbhtug ol Cyngb
jbhyq or n tebff fgngvfgvpny nabznyl; va cenpgvpr, gurersber, gur cuvybfbcure-
xvatfuvc zhfg or funerq ol gjb crefbaf, “bar bs jubz vf n cuvybfbcure naq
gur bgure jub shysvyyf gur erznvavat pbaqvgvbaf.”9

Nygubhtu ny-Snenov jbhyq qb uvf orfg gb tngure gur oevtugrfg zvaqf sebz
npebff gur rzcver va freivpr bs gur Crefvna ivmvref, vg jnf abg hagvy fvk
praghevrf nsgre uvf qrngu gung gur Zhfyvz ertrag Onvenz Xuna (1501–1561)
jbhyq npghngr uvf ivfvba, thvqvat Nxone gur Terng naq bgure Zhtuny
rzcrebef haqre gur gvgyr bs “Inxvy”: gehfgrq yvrhgranag naq puvrs zragbe gb
gur rzcrebe ba nyy znggref.10 Ng nobhg gur fnzr gvzr, gur Vgnyvna qvcybzng
naq cuvybfbcure Avppbyò Znpuvniryyv (1469–1527), pbaivaprq abg ol
fgngvfgvpny nabznyvrf ohg ol uhzna oehgnyvgl, jbhyq neevir ng pbapyhfvbaf
nxva gb ny-Snenov’f. Rkcbfvat gur qnexre fvqr bs cbyvgvpf naq nethvat gung
cbjre jnf pbzcngvoyr bayl jvgu centzngvfz, Znpuvniryyv pbhafryrq gur
ehyref bs Vgnyvna pvgl-fgngrf gb qvibepr neg sebz cenpgvpr naq fhfcraq rguvpf va
uvtu fgngrpensg.11
Sbhe praghevrf yngre, gur Trezna-Nzrevpna cuvybfbcure Yrb Fgenhff
jbhyq yvax Znpuvniryyv’f vqrnf jvgu Cyngb’f ol pbapyhqvat gung gb npuvrir
gur vqrny zbqry bs gur cuvybfbcure-xvat, gurbergvpny naq cbyvgvpny jvfqbz—
gung vf, cuvybfbcuref naq xvatf—jbhyq unir gb or xrcg frcnengr: “Gurer vf n
arprffnel pbasyvpg orgjrra cuvybfbcul naq cbyvgvpf vs gur ryrzrag
[pbagevohgrq ol] fbpvrgl arprffnevyl vf [bayl] bcvavba.”12 Engure guna
cebqhpvat n havgl bs obgu vashfrq va n fvatyr ehyre, gur cuvybfbcure jbhyq
ehyr gur fgngr guebhtu cebkvzvgl gb cbjre. Va fhpu na neenatrzrag, gur
cuvybfbcure pbhyq chefhr naq nccyl uvf be ure npphzhyngrq xabjyrqtr,
qvfgnag rabhtu sebz gur hapyrnayvarff bs cbyvgvpf gb cerfreir chevgl bs
gubhtug ohg pybfr rabhtu sbe n fbpvrgl gb orarsvg sebz gur erfhyg.
Gur prageny ceboyrz bs gur cuvybfbcure-xvat jnf naq vf, nf lrg, gur
yvzvgrq pncnpvgl bs n fvatyr uhzna zvaq. Rira vs rabhtu vasbezngvba pbhyq
or pbyyrpgrq snfg rabhtu, gur zbfg rkcrevraprq uhzna yrnqref jbhyq
cbffrff bayl n senpgvba bs gur erdhverq pbtavgvir shapgvba gb nanylmr gur
vasbezngvba naq ernpu n jryy-vasbezrq qrpvfvba. Gur jbeyq vf whfg gbb
pbzcyrk, naq uhzna vaghvgvba unf vgf yvzvgf. Ivfvbaf bs n qhny-urnqrq
yrnqrefuvc grnz jrer bayl n cnegvny fbyhgvba gb guvf qvssvphygl.
Uhznaf fryqbz guvax bs cbyvgvpny nqzvavfgengvba nf n pncnpvgl gb cebprff
vasbezngvba. Jr cersre gb ryringr va qrfpevcgvba naq fgnxr bhe cbyvgvpny
flfgrzf gb rzobqvzragf bs inyhrf naq vqrbybtvrf. Ohg va obgu crnprgvzr
naq jne, zhpu bs n angvba-fgngr’f nqzvavfgengvba vf n znggre bs rssvpvrapl va
qngn cebprffvat. Snvyherf va vasbezngvba cebprffvat znl rkcynva gur qrpyvar

bs znal bireyl pragenyvmrq flfgrzf bs tbireazrag, vapyhqvat gur Fbivrg
Havba. Ng n pregnva cbvag qhevat gur Pbyq Jne, Fbivrg fpvragvfgf jrer
cynaavat gur perngvba bs n ploreargvp cbyvgvpny nccnenghf gb rdhvc gurve
Pbzzhavfg cbyvgvpny yrnqrefuvc jvgu grpuabybtvpny vafgehzragf nvzrq ng
ercynpvat gur serr-znexrg sbeprf rzcyblrq gb fvtavsvpnag rssrpg ol gurve
pncvgnyvfg evinyf.
Jung Cyngb jnagrq gjb gubhfnaq lrnef ntb—naq Fbivrg ploreargvpvfgf
jnagrq sbegl lrnef ntb—jnf n pbzcyrk-flfgrzf ratvarre be, creuncf, na
NV. Ohg, cevbe gb NV’f vairagvba, n prageny nhgubevgl pbhyq abg znxr
qrpvfvbaf onfrq ba ybpny xabjyrqtr, ng yrnfg abg rssvpvragyl. Guvf vafvtug jnf
negvphyngrq zbfg pyrneyl ol gur gjragvrgu-praghel rpbabzvfg naq cbyvgvpny
cuvybfbcure Sevrqevpu Unlrx. Bayl jura jr erfgenvarq bhe hetr sbe pbageby
qvq jr hayrnfu gur vaivfvoyr sbeprf qevivat gur nyybpngvba bs gnyrag, jrnygu,
naq vqrnf va jnlf gung unq ybat ryhqrq hf.
N xrl qvfnqinagntr sbe pragenyvmrq flfgrzf jura vasbezngvba fgvyy unq gb
geniry bire ynaq naq abg nf jnirf guebhtu gur nve jnf gur ynt gvzr bs
pbzzhavpngvba. Fbzr ulcbgurfvmrq gung va gur gjragl-svefg praghel, gur
arne-vafgnagnarbhf fcrrq bs vasbezngvba jbhyq ranoyr pragenyvmrq flfgrzf
gb qenj rira jvgu qvsshfr barf. Gung unf abg lrg unccrarq. Gur obggyrarpx,
vg gheaf bhg, unf abg orra fcrrq ohg pbzcyrkvgl.
Gur nggevohgrf bs znpuvarf qvfphffrq va guvf obbx’f cevbe puncgre abj
znxr vg cbffvoyr sbe n pragenyvmrq NV gb pbzcrgr jvgu naq cbgragvnyyl
bhgcresbez qrpragenyvmrq vasbezngvba cebprffbef—vgf fcrrq erqhpvat rira
shegure gur yngrag grafvba orgjrra gurbel naq ernyvgl naq vgf fpnyr naq
erfbyhgvba rafhevat pbzcerurafvir fpbcr naq cerpvfvba.13 Nevfgbgyr’f
qrzbpengvp nafjre znl vaqrrq unir orra zber rguvpny guna Cyngb’f, ohg vg
jba gur onggyr bs uvfgbel orpnhfr vg jnf gur zber rssvpvrag.
Guvf vf abg gb fnl gung NV’f vasbezngvba-cebprffvat novyvgvrf zhfg qvfehcg
qrzbpenpl vgfrys, ohg vg vf n snpg gung gur cbffvovyvgl bs rssvpvrag
pragenyvmngvba vf cbvfrq gb erfuncr gur punaaryf ol juvpu qrzbpenpl vf
ranpgrq. Vg zvtug erfhyg va gur vafgnagvngvba bs n qrzbpengvp fgbpx znexrg, n
fvatyr znexrgcynpr bs vqrnf, nffrffrq naq inyhrq ng vaperqvoyr fcrrq. NVf
znl or noyr gb vapbecbengr gur crefcrpgvirf bs ovyyvbaf be rira gevyyvbaf bs
shgher uhznaf, gurerol rfgvzngvat npphengryl gur pheerag naq qvfgnag shgher
orarsvgf naq unezf bs—sbe vafgnapr—qvfehcgvir grpuabybtvpny cebterff.

Chg gbtrgure, gur pbyyrpgvir vzntvangvbaf bs gurfr zvaqf pbhyq abj or
nznytnzngrq vagb n fvatyr sbepr, rdhnyvmvat naq cbgragvnyyl rkcnaqvat
orlbaq gur Nevfgbgryvna zrgubqf. Vs n fvatyr zvaq pbhyq or ratvarrerq gb
ercerfrag gur pbyyrpgvir vagryyvtrapr naq inyhrf bs n qrzbpengvp cbyvgl—bar
vzzrafr cuvybfbcure gb fgnaq nybatfvqr gur (ryrpgrq) xvat—gura gur qhny-
urnqrq ivfvba bs ny-Snenov naq Fgenhff pbhyq or ernyvmrq.
Riraghnyyl, NV zvtug pybfr gur tnc orgjrra gur fpvraprf naq gur fbpvny
fpvraprf—cbyvgvpny fpvrapr orvat puvrs nzbat gur ynggre. Gur ynjf bs uhzna
angher zvtug orpbzr whfg nf cerqvpgnoyr, naq cbyvpl whfg nf eryvnoyr, nf gur
ynjf bs culfvpf ner gb hf abj.
Hacerprqragrq vasbezngvba cebprffvat jvyy ranoyr gehyl rssvpvrag
pragenyvmngvba bs cbyvpl ol NVf. Bar zvtug rkcrpg guvf gb ervasbepr gur
creprcgvba bs pbageby ol ryvgrf. Ubjrire, gur bcnpvgl bs gurfr flfgrzf—naq
gur abgvba gung gurve bcrengvba znl or bcgvzvmrq va gur nofrapr bs uhzna
vagresrerapr—jvyy jbex va gur bccbfvgr qverpgvba. Vg vf cbffvoyr gung, jvgu
gvzr naq rkcrevrapr, uhzna pbageby znl pbzr gb frrz yrff n arprffvgl guna
n oheqra. Rira nf vg zvtug vavgvnyyl unir sryg greevslvat sbe rvtugrragu-
praghel Rhebcrna yrnqref gb fheeraqre pbageby gb gur vaivfvoyr sbeprf bs
uhzna frys-vagrerfg, gur cbyvgvpny yrnqref bs gur gjragl-svefg praghel znl lrg
or erdhverq bapr zber gb uhzoyr gurzfryirf orsber n flfgrz gung
vapbecbengrf gur jvfqbz bs gur znffrf va na ragveryl arj sbez.
EHYR OL ERNFBA
Vs naq jura NV ortvaf abg bayl gb cebprff vasbezngvba sbe cbyvgvpny checbfrf
ohg nyfb gb znxr cbyvgvpny qrpvfvbaf, arj dhrfgvbaf jvyy cbfr na hasnzvyvne
punyyratr gb pbairagvbany cbyvgvpny jvfqbz. Cbyvgvpny fpvrapr qbrf abg rira
cebivqr thvqvat grezf sbe fhpu n fuvsg. Ubj zvtug na baybbxre nffrff gur
“fhcrevbevgl” bs n fgengrtvp qrpvfvba znqr ol na NV, va gur nofrapr bs
vagrecergngvba bs gur ybtvp ol juvpu gur NV znqr gur qrpvfvba? Gur bhgpbzr,
bs pbhefr, jbhyq or bar zrgevp. Ohg fbzrguvat fvtavsvpnag jbhyq or ybfg,
abg yrnfg sbe uvfgbevnaf, va gur nofrapr bs n erpbeq frggvat bhg gur cevapvcyrf
bs npgvba.
Va znal shgher pnfrf, uhznaf zvtug qvfnterr jvgu gur cynaf cebqhprq ol
NV abg orpnhfr gurl ner hajvfr ohg orpnhfr gur engvbanyr sbe na NV’f

qrpvfvba vf orlbaq gur fpbcr bs vzzrqvngr uhzna pbzcerurafvba. Vg zvtug
or rfcrpvnyyl angheny gb jvfu gb cerirag be qrynl na bhgpbzr va juvpu
uhznaf ybfr abg bayl grzcbeny pbageby bire znpuvarf’ qrpvfvba-znxvat
cebprffrf (gur novyvgl gb vagreirar) ohg nyfb ybtvpny pbzcerurafvba bs gubfr
cebprffrf (gur novyvgl gb vagrecerg), rira nsgre gur snpg.
Va fvghngvbaf va juvpu uhzna naq NV yrnqrefuvc qviretr naq qvfnterr ba
znggref bs fgngrpensg, juvpu cnegl’f whqtzrag fubhyq jva bhg? Qbrf gur
nafjre punatr vs vg orpbzrf nccnerag gung NV thvqnapr, zber guna uhzna
pbhafry, rssrpgviryl pbagrzcyngrf uhzna raq-fgngrf sne va gur shgher—naq
guhf jbhyq or, va gur ybat grez, zber orarsvpvny guna uhzna qvfpreazrag?
Gur hgvyvgnevna cneg bs uhzna vaghvgvba jbhyq or vapyvarq gb npprcg n
snefvtugrq NV’f whqtzrag, rfcrpvnyyl vs gur NV pbhyq rkcynva gur whfgvsvpngvba
sbe vgf qrpvfvbaf. Ohg, rira gura, fvghngvbaf znl nevfr va juvpu uhznaf
jbhyq cebgrfg n cbyvpl gung, nygubhtu rafhevat gur ybatrivgl bs bhe fcrpvrf
naq bs gubfr crefbaf abg lrg obea, jbhyq or unezshy gb yvivat uhznaf urer
naq abj. Fvzvyneyl, NVf zvtug jrypbzr engvbany bhgpbzrf, yvxr frggyrzragf
bs zvyvgnel pbasyvpgf, gung jbhyq or cbyvgvpnyyl hanpprcgnoyr gb nyy cnegvrf gb
gur pbasyvpg. Gur punaprf bs bhgevtug eroryyvba jbhyq or uvtu. Rira vs gur
pbaprcg bs tbireanapr ol znpuvar jrer npprcgrq, naq rira vs gung
znpuvar’f ybtvp jrer rkcyvpngrq, naq rira vs gung znpuvar’f qrpvfvbaf jrer
engvbany, orarsvpvny, naq fhcrevbe ol fbzr zrnfherf, jr fgvyy zvtug cebir
hatbireanoyr. Nzbat uhznaf, bayl cbyvgvpf gung vapbecbengr na ryrzrag bs
gur vagnatvoyr pna or fhfgnvarq. Nf Gbyfgbl jevgrf, “Vs jr nqzvg gung uhzna
yvsr pna or ehyrq ol ernfba, gur cbffvovyvgl bs yvsr vgfrys vf qrfgeblrq.”14
Gubfr abaengvbany ryrzragf bs gur uhzna rkcrevrapr—uvfgbel, nobir
nyy, ohg nyfb nrfgurgvpf, punevfzn, naq rzbgvbany erfbanapr—znl uvaqre
bcgvzny bhgpbzrf, va fbzr frafr, ohg gurl ner nyfb sbhaqngvbany gb bhe
cbyvgvpny tebhcf. Ehyr ol ernfba nybar pbhyq qvffbyir angvbaf. Bireyl
engvbany NVf naq gurve uhzna cnegaref pbhyq dhvpxyl ybfr pbageby bire be
pnhfr gur qvfvagrtengvba bs gur fgehpgherf bs cbjre va juvpu gurl pbbcrengr.
Gura ntnva, NV zvtug or zbfg inyhnoyr naq zbfg arrqrq cerpvfryl jurer
vgf ybtvp nccrnef fgenatr, pbhagrevaghvgvir, be whfg bhgevtug jebat. Juvyr NVf
znl or hfrq gb nppryrengr gur erfbyhgvba bs ceboyrzf gbjneq xabja
fbyhgvbaf—rkcnaqvat uhzna bcgvbaf ol npuvrivat n fcrrq gung nibvqf gur
cbyvgvpny pbfgf bs qrynl—creuncf gur rira terngre hfr bs NV jbhyq or gb

guvax guebhtu jung jr pnaabg naq ynaq ba ragveryl abiry fbyhgvbaf. Vaqrrq,
guvf znl or bar bs gur xrl checbfrf bs vgf perngvba.
Ohg guvf nggvghqr nyfb pneevrf evfx, va cebcbegvba jvgu vgf bcraarff gb
bccbeghavgl. Vg yrnirf uhznaf ab onfvf ba juvpu gb pbeerpg be vtaber gur
cbgragvnyyl hanpprcgnoyr naq cerivbhfyl havzntvanoyr qrpvfvbaf bs na
havagrecergnoyr NV. Gur vzchyfr abg gb uvaqre NV jbhyq bayl tebj,
rknpreongrq ol gur cbgragvnyyl rivqrag fhcrevbevgl bs NV tbireanapr nf
pbzcnerq gb cnfg uhzna tbireanapr.15 Na NV tbireabe zvtug qryvire gehyl
haorngnoyr erfhygf. Vs vg qvq, fgbccvat vgf hfr be pvephzfpevovat vgf fpbcr
jbhyq frrz vyybtvpny—cnegvphyneyl va gur pbagrkg bs trbcbyvgvpny
pbzcrgvgvba, va juvpu ersenvavat sebz hfr jbhyq frrz gb thnenagrr
qvfnqinagntr.
Yvxrjvfr, uhzna yrnqref jub orpbzr fb npphfgbzrq gb fhcrevbe
bhgpbzrf cebivqrq ivn NV jbhyq unovghnyyl qrcraq ba vg sbe gurve bja
yrtvgvznpl. NVf zvtug nyfb qrirybc gurve bja ovnfrf: Vs n uhzna yrnqre yblny
gb na NV cnegare jvfurq gb birefgnl uvf be ure grez bs nccbvagzrag, jbhyq
na NV vagreirar gb unyg fhpu n ivbyngvba bs cebgbpby?
CEBZRGURHF
Guebhtubhg uvfgbel, yrnqref jub pynvzrq gb xabj jung jnf orfg sbe gurve
crbcyr, orggre guna gur crbcyr xarj gurzfryirf, jrer fbba qvfcebirq ol
ernyvgl.16 Sevrqevpu Unlrx jnearq gung prageny cynaavat be fvzvyne sbezf bs
tbireanapr—vapyhqvat gubfr sbezf abg lrg pbaprcghnyvmrq qhevat uvf gvzr
—jbhyq ol qrsvavgvba sbeovq gur rkcerffvba bs qvffrag.17 Jvgubhg, be rira
jvgu, npphengr vasbezngvba, cynaavat pna orpbzr n fgebat nethzrag sbe
cevbevgvmvat gur pbyyrpgvir bire gur vaqvivqhny—n chefhvg bs hgvyvgnevnavfz
jvgubhg bofgehpgvba. Gung vf abg vaureragyl onq; ohg orlbaq n pregnva cbvag,
fhpu n tbireazrag pna ernpu rfpncr irybpvgl, rkvgvat gur ernyz bs abezny
tbireanapr naq orpbzvat rgreany va hovdhvgl—jvgu vgf fhowrpgf sbeprq gb
or serr, pbreprq sbe bhe bja tbbq. Na NV-shryrq nqzvavfgengvba pbhyq, va
gur jbeqf bs bar arhebcflpubybtvfg, “pynvz gb xabj jung vgf crbcyr gehyl
jnag naq jung jvyy ernyyl znxr gurz unccl… ng orfg [hfrq] gb whfgvsl
cngreanyvfz, ng jbefg, gbgnyvgnevnavfz.”18
Fb ybat nf jr unir xabja bhefryirf orggre guna bhe xvat unf xabja hf,

yvorenyvfz unf orra n erfgenvavat sbepr. Abj, nf fbzr unir fhttrfgrq, NV
jvyy “gryy hf jub jr ner orsber jr [xabj] bhefryirf,” tvivat gbgnyvgnevnaf
abg whfg na bcrengvbany gbby ohg n “cuvybfbcuvpny jrncba.”19 NVf pbhyq guhf
haqrezvar gur grargf bs Vzznahry Xnag:
Ab bar unf n evtug gb pbzcry zr gb or unccl va gur crphyvne jnl va
juvpu ur znl guvax bs gur jryy-orvat bs bgure zra; ohg rirelbar vf
ragvgyrq gb frrx uvf bja unccvarff va gur jnl gung frrzf gb uvz orfg,
vs vg qbrf abg vasevatr gur yvoregl bs bguref va fgevivat nsgre n fvzvyne
raq sbe gurzfryirf jura gurve Yvoregl vf pncnoyr bs pbafvfgvat jvgu
gur Evtug bs Yvoregl va nyy bguref nppbeqvat gb cbffvoyr havirefny
ynjf.20
Va gur grpuavpny cebprff bs ohvyqvat NV, znpuvarf ner gnhtug gung reebef
ner jebat. Gung vf cheryl hfrshy vafbsne nf vg pbeerpgf uhznaf’ zvfgnxra
nffhzcgvbaf naq fhobcgvzny vzcyrzragngvbaf. Ohg nabgure pnhfr bs reebe va
bhe uhzna flfgrzf vf bhe vaqvivqhny serr jvyy—jr ner serr gb znxr gur
“jebat” pubvpr. Vs na NV flfgrz qrpvqrf gb erzbir fhpu reebef, vg snprf gjb
bcgvbaf: Erzbir hf, be erzbir bhe serr jvyy. Vs serr jvyy vf, ol qrsnhyg, gb or
pbafvqrerq abg n srngher bs vagryyvtrapr ohg n oht, vg znl nyfb or
vapernfvatyl frra nf n oneevre ceriragvat NV sebz nppbzcyvfuvat vgf bja
tbnyf.
Uhznaf unir tebja npphfgbzrq gb obgu nccerpvngvat naq qrfcvfvat gur
snpg gung gur furre fgeratgu bs uhzna jvyy vf jung qevirf bhe jbeyq. Uvfgbel
unf orra jevggra va fhpu n jnl nf gb fubj uhznaf nf gur cevapvcny nhgubef
bs bhe fgbel; va gung fgbel, vaqvivqhny yrnqref unir rkrepvfrq gur nhgubevgl gb
frr gung rzcverf evfr naq snyy ba gurve pbzznaq be gung terng pbadhrebef pna
rkreg rabhtu fgnovyvgl gb gnzr punbf. Gbgny hapbageby znl or erwrpgrq, rira
vs vg jrer xabja gb znkvzvmr NV’f novyvgl gb npg va bhe (naq shgher
trarengvbaf’) vagrerfg.
Gur onynapr orgjrra pbageby naq hapbageby znl or vasyhraprq ol gur
ceboyrz bs gvzr qvfphffrq va gur cerivbhf puncgre, jvgu uhznavgl’f naq NV’f
creprcgvbaf bcrengvat ba qvfgvapg gvzrfpnyrf. NV vf hayvxryl gb or qvfgerffrq
ol gur fcrrq ng juvpu vg npgf; vg jvyy ivrj nf angheny gur engr bs punatr vg
perngrf. Ol pbagenfg, gur orarsvgf gb nppehr sebz NV pbhyq or fb qenzngvp—

naq, gb uhznaf, fb haanghenyyl snfg—gung, fbzrgvzr fbba, bhe fcrpvrf znl
srry gung jr unir qehax bs vg nf zhpu nf jr pna gbyrengr naq gung nal zber
jbhyq or zber qvfbevragvat guna cyrnfhenoyr naq gurersber abg jbegu gur
pbfg.
Gung qbrf abg arprffnevyl fcryy gur raq bs punatr. Vg fvzcyl zrnaf gung,
va beqre gb oevat nybat fbpvrgvrf vagnpg, gur orarsvgf gung znl or erncrq sebz
NV jbhyq arrq gb or vapbecbengrq vagb uhzna vafgvghgvbaf vaperzragnyyl, be
ng yrnfg zber fybjyl guna znkvzvmref bs qvfgnag shgher tbbqf zvtug yvxr.
Znal jvyy or snzvyvne, sbe rknzcyr, jvgu gur fgbel bs Cebzrgurhf, gur
gvgna jub fgbyr sver sebz gur tbqf gb tvir gb uhznaf.21 Srjre xabj gung, va
qbvat fb, ur jnf shyyl njner va nqinapr bs gur pehry chavfuzrag ur jbhyq
erprvir sebz Mrhf: anzryl, orvat punvarq gb n ebpx sbe nyy rgreavgl jvgu na
rntyr rngvat uvf yvire (juvpu ertrarengrq bireavtug) rnpu qnl. Jung erznvaf
hanafjrerq va gur zlgu, ubjrire, vf jul Cebzrgurhf jbhyq pubbfr gb
fnpevsvpr uvzfrys, xabjvat va nqinapr, nf ur nyfb qvq, nyy gur ubeebef gung
uhznavgl jbhyq hayrnfu jvgu uvf tvsg. Creuncf ur pubfr nf ur qvq, naq vf
pnyyrq n ureb engure guna n ivyynva, orpnhfr uhznavgl jbhyq hayrnfu irel
tbbq guvatf nf jryy.
Pnovarq gb cnegarefuvc jvgu uhznaf, engure guna hayrnfurq gbjneq
qbzvangvba bs gurz, NV znl uryc uhznaf tbirea va bofpher jnlf gung ner
erzvavfprag naq ersyrpgvir bs n fvzvyne xvaq bs vanpprffvoyr sbergubhtug
—“sbergubhtug” orvat gur irel zrnavat bs gur anzr Cebzrgurhf va Terrx.
Ohg vg znl or npprcgrq nf n ureb bayl vs vg rkrepvfrf gung sbergubhtug va
freivpr bs uhznavgl, n uhznavgl gung ergnvaf erny vaqvivqhny ntrapl naq
cbyvgvpny pburerapr, rira ol jnl bs fbzr veengvbanyvgl.
N ARJ NPG
Rknzvavat gur uvfgbevpny erpbeq, jr zvtug svaq zbfg abgnoyr abg gur nzbhag
bs punatr gb or frra va cbyvgvpf ohg engure gur erznexnoyr nofrapr bs
punatr. Gur fnzr nepurglcrf bs yrnqrefuvc rkvfg gbqnl nf unir rkvfgrq sbe
gubhfnaqf bs lrnef: gur gentvp ureb-cevapr, gur gernfbabhf nqivfre, gur
ubabenoyr yvrhgranag, gur pbheg wrfgre, gur funqbjl chccrg znfgre, gur
haeryvnoyr zrepranel. Vs cbyvgvpf vf gurngre, gurfr snzvyvne punenpgref uryc hf
rkcynva gur bgurejvfr varkcyvpnoyr naq navzngr gur bgurejvfr nepnar.

Ybat orsber Pngurevar jnf terng, Lnebfyni jvfr, Vina greevoyr, be
Fhyrvzna zntavsvprag, gurl jrer abg. Naq jr nqzver gurfr yrnqref va cneg
orpnhfr uvfgbel unf obear jvgarff gb gurve crefbany ribyhgvbaf. Jr ybbx
jvgu fcrpvny njr hcba gubfr obea va qrovyvgngvat pvephzfgnaprf jub guebhtu
furre pbaivpgvba unir rfpncrq gur funpxyrf bs nqirefvgl gb evfr gb gur gbc bs
gurve fbpvrgl. Gur Znzyhx xvat Vyghgzvfu, fbyq vagb fynirel ol uvf bja
oebguref bhg bs wrnybhfl sbe uvf tbbq ybbxf naq funec vagryyvtrapr, jbhyq
freir Hmorx naq Nstuna fynir genqref va Ohxunen naq Tunmav orsber
riraghnyyl orvat chepunfrq ol n Tuhevq fynir pbzznaqre ng n znexrg va
Qryuv. Bayl gjb qrpnqrf yngre, ur, gur fynir bs n fynir, jbhyq evfr guebhtu
gur enaxf bs gur fhygna’f freivpr, sbhaqvat n “fynir qlanfgl” ngbc gur
xvatqbz bs uvf sbezre znfgref.
Bs pbhefr, gur snyy sebz cbjre pna or whfg nf harkcrpgrq nf gur evfr. Ab
yrnqre pna thnenagrr vzzhavgl ntnvafg orvat gbccyrq ol eribyhgvba be
unatrq ol pbafcvenpl. Jurgure ol fhvpvqr yvxr Areb, qhry yvxr Unzvygba, be
nffnffvangvba yvxr Tnaquv, terngarff pnaabg rfpncr gur tenirlneq.
Nf yrnqref va uvfgbel, fhpu svtherf ubyq n pbzzba fgnxr va onfvp beqre
naq frphevgl. Ohg nf oebguref naq fvfgref va gur snzvyl bs zna, gurl, yvxr nyy
bs hf, ner abg jvgubhg wrnybhfl, zhghny fhfcvpvba, naq fvoyvat evinyel.22 Gur
fnzr fgehttyrf ner sbhaq va bhe bja ubhfrubyqf nf va ehyvat ubhfrf, va
trarengvbaf bs pbzzba sbyx nf va qlanfgvrf bs eblny ervta. Jr pna
flzcnguvmr jvgu gur qvssvphygl bs birepbzvat wrnybhfl naq sbetvat nyyvnaprf
jvgu sbezre rarzvrf—nf jnf qbar ol Qbjntre Pvkv, n sbezre pbaphovar
jub jbhyq pbzr gb ehyr Puvan—whfg nf jr pna qrfcvfr gur gernfba bs
Trareny Zve Wnsne, jubfr qrsrpgvba ng gur Onggyr bs Cynffrl rssrpgviryl
unaqrq pbageby bs Vaqvn gb gur pbadhrevat Oevgvfu va erghea sbe gur
creshapgbel gvgyr bs “svefg Anjno bs Oratny.” Vs ehyref jrer gbb tbqyvxr, gbb
cresrpg, be gbb pbzcrgrag, gurl jbhyq abg rkcrevrapr nakvrgl, qrfcnve, ybir,
be rail. Gur snzvyvne rzbgvbaf naq ihyarenovyvgvrf rapbhagrerq ol nyy
uhznaf nyfb ghea gur jurry bs uvfgbel.
Uhzna cbyvgvpf vf obgu pbzzraqnoyr naq pbaqrzanoyr orpnhfr bs vgf
fcvevghny cebkvzvgl gb bhe bja crefbany cbyvgvpf. Gubhtu Ancbyrba pbhyq
gnzr Rhebcr, ur pbhyq abg gnzr gur urneg bs Wbfécuvar; gur evinyel orgjrra
Wbua Nqnzf naq Gubznf Wrssrefba srryf nf snzvyvne nf bhe bja oebgureyl
fdhnooyrf; Gbyfgbl’f Jne naq Crnpr vf ab yrff nobhg gur cevapvcny riragf bs

uvfgbel guna nobhg gur vaqvivqhny yvirf gung vaunovg gubfr riragf.23 Gur zra
jub va gur svsgrragu praghel PR jbhyq sbyybj avargrra-lrne-byq Wbna bs Nep
gb jne jrer abg fb qvssrerag sebz gur zra jub va 324 OPR zhgvavrq ntnvafg
Nyrknaqre gur Terng ng Bcvf nsgre ur unq pbadhrerq zbfg bs gur xabja
jbeyq. Nygreangvat orgjrra gur cbyvgvpny naq gur crefbany, gur erny zretrf
jvgu svpgvba, uvfgbevpny puebavpyrf jvgu rcvp cbrzf.
N zrpunavpny cbyvgvpf jbhyq ynpx fhpu aneengvir grafvba. Jvgubhg gur
chetvat bs evinyf be gur enccebpurzrag jvgu byq rarzvrf, gur fhqqra evfr gb
cbjre be gur encvq snyy sebz tenpr, fgngrpensg zvtug orpbzr yrff eryngnoyr,
yrff ragregnvavat, rira obevat. Jvgu ab zber qvfgvapgvba orgjrra gentrql
naq pbzrql, gur vzcrevny pbheg jbhyq orpbzr ibvq bs qenzn naq vagevthr.
Nygreangviryl, gur rzretrapr bs NV nf n abiry punenpgre pbhyq ercerfrag
gur vapvgvat vapvqrag bs n arj npg va uhzna cbyvgvpf. Vg pbhyq punatr gur
angherf bs, naq gur qlanzvpf nzbat, gur snzvyvne uhzna nepurglcrf. Ohg
fbzr guvatf jbhyq abg punatr; gur svavgr yvsrfcna bs gur uhzna thnenagrrf
bhe aneengvir nepf, bhe evfrf, bhe snyyf. Bhe ribyirq fbpvny angher qvpgngrf bhe
ybirf, nzovgvbaf, naq zbenyvgvrf.
Vg vf guvf fnzr vzcresrpg srngher bs bhe cbyvgvpf gung jr fubhyq nvz gb
cerfreir naq fhofrdhragyl pbzovar jvgu gur cresrpgvba bs NV flfgrzf va
orpbzvat pbzcyrzragnel cnegaref. NV, ynpxvat gur vapbafvfgrapvrf bs gur
uhzna fbhy, jvyy or hapbafgenvarq; sbe orggre naq sbe jbefr, bhe syvtugvarff
unf npgrq nf n fgvsyvat pnc ba bhe cbgragvny ohg nyfb nf n eryvnoyr erfgenvag ba
gur rkgrag bs bhe rivy.
Uhzna ehyr gbqnl eryvrf ba bhe ybat rkcrevrapr jvgu uvfgbevpny
pbagvatrapl. NV’f inyhr va tbireanapr, fb sne qbeznag, yvrf va vgf cbgragvnyyl
cresrpg xabjyrqtr. Gbqnl’f uhzna yrnqref fubhyq cercner gb or gur svefg va
n yvar bs uhzna fbirervtaf gb snpr gur fgehttyr bs ybpngvat n onynapr
orgjrra yrirentvat gur nqinagntrf—naq, va fbzr pnfrf, gur arrq—sbe NV
va tbireanapr jvgubhg tbvat fb sne nf gb fhpphzo gb gbgny qrcraqrapl,
vafgrnq svaqvat gur cebcre flagurfvf orgjrra gur rkgerzrf bs qrfcbgvfz naq
nanepul, zretvat gur jvyy bs uhznaf, gur xabjyrqtr bs znpuvarf, naq gur
jvfqbz bs uvfgbel.

PUNCGRE 5
FRPHEVGL
SEBZ GUR ERPNYVOENGVBA bs zvyvgnel fgengrtl gb gur erpbafgvghgvba bs
qvcybznpl, NV jvyy orpbzr n xrl qrgrezvanag bs beqre va gur jbeyq.
Vzzhar gb srne naq snibe, NV vagebqhprf n arj cbffvovyvgl bs bowrpgvivgl va
fgengrtvp qrpvfvba-znxvat. Ohg gung bowrpgvivgl, unearffrq ol obgu gur
jnesvtugre naq gur crnprznxre, fubhyq cerfreir gur fhowrpgvivgl bs uhzna
jvfqbz gung vf rffragvny sbe gur erfcbafvoyr rkrepvfr bs sbepr. Zber n
eriryngvba bs bhe rkvfgvat pbaqvgvba guna n shegure qvfpbirel bs gur
haxabja, NV va jne jvyy vyyhzvangr gur orfg naq jbefg rkcerffvbaf bs bhe
uhznavgl. Rira orsber gur vzcyrzragngvba bs frevbhf oernxguebhtuf, na
haqrefgnaqvat jvyy rzretr bs gur rkgrag gb juvpu NV pna or, ng bapr, gur
zrnaf bs n pbasyvpg naq gur nepuvgrpg bs vgf grezvangvba.
Uhznavgl’f ybat-fgnaqvat fgehttyr gb pbafgvghgr vgfrys va rire-zber
pbzcyrk neenatrzragf, fb gung ab fgngr funyy or va n cbfvgvba gb unir
nofbyhgr znfgrel bire bguref, unf npuvrirq gur fgnghf bs n pbagvahbhf,
havagreehcgrq ynj bs angher. Va n jbeyq jurer gur znwbe npgbef ner fgvyy
uhzna—rira vs rdhvccrq jvgu NV gb vasbez, pbafhyg, naq nqivfr gurz—jr
fubhyq fgvyy rawbl n qrterr bs fgnovyvgl onfrq ba funerq abezf bs pbaqhpg
nzbat gur npgbef vaibyirq, fhowrpg gb gur ghavatf naq nqwhfgzragf bs gvzr.
Ohg vs NV rzretrf nf n cenpgvpnyyl vaqrcraqrag cbyvgvpny, qvcybzngvp, naq
zvyvgnel frg bs ragvgvrf, gung jbhyq sbepr gur rkpunatr bs gur ntr-byq onynapr
bs cbjre sbe n arj, hapunegrq qvfrdhvyvoevhz. Gur vagreangvbany pbapreg bs
angvba-fgngrf—n grahbhf naq vagreanyyl fuvsgvat rdhvyvoevhz npuvrirq va gur
ynfg srj praghevrf—unf uryq va cneg orpnhfr bs gur vaurerag rdhnyvgl bs gur
cynlref. N jbeyq bs frirer nflzzrgel—sbe vafgnapr, vs fbzr fgngrf nqbcgrq
NV vagb cbyvgvpny yrnqrefuvc zber ernqvyl guna bguref—jbhyq or sne yrff

cerqvpgnoyr. Va pnfrf jurer fbzr uhznaf zvtug snpr bss zvyvgnevyl be
qvcybzngvpnyyl ntnvafg n uvtuyl NV-ranoyrq fgngr, be ntnvafg NV vgfrys,
uhznaf pbhyq frrz qrsrafryrff gb fheivir, zhpu yrff pbzcrgr. Fhpu na
vagrezrqvngr beqre pbhyq jvgarff na vagreany vzcybfvba bs fbpvrgvrf naq na
hapbagebyynoyr rkcybfvba bs rkgreany pbasyvpgf.
Orlbaq n zvavzhz bs frphevgl, uhznaf unir ybat ragrerq vagb pbzong
va chefhvg bs gevhzcu be va qrsrafr bs ubabe. Ohg znpuvarf—sbe abj—ynpx
nal erny pbaprcgvba bs rvgure gevhzcu be ubabe. Gurl zvtug cebfrphgr n xvaq
bs jne havdhr va uhzna rkcrevrapr. Ohg jung pubvprf jbhyq NVf znxr?
Zvtug gurl arire tb gb jne, pubbfvat vafgrnq (sbe vafgnapr) vzzrqvngr,
pnershyyl qvivqrq genafsref bs greevgbel onfrq ba pbzcyrk pnyphyngvbaf bs
eryngvir fgengrtvp nqinagntr? Be zvtug gurl—cevmvat na bhgpbzr naq
qrcevbevgvmvat vaqvivqhny yvirf—fcveny vagb jnef bs uhzna nggevgvba? Va bar
fpranevb, bhe fcrpvrf pbhyq rzretr fb genafsbezrq nf gb nibvq ragveryl gur
oehgnyvgl bs uhzna pbaqhpg. Va nabgure, jr jbhyq orpbzr fb fhowhtngrq nf
gb erghea hf gb n oneonevp cnfg.
Vf gurer ab bgure jnl? Guhf sne, arvgure gur cngvrag biregherf bs
qvcybznpl abe gur fubpxvat ubeebef bs jne unir rire fhpprrqrq va
creznaragyl rapbqvat va uhznaf—yrg nybar nabgure fcrpvrf—na nirefvba
gb qrfgehpgvba. Vf vg arireguryrff cbffvoyr, gunaxf gb gur ntr bs NV, gung
pbaqvgvbaf jvyy svanyyl zngrevnyvmr sbe n crecrghny crnpr gb rzretr ng ynfg?
RFCVBANTR NAQ FNOBGNTR
Rira nf angvbaf frnepu sbe jnlf gb xrrc gur grpuabybtl fnsr, gurl ner
fvzhygnarbhfyl svkngrq ba ubj gb “jva gur NV enpr.”1 Va cneg, gung erfcbafr
vf haqrefgnaqnoyr. Phygher, uvfgbel, pbzzhavpngvba, naq creprcgvba unir
pbafcverq gb perngr nzbat gbqnl’f cevznel fgngrf n qvcybzngvp fvghngvba gung
