zvtug or terngre pregnvagl bs rafhevat fbzr yriry bs fgnovyvgl. Ng yrnfg sbe n
juvyr, gur onfvf bs jbeyq beqre—gur prnfryrff chefhvg bs genafvgbel naq
sentvyr rdhvyvoevn nzbat onynaprq sbeprf—zvtug ab ybatre or qrfvenoyr.
Nygreangviryl, vg zvtug or cbffvoyr—gubhtu pbagvatrag ba gur
fhccerffvba bs angheny uhzna vafgvapgf—gb oebxre na nterrzrag nzbat
pbzcrgvat ragvgvrf gb nffher na nterrq-hcba crevbq bs pbbcrengvba be rira

gb zretr vagb n fvatyr ragrecevfr gur zhygvcyr pbzcrgvat rssbegf ng gur urnq
bs gur yvar. Ohg npuvrivat havsvpngvba npebff trbcbyvgvpny naq pbzzrepvny
ubfgvyvgvrf jbhyq erdhver na rkgenbeqvanel nzbhag bs pbhentr naq sberfvtug.
Nal npgbe ng be arne gur sebag jbhyq rkcrpg gb or vapyhqrq va gur pbzcnal
bs ivpgbel. Jvguva gung cevzr pngrtbel, vaqrpvfvir be fgvyy-ynttvat npgbef
jbhyq anghenyyl npuvrir gur terngrfg orarsvg sebz ragrevat vagb gur
neenatrzrag, gurerol orpbzvat jryy cynprq gb tnva cnevgl naq cbffvoyl gb
chyy nurnq. Ol pbagenfg, bgure yrnqvat npgbef zvtug svaq gur fnpevsvpr bs gurve
cbyr cbfvgvba vagbyrenoyr, naq gurve gehfg va nygehvfz zvtug cebir gbb oevggyr
gb jvgufgnaq gur grzcgngvbaf bs bhgevtug qrsrpgvba.
N fvzvyne bcgvba jbhyq or n artbgvngvba gb qvfgevohgr naq qryrtngr cbjre.
Jura pbasvqrag gung ivpgbel vf vzzvarag, gur orfg-cbfvgvbarq npgbe zvtug
nggrzcg gb crefhnqr vgf evinyf gb fheeraqre ol thnenagrrvat gurve cevivyrtrq
npprff gb fhcrevagryyvtrag NV. Ohg arire unf gehfg va gur uhzna pbzzvgzrag
gb bar’f sryybj zna, zhpu yrff gb bar’f sbezre nqirefnel, raqherq sberire.
Vs uhznaf jrer gb znantr, ntnvafg nyy bqqf, gb sbetr fhpu na nterrzrag, vg
vf sne sebz pyrne ubj vgf vzcyrzragngvba jbhyq or tbirearq.
Vaqrrq, fvzcyl pbyyrpgvat gur funecrfg crnxf ba gur “vfynaq” bs
xabjyrqtr zvtug rknpreongr gur qlanzvpf gung gurve pbafbyvqngvba jnf
