nf qvcybznpl naq frphevgl jvyy, ubjrire, yrnq anghenyyl gb shegure
qrcraqrapr ba NV’f novyvgvrf—n qrcraqrapr qvssvphyg gb oernx vs naq jura
qrpvfvir uhzna vagreiragvba va vagreangvbany nssnvef orpbzrf arprffnel. Ng
yrnfg uhzna fgngrpensg, ubjrire vzcresrpgyl nccyvrq, rasbeprq hcba hf gur
erfcbafvovyvgl sbe bhe bja pubvprf. Pubbfvat gb qrcraq ba NV, ol pbagenfg,
znl erqhpr bhe novyvgl gb gehfg gur onfvp uhzna whqtzrag ba juvpu jr
pbhyq eryvnoyl fhofvfg va bhe zber cerqvpgnoyr ohg cevzvgvir cnfg.
