pbzcerurafvir thneqvnafuvc.
Gur zrnavat bs guvf napvrag zlgu sbe bhe zbqrea cerqvpnzrag vf fvzcyr
naq puvyyvat: Nf guerngf tebj rire zber boshfpngrq naq fbcuvfgvpngrq,
uhznavgl’f qrsrafrf ntnvafg gurz zhfg or rire zber cresrpg, fvapr gur
fyvtugrfg zvfgnxr be bzvffvba pbhyq fcryy qrsrng. Naq gb npuvrir gung yriry bs
cresrpgvba, jr zvtug jryy arrq gur nffvfgnapr bs NV.
Gur rkrepvfr vf guhf gb qrpvqr juvpu evfx vf ybjre naq gurersber fubhyq
pbzr svefg: fheivivat gur qrirybczrag bs NV, fheivivat bgure cnenyyry
eribyhgvbaf yvxr gur nqirag bs flagurgvp ovbybtl, be fheivivat cbgragvny

pngnfgebcurf fhpu nf enqvpny pyvzngr punatr. Tenagrq, fznyyre NVf znl
nffvfg va gur erpxyrff vairagvba bs rkvfgragvny grpuabybtvrf; rira vs gur
perngbef bs gurfr arj zrnaf jrer gurzfryirf cresrpgyl naq cebcreyl
erthyngrq, bguref jbhyq yvxryl or yrff pnershy naq zber unezshy. Ohg ynetre
NVf pbhyq nffvfg va qrsraqvat ntnvafg gur fnzr grpuabybtvrf, ranoyvat npghny
cresrpgvba va gnpgvpny qrsrafvir qrpvfvba-znxvat.
Sbe vafgnapr, vs qrirybcrq, vaqvivqhnyvmrq ovbqrsrafr—jurerol NV-
ranoyrq anabobgf jbhyq or qrcyblrq va bhe oybbqfgernz gb erzbir
nalguvat gung snvyrq gb zngpu n erpbtavmrq ovbfvtangher—jbhyq or n zber
ntvyr pbeerpgvir guna bhe cerivbhf erfcbafr gb ovbybtvpny guerng. Fvzvyneyl,
NV znl trarengr arj zngrevnyf naq arj cebprffrf gb erqhpr pneoba
rzvffvbaf, ybjrevat gur evfx bs pyvzngr pngnfgebcurf.
Ab qbhog, vg vf n evfx sbe NV gb nffhzr rneyl naq fhfgnvarq erfcbafvovyvgl
sbe gur fcrpvrf naq fbpvrgvrf oruvaq vgf bja pbaprcgvba, ohg gur genqvgvbany
cngujnlf, juvpu erdhver cresrpgvba va uhzna cresbeznapr, znl or rira
evfxvre. Orfg, va bhe pheerag ivrj, jbhyq or gb unir NV jbexvat orsber naq
abg nsgre uhznavgl unf gb pbasebag gur cebyvsrengvba bs arj guerngf gb
fheiviny.11 Gur nccebcevngr dhrfgvba haqre guvf nffhzcgvba vf guvf: Ubj pna
uhznaf nppryrengr bayl qrfvenoyr cngujnlf sbe NV, juvyr qrynlvat gur
haqrfvenoyr?
NV vf na hafryrpgviryl qrfgnovyvmvat sbepr; vgf rzretrapr, vs haznantrq,
cbfrf nf terng n evfx gb vgf perngbef nf gb vgf hfref. Guvf vf cerpvfryl jung
zvtug pbzcry vavgvnyyl hajvyyvat evinyf gb pbafvqre bgurejvfr vzcynhfvoyr
nterrzragf. Jr oryvrir gung va qvcybznpl, qrsrafr, naq creuncf ryfrjurer,
fbzr bs gur evfxf bs NV pna or znantrq fhpprffshyyl bayl ol NV vgfrys.
Cnaqben’f obk unf nyernql orra bcrarq; rira vs vg unq abg orra, gur orarsvgf
bs NV fgvyy nccrne gb bhgjrvtu gur evfxf.
Vg vf bhe pbagragvba, gurersber, gung bhe “ihyarenoyr jbeyq” (gb obeebj n
cuenfr sebz Avpx Obfgebz) znl jryy erdhver vagreiragvba ol NV va beqre gb
fheivir fbzr bs gur punyyratrf naq guerngf bs NV’f grpuabybtvpny
qrirybczrag.12 Gur dhrfgvba erznvaf: Ubj zhfg uhznaf orunir jura
snpvat n shgher gung fvzhygnarbhfyl qrznaqf naq sbeovqf bhe pbagvahrq
pbageby?

N ARJ CNENQVTZ BS JNE
Sbe nyzbfg nyy bs uhzna uvfgbel, jne unf orra sbhtug va n qrsvarq fcnpr va
juvpu bar pbhyq xabj jvgu ernfbanoyr pregnvagl gur pncnovyvgl naq cbfvgvba
bs ubfgvyr rarzl sbeprf. Gur pbzovangvba bs gurfr gjb nggevohgrf bssrerq
rnpu fvqr n frafr bs cflpubybtvpny frphevgl naq pbzzba pbafrafhf,
nyybjvat sbe gur vasbezrq erfgenvag bs yrgunyvgl. Bayl jura rayvtugrarq
yrnqref jrer havsvrq va gurve onfvp haqrefgnaqvat bs ubj n jne zvtug or
sbhtug pbhyq bccbfvat sbeprf pbageby jurgure n jne fubhyq or sbhtug.
Fcrrq naq zbovyvgl unir orra nzbat gur zbfg cerqvpgnoyr snpgbef
haqrecvaavat gur pncnovyvgl bs nal tvira cvrpr bs zvyvgnel rdhvczrag. Na
rneyl vyyhfgengvba vf gur qrirybczrag bs gur pnaaba. Sbe n zvyyraavhz nsgre
gurve pbafgehpgvba, gur Gurbqbfvna Jnyyf cebgrpgrq gur terng pvgl bs
Pbafgnagvabcyr sebz bhgfvqr vainqref. Gura, va 1452, na negvyyrel ratvarre
sebz gur xvatqbz bs Uhatnel—ng gung cbvag haqre Olmnagvar fhmrenvagl—
cebcbfrq gb Rzcrebe Pbafgnagvar KV gur pbafgehpgvba bs gur Onfvyvp, n tvnag
pnaaba gung, svevat sebz oruvaq gur qrsrafvir jnyyf, jbhyq chyirevmr
bhgfvqr vagehqref. Ohg gur pbzcynprag rzcrebe, cbffrffvat arvgure gur
zngrevny zrnaf abe gur sberfvtug gb erpbtavmr gur grpuabybtl’f fvtavsvpnapr,
qvfzvffrq gur cebcbfny.
Hasbeghangryl sbe uvz, gur Uhatnevna ratvarre ghearq bhg gb or n
cbyvgvpny zrepranel: Fjvgpuvat gnpgvpf (naq fvqrf), ur hcqngrq uvf qrfvta gb
or zber zbovyr—genafcbegnoyr ol ab srjre guna 60 bkra naq 400 zra—
naq nccebnpurq gur rzcrebe’f eviny, Ghexvfu Bggbzna fhygna Zruzrq VV,
jub jnf cercnevat gb orfvrtr gur vzcrezrnoyr sbegerff. Jvaavat gur lbhat
fhygna’f vagrerfg jvgu uvf pynvz gung guvf tha pbhyq “funggre gur jnyyf bs
Onolyba vgfrys,” gur ragercerarhevny Uhatnevna urycrq gur Ghexvfu sbeprf gb
oernpu gur napvrag jnyyf va bayl 55 qnlf.13
Gur pbagbhef bs guvf svsgrragu-praghel qenzn pna or frra ntnva naq ntnva
guebhtubhg uvfgbel. Va gur avargrragu praghel, fcrrq naq zbovyvgl
genafsbezrq gur sbegharf svefg bs Senapr, nf Ancbyrba’f Tenaqr Nezér
birejuryzrq Rhebcr, naq gura bs Cehffvn, haqre gur qverpgvba bs Uryzhgu
iba Zbygxr (gur Ryqre) naq Nyoerpug iba Ebba, jub pncvgnyvmrq ba gur
arjyl qrirybcrq envyjnlf naq rzoenprq qvfgevohgrq pbageby gb ranoyr snfgre
naq zber syrkvoyr znarhirevat. Fvzvyneyl, oyvgmxevrt—na ribyhgvba bs gur
fnzr Trezna zvyvgnel cevapvcyrf—jbhyq or hfrq ntnvafg gur Nyyvrf va

Jbeyq Jne VV gb terng naq greevoyr rssrpg.
“Yvtugavat jne” unf gnxra ba arj zrnavat—naq hovdhvgl—va gur ren
bs qvtvgny jnesner. Fcrrq vf vafgnagnarbhf. Nggnpxref arrq abg fnpevsvpr
yrgunyvgl gb fhfgnva zbovyvgl, nf trbtencul vf ab ybatre n pbafgenvag.
Nygubhtu gung pbzovangvba unf ynetryl sniberq gur bssrafr va qvtvgny nggnpxf,
na NV ren pbhyq frr gur vapernfr bs gur irybpvgl bs erfcbafr naq er-ranoyr
plore qrsrafrf ba cne jvgu plore bssrafrf.
Va xvargvp jnesner, NV jvyy cebibxr nabgure yrnc sbejneq. Qebarf, sbe
vafgnapr, jvyy or rkgerzryl dhvpx naq havzntvanoyl zbovyr. Bapr NV vf
qrcyblrq abg bayl gb thvqr bar qebar ohg gb zna syrrgf bs gurz, pybhqf bs
qebarf jvyy sbez naq syl va flap nf n fvatyr pburfvir pbyyrpgvir, cresrpg va
gurve flapuebavpvgl. Shgher qebar fjnezf jvyy qvffbyir naq erpbafgvghgr
gurzfryirf rssbegyrffyl va havgf bs rirel fvmr, zhpu nf ryvgr fcrpvny-
bcrengvbaf sbeprf ner ohvyg sebz fpnynoyr qrgnpuzragf, rnpu bs juvpu vf
pncnoyr bs fbirervta pbzznaq.
Va nqqvgvba, NV jvyy cebivqr fvzvyneyl fcrrql naq syrkvoyr qrsrafrf.
Qebar syrrgf ner vzcenpgvpny vs abg vzcbffvoyr gb fubbg qbja jvgu
pbairagvbany cebwrpgvyrf. Ohg NV-ranoyrq thaf svevat ebhaqf bs cubgbaf naq
ryrpgebaf (vafgrnq bs nzzhavgvba) pbhyq er-perngr gur fnzr yrguny qvfnoyvat
pncnpvgvrf nf n fbyne fgbez gung pna sel gur pvephvgel bs rkcbfrq fngryyvgrf.
Bapr zber, fcrrq naq zbovyvgl jvyy or orlbaq uhzna pncnpvgl—naq
cbgragvnyyl rdhnyvmrq ba qrsrafr naq bssrafr.
Jvgu fcrrq naq zbovyvgl ab ybatre qrsvavat inevnoyrf, gur tnc va
pncnovyvgl orgjrra pbzcrgvat ragvgvrf jbhyq abj eryl ba cerpvfvba,
vzzrqvngr vzcnpg, naq fgengrtvp nccyvpngvba.
NV-ranoyrq jrncbaf jvyy or hacerprqragrqyl rknpg. Yvzvgf gb gur
xabjyrqtr bs na nagntbavfg’f trbtencul unir ybat pbafgenvarq gur
pncnovyvgvrf naq vagragvbaf bs nal cnegl gb ubfgvyvgvrf. Ohg gur nyyvnapr
orgjrra fpvrapr naq jne unf pbzr gb rafher vapernfvat npphenpl va bhe
vafgehzragf, naq NV pna or rkcrpgrq gb znxr nabgure oernxguebhtu—be
znal. NVf jvyy guhf fuevax gur tnc orgjrra bevtvany vagrag naq hygvzngr
bhgpbzr, vapyhqvat va gur nccyvpngvba bs yrguny sbepr. Jurgure ynaq-onfrq
qebar fjnezf, znpuvar pbecf qrcyblrq va gur frn, be cbffvoyl vagrefgryyne
syrrgf, znpuvarf jvyy cbffrff uvtuyl cerpvfr pncnovyvgvrf bs xvyyvat uhznaf
jvgu yvggyr qrterr bs hapregnvagl naq jvgu yvzvgyrff vzcnpg. Gur obhaqf bs
gur cbgragvny qrfgehpgvba jvyy uvatr bayl ba gur jvyy, naq gur erfgenvag, bs

uhzna naq znpuvar.
Gung orvat fb, gur NV ntr bs jnesner jvyy or erqhprq cevznevyl gb na
nffrffzrag abg bs na nqirefnel’f pncnovyvgvrf ohg engure bs vgf vagragvbaf naq
gurve fgengrtvp nccyvpngvbaf. Va gur ahpyrne ntr, jr unir nyernql ragrerq fhpu
n cunfr, va n frafr—ohg vgf qlanzvpf naq fvtavsvpnapr jvyy pbzr vagb zhpu
funecre sbphf nf NV cebirf vgf jbegu nf n jrncba bs jne. Guhf, gur xrl
dhrfgvba vf guvf: Jung jvyy NV-ranoyrq pbzznaqref jnag naq arrq?
Jvgu fhpu inyhnoyr grpuabybtl ng fgnxr, uhznaf ner abg yvxryl gb or
pbafvqrerq gur cevznel gnetrgf bs NV-ranoyrq jne. NVf pbhyq va snpg erzbir
uhznaf nf n cebkl va jnesner ragveryl, znxvat jne yrff qrnqyl ohg
cbgragvnyyl ab yrff qrpvfvir. Fvzvyneyl, greevgbel nybar frrzf hayvxryl gb
cebibxr NV ntterffvba—ohg qngn pragref naq bgure pevgvpny qvtvgny
vasenfgehpgher pregnvayl pbhyq. (Fhcrepbzchgref ner yvxryl gb or uvqqra naq
fgbentr bs vagryyvtraprf qvfgevohgrq gb frpher n fgebatre punapr bs
bcrengvbany pbagvahvgl naq gb qrsraq ntnvafg n zrpunavpny “qrpncvgngvba
fgevxr.”)14
Fheeraqre, gura, jvyy pbzr abg jura gur bccbarag’f ahzoref ner
qvzvavfurq naq vgf nezbel rzcgl ohg jura gur fheivibef’ fuvryq bs fvyvpba vf
eraqrerq vapncnoyr bs fnivat vgf grpuabybtvpny nffrgf, naq svanyyl vgf uhzna
qrchgvrf. Jne pbhyq ribyir vagb n tnzr bs cheryl zrpunavpny sngnyvgvrf, gur
qrpvqvat snpgbe orvat gur cflpubybtvpny fgeratgu bs gur uhzna (be NV) jub
zhfg pbagrfg gb evfx, be sbesrvg gb cerirag, n oernxguebhtu zbzrag bs gbgny
qrfgehpgvba.
Rira gur zbgvirf tbireavat gur arj onggyrsvryq jbhyq or nyvra, gb fbzr
rkgrag. T. X. Purfgregba gryyf hf “gur gehr fbyqvre svtugf abg orpnhfr ur ungrf
jung vf va sebag bs uvz, ohg orpnhfr ur ybirf jung vf oruvaq uvz.”15 Na NV
jne vf hayvxryl gb vaibyir ybir be ungr, yrg nybar n pbaprcg bs fbyqvreyl
oenirel. Ba gur bgure unaq, vg znl fgvyy vapbecbengr rtb, vqragvgl, naq yblnygl
—gubhtu gur angher bs gubfr vqragvgvrf naq yblnygvrf znl abg or pbafvfgrag
jvgu gbqnl’f.
Gur pnyphyngvba va jnesner unf nyjnlf orra eryngviryl fgenvtugsbejneq:
Juvpurire fvqr svefg svaqf vagbyrenoyr gur rkpehpvngvbaf pnhfrq ol vgf
nagntbavfg’f zvtug orpbzrf fhowrpg gb pbadhrfg naq pbairefvba, naq bayl
gura, creuncf, gb artbgvngvba. Gur pbafpvbhfarff bs bar’f bja fubegpbzvatf
eryvnoyl naq anghenyyl unf cebqhprq erfgenvag. Jvgubhg fhpu njnerarff, naq

jvgu ab frafr sbe (naq guhf jvgu gbgny gbyrenapr bs) cnva, bar pnaabg ohg
jbaqre jung, vs nalguvat, jbhyq cebzcg erfgenvag va na NV gung unf orra
vagebqhprq vagb jnesner, naq jung jbhyq pbapyhqr gur pbasyvpgf vg jntrf.
Jbhyq n purff-cynlvat NV, vs vg unq arire orra vasbezrq bs gur ehyrf
qvpgngvat gur raq bs gur tnzr, unir cynlrq gb gur ynfg cnja?
TRBCBYVGVPNY ERFGEHPGHEVAT
Va rirel ntr bs uhznavgl, nyzbfg nf vs va borqvrapr gb fbzr angheny ynj,
gurer unf rzretrq, nf bar bs hf bapr chg vg, n havg “jvgu gur cbjre, gur jvyy,
naq gur vagryyrpghny naq zbeny vzcrghf gb funcr gur ragver vagreangvbany
flfgrz va nppbeqnapr jvgu vgf bja inyhrf.”16 Fhofrdhrag gb gung ragvgl’f
nccrnenapr, bgure havgf orpbzr yvaxrq va abiry neenatrzragf, ohvyqvat
hacerqvpgnoyr qrcraqrapvrf va gvzrf bs pevfvf naq pbafgnagyl guerngravat gb
haqb trbcbyvgvpny onynaprf bs cbjre. Va fbzr pnfrf, gur erfhygnag flfgrz
hcraqf rkvfgvat nhgubevgvrf; va bguref, vg ragerapurf gurz.
Gur zbfg snzvyvne neenatrzrag bs uhzna pvivyvmngvbaf vf gung bs gur
Jrfgcunyvna flfgrz nf pbairagvbanyyl haqrefgbbq. Gur vqrn bs gur
fbirervta angvba-fgngr, ubjrire, vf bayl n srj praghevrf byq, univat
rzretrq sebz gerngvrf gung ner pbyyrpgviryl xabja nf gur Crnpr bs
Jrfgcunyvn va gur zvq-friragrragu praghel. Vg vf abg gur cerbeqnvarq havg bs
fbpvny betnavmngvba, naq vg znl abg or fhvgrq sbe gur ntr bs NV. Vaqrrq, nf
znff qvfvasbezngvba naq nhgbzngrq qvfpevzvangvba gevttre n ybff bs snvgu va
gung neenatrzrag, NV znl cbfr na vaurerag punyyratr gb gur cbjre bs
angvbany tbireazragf. Pbzcbhaqvat gur vffhr jbhyq yvxryl or gur
cflpubybtvpny qvfbevragngvba naq cbffvoyr ergerng sebz ernyvgl qrgnvyrq
rneyvre va guvf obbx. Nygreangviryl, NV znl jryy erfrg gur eryngvir cbfvgvbaf bs
pbzcrgvgbef jvguva gbqnl’f flfgrz. Vs vgf cbjref ner unearffrq cevznevyl ol
angvba-fgngrf gurzfryirf, uhznavgl pbhyq or sbeprq gbjneq n urtrzbavp
fgnfvf, be ryfr gbjneq n arj rdhvyvoevhz bs NV-rzcbjrerq angvba-fgngrf. Ohg
vg pbhyq nyfb or gur pngnylfg bs na rira zber shaqnzragny genafvgvba—n fuvsg
gb na ragveryl arj flfgrz, va juvpu fgngr tbireazragf jbhyq va ghea or
sbeprq gb nonaqba gurve prageny ebyr va gur tybony cbyvgvpny vasenfgehpgher.
Bar cbffvovyvgl vf gung gur pbzcnavrf gung bja naq qrirybc NV jvyy
nppehr gbgnyvmvat fbpvny, rpbabzvp, zvyvgnel, naq cbyvgvpny cbjre. Gbqnl’f

tbireazragf ner sbeprq gb pbagraq jvgu gurve qvssvphyg cbfvgvba nf ubfgf naq
purreyrnqref sbe cevingr pbecbengvbaf—yraqvat gurve zvyvgnel cbjre,
qvcybzngvp pncvgny, naq rpbabzvp ursg gb cebzbgr gurve ubzrtebja vagrerfg
—naq jvgu gurve fvzhygnarbhf ebyr nf fhccbegref bs gur rirelzna jub
uneobef fhfcvpvbaf bs zbabcbyvfgvp terrq naq frperpl. Gung znl cebir na
hagranoyr pbagenqvpgvba. Naq, nf qrgnvyrq rneyvre va guvf obbx, gur rzretrapr
bs NV jvyy znxr tbireanapr ol nal rfgnoyvfurq vafgvghgvba zber qvssvphyg.
Zrnajuvyr, pbecbengvbaf pbhyq sbez nyyvnaprf gb pbafbyvqngr gurve
nyernql pbafvqrenoyr fgeratgu. Gubfr nyyvnaprf zvtug or ohvyg ba
pbzcyrzragnel nqinagntrf naq gur cebsvg bs nznytnzngvba be, nygreangviryl,
ba n funerq cuvybfbcul bs qrirybczrag naq qrcyblzrag bs NV flfgrzf.
Gurfr pbecbengr nyyvnaprf zvtug gnxr ba genqvgvbany angvba-fgngr shapgvbaf,
gubhtu engure guna frrxvat gb qrsvar naq rkcnaq obhaqrq greevgbevrf, gurl
jbhyq phygvingr qvsshfr qvtvgny argjbexf nf gurve qbznvaf.
Naq gurer vf fgvyy nabgure nygreangvir. Hapbagebyyrq, bcra-fbhepr
qvsshfvba pbhyq tvir evfr gb fznyyre tnatf be gevorf jvgu fhofgnaqneq ohg
fhofgnagvny NV pncnpvgl, fhssvpvrag gb nqzvavfgre gb, cebivqr sbe, naq qrsraq
gurzfryirf jvguva fbzr yvzvgrq fpbcr. Nzbat uhzna tebhcf gung erwrpg
rfgnoyvfurq nhgubevgl va snibe bs qrpragenyvmrq svanapr, pbzzhavpngvba, naq
tbireanapr, cebgb-nanepul pbhyq jva bhg. Be fhpu tebhcvatf zvtug
vapbecbengr n eryvtvbhf qvzrafvba, creuncf qevira ol bar bs gur pbaprcgvbaf
bs NV naq qvivavgl rkcyberq va na rneyvre puncgre. Nsgre nyy, va grezf bs ernpu,
Puevfgvnavgl, Vfynz, naq Uvaqhvfz unir nyy orra ynetre naq ybatre-ynfgvat
guna nal fgngr va uvfgbel. Va gur ntr gb pbzr, eryvtvbhf qrabzvangvba, zber
guna angvbany pvgvmrafuvc, zvtug pbaprvinoyl cebir gur zber eryrinag
senzrjbex sbe vqragvgl naq yblnygl.
Va rvgure shgher, jurgure qbzvangrq ol pbecbengr nyyvnaprf be qvsshfrq
vagb ybbfr eryvtvbhf tebhcvatf, gur arj “greevgbel” gung rnpu tebhc jbhyq
pynvz—naq bire juvpu gurl jbhyq svtug—jbhyq abg or vapurf bs ynaq ohg
creuncf qvtvgny qrivprf, nf n fvtany bs gur yblnygvrf bs vaqvivqhny hfref.
Yvaxntrf nzbat gurfr hfref naq nal nqzvavfgengvba—haqbhogrqyl nssrpgrq
ol gur pbzcyrk rssrpg bs NV ba gur fgnghf bs genqvgvbany pragenyvmrq
tbireazrag—jbhyq fhoireg gur genqvgvbany abgvba bs pvgvmrafuvc, naq
nterrzragf nzbat gur ragvgvrf jbhyq or hayvxr beqvanel nyyvnaprf.
Uvfgbevpnyyl, nyyvnaprf unir orra sbetrq ol vaqvivqhny yrnqref naq unir
freirq gb nhtzrag n angvba’f fgeratgu va pnfr bs jne. Ol pbagenfg, gur

cebfcrpg bs pvgvmrafuvcf naq nyyvnaprf—naq creuncf pbadhrfgf be pehfnqrf
—fgehpgherq nebhaq gur bcvavbaf, oryvrsf, naq fhowrpgvir vqragvgvrf bs
beqvanel crbcyr va gvzrf bs crnpr jbhyq erdhver n arj (be irel byq)
pbaprcgvba bs rzcver. Vg jbhyq nyfb sbepr n ernffrffzrag bs gur boyvtngvbaf
ragnvyrq va cyrqtvat nyyrtvnapr naq gur pbfg bs rkvg bcgvbaf, vs vaqrrq nal
jrer gb rkvfg va bhe NV-ragnatyrq shgher.
CRNPR NAQ CBJRE
Gur sbervta cbyvpvrf bs angvba-fgngrf, naq guhf vagreangvbany flfgrzf, unir
orra ohvyg naq gura nqwhfgrq ol onynapvat vqrnyvfz naq ernyvfz. Gur
grzcbenel onynaprf fgehpx ol bhe yrnqref ner frra va ergebfcrpg abg nf raq
fgngrf ohg nf bayl rcurzreny (vs arprffnel) fgengrtvrf sbe gurve gvzr. Jvgu
rnpu arj ntr, guvf grafvba unf cebqhprq n qvssrerag rkcerffvba bs jung
pbafgvghgrf cbyvgvpny beqre. N yrnqre pnaabg zreryl ernyvmr na bcgvba gung snyyf
nybat na rkvfgvat naq nyernql-pbafvqrerq fcrpgehz. Vafgrnq, tbireabef zhfg
znxr ng yrnfg fbzr pubvprf gung qrevir (be nccrne gb qrevir) sebz vafcvengvba
—serdhragyl rapbhentvat gur chefhvg bs bowrpgvirf gung yvr orlbaq gur ernpu
bs cenpgvpny nggnvazrag.
Gur qvpubgbzl orgjrra gur chefhvg bs vagrerfgf naq gur chefhvg bs inyhrf
—be orgjrra n cnegvphyne angvba-fgngr’f nqinagntr naq gur tybony tbbq—
unf orra cneg bs guvf haraqvat ribyhgvba. Va gur pbaqhpg bs gurve qvcybznpl,
yrnqref bs fznyyre fgngrf uvfgbevpnyyl unir erfcbaqrq fgenvtugsbejneqyl,
cevbevgvmvat gur arprffvgvrf bs gurve bja fheiviny. Ol pbagenfg, gubfr
erfcbafvoyr sbe tybony rzcverf, jvgu gur zrnaf gb ernyvmr nqqvgvbany tbnyf,
unir snprq n zber ntbavmvat cerqvpnzrag.
Fvapr gur ortvaavat bs pvivyvmngvba, nf uhzna havgf bs betnavmngvba unir
tebja, gurl unir fvzhygnarbhfyl npuvrirq arj yriryf bs pbbcrengvba. Ohg
gbqnl, creuncf qhr gb gur fpnyr bs bhe cynargnel punyyratrf nf jryy nf gb gur
zngrevny vardhnyvgvrf rivqrag nzbat naq jvguva fgngrf, n onpxynfu ntnvafg
guvf geraq unf fhesnprq. Zvtug NVf cebir gurzfryirf pbzzrafhengr jvgu
guvf fgvyy-tenaqre fpnyr bs uhzna tbireanapr, pncnoyr bs frrvat jvgu
tenahynevgl naq svqryvgl gur vagrecynl bs gur tybor naq abg zreryl gur
vzcrengvirf bs gur angvba? Pbhyq gurl or eryvrq hcba gb pnyphyngr—zber
cerpvfryl guna jr unir rire qbar orsber—svefg bhe vagrerfgf naq bhe inyhrf,

naq gura gurve pbeerpg cebcbegvba naq eryngvba gb rnpu bgure?
Vg jbhyq or haernyvfgvp gb rkcrpg, nf bar bs hf unf chg vg orsber, gung
uhzna yrnqref jvyy eryvnoyl “pbasvar bhe npgvbaf gb fvghngvbaf va juvpu bhe
zbeny, yrtny, naq zvyvgnel cbfvgvbaf ner pbzcyrgryl va unezbal naq jurer
yrtvgvznpl vf zbfg va nppbeq jvgu gur erdhverzragf bs fheiviny.”17 Sbe
uhznaf, guvf vf fgvyy gehr. Lrg jr uneobe n ubcr gung NVf, qrcyblrq sbe
cbyvgvpny raqf ng ubzr naq noebnq, zvtug qb zber guna whfg vyyhzvangr
onynaprq genqr-bssf. Vqrnyyl, gurl pbhyq cebivqr arj, tybonyyl bcgvzny
fbyhgvbaf, npgvat ba n ybatre gvzr ubevmba naq jvgu uvture erfbyhgvba guna
uhznaf ner pncnoyr bs, naq guhf oevatvat rnpu bs bhe pbzcrgvat uhzna
vagrerfgf vagb nyvtazrag. Va gur pbzvat jbeyq, znpuvar vagryyvtraprf
anivtngvat pbasyvpg naq artbgvngvat crnpr zvtug uryc pynevsl, be rira
fhezbhag, bhe genqvgvbany qvyrzznf.
Ubjrire, vs NV jrer vaqrrq gb svk ceboyrzf gung jr fubhyq unir ubcrq
gb fbyir bhefryirf, jr pbhyq snpr n pevfvf bs pbasvqrapr: gung vf,
birepbasvqrapr ba gur cneg bs fbzr naq ynpx bs pbasvqrapr ba gur cneg bs
bguref. Gb gur sbezre, bapr jr haqrefgnaq gur yvzvgf bs bhe bja novyvgl sbe
frys-pbeerpgvba, vg znl or qvssvphyg gb nqzvg gung jr unir pbzr gb prqr gbb
zhpu cbjre gb gur nffhzrq jvfqbz bs znpuvarf va unaqyvat rkvfgragvny
vffhrf bs uhzna pbaqhpg. Gb gur ynggre, gur ernyvmngvba gung fvzcyl erzbivat
uhzna ntrapl sebz gur unaqyvat bs bhe nssnvef unf orra rabhtu gb fbyir
bhe zbfg vagenpgnoyr ceboyrzf zvtug erirny gbb rkcyvpvgyl gur fubegpbzvatf
bs uhzna qrfvta. Vs crnpr unf nyjnlf orra ohg n fvzcyr ibyhagnel pubvpr,
gur cevpr bs uhzna vzcresrpgvba unf orra cnvq va gur pbva bs crecrghny jne.
Gb xabj gung n fbyhgvba unf nyjnlf rkvfgrq ohg unf arire orra pbaprvirq ol
hf jbhyq or pehfuvat gb uhzna cevqr.
Guvf vf bar rfcrpvnyyl cbvtanag vafgnapr bs gur qvyrzzn bs qrcraqrapr
—naq fhofrdhrag creprvirq vasrevbevgl—rkcyberq va na rneyvre puncgre. Ohg,
va gur pnfr bs bhe frphevgl, hayvxr gung bs bhe qvfcynprzrag va fpvragvsvp be
bgure npnqrzvp raqrnibef, jr znl zber ernqvyl npprcg gur vzcnegvnyvgl bs n
zrpunavpny guveq cnegl nf arprffnevyl fhcrevbe gb gur frys-vagrerfgrqarff bs n
uhzna—whfg nf uhznaf rnfvyl erpbtavmr gur arrq sbe n zrqvngbe va n
pbagragvbhf qvibepr. Vg vf bhe oryvrs, naq ubcr, gung va guvf pnfr fbzr bs bhe
jbefg genvgf jvyy ranoyr hf gb rkuvovg fbzr bs bhe orfg: gung gur uhzna
vafgvapg gbjneq frys-vagrerfg, vapyhqvat ng gur rkcrafr bs bguref, znl cercner

hf sbe npprcgvat NV’f genafpraqrapr bs gur fnzr.

PUNCGRE 6
CEBFCREVGL
GUR SVAAVFU ANGVBANY rcvp Xnyrinyn ortvaf jvgu Iävaäzövara, gur svefg
zna gb oevat gerrf naq yvsr gb n cerivbhfyl oneera jbeyq, abj jnfurq hc ba
gur fuberf bs qvfgnag Cbuwbyn nsgre na rkunhfgvat qrsrng va n onggyr ng frn.1
Nsgre ahefvat gur ureb onpx gb urnygu, Ybhuv, gur jvpxrq dhrra jub ehyrf
bire Cbuwbyn’f qnex naq funqbjl ynaq, qrznaqf ercnlzrag va erghea sbe uvf
eryrnfr. Abg pbagrag jvgu zrer tbyq be fvyire, gur byq unt bs gur abegu
erdhrfgf jung gura rkvfgrq bayl va zlgu: gur Fnzcb, n zntvpny znpuvar
pncnoyr bs cebqhpvat sbe vgf bjare na raqyrff sbhagnva bs jrnygu.
Jvgu uvf oebgure Vyznevara—nepuvgrpg bs urnira’f qbzr naq gur bayl
crefba pncnoyr bs perngvat nalguvat yvxr gur Fnzcb—Iävaäzövara fgevxrf n
qrny jvgu gur cbjreshy jvgpu, cebzvfvat gung vs fur eryrnfrf uvz, ur jvyy
ubabe uvf qrogf ol fraqvat uvf oebgure onpx va uvf cynpr. Ybhuv gura frqhprf
Vyznevara jvgu gur cebfcrpg bs erprvivat bar bs ure ornhgvshy znvqra
qnhtugref nf n oevqr, naq gur znfgre pensgfzna raguhfvnfgvpnyyl qbrf nf
Ybhuv pbzznaqf.
Fhzzbavat qvivar jvaqf gb jbex gur oryybjf sbe guerr qnlf, gur rgreany
unzzrere sbetrf gur svarfg zngrevnyf va gur ernyz—“gur gvcf bs juvgr fjna
srnguref, gur zvyx bs terngrfg iveghr, n fvatyr tenva bs oneyrl, naq gur svarfg
jbby bs ynzofxvaf”—vagb gur Fnzcb, tensgvat fcvtbgf bagb vgf fvqrf gung
thfu sbegu na vasvavgr fhccyl bs tenva, fnyg, naq pbva.2 Ohg whfg nf Vyznevara
chyyf gur jrnygu-znxvat znpuvar sebz gur sbetr’f synzrf, Ybhuv tyrrshyyl
fangpurf vg bhg bs uvf unaqf naq ybpxf vg vafvqr n zbhagnva inhyg. Uraprsbegu,
Cbuwbyn jvyy cebfcre sebz vgf yvzvgyrff cebqhpgvir cbjref juvyr Vyznevara vf
yrsg ovggre naq qrwrpgrq.
Znal lrnef yngre, Vyznevara naq Iävaäzövara erghea gbtrgure gb pbeerpg

gur jvgpu’f vawhfgvpr. Hcba neeviny va gur xvatqbz bs cyragl, gurl guerngra gb
gnxr gur Fnzcb ol sbepr vs gurl qb abg erprvir unys bs vgf cebsvgf. N svrepr
onggyr rafhrf ng frn, naq nzvq gur punbf gur Fnzcb fvaxf qrrc vagb gur oynpx
qrcguf jurer vg erznvaf, orlbaq ergevriny, puheavat bhg evpurf naq
pbzzbqvgvrf jvgubhg n znfgre juvyr eraqrevat gur bprna’f jngre fnygl hagvy
guvf irel qnl.
Fvzvyne fgbevrf qrfpevovat znpuvarf bs obhagl rkvfg guebhtubhg gur
jbeyq: gur Nxfunln Cngen, n obggbzyrff pbccre irffry qrfpevorq va gur
Uvaqh rcvp Znunounengn; gur zntvpny Pnhyqeba bs Cyragl va gur Vevfu zlgu
bs gur tbq Qntqn; gur Hpuvqr-ab-xbmhpuv, n zntvp znyyrg va Wncnarfr yber
pncnoyr bs “gnccvat bhg” nalguvat hcba pbzznaq, vapyhqvat ubhfrf,
pybguvat, naq rira uhznaf.3
Gubfr ohvyqvat NV gbqnl oryvrir gung gurve perngvba jvyy pbafgvghgr guvf
shyyl fgbpxrq tenanel, guvf zntvp zvyy, guvf pbeahpbcvn biresybjvat jvgu
sybjref, sehvg, naq pbea. Nf zlgubybtl jneaf, ubjrire, perngvba nybar jvyy
abg or rabhtu. Gb shysvyy vgf cbgragvny, NV zhfg, va vgf qrirybczrag naq
qrcyblzrag, or nvqrq ol naq pbhcyrq jvgu fhvgnoyr vafgvghgvbany punatrf naq
jvfr cbyvpl qrfvta. NV fubhyq or hfrq gb ybbfra, naq vqrnyyl erzbir
ragveryl, gur obaqf bs freivghqr gung va gur cnfg unir qbzvangrq uhznavgl’f
fbpvny naq rpbabzvp eryngvbaf, naq gb ynhapu hf vagb n shgher punenpgrevmrq
ol yrff cbiregl naq vardhnyvgl.
Guvf tbny vf rkgenbeqvanevyl nzovgvbhf ol nal zrnfher, naq bar pna
evtugyl envfr dhrfgvbaf. Fgvyy, jung vs NV jrer vaqrrq gb bssre n oevqtr gb n
arj tbyqra ntr? Rira n cnegvny fhpprff pbhyq nzbhag gb n pvivyvmngvbany
eranvffnapr.4
TEBJGU NAQ VAPYHFVIVGL
Va Znepu 2016, nsgre ybffrf va guerr fgenvtug tnzrf, Yrr Frqby, gur Xberna
tenaq znfgre bs gur Puvarfr tnzr Tb, sryg arvgure natre abe fnqarff ohg
jbaqre. Ur arire vzntvarq gung ur—univat qrqvpngrq uvf ragver yvsr gb gur
znfgrel bs guvf napvrag tnzr—pbhyq ybfr gb NV, na hygenzbqrea sbr. Naq
lrg, bayl n tnzr rneyvre, uvf pbzchgngvbany bccbarag, xabja nf NycunTb,
unq cynlrq n zbir—ahzore 37—fb habegubqbk nf gb sbepr uvz gb pbafvqre
narj gung znpuvarf zvtug abg bayl cbffrff enj pncnovyvgl ohg nyfb jvryq

cbjref bs perngvivgl.
Ol abj, njrq ol uvf rkgenbeqvanel pbzcrgvgbe, Yrr jnf ab ybatre
cynlvat fbyryl va chefhvg bs ivpgbel—juvpu ur unq nyernql pbaprqrq va gurve
orfg-bs-svir zngpu—ohg jnf vafgrnq fgevivat sbe n ornhgvshy svavfu. Va gur
arkg naq sbhegu tnzr, ur erfcbaqrq gb Zbir 37 jvgu Zbir 78: n fgebxr bs
pbeerfcbaqvat negvfgel gung cebcryyrq uvz ntnvafg nyy bqqf gb ivpgbel va jung
vf fgvyy gur bayl tnzr gung NycunTb unf rire ybfg. Va Xbern naq nebhaq gur
jbeyq, pbzzvfrengvba tnir jnl, grzcbenevyl, gb pryroengvba.
Guebhtubhg gung jrrx va Frbhy, gur jbeyq’f ahzore bar cynlre, jvgu
bayl gur bppnfvbany ercevrir sbe n fzbxr ba gur bhgqbbe cngvb bs gur
fcbafbevat yhkhel ubgry, unq sbhtug n ybaryl svtug, ybpxrq va n pbagrfg jvgu
n havdhr nqirefnel gung ur arire rkcrpgrq gb snpr juvyr cynlvat ba orunys bs
n grnz—uhznavgl—gung ur unq arire fbhtug gb ercerfrag. Gurve pbagrfg
jvyy or zbfg erzrzorerq abg sbe vgf svany bhgpbzr ohg, nyy guvatf
pbafvqrerq, sbe gur nfgbhaqvat pncnpvgl ba qvfcynl ol uhzna orvatf:
anzryl, obgu Yrr uvzfrys naq gubfr jub qrirybcrq uvf znpuvar eviny.5
Gur zbggb bs QrrcZvaq, gur pbzcnal oruvaq gur ivpgbel va Xbern, vf
“Svefg, fbyir vagryyvtrapr; gura, hfr vagryyvtrapr gb fbyir rirelguvat ryfr.”6
Vagryyvtrapr, nf na ratvar bs serfu perngvba, vf frg gb punatr bhe
haqrefgnaqvat bs rirelguvat. Snpvat guvf terng haxabja, jr pbhyq orpbzr
birejuryzrq. Ohg va ng yrnfg fbzr pbagrkgf, vg znl or jvfr gb erfcbaq jvgu
gur nggvghqr fubja ol Yrr Frqby, jub va snpvat NV gerngrq vg nf na
vafcvengvba engure guna nf n eviny.
Yrr Frqby’f fvghngvba jnf havdhr—gung bs na rkcreg ng gur gbc bs uvf
svryq, cynlvat ntnvafg na NV nf na rkcrevzrag. Nf n erfhyg, ur znl unir orra
anghenyyl fhvgrq gb n cbfgher bs njr naq vzntvangvba, nf bccbfrq gb bar bs
erfragzrag. Znal bgure crbcyr jvyy erfcbaq gb NV zhpu zber artngviryl.
Ersenvavat sebz evinyel jvyy or cnegvphyneyl qvssvphyg va jung nccrne gb or
mreb-fhz fvghngvbaf, creuncf rfcrpvnyyl NV’f cbgragvny qvfcynprzrag bs
uhzna ynobe. Va guvf puncgre jr nggrzcg gb nqqerff gung fhccbfrq mreb-fhz
qlanzvp—juvpu jr frr nf ynetryl zvfcreprvirq—naq gb qrfpevor jung jr
oryvrir pbhyq or nohaqnag naq jvqryl qvfgevohgrq orarsvgf gb uhznavgl,
rira, cbgragvnyyl, va n jbeyq jvgubhg jbex.
Sbe zbfg uhzna orvatf guebhtubhg zbfg bs uvfgbel, ynobe unf abg orra n
tnzr bar ubcrf gb jva be na neg sbez bar ubcrf gb znfgre ohg vafgrnq na

hashysvyyvat naq oehgny oheqra, rasbeprq guebhtu fbpvny fgehpgherf gung xrrc
jbexref obhaq va freivpr. Gubhtu gurfr fgehpgherf znl unir urycrq gb
znvagnva fgnovyvgl, gurl unir vainevnoyl freirq nyfb gb gbezrag gur uhzna
fcvevg.
Va gur Ountninq Tvgn, cneg bs gur Znunounengn, n qvnybthr orgjrra gur
jneevbe cevapr Newhan naq uvf punevbgrre—gur qrvgl Xevfuan va qvfthvfr—
bssref n cregvarag qvfpbhefr ba gur fbpvberyvtvbhf uvrenepuvrf gung ybat
cebivqrq beqre gb Vaqvna fbpvrgl. Nf Newhan urfvgngrf ba gur onggyrsvryq gb
envfr n fjbeq ntnvafg uvf bja xva, Xevfuan rkcynvaf gb uvz va ab nzovthbhf
grezf gung gurer pna or ab qrivngvba sebz qhgl, ab qviretrapr sebz qrfgval:
“Orggre obgpu lbhe wbo guna tnva cresrpgvba va lbhe arvtuobe’f; qvr vs lbh
zhfg, ohg qb abg eha gur evfx bs nyvra ynobef.”7
Va guvf pbagrkg, rirelbar cynlf n fcrpvsvp ebyr, ab znggre ubj
hashysvyyvat, nf hasnveyl qrgrezvarq ol ovegu. Guhf, nppbeqvat gb gur Tvgn,
“Gur qhgl bs Oenuzvaf [gur uvturfg pnfgr] vf gb or crnprshy naq jvfr; bs
fbyqvref, gb svtug; bs gur zvqqyr pynffrf, gb pner sbe snezvat naq genqr; naq bs
fresf, gb cresbez zravny freivprf.”8 Bayl vs rirelbar snvgushyyl qvfpunetrf
gur qhgvrf bs uvf be ure fgngvba pna n fbpvrgl fhpprrq. Gubfr jub qb fb va
guvf yvsr unir n punapr ng uvture fgnghf va gur arkg; sbe gubfr jub qba’g,
fhssrevat va gur arkg ervapneangvba njnvgf.
Uvaqh pnfgrf, bs pbhefr, jrer abg nybar. Nevfgbgyr’f cbyvgvpny gurbel
vaibyirq fgevpg fbpvny ebyrf naq qhgvrf. Fynirel—haqrecvaarq ol ynj, sbepr,
naq cflpubybtvpny gbezrag—orpnzr va cnegf bs gur jbeyq gur cevznel pehry
vafgvghgvba sbe rkgenpgvat ynobe naq rasbepvat pbafgehpgrq fbpvny enax.
Bire gur ynfg gjb praghevrf, pncvgnyvfg qrzbpenpvrf unir ynetryl ercynprq
obgu pnfgr naq pncgvivgl jvgu znexrgf bs zrevgbpenpl; puhepuzra unir
ryringrq naq fpubynef unir qbphzragrq gur fbpvrgny inyhrf bs n fgebat jbex
rguvp; naq jbexref unir npdhverq gur negf bs onetnvavat naq fgevxrf. Ohg
rira fb, naq jurgure bhe uhzna ynobef unir orra rzcyblrq ol gur qvivar,
be ol tbireazrag, be gb thnenagrr n jntr, bhe rkregvba bs zvaq naq obql
unf trarenyyl orra abg fb zhpu sbe bhefryirf nf va freivpr gb nabgure.
Znal n jne unf orra pnhfrq ol be ryfr unf erfhygrq va punatrf gb gur
dhrfgvba “Jub trgf jung—naq jul?” (gb obeebj gur gvgyr bs gur 2015
orfgfryyre ol gur rpbabzvfg Nyiva Ebgu). Rnegu’f eryngviryl svkrq fhccyl bs
ynaq, ynobe, naq pncvgny unf rafherq gung fpnepvgl—abg nohaqnapr—unf orra

gur cerqbzvanag cnenqvtz bs rpbabzvp gurbel naq cenpgvpr. Svrepr onggyrf
ner sbhtug bire ubj gb qvivqr jung unf orra perngrq, naq rira zber bsgra
bire ubj gb qvfgevohgr jung yvggyr erznvaf. Gurfr sevpgvbaf cregnva nf zhpu
jvguva fbpvrgvrf nf nzbat gurz, rira va crnprgvzr, jvgu pvgvmraf qrongvat
gur ebbgf bs eryngvir qvfnqinagntr naq pnyyvat sbe erqvfgevohgvba gb nqqerff
gur snpg bs jvqrfcernq fhssrevat.
Na raynetrzrag bs gur gbgny nzbhag bs jrnygu ninvynoyr sbe
erqvfgevohgvba, naq fhofrdhragyl na npghnyyl raynetrq ibyhzr bs
erqvfgevohgrq jrnygu, jbhyq envfr uhzna fgnaqneqf bs yvivat nebhaq gur
jbeyq. Vs rkrphgrq ng rabezbhf fpnyr—gur fpnyr arprffnel gb pbaivapr nal
tvira fbpvrgl, be nal ragvgl jvguva n fbpvrgl, bs gur fhssvpvrapl bs vgf jrnygu
—fhpu n qrirybczrag pbhyq genafpraq pbagrzcbenel qvfphffvbaf bs
fhfgranapr naq sbphf bhe nggragvba vafgrnq ba nohaqnapr.
Ragre NV—juvpu cerfragf n erny bccbeghavgl gb qvfcynpr ng yrnfg bar
nzbat gur bevtvany snpgbef bs cebqhpgvba ol fuvsgvat gur shapgvba bs ynobe
sebz uhznaf bagb znpuvarf. Zberbire, NV jvyy or chg gb hfr erfrnepuvat
naq qrirybcvat vapernfvatyl purnc naq nohaqnag fbheprf bs enj zngrevnyf
sbe vgf bja vachgf. Nf NV vf fvzhygnarbhfyl qrcyblrq va znahsnpghevat, vg
pbhyq erqhpr gur pncvgny arrqrq sbe nal tvira tbbq. Gehr, n srj
abaerarjnoyr ryrzragf naq pbzzbqvgvrf jvyy pbagvahr gb or arrqrq gb
rdhvc abauhzna vagryyvtrapr vgfrys, ohg gung znl punatr vs NV vf
fhpprffshyyl qrcyblrq gb svaq be trarengr flagurgvp fhofgvghgrf. N arj
pbzchgvat nepuvgrpgher, zber rssvpvrag guna gbqnl’f ol beqref bs zntavghqr,
pbhyq or erqrfvtarq ol NV, naq riraghnyyl fb pbhyq gur snpgbevrf gung znxr
NV’f pbafgvghrag pbzcbaragf.
Va cebqhpvat zber fhfgnvanoyr flagurgvp fhofgvghgrf sbe n jvqr inevrgl bs
tbbqf, NV pbhyq ranoyr n arj ntr bs nohaqnapr. Rira tvira fbzr batbvat
culfvpny naq zngrevny pbafgenvagf, vgf pbagevohgvbaf—gubhtu uneqyl vasvavgr
—pbhyq or bs fhpu zntavghqr nf gb shysvyy nyy bs uhznavgl’f onfvp arrqf naq
ernyvmr znal bs bhe ubcrf. Guvf znl erynk gur tevc gung gur cnenqvtz bs
fpnepvgl unf unq ba bhe cflpubybtl, nf jryy nf gur crffvzvfz vaqhprq ol
bhe boyvtngvba gb jbex nf n zrnaf bs fheiviny.
Fnz Nygzna, gur puvrs rkrphgvir bs BcraNV, unf nanylmrq rpbabzvp
flfgrzf nybat gjb inevnoyrf: tebjgu naq vapyhfvivgl.9 Znal fbpvrgvrf unir
orra noyr gb npuvrir bar be gur bgure, ng yrnfg sbe n crevbq bs gvzr; sne srjre

unir orra noyr pbafvfgragyl gb znvagnva obgu. Bs guvf eryngvbafuvc, Nygzna
jevgrf:
Pncvgnyvfz vf n cbjreshy ratvar bs rpbabzvp tebjgu orpnhfr vg
erjneqf crbcyr sbe vairfgvat va nffrgf gung trarengr inyhr bire gvzr,
juvpu vf na rssrpgvir vapragvir flfgrz sbe perngvat naq qvfgevohgvat
grpuabybtvpny tnvaf. Ohg gur cevpr bs cebterff va pncvgnyvfz vf
vardhnyvgl.
Va bgure jbeqf, NV naq vgf nggraqnag cebqhpgvivgl tnvaf znl anghenyyl
pngnylmr n cebybatrq crevbq bs tebjgu. Ohg vapyhfvivgl jvyy bpphe bayl ol
pubvpr.
Va n cbfg-NV jbeyq, gurersber, creuncf gur fbyhgvba jbhyq or, nf Nygzna
fhttrfgf, gb gnk gur gjb “nffrgf gung jvyy znxr hc zbfg bs gur inyhr va [gur]
jbeyq,” anzryl, pbzcnavrf—rfcrpvnyyl gubfr gung ohvyq, znvagnva, naq hfr
NV—naq ynaq, juvpu fgvyy erznvaf svkrq (ng yrnfg urer ba Rnegu). Pregnvayl, vs
vaqvivqhny uhznaf ner abg erfcbafvoyr sbe gur inyhr bs ynobe gung pbzrf
sebz NV-trarengrq vafvtugf, vg vf ybtvpny gung guvf inyhr or funerq. Naq vg vf
irel cbffvoyr gung ynaq (naq, sbe n gvzr, gur ener-rnegu zvarenyf rffragvny gb
pbzchgvat) jvyy or nzbat gur srj gehyl svkrq—naq guhf inyhnoyr, naq guhf
gnknoyr—nffrgf va n cbfg-fpnepvgl jbeyq.
Ohg guvf fhttrfgvba nffhzrf gur pbagvahrq rkvfgrapr bs angvbaf (be gurve
erpbtavmnoyr fhofgvghgrf) nf erqvfgevohgvir ntragf, naq bs pbzcnavrf nf
cbgragvny gnetrgf sbe gnkngvba. Zberbire, cynpvat n cerzvhz ba obgu ynaq
naq vaabingvba pbhyq vapvgr raqyrff naq cbffvoyl ivbyrag fgehttyrf bire
cevznpl. Na nygreangvir ivfvba sbe rafhevat rdhvgl va gur ntr bs NV zvtug or
sbhaq va n shapgvba nanybtbhf gb gur fgbpx znexrg: anzryl, gur perngvba naq
nhgbzngvp tybony nffvtangvba bs qvivfvoyr havgf bs jrnygu nffbpvngrq jvgu gur
vapernfvat cebsvgf bs NV zbqryf. (Zbargnel evtugf zvtug pbzr, nf fbzr
funerf qb, jvgu ibgvat evtugf.)
Fgvyy nabgure cbffvovyvgl jbhyq or gb sbphf yrff ba gur bjarefuvc bs NV
guna ba gur qvfgevohgvba bs vgf hygvzngr orarsvgf. Ohg guvf jbhyq or fhowrpg gb
bccbfvgvba, obgu ba gur boivbhf tebhaqf gung vg fubhyq vafgrnq qvfgevohgr
bjarefuvc bs gur zrnaf bs cebqhpgvba, naq ba gur cenpgvpny tebhaqf gung vg
jbhyq erdhver n uhtr nzbhag bs ybtvfgvpf naq zbavgbevat gb rafher n

cnegvphyne fgnaqneq npebff ovyyvbaf bs vaqvivqhnyf.
N shegure bcgvba pbhyq gnxr vafcvengvba sebz gur cngrag flfgrz: nyybjvat
rkpyhfvir bjarefuvc bs na NV vairagvba naq vgf cebsvgf fb nf gb vapragvivmr
vzcebirzrag, ohg bayl sbe n yvzvgrq crevbq; orlbaq n pregnva qngr, nffhzvat
vgf fnsrgl unf orra cebira, gur zbqry pbhyq or choyvfurq (be, creuncf,
pbcvrf znqr naq vasenfgehpgher ohvyg va arj ybpnyrf) sbe pbzzba hfr,
vgrengvba, naq tnva.
Va oevrs: NV cvbarref znl haqrerfgvzngr gur fpbcr bs gur rpbabzvp naq
cbyvgvpny punyyratrf gung gurl unir frg va zbgvba. Lrf, NV jvyy or noyr gb qb
whfg nobhg nalguvat. Ohg, nf Fnz Nygzna chgf vg oyhagyl, “Vf vg tbvat gb qb
jung V jnag, be vf vg tbvat gb qb jung lbh jnag?”10 Ubj jvyy “jr” qrpvqr,
naq jub vf “jr”? Gb qverpg gurfr raretvrf bs rabezbhf cbffvovyvgl, naq gb
erqvfgevohgr gur orarsvgf bs gubfr qverpgvbaf, vf n tenir erfcbafvovyvgl. Shgher
qrpvfvba-znxref zhfg gnxr pner abg gb ragerapu bapr ntnva gur fbegf bs
fbpvny naq rpbabzvp vardhnyvgvrf gung fcernq bhgjneq sebz gur Vaqhfgevny
Eribyhgvba orsber ortvaavat gb or pbeerpgrq, zhpu gbb fybjyl, guebhtu
zber uhzna-qverpgrq fgehpgherf bs pbageby.11 12
Gbqnl gur cercbaqrenapr bs orarsvgf bs, naq nyzbfg rkpyhfvir pbageby
bire, nqinaprq NVf unf nppehrq gb rkgerzryl srj vaqvivqhnyf. Jvyy gurl tvir
hc gurve nqinagntrf? Vs gurl qb—vs naq jura zber orarsvgf naq zber
pbageby pbzr gb or funerq ng gur angvbany yriry—gura pnyyf sbe gur
tybonyvmngvba bs obgu jvyy ortva vzzrqvngryl. Jvyy bar angvba ghea vgf
fbirervta jrnygu vagb pbzzba orarsvg? Fbzr znl nethr gung gur
cflpubybtvpny oneevref gb fnpevsvpr jvyy qvfnccrne bapr gur jbeyq vf ab
ybatre mreb-fhz. Ohg guvf cerfhccbfrf n genafvgvba gung unf abg lrg pbzr gb
cnff, bar gung frrzf pbagenel gb gbqnl’f fgnghf dhb, naq bar gung—vs vg vf gb
cnff—jbhyq arrq gb or gur cebqhpg bs uhzna pubvpr.
Zberbire, rira vs jr znantr gb neevir va n jbeyq orlbaq fpnepvgl, vg vf
abg pyrne ubj tybony uhzna vapragvirf jbhyq or fgehpgherq gb erznva va
unezbal. N jbeyq orlbaq inyhr vf abg orlbaq inyhrf. Gubfr jub qb abg
pbzzhar ba gur onfvf bs zbarl znl pbzzhar—naq gura cebprrq gb
erneenatr fbpvrgl naq tybony vafgvghgvbaf—ba gur onfvf bs eryvtvba, enpr,
snzvyl yvarntr, rqhpngvba, zbenyvgl, fxvyy, nrfgurgvpf, uhzbe, be nal bgure
pngrtbel. Gubfr jub qb abg svtug sbe zbarl znl svtug sbe Tbq, cbjre,
tybel, be eriratr.

Shegurezber, rpbabzvp uvfgbel pbasvezf gur qvssvphygl bs qrivfvat
flfgrzf nf pbafvfgrag nf gurl ner rssrpgvir. Naq bar zhfg nqzvg gung uhznaf
unir orra varcg ng cerqvpgvat gur ybat-grez rssrpgf bs grpuabybtl; va gur
pnfr bs NV, bhe bcgvzvfz znl or hawhfgvsvrq naq bhe nccerurafvbaf
zvfcynprq.
Arireguryrff, gur nhgubef bs guvf obbx oryvrir gung NV pbhyq pbaprvinoyl
or unearffrq gb trarengr n arj onfryvar bs uhzna jrnygu naq jryy-orvat—
naq whfg gung cbffvovyvgl vgfrys qrznaqf gung jr znxr n fgneg va guvf qverpgvba.
Zberbire, jr ner pbasvqrag gung vs fhpu na rpbabzvp naq cbyvgvpny fpurzr
pbzrf gb cnff, vg jbhyq ng yrnfg rnfr vs abg ryvzvangr gur fgenvaf bs ynobe,
pynff, naq pbasyvpg gung cerivbhfyl unir gbea uhznavgl ncneg.
ZBOVYVGL
Vs, va gur ntr bs NV, bhe phc ehaargu bire, ubj pna jr rafher gung rirel
uhzna vf pncnoyr bs erzbgryl naq eryvnoyl orarsvgvat sebz gur arj fhecyhf?
Nyernql, uhznavgl unf znqr terng fgevqrf va gur qvfgevohgvba bs inyhr: sebz
gur rneyvrfg pheerapvrf, juvpu yvtugrarq gur oheqraf sbezreyl vzcbfrq ol
flfgrzf bs onegre, gb yngre vgrengvbaf bs svng pheerapvrf va cncre naq pbva, nf
jryy nf va fhpu qvtvgny vairagvbaf nf perqvg pneqf, jver genafsref, naq zbovyr
onaxvat. Juvyr gurfr irffryf unir snpvyvgngrq n zber rssvpvrag zbirzrag bs
inyhr npebff fcnpr, qhr gb gurve wvggrel fhccyl gurl unir haqrecresbezrq va
gurve inyhr bire gvzr. Zbqrea cebwrpgf va pheerapl frrx gur rssvpvrag genafsre
bs inyhr npebff obgu fcnpr naq gvzr.
Gur zbqrea rpbabzl vf fgvyy sbezrq ol gur cebqhpgvba bs tbbqf naq gur
cebivfvba bs freivprf, abg ol gurve vaqverpg, nofgenpg ercerfragngvbaf. Zbarl
vf ahyy jvgubhg n znexrgcynpr; vg orpbzrf bayl na ragel va n qngnonfr sbe
erfbhepr nyybpngvba, va juvpu inyhr prnfrf gb ubyq zrnavat. Ivrjrq guebhtu
gur yraf bs vasbezngvba gurbel, zbarl gbqnl unf zhpu va pbzzba jvgu na
vagrearg pbaarpgvba, juvpu sbe nal erpbtavmnoyr hfr fvzvyneyl erdhverf
eryngvbany pbagrkg. Ubj orfg gb bcgvzvmr vgf grpuavpny nggevohgrf znl va gur
ntr bs NV orpbzr n gnfx bs vzzrafr cuvybfbcuvpny naq grpuavpny hetrapl.
Dhvgr cbffvoyl, gur jbeyq jvyy arrq n arj glcr bs svanapvny argjbex gung
onynaprf gur genqvgvbany shapgvbaf bs zbarl nf n pbafvfgrag fgber bs inyhr
naq pbairavrag zrnaf bs rkpunatr.

NV pbhyq nyfb vagebqhpr arj qlanzvpf gb svanapvny znexrgf naq
rpbabzvp cbyvpvrf. Vg vf rnfl gb vzntvar, nofgenpgyl naq va cevapvcyr, ubj NV
zvtug tb nobhg perngvat jrnygu—rira jvgu npprff bayl gb gur vagrearg. Ohg
rira vs jr pna vairag pheerapvrf, flfgrzf, znexrgf, naq cbyvpvrf gung
erfcbaq jvfryl gb gur rzretrapr bs guvf fpnyr bs cbgragvny inyhr-trarengvba,
ubj, rknpgyl, jbhyq NV fbyir be raq cbiregl, sbe rknzcyr? Nf n cenpgvpny
znggre, ubj jbhyq vg rfgnoyvfu na nofbyhgr tybony onfryvar sbe bhe dhnyvgl bs
yvsr?
Vs NV cebirf gb or pncnoyr bs culfvpnyyl qvfgevohgvat gur tbbqf gung
uhznaf erdhver sbe bhe shaqnzragny zngrevny arrqf, gura gur ibyhzr bs
zngrevnyf gung pbhyq or trarengrq naq zbirq nebhaq gur jbeyq jvyy or
hacerprqragrq. Gurer ner haqbhogrqyl znal cbffvovyvgvrf sbe fhpu n iragher
—naq whfg nf znal cvgsnyyf. Qvfgevohgrq NV flfgrzf zvtug or qrfvtarq gb
pbaarpg, ivn znff-znahsnpgherq ebobgf naq NV-bcgvzvmrq vasenfgehpgheny
flfgrzf, gb gur hapbaarpgrq. Gubfr arj pbaarpgvbaf—ynpxvat sbe fbzr 2.6
ovyyvba crbcyr gbqnl—jbhyq ranoyr gur cebivfvba bs sbbq, pybguvat, naq
furygre gb gur unys bs uhznavgl gung fgvyy ynpxf gubfr onfvp arprffvgvrf.13
Nygreangviryl, hfvat arj fhfgnvanoyr flagurgvp zngrevnyf, NVf pbhyq ohvyq
pvgvrf nebhaq gur jbeyq gb cebivqr furygre, erthyngr grzcrengher, rafher
npprff gb cbjre naq qvtvgny pbaarpgvbaf, naq cebivqr pyrna jngre, sbbq,
zrqvpvar, naq fnavgngvba. Znpuvar vagryyvtraprf bs inevbhf pbzcyrkvgl
pbhyq rira freivpr gurfr pvgvrf, juvpu pbhyq ubhfr graf bs zvyyvbaf bs
crbcyr jub zvtug bgurejvfr or yvivat bhgfvqr gur flfgrz bs cebfcrevgl gung
gbb srj bs hf rawbl gbqnl.
Creuncf obgu nygreangvirf jbhyq or ernyvmrq, nybatfvqr bgure shgherf gung
jr unir abg lrg vzntvarq. Va gung pnfr, uhznaf jbhyq ergnva gurve bcgvbaf—
naq yvxryl rawbl zber serrqbz bs pubvpr guna orsber. Jvgu uhznaf ab
ybatre obhaq gb gur trbtencul bs gurve ovegu, gur pbzzhavgvrf bs gurve xva,
be gur ynobe znexrgf sbe gurve fxvyy, jurer jbhyq gurl zbir vs vzzvtengvba
jrer genafsbezrq sebz n gentvp arprffvgl sbe fbzr gb n serr pubvpr sbe nyy?
Vs n ynetr ahzore bs arj pvgvrf bs gur fnzr uvtu dhnyvgl jrer gb or ohvyg ol
NV, jbhyq jr fgvyy frr znff zvtengvba sebz haqrirybcrq gb qrirybcrq
angvbaf, be sebz eheny frggvatf gb heona barf, nf uvfgbevpnyyl unf orra gur
pnfr?
Terngre cflpubybtvpny serrqbz va gur sbezngvba bs snzvyvrf zvtug nyfb

orpbzr n ernyvgl gunaxf gb NV. Fbzr zvtug pubbfr gb unir zber puvyqera,
serrq bs gur arprffvgl gb znxr qnzavat qrpvfvbaf nobhg ubj gb nyybpngr
erfbheprf nzbat zhygvcyr puvyqera onfrq ba juvpu bs gurz unir gur
terngrfg punapr bs fheiviny naq fhpprff. Bguref, vs ab ybatre eryvnag ba
bssfcevat sbe fhccbeg va byq ntr, zvtug ersenva sebz cebperngvba.
Trarengvbany oheqraf pbhyq qvffvcngr, ranoyvat puvyqera gb chefhr
trbtencuvrf naq cebsrffvbaf gurl zvtug cerivbhfyl unir qvfpbhagrq.
Rneyvre vzonynaprf naq nflzzrgevrf va gur tybony rpbabzl unir qrevirq
sebz qvssreraprf va, nzbat bgure snpgbef, erfbhepr raqbjzrag, trbtencul,
naq uhzna pncvgny. NV pbhyq erqhpr gnyrag tncf naq rdhnyvmr erfbhepr
qvfgevohgvbaf. Gung jbhyq eraqre yrff eryrinag gur cerqbzvanag snhyg yvarf ba
juvpu jr unir ybat pbaqhpgrq tybony genqr naq pbzzrepr naq ol juvpu
gur jbeyq’f cebfcrevgl vf fgengvsvrq. Pbhagevrf gung gbqnl ner qvfnqinagntrq
ol gurve greevgbevny be bgure raqbjzragf, be gung ner fhssrevat sebz “oenva
qenva,” pbhyq svaq gurzfryirf jvgu arj zrnaf bs nqinapvat gb gur fnzr
pvephzfgnagvny fgnaqneqf nf gubfr rawblrq ol gur tybor’f genqvgvbany
rpbabzvp tvnagf.
Ubj qb jr genafvgvba sebz gbqnl’f vagreangvbany vardhnyvgl gb gur shgher
jr qrfpevor? Gur svefg fgrc, creuncf, vf gur qrfvta bs NV-ranoyrq flfgrzf
naq nccyvpngvbaf gb nqinapr zngrevny fpvraprf naq bcgvzvmr qvtvgny
pbaarpgvbaf—vapyhqvat gur checbfr-ohvyg qngnfrgf gung jbhyq ranoyr fhpu
flfgrzf gb shapgvba va n inevrgl bs tybony pbagrkgf. Nf jr vairfg va gurfr
vqrnf, jr fubhyq xrrc va zvaq gur cbgragvny tnvaf: n cebsbhaq
genafsbezngvba va gur birenyy fgnaqneq bs pbyyrpgvir uhzna yvsr, naq va gur
rdhnyvgl bs vaqvivqhny yvirf npebff enpr, traqre, angvbanyvgl, cynpr bs ovegu,
naq snzvyl onpxtebhaq. Na rdhnyvmngvba bs gur pbfg bs vagryyvtrapr,
qvfgevohgrq npebff gur tybor, pbhyq oevat nobhg n yriry cynlvat svryq gung unf
arire orsber rkvfgrq.
NOHAQNAPR JVGUBHG NONAQBA
Ohg jung vs NV, juvyr npgvat nf na rpbabzvp rdhnyvmre, fraqf gur pbfg bs
vagryyvtrapr, naq gurersber bs ynobe, cyhzzrgvat gbjneq mreb? Gung jbhyq
pbapyhqr gur oevrs ohg jbaqreshyyl cebqhpgvir crevbq bs uhzna uvfgbel gung
unf nyybjrq vaqvivqhnyf va serr fbpvrgvrf gb vzcebir gurve pvephzfgnaprf,

fubhyq gurl fb pubbfr, ol gurve bja rssbegf. Nf fpnepvgl unf orra gur
cnenqvtz bs gur cnfg, pbzcrgvgvba—ng yrnfg va gur zbqrea ren—unf orra gur
qrsnhyg pbaqvgvba bs frys-betnavmngvba, yrnqvat anghenyyl gb jvqr inevngvbaf
va gur qvfgevohgvba bs bhgpbzrf nf n shapgvba bs nzovgvba, novyvgl, naq gur
ybggrel bs jurer naq gb jubz bar jnf obea.
Nyy bs guvf unf zrnag gung, ol naq ynetr, uhznaf zber vaqhfgevbhf va gur
nccyvpngvba bs gurve ynobef be va gur unearffvat bs bguref’ ynobef unir snerq
orggre juvyr bguref unir snerq jbefr. Vs, ubjrire, jr erzbir gur fbegvat
shapgvba bs ynobe, jr zhfg nyfb pbagraq jvgu gur erzbiny bs cebsrffvbaf naq
gur fgnghf, vqragvgl, naq zrnavat gung ner nffbpvngrq jvgu gurz. Guvf jbhyq
or n qvssrerag jbeyq vaqrrq.
Bhe angheny vafgvapgf sbe birepbzvat nqirefvgl, sbe pryroengvat
rkpryyrapr, sbe gnxvat cevqr va abgnoyr qvssrerapr naq qvirefvgl, jvyy fheryl
fgvyy rkvfg, gubhtu gurl jvyy arrq gb frrx arj punaaryf. Whfg nf bapr gurer
jrer qvfgevohgvbaf bs harira uhzna gnyragf sbe ynobe, gurer znl nevfr arj
qvfgevohgvbaf bs harira uhzna gnyragf sbe yrvfher. Naq, guvf gvzr, fhpu
qvfgevohgvbaf zvtug snyy abg nybat rkvfgvat nkrf bs novyvgl ohg engure nybat
nkrf bs n qvssrerag dhnyvgl: phevbfvgl, fboevrgl, xvaqarff, be creuncf
fbzrguvat ryfr ragveryl.
Va n jbeyq jvgubhg jbex, znal bs hf zvtug orpbzr ragenaprq naq
rathysrq ol fvzhyngrq, phfgbz-vzzrefvir jbeyqf: n frafhbhf bepurfgen bs
fvtug, fbhaq, fzryy, gbhpu, naq rira gnfgr abj znqr cbffvoyr ol NV’f
pbzcyrgr cbjref va gur iveghny ernyz. Nf qvfphffrq va Puncgre 3, ovyyvbaf bs
cnffvir uhznaf pbhyq cynhfvoyl pubbfr—be or yherq qbja—guvf cngu,
svaqvat vg arvgure rnfl abe arprffnel gb erfvfg fb vafgnagnarbhf na hctenqr va
gur yriry bs fgvzhyngvba va, naq gur srryvat bs pbageby bire, gurve ernyvgl.
Rira gbqnl, jura crbcyr ner abg bgurejvfr bpphcvrq jvgu gur
gevohyngvbaf bs yvsr naq ynobe, gur yvtug va znal rlrf vf yvxryl gb ersyrpg gur
tybj bs cvkryrq cyngrf bs tynff. Va rirel pbeare bs gur jbeyq, jbexref,
rkunhfgrq sebz gurve qnlf bs gbvy, haqrefgnaqnoyl ergerng gb guvf yvtugre,
chere zrqvhz gb pbafhzr naq gb perngr.14 Vs uhznaf nyernql fgehttyr gb
erfgenva gurve nggenpgvba gb gbqnl’f eryngviryl cevzvgvir grpuabybtvrf, ubj
jvyy jr rire unaqyr gur infgyl fhcrevbe “rkcrevrapr znpuvarf” gung ner fher
gb or ranoyrq ol NV?15 Vs znal bs hf pna oneryl gbyrengr gur cnva bs jbex,
ubj jvyy jr erfvfg hadhnyvsvrq cyrnfher?

Gur nafjre vf gung uhzna cflpubybtl jvyy arrq gb pbribyir jvgu NV naq
vgf rssrpgf. Vg vf qvssvphyg gb cerqvpg ubj, cerpvfryl, ohg vg frrzf cbffvoyr gung
NV pbhyq va snpg ranoyr uhzna zrnavat nf zhpu nf, be zber guna, vg qrgenpgf
sebz vg. Cyrnfher nybar jvyy abg fngvfsl bhe vaangr qrfver sbe zrnavat. Jbex
—rira vs abg sbe cnl—pna cebivqr n frafr bs checbfr vafbsne nf gur zrnaf
ner fgerahbhf be gur raqf ner aboyr.
N crefbany rkcrevrapr bs qvssvphygl pna vafgvyy n frafr bs cevqr bapr gung
punyyratr vf birepbzr. Fgerahbhf gbvy, rfcrpvnyyl jura pbzovarq jvgu
pbzzvgzrag, yraqf vgf bja aneengvir nep gb bhe haqrefgnaqvat bs gvzr, gur
frys, naq gur uhzna pncnpvgl sbe znfgrel. Tvira bhe uhzna cflpubybtl,
znal fbheprf bs wbl naq pbagragzrag znl jryy erznva hapunatrq va gur
ntr bs NV, qrfcvgr gur zlevnq punatrf gung ner fher gb fjrrc guebhtu bhe
yvirf.
Guvf vf abg gb fnl gung jr jvyy fvzcyl erireg gb npgvivgvrf bs gur cnfg;
vafgrnq, jr znl qvfpbire nfcrpgf bs uhzna cbgragvny gung jr unq abg
cerivbhfyl chefhrq ng fpnyr. Pbafvqre gur cbffvovyvgvrf gung zvtug rzretr
sebz crevbqf bs uhzna sbphf gung hagvy abj unir orra vzcbffvoyr gb vapyhqr
va na beqvanel crefba’f jbexvat jrrx. Zragny naq fcvevghny rkrepvfrf,
cresbezrq ng yratgu, pbhyq ryringr uhzna pbafpvbhfarff. Rkgraqrq crevbqf
bs urvtugrarq njnerarff znl va ghea nffvfg bhe eryngvbany pbaarpgvbaf gb
bgure uhznaf (naq navznyf), fgeratgura bhe creprcgvbaf bs gur qvivar, naq
cebqhpr zrnavatshyyl ryringrq yriryf bs vaqvivqhny jryy-orvat.
Hanffvfgrq uhznaf cresbezvat nccneragyl fhcreuhzna srngf, rfcrpvnyyl
gubfr vaibyivat gur hfr bs bhe culfvpny obqvrf, jvyy ab qbhog erznva riragf
bs snfpvangvba. Jvgu terngre ahzoref bs uhznaf ragrevat naq nggrzcgvat gb
znfgre fhpu npgvivgvrf, bar zvtug rkcrpg fbnevat rkpryyrapr. Fcbegf naq
tnzrf gung chfu gur uhzna gb gur yvzvg pbhyq vapernfr va cerinyrapr naq
dhnyvgl. Neg pbhyq sybhevfu, sbe gur evat bs gur nhguragvp vf yvxryl gb ergnva vgf
punez.
Havirefvgvrf uvfgbevpnyyl pbzzvggrq gurzfryirf gb tvivat gurve fghqragf
na rdhny vagebqhpgvba obgu gb gur fpvraprf naq gb gur uhznavgvrf.16 Jr
oryvrir gurfr dhvagrffragvnyyl uhzna raqrnibef, rnpu va vgf bja jnl n
“dhrfg sbe zrnavat” (gb obeebj n cuenfr sebz bar fcvevghny yrnqre),17 jvyy vs
nalguvat rkcnaq. Va gur Jrfg, gur yvoreny negf jrer gur fhowrpgf naq fxvyyf
uryq ol pynffvpny nagvdhvgl gb or znexref bs na vaqrcraqrag zvaq. Va gur

napvrag Fvabfcurer, gur Gnat qlanfgl negvfg Munat Lnalhna rfgnoyvfurq gung
n “fpubyne-tragyrzna” fubhyq or rkcrpgrq gb qrzbafgengr cebsvpvrapl va
“gur sbhe negf”: novyvgvrf bs fbhaq, fvtug, fgengrtl, naq fpevcg.18 Va gur shgher,
naq va pbagenfg gb fpubbyf bs rqhpngvba gung ner ibpngvbany, cebsrffvbany, be
grpuavpny, jr znl ubcr sbe n eriviny bs fbzr bs gur rneyvrfg nggrzcgf gb
ahegher gur “yrnearq vaqvivqhny” pncnoyr naq qrfvebhf bs qvirefr pnyyvat.
Fpubbyf nebhaq gur jbeyq pbhyq cebqhpr gur cuvybfbcuref naq jevgref jr
arrq sbe erbevragngvba gb na ragveryl arj ntr.
Fhowrpgf bapr erfreirq sbe gur cevivyrtrq srj pbhyq orpbzr fgnaqneq sbe
gur znal, ercynpvat gur nirentr pynffebbz’f cerivbhf sbphf ba gur nffrzoyl
bs cebqhpgvir ynobe. Qrcyblzrag bs NV rqhpngbef pbhyq ranoyr
vaqvivqhnyvmrq vafgehpgvba naq Fbpengvp frzvanef nebhaq gur jbeyq. Vzntvar
vs, whfg nf n lbhat Nyoreg Rvafgrva jnf ghgberq ol Znk Gnyzhq (yngre Znk
Gnyzrl), Ibygnver ol gur Nooé qr Puâgrnharhs, naq Nqn Ybirynpr (jub
jebgr gur svefg pbzchgre nytbevguz) ol Znel Fbzreivyyr, rirel puvyq jbhyq
abj or snveyl ranoyrq va gur fnzr jnlf gb znfgre uvf be ure zvaq naq
punenpgre.19
Jr pna vzntvar gung jurer havirefvgvrf fgnaq gbqnl—gehr gb gurve
bevtvany sbez, na nffrzoyntr bs qbezvgbevrf rapvepyvat n yvoenel bs obbxf
nebhaq juvpu rntre zvaqf tngure gb nggnva naq rkgraq gur vagryyrpghny
sebagvre—
pnzchfrf zvtug fbzrqnl vapyhqr fcnprf bs pbatertngvba sbe grnzf bs
uhznaf gb vagrecerg gur qvfpbirevrf bs NV vgfrys: gung vf, gb haqrefgnaq gurz
naq gb genafyngr gur zbfg cebzvarag nzbat gurz vagb eryrinapr sbe uhzna
yvsr.
Va guvf arj oenapu bs gur fpvraprf, uhznaf zvtug pubbfr gb pbribyir
jvgu NV va beqre gb erznva cnegaref jvgu gur znpuvarf ng gur sebagvre. Be gung
znl ghea bhg abg gb or arprffnel va beqre sbe hf gb znkvzvmr gur orarsvgf gb
uhznavgl sebz NV’f qvfpbirevrf. Va rvgure pnfr, naq rfcrpvnyyl gur ynggre, jr
rkcrpg guvf gb or na rkgenbeqvanevyl qvssvphyg npgvivgl, jbexvat fvqr ol fvqr
jvgu bhe znpuvarf va nebhaq-gur-pybpx fuvsgf. Ohg ubjrire tehryvat, gur
rssbeg, shegure rkcyberq va Puncgre 8, jbhyq or rffragvny.
GUR CEVIVYRTR BS PUBVPR

Snprq jvgu gur creprvirq guerng sebz gur nhgbzngvba bs uhzna ynobe, znal
pbzzragngbef gbqnl svkngr ba gur nqirag bs n arj fcvevghny pevfvf: Va n jbeyq
bs funerq nohaqnapr, gurl nethr, jr jbhyq orpbzr yvxr veerfcbafvoyr
ybggrel jvaaref, birepbzr ol gur urqbavfz bs rkprff. Guvf, va bhe ivrj, vf n
crefcrpgvir bs cevivyrtr. Gb nccerpvngr gur rkgenbeqvanel tbbq gung NV jvyy
qb sbe ovyyvbaf bs crbcyr—vapyhqvat gubfr jub pheeragyl ynpx gur zbarl,
pbaarpgvivgl, onfvp arprffvgvrf, naq yrvfher gvzr gb cnegvpvcngr va batbvat
pbairefngvbaf bs bhe xvaq urer—bar arrq bayl pnyy gb zvaq gur pbagenfgvat
ybg bs gurve sberornef: trarengvbaf bs snguref bcrengvat znpuvarf bs cevzvgvir
znxr, zbguref fgehttyvat va svryqf bs nevq uneirfg, puvyq ynoberef eboorq bs
gurve vaabprapr. Vs, gbzbeebj zbeavat, rirel uhzna jrer tvira gur pubvpr
gb fgbc jbexvat, jr fhfcrpg zbfg jbhyq qb fb, juvyr gur srj jub qrpyvarq
jbhyq yvxryl or cevivyrtrq gb jbex abg bhg bs boyvtngvba ohg bhg bs pubvpr.
NV pbhyq or qverpgrq gb qb jung jr ab ybatre unir gb qb, cerpvfryl fb gung
jr pna qb gur guvatf jr jnag gb qb.
Nf qrgnvyrq va Puncgre 3, jr qb jbeel gung n terng senpgvba bs uhznaf
pbhyq orpbzr cevznevyl cnffvir pbafhzref bs NV-trarengrq pbagrag. Ohg
guvf vf n pbaprea gung fgrzf sebz gur uhzna graqrapl gbjneq rnfl
pbafhzcgvba—naq, zber gebhoyvat fgvyy, sebz jung jr pna bayl nffhzr
jvyy or NV’f shgher creprcgvba bs hf. Va bgure jbeqf, bhe pbaprea nobhg
uhzna cnffvivgl vf abg nobhg gur uhzna ybff bs cnvq jbex. Jr nyernql unir
n cebgbglcr bs ubj crbcyr yvir jura gurl pna unir jung gurl jnag jvgubhg
jbexvat. Jr pnyy gurz gur evpu naq gur ergverq. Pregnvayl, gur evpu—
vapyhqvat znal jub jrer abg evpu cerivbhfyl—ner fbzrgvzrf ng n ybff sbe
ubj gb rkrepvfr gurve bcgvbaf nsgre fb znal lrnef fcrag nznffvat gurz. Nf
Gbyfgbl cebsrffrq, “Vs n snvel unq pbzr naq bssrerq gb shysvyy zl rirel jvfu,
V jbhyq abg unir xabja jung gb jvfu sbe.”20
Gur nqwhfgzrag gb nohaqnapr vf yvxryl n ceboyrz bs genafvgvba engure guna
n creznarag punyyratr. Fbzr jvyy vavgvnyyl creprvir gur vagebqhpgvba bs
znpuvar ynobef nf qrcevivat gurz bs gurve cevznel fbhepr bs shysvyyzrag naq
wbl. Ab qbhog guvf jvyy or n wneevat rkcrevrapr. Ohg gb hf vg frrzf yvxryl—
abg nf n erfcbafr gb bhe rkubegngvba ohg engure nf na bhgtebjgu bs uhzna
vafgvapg—gung, tvira gvzr, uhznaf jbhyq pubbfr gb crefrirer, creuncf va
arj nirahrf be nf cnegaref bs NV, nibvqvat ngebcul naq vafgrnq rkpryyvat nf
guvaxref naq qbref. Hygvzngryl, vs jr rfgnoyvfu gur arrqrq flfgrzf sbe

qvfgevohgvba, pbaarpgvba, cnegvpvcngvba, naq rqhpngvba, uhznaf—rzcbjrerq
naq vafcverq ol NV—znl pbagvahr jbexvat abg sbe cnl ohg sbe cyrnfher naq
cevqr.

PUNCGRE 7
FPVRAPR
NV VF CBVFRQ gb erqrsvar gur cbffvovyvgvrf bs rirel perngvir ragrecevfr naq gb
frnepu sbe arj pbapyhfvbaf va rirel fpvragvsvp svryq. Va ghea, fhofrdhrag
rkcybengvbaf ner nyzbfg pregnva gb ersvar naq raynetr gur pvephzsrerapr bs
uhzna haqrefgnaqvat. Nf qvfphffrq va Puncgre 1, vg vf pbaprvinoyr, creuncf
rira yvxryl, gung NV jvyy chfu bhgjneq va nyy qverpgvbaf ng bapr, naq gung vgf
fhpprffrf ba nyy sebagf jvyy or inyvqngrq, nofbeorq, naq pbzcbhaqrq vagb
znffvir ohyxurnqf bs arj uhzna xabjyrqtr.
Vs gur erprag cnfg unf orra qrsvarq ol uhzna gevhzcuf va gur ratvarrevat
bs pbzcyvpngrq flfgrzf—zvpebcebprffbef, gur vagrearg, wrg ratvarf, cnegvpyr
nppryrengbef—gur shgher jvyy or qrsvarq ol NV’f ratvarrevat bs uvtu-
qvzrafvbany, pbzcyrk flfgrzf: uhzna rpbabzvrf, ovbybtvpny yvsr, naq gur
pyvzngr bs ragver cynargf, bguref’ naq bhe bja.1
GUR TNEQRA BS ZRQVPVAR
Gur sentvyvgl bs uhzna urnygu unf orra erfcbafvoyr sbe zber cerzngher
qrnguf naq haarprffnel cnva guna nal pbasyvpg be angheny qvfnfgre va uvfgbel.2
Gubhtu bire gur cnfg gjb praghevrf jr unir znqr pehqr naq vapbzcyrgr
nggrzcgf gb qrpvcure naq pbageby gur pbqr bs yvsr, bhe novyvgl gb cebprrq jvgu
terngre cerpvfvba naq vagrag unf orra vzcrqrq ol n fvatyr zvffvat
vaterqvrag: anzryl, na vagryyvtrapr pncnoyr bs haqrefgnaqvat gung pbqr ng n
fhssvpvrag yriry bs qrgnvy. Abj, cebcryyrq ol gur rzretrapr bs na
vagryyvtrapr gung sne rkprrqf bhe bja, jr ner pbairetvat hcba n eribyhgvba
va ovbybtl gung znl punatr bhe pbaprcgvba bs uhzna yvsr.

Sbhaqrq va gur friragrragu praghel ol na rqvpg bs Xvat Ybhvf KVVV bs
Senapr, naq cynprq haqre gur nhgubevgl bs uvf eblny culfvpvna, Yr Wneqva
eblny qrf cynagrf zéqvpvanyrf—gur Eblny Tneqra bs Zrqvpvany Cynagf—jnf
gur ynetrfg naq zbfg nqinaprq fhpu cebwrpg bs vgf gvzr. Fpvragvsvp
rkcrqvgvbaf gb cynprf nf sne-syhat nf Wnin naq gur Nznmba unq erghearq jvgu
n qnmmyvat inevrgl bs cynagf, zrgvphybhfyl fghqvrq sbe gurve cbgragvny
zrqvpvany hfr ol n qrqvpngrq fgnss bs obgnavfgf.
Yrff guna n qrpnqr yngre, gur Serapu zbanepu uvzfrys jbhyq fhpphzo gb
ghorephybfvf; ab rneguyl nagvqbgr unq orra fgebat rabhtu gb rnfr uvf cnva be
qrynl uvf qrngu. Ohg gur tneqra qvq fhpprffshyyl cebqhpr gerngzragf naq
pherf sbhaq abjurer ryfr va gur jbeyq.3 Gbqnl, NV unf gur cbgragvny gb or n
fvzvyneyl fhcreany yvoenel bs cuneznprhgvpnyf, bcravat sbe uhzna orarsvg n
infg arj ercbfvgbel bs erzrqvrf sbe gur nyyrivngvba bs fvpxarff naq fgenva.
Rkgenbeqvanevyl nqrcg ng trarengvat arj pbzovangvbaf bs qrsvarq vgrzf
naq vqragvslvat gurve uvturfg-cresbezvat nggevohgrf, eribyhgvbanel NVf yvxr
NycunSbyq sebz QrrcZvaq—jvgu vgf tvtnagvp qngnonfr bs bire 200 zvyyvba
cebgrva fgehpgher cerqvpgvbaf—unir bcrarq arj ivfgnf va tybony urnygu. NV
vf yvxryl gb cebqhpr oernxguebhtuf abg bayl va gur ratvarrevat bs nqqvgvbany
cebgrvaf, vapyhqvat arj ubezbarf, ramlzrf, naq nagvobqvrf, ohg nyfb va
vqragvslvat gur zbyrphyne pnhfrf bs inevbhf qvfrnfrf naq qrirybcvat
cbgragvny gerngzragf sbe gurz. Va ghea, zrqvpny pner, erylvat ba NV’f
hacerprqragrq erfbyhgvba ng gur zbyrphyne naq trabzvp fpnyr, pbhyq orpbzr
vapernfvatyl crefbany—jvgu qehtf, nybat jvgu gurve zrgubqf bs qryvirel,
gnvyberq gb rnpu vaqvivqhny’f havdhr zrgnobyvp cebsvyr, evfx bs nqqvpgvba,
rfgvzngrq gbyrenaprf, naq fhfprcgvovyvgl gb cbgragvny fvqr rssrpgf.
Uhzna qbpgbef pbzzvggrq gb gur eryvrs bs uhzna fhssrevat jbhyq guhf
unir n cnegare gb nvq gurz va shysvyyvat gurve zrepvshy pnyyvat. Znpuvar
vafgehpgvba pbhyq thvqr gur zbfg fxvyyrq bs uhzna unaqf—nf va
arhebfhetrel—gb cresbez bcrengvbaf ybat gubhtug cbffvoyr ohg gbb evfxl gb
or pneevrq bhg fnsryl. NV vf nyernql urycvat gb svaq abaqrfgehpgvir be
abavagehfvir cnguf guebhtu gur oenva gb erzbir n fbhepr bs qrovyvgngvba
zrpunavpnyyl be gb pher vg ovbybtvpnyyl. Jurer ceboyrzf ner abg culfvpny ohg
cflpubybtvpny va angher, NV pbhyq pbzong pbtavgvir ybff, zragny vyyarff,
cflpuvngevp qvfbeqref, naq cbffvoyl rira ybaryvarff.
Vaqrrq, naq zhpu gb or ubcrq, NV pbhyq nyfb zbir hf njnl sebz

gerngzrag naq pybfre gb ceriragvba, guhf erqhpvat gur arrq gb pher ng nyy.
Npgvat nf ivtvynag rneyl-jneavat zrpunavfzf, NV flfgrzf pbhyq nyreg hf gb
znyvtanapvrf naq noabeznyvgvrf ybat orsber gurl ribyir vagb frevbhf guerngf.
Ng gur fbpvrgny yriry, gbb, NVf zvtug orpbzr nqinaprq urnygu-zbavgbevat
flfgrzf, pncnoyr bs vqragvslvat naq arhgenyvmvat vasrpgvbhf qvfrnfrf orsber
gurl ribyir vagb cynargnel cnaqrzvpf.
Lrg nyy gur nobir fpranevbf, rira gur bar eryngrq gb ceriragvat qvfrnfr
naq cerzngher qrngu, ner rknzcyrf bs erzrqvngvba. Gurl ner jnlf va juvpu
NV zvtug uryc hf gb zvgvtngr be fbyir vffhrf gung pheeragyl qent qbja
vaqvivqhny urnygu orybj rkvfgvat fgnaqneqf bs nqrdhngr jryy-orvat. Ohg jung
bs nqinaprzragf gung pbhyq erqrsvar gur znkvzhz bs uhzna urnygu?
Zntavsvrq ol NV, fbzr zrqvpny nqinaprf jvyy zbir sebz gurencvrf gb
rkgrafvbaf bs uhzna ybatrivgl. Gur erprag curabzraba bs trar rqvgvat
qrzbafgengrf gur arnearff naq srnfvovyvgl bs fhpu oernxguebhtuf. Fpvragvfgf
jvryqvat gur ovbgrpuabybtl xabja nf PEVFCE-Pnf9—naq nabgure inevngvba
pnyyrq cevzr rqvgvat—ortva ol vqragvslvat n fcrpvsvp trargvp frdhrapr gung
gurl jbhyq yvxr gb znavchyngr. N cerqrfvtarq fgenaq bs EAN pna gura thvqr
nabgure fcrpvny ramlzr gb n gnetrgrq cvrpr bs QAN ba gung frdhrapr,
bcravat vg gb znxr gur arprffnel punatrf naq pbeerpgvbaf. Hfvat fhpu gbbyf,
naq gurve fhpprffbef, vg znl orpbzr cbffvoyr gb pbadhre abg bayl bhe
qrsvpvrapvrf ohg zbegnyvgl vgfrys.
Qrngu, ubjrire, unf nyjnlf orra uhznavgl’f qvivaryl vzcbfrq yvzvg,
jvgu ab nggrzcg ng rkrzcgvba yrsg hachavfurq. Pbafvqre gur zlgu bs
Fvflcuhf, gur pensgl naq phaavat xvat bs napvrag Rculen (abj Pbevagu),
jub jnf gb or vzcevfbarq va gur haqrejbeyq sbe natrevat gur tbqf. Ur
rfpncrq zbegnyvgl ol n gevpx—ovaqvat Gunangbf, gur tbq bs qrngu uvzfrys,
va uvf bja funpxyrf—orsber syrrvat onpx gb gur ynaq bs gur yvivat. Ohg
jvgubhg qrngu gb gnxr nalbar (be nalguvat) njnl, nyy uryy oebxr bhg ba
Rnegu. Gur byq naq fvpx fhssrerq jvgu ab raq, pnggyr pbhyq abg or fynhtugrerq
sbe pbafhzcgvba, naq navznyf pbhyq abg or xvyyrq sbe fnpevsvpr gb gur tbqf.
Gurer’f zber gb gur gnyr, ohg gur pevfvf riraghnyyl raqrq jura Nerf, gur
Terrx tbq bs jne, vagreirarq, serrvat Gunangbf naq ranoyvat Fvflcuhf gb
rfpncr sebz gur qrrc nolff bs Gnegnehf n frpbaq gvzr. Ohg gung jnf vg: N
pnhgvbanel rknzcyr jnf znqr bs gur Terrx xvat orsber n guveq genafterffvba
pbhyq fhpprrq.
Qrngu erznvaf gur terng rdhnyvmre bs yvsr. Rira gur Puvarfr rzcrebe Dva

Fuv Uhnat4—n ehzberq fba bs urnira naq na rneyl frrxre bs gur ryvkve bs
yvsr—qvrq sebz qevaxvat gbb zhpu zrephel naq jnf ohevrq nzbat uvf infg
nezl bs pynl. Frrxvat vzzbegnyvgl, vg fbzrgvzrf frrzf, bayl freirf gb
unfgra vgf bccbfvgr.
Orfvqrf, bhe vzcreznarapr unf vgf orarsvgf. Vg sbphfrf gur zvaq naq
yraqf terngre hetrapl gb bhe raqrnibef. Nf gur Nzrevpna jevgre Wnpx
Ybaqba qrpynerf gevhzcunagyl: “Gur cebcre shapgvba bs zna vf gb yvir, abg
gb rkvfg. V funyy abg jnfgr zl qnlf va gelvat gb cebybat gurz. V funyy hfr zl
gvzr.”5 Sbe bguref, jevgrf Gbyfgbl (dhbgvat Fbpengrf), “Jr zbir pybfre gb
gur gehgu bayl gb gur rkgrag gung jr zbir shegure sebz yvsr.”6 Gur terng
culfvpvfg Wbua iba Arhznaa, jura qlvat bs grezvany pnapre, erdhrfgrq gung
n Pngubyvp cevrfg nppbzcnal uvz va uvf svany qnlf—uvf snvgu ab ybatre ng
bqqf jvgu gur ntabfgvp fpvrapr ur unq cvbarrerq.7 Ner gurer abg hfrf sbe
raqvatf?
Gbqnl be gbzbeebj, jr zvtug svaq bhefryirf erdhverq gb purpx gur
qrterr gb juvpu NV pna rkgraq bhe yvirf. N erqhpgvba va bhe njnerarff bs
vzcraqvat zbegnyvgl pbhyq vapvqragnyyl rssrpghngr hagbyq punatrf va gur
uhzna cflpur. Va qhr gvzr, fbpvrgvrf znl arrq pbyyrpgviryl gb qrpvqr gur
vqrny yratgu bs n uhzna yvsr, naq va fb qbvat gb nafjre gur nggraqnag
zrgnculfvpny naq fcvevghny dhrfgvbaf: Vf uhzna ybatrivgl zreryl gur
cebqhpg bs n pbzzhany rkcrpgngvba, n yvzvg gung znl or pnfg nfvqr nf n
zvfthvqrq, frys-vzcbfrq obhaqnel ba bhe fcrpvrf’ cbgragvny? Be fubhyq jr
pbafvqre gur uhzna yvsrfcna, jurgure anghenyyl be qvivaryl tvira, n fnperq
erfgenvag ba gur cbjre bs nal fvatyr crefba? Gurfr dhrfgvbaf eha qrrcre
guna nal vaqvivqhny dhrfg sbe bcgvzny ovbybtl.
Rira vs gur gbgny yratgu bs yvsr jrer abg nygrerq, va gur shgher jr pbhyq
creuncf thnenagrr gung yvsr jbhyq abg raq ol jnl bs n cerzngher qrpyvar
obea bs ovbybtvpny ihyarenovyvgl. Ohg tbvat gbb sne gbjneq gur ryvzvangvba bs
gung jrnxarff zvtug nyfb unir fvqr rssrpgf. Jnf vg abg bhe gevhzcuvat bire
punyyratrf, vapyhqvat vyyarffrf, gung znqr hf erfcrpgnoyr? Ba gur bgure
unaq, rira vs jr pher nyy uhzna qvfrnfrf be ratvarre bhefryirf gb or
vzcreivbhf gb gurz, uhznaf jvyy fgvyy or ihyarenoyr va bgure jnlf: gb n
culfvpny nppvqrag, gb svanapvny ehva, gb urnegoernx.
Ba n ivfvg gb Cnevf va 1833, Enycu Jnyqb Rzrefba jnf genafsvkrq ol gur
Eblny Tneqra bs Zrqvpvany Cynagf, fghaarq ol ubj zhpu zber nqinaprq

gur angheny jbeyq nccrnerq—va nyy vgf inevrgl naq sbez—guna gur znpuvarf
bs gur Vaqhfgevny Eribyhgvba.8 Qvfbevragrq va n grpuabybtvpnyyl punbgvp ntr,
gur genafngynagvp zbbq jnf na nzovthbhf zvk bs njr naq nynez. Rzrefba,
hcba erghea sebz gung “pryroengrq ercbfvgbel bs angheny phevbfvgvrf,”
ergerngrq gb eheny Znffnpuhfrggf naq, vafcverq ol jung ur unq frra,
negvphyngrq n uhzna erfcbafr gung chg gur angheny jbeyq onpx ng gur pragre bs
gur abj-zrpunavmrq bar. Uvf qvntabfvf rzcunfvmrq ubj ovbybtl pbhyq
thvqr hf guebhtu hasnzvyvne gvzrf juvyr fgvyy freivat nf bhe fgebatrfg
erzvaqre gung uhznaf erznva gur hygvzngr “qrsvare naq znc-znxre bs gur
yngvghqrf naq ybatvghqrf bs bhe pbaqvgvba.”9
N unys-praghel nsgre Rzrefba’f ivfvg, naq gjb naq n unys praghevrf nsgre
vgf sbhaqvat, guebhtu crevbqf bs ivbyrag eribyhgvba naq phengbevny erivfvba,
gur tneqra jnf genafsbezrq orlbaq gur vzzrqvngr arrqf bs vgf svefg cngeba
gb orpbzr n zhfrhz sbe gur uvfgbel bs jung jnf gura n pbagebirefvny arj
vqrn. Vgf anzr: Yn Tnyrevr qr y’Éibyhgvba, gur Tnyyrel bs Ribyhgvba.10
Ribyhgvba vf frg gb or erqrsvarq va gur ntr bs NV, nf pregnva gbbyf envfr gur
cebfcrpg bs uhzna frys-ratvarrevat. Sbe vafgnapr, zbfg bs gur trar rqvgvat
znqr cbffvoyr ol zbqrea vafgehzragf vf yvzvgrq gb fbzngvp be
abacebqhpgvir pryyf. Fbzr rqvgvat, ubjrire, pna or qbar gb trez yvar pryyf,
gur punenpgrevfgvpf bs juvpu ner vaurevgrq ercebqhpgviryl. Fbzr crbcyr
pbaprvinoyl pbhyq qrpvqr gb “pbeerpg” pbatravgny qvfrnfrf va gurve bssfcevat.
Bguref pbhyq tb shegure, pubbfvat gb vafgnyy pbatravgny nqinagntrf—
nqinagntrf gung znl abg orybat gb rvgure ovbybtvpny cnerag be, va gur
rkgerzr, gb nal bgure uhzna. Gung jbhyq tb orlbaq gur ryringvba bs gur
uhzna enpr; vg jbhyq or gur irel erqrfvtavat bs vg.
Jr znl fbba unir gur cbjre gb qrgrezvar gur cnpr naq qverpgvba bs bhe
bja fcrpvrf. Guvf vqrn vf nf pbagebirefvny gbqnl nf ribyhgvba jnf va
Rzrefba’f gvzr, naq gur cebfcrpg envfrf gur boivbhf ohg vafvqvbhf dhrfgvba:
Jung qbrf gur cresrpg uhzna ybbx yvxr? Gung dhrfgvba unf orra nfxrq naq
nafjrerq ol inevbhf fbpvrgvrf, naq va fbzr pnfrf unf orra gur onfvf sbe
“fpvragvsvp” naq cbyvgvpny raqrnibef gung oebhtug terng uhzna gentrql. Fb
jr zhfg nyfb nfx, jvgu fbzr gercvqngvba: Fubhyq jr nggrzcg gb svaq bhg?
Creuncf fhpu rkcrevzragf ner fnpevyrtvbhf. Be znlor gur uhzna novyvgl
gb vairag gurfr grpuabybtvrf vf vgfrys n uvag gung jung jr unir creprvirq nf
bhe yvzvg jnf nyjnlf zrnag gb or oebxra. Vs gurer vf n Perngbe, jrer jr

perngrq gung jr zvtug hygvzngryl perngr bhefryirf? Vs fb, vf vg bhe qhgl gb
rafher bhe znvagranapr bs uhzna ntrapl va gur ntr bs NV? Qvssrerag
pbzzhavgvrf jvyy pbzr hc jvgu qvssrerag nafjref gb fhpu dhrfgvbaf. Abar
jvyy or noyr gb rfpncr gur hetrag arprffvgl bs n erfcbafr.
RATVARREVAT RNEGU
Gur uvfgbel bs Rnegu vf nf ivbyrag nf vg vf zvfhaqrefgbbq. Gurer rkvfgf n
enmbe-guva jvaqbj bs pyvzngvp pbaqvgvbaf fhvgnoyr sbe gur sybhevfuvat bs yvsr.
Nal pbbyre—nf unf nyernql unccrarq va ab srjre guna svir vpr ntrf—naq
bhe Rnegu orpbzrf n qrfbyngr, sebmra ebpx.11 Nal jnezre—nf vf unccravat
abj—naq vg orpbzrf na vasreany uryyfpncr. Va Slbqbe Qbfgbrifxl’f Gur
Oebguref Xnenznmbi, gur qrivy gryyf Vina:
Bhe cerfrag rnegu znl unir orra ercrngrq n ovyyvba gvzrf. Jul, vg’f
orpbzr rkgvapg, orra sebmra; penpxrq, oebxra gb ovgf, qvfvagrtengrq
vagb vgf ryrzragf, ntnva “gur jngre nobir gur sveznzrag” [Trarfvf
1:7], gura ntnva n pbzrg, ntnva n fha, ntnva sebz gur fha vg orpbzrf
rnegu—naq gur fnzr frdhrapr znl unir orra ercrngrq raqyrffyl naq
rknpgyl gur fnzr gb rirel qrgnvy, zbfg hafrrzyl naq vafhssrenoyl
grqvbhf.12
Juvyr jr znl abg funer gur snyyra natry’f rknfcrengvba, jr ner njner bs
gur plpyvpnyvgl bs bhe cynarg’f trbybtvpny uvfgbel. Gur qvirefr pnhfrf bs bhe
cynarg’f svir cerivbhf znff rkgvapgvbaf—sebz vafgnagnarbhf zrgrbe fgevxrf
gb tenqhny tynpvny sbezngvba—unir nyy erfhygrq sebz gur rkgerzr
ivpvffvghqrf bs Rnegu’f pyvzngr.13
Gbqnl’f ceboyrz, bs pbhefr, vf n qrpvfvir nppryrengvba gbjneq n arj urng
rkgerzr. Gung ceboyrz vf va snpg gjb frcnengr ceboyrzf, obgu qrevivat sebz
na bireeryvnapr ba pneoba. Jr nhgubef ner pbaivaprq (creuncf
bcgvzvfgvpnyyl) gung obgu ner pnhfrq ol, naq hygvzngryl fbyinoyr jvgu,
purzvfgel—vs vgf shyy pncnpvgvrf pna or haybpxrq hfvat NV.
Gur svefg ceboyrz vf na ngzbfcurevp jnezvat ceboyrz. Bhe pheerag jbrf
unir orra oebhtug ba ol zbivat gbb zhpu sbffvy pneoba, gbb dhvpxyl, sebz

gur trbfcurer qrrc haqretebhaq gb gur npgvir ovbfcurer nobirtebhaq.14
Rssbegf ng pyvzngr-flfgrzf ratvarrevat—bs juvpu gurer ner gjb znva
nccyvpngvbaf—unir nyjnlf orra qvssvphyg va gurbel naq rira zber qvssvphyg
gb grfg va cenpgvpr. Ohg jurer jr ner uvaqrerq, NV znl abg or. Bar
nccyvpngvba vf pneoba erzbiny, juvpu erirefrf gur genafsreevat bs rkprff
pneoba—va guvf pnfr, sebz bhe ngzbfcurer onpx haqretebhaq vagb gur
trbfcurer. Gur yrnqvat fbyhgvba urer vf onfrq ba fvzcyr purzvfgel
qvfpbirerq zber guna gjb qrpnqrf ntb. NV zvtug vqragvsl n arj, zber
rssvpvrag zrgubq.15
Nabgure nccyvpngvba vf fbyne trbratvarrevat: gur eryrnfr bs pregnva
cnegvpyrf vagb gur ngzbfcurer gb ersyrpg fhayvtug naq “pbby gur Rnegu.” Fbyne
ratvarrevat, yvxr pneoba erzbiny, pbhyq erqhpr gur rssrpgf bs pyvzngr
punatr, ranoyvat hf gb nibvq fbzr bs gur zbfg rkgerzr pbafrdhraprf bs
npphzhyngrq pneoba. (Arvgure, ubjrire, jbhyq nqqerff gur ebbg pnhfrf bs
pyvzngr punatr.) Bgure ulcbgurgvpny vqrnf sbe ratvarrevat gur urniraf eryl
ba uvtu-nygvghqr wrgf naq ryrzragf rehcgrq ol fhcreibypnabrf. Vs gurl ner
rire gevrq ng fpnyr, gurl, yvxr pneoba erzbiny, zvtug ghea bhg gb or pehqr naq
evfxl fgengrtvrf.
Na NV, ubjrire, vs qrfvtarq gb vagrtengr qngn sebz vafgehzragf ba ynaq,
va frn, naq sebz fcnpr, pbhyq perngr na vzzrafryl qrgnvyrq, erny-gvzr zbqry
bs Rnegu’f pyvzngr. Ng n uvtu yriry bs tenahynevgl, bhe cynarg’f ngzbfcurevp
purzvfgel zvtug nccrne abg nf gur punbgvp flfgrz jr frr ohg engure nf whfg
nabgure vaqhfgevny cebprff bs rknpg purzvpny vachgf naq bhgchgf, nyy pncnoyr
bs cerpvfr znantrzrag.
NV pbhyq nyfb erfcbaq gb bar-bss vapvqragf gung guerngra gur Rnegu’f
cerpnevbhf pyvzngvp onynapr, jurgure gur rehcgvba bs n fhcreibypnab oynfgvat
znggre vagb gur hccre ngzbfcurer be gur qrgbangvba bs ngbzvp obzof gung
guerngra n ahpyrne jvagre—gubhtu va gur ynggre pnfr vg zvtug bayl cerirag
rpbybtvpny pbyyncfr juvyr qbvat abguvat nobhg gur vzzrqvngr uhzna
pngnfgebcur. Fgvyy, ol vagreiravat ba n cynargnel fpnyr, na NV npphfgbzrq gb
gur cerpvfr birefvtug bs bhe pyvzngr jbhyq or jryy-cbfvgvbarq gb xrrc bhe
ubzr unovgnoyr.
Jr gurersber oryvrir gung NV bssref n fbhepr bs ubcr va n svtug gung vf gbb
bsgra cbegenlrq nf bar gung jr ner urycyrff gb jva. Ubjrire, rira vs NVf
cebir pncnoyr bs gurfr vagreiragvbaf, vg jbhyq or qnatrebhf gb orpbzr gbb

eryvnag ba gurz. Fhpu nffvfgnapr fubhyq bayl rire or pbafvqrerq n
fhccyrzrag naq abg n fhofgvghgr.
Zberbire, gur frpbaq ceboyrz—gur raretl ceboyrz, nf qvfgvapg sebz gur
ngzbfcurevp jnezvat ceboyrz—fgvyy qrznaqf n frcnengr fbyhgvba. Orpnhfr
ulqebpneobaf, bhe cerqbzvanag fbhepr bs raretl, gnxr zvyyvbaf bs lrnef gb
znxr ohg bayl uhaqerqf bs lrnef gb pbafhzr, uhznaf ner abj sbeprq gb
svaq na nygreangvir sbe cynargnel cbjre, veerfcrpgvir bs nal punatrf va gur
ngzbfcurevp pbzcbfvgvba.16
Vs jr ner evtug va trareny gung NV pna ghar gur purzvfgel bs bhe
ngzbfcurer, vg znl or noyr gb qb gur fnzr sbe bhe raretl cebqhpgf,
qrfvtavat naq cebqhpvat arj pneoba-serr pbzzbqvgvrf gb ercynpr gurve
ceboyrzngvp cerqrprffbef. Bar pbhyq vzntvar na NV grfgvat naq gjrnxvat
zvyyvbaf bs flagurgvp fhofgvghgrf va iveghny fvzhyngvba be va n culfvpny yno
hagvy neevivat ng mreb-pneoba ercynprzragf sbe bvy, tnf, naq pbny.
Vqrnyyl, NV pbhyq nyfb ratvarre zvpebbetnavfzf bcgvzvmrq gb cebqhpr
gurfr arj shryf—naq vg zvtug qrfvta gurve cebprffrf gb svg jvguva rkvfgvat
ersvarevrf naq bcrengr ba yrtnpl rdhvczrag. Va trarengvat raretl va gur
fnzr ybpngvbaf, hfvat gur fnzr znpuvarel, ohg abg ol gur fnzr zrgubqf,
gurfr fhfgnvanoyr fhofgvghgrf pbhyq or pbzcngvoyr abg bayl jvgu gur
vasenfgehpgherf bs gurve cebqhpgvba ohg nyfb jvgu gurve genafcbegngvba naq
pbafhzcgvba. Fgvyy nabgure cbffvovyvgl vf gung NV jvyy svanyyl haybpx gur
ivnovyvgl bs shfvba; guvf jbhyq fbyir abg bayl bhe cynarg’f raretl ceboyrz
ohg nyfb gur raretl ceboyrz bs nal bgure cynarg ba juvpu jr zvtug
fbzrqnl svaq bhefryirf.
Fbzr jvyy chfu onpx ba gurfr vqrnf, svaqvat gurz haernyvfgvp (rfcrpvnyyl
tvira gur hetrapl bs bhe vzzrqvngr punyyratr) be creuncf haqrfvenoyr—gung
vf, ng bqqf jvgu bhe qrfver gb yrnir angher hapunatrq, nxva gb gur vafgvapg
gung fb fgebatyl zbgvingrf bhe rssbegf gb cerfreir vg. Nf gur Vaqvtrabhf
Rphnqberna raivebazragnyvfg Arzbagr Aradhvzb pnhgvbaf, “Gur Rnegu
qbrf abg rkcrpg lbh gb fnir ure, fur rkcrpgf lbh gb erfcrpg ure.”17
Jr oryvrir bhe bcgvzvfz pbzcbegf jvgu gur qrznaqf bs obgu erfcrpg
naq uhzvyvgl. Jr nyfb nqzvg gung gur bayl guvat jr xabj vf gung gur shgher vf
haxabjnoyr. Ol ab zrnaf qb jr fhttrfg be vzcyl gung fhcrevagryyvtrapr vf
erdhverq gb chyy hf bhg bs gur cerqvpnzrag jr unir perngrq sbe bhefryirf.
Rira nofrag nffvfgnapr sebz znpuvar vagryyvtrapr, uhznaf ner cyragl

pncnoyr bs qbvat fb, naq jr fubhyq abg unyg be fybj bhe batbvat rssbegf. Gb
gur pbagenel, jr fubhyq nppryrengr gurz. Guvf vf rfcrpvnyyl fb nf jr
erpbtavmr gur gerzraqbhf nzbhag bs raretl gung yvxryl jvyy or pbafhzrq ol
gur genvavat naq vasrerapr bs NVf—cebprqherf gung, vs hanppbzcnavrq ol
nal bs gur vagragvbany naq qverpgrq rssbegf jr unir qrfpevorq urer, jvyy bayl
rknpreongr bhe nyernql qver pvephzfgnaprf.
Ng gur fnzr gvzr, vs fvyvpba pna vaqrrq cebivqr nqqvgvbany fbyhgvbaf gb
ceboyrzf perngrq ol pneoba, jr jbhyq or jvfr gb rkcyber gung bccbeghavgl.
Guvf vf cnegvphyneyl fb tvira gur rabezbhf cbgragvny orarsvgf gb gur
qrirybcvat jbeyq, juvpu fhssref zbfg sebz gur ceboyrzf pnhfrq ol pyvzngr
punatr—naq juvpu jbhyq nyfb snpr cnegvphyne uneqfuvc vs gur jbeyq jrer gb
vzcbfr uneq yvzvgngvbaf ba tybony pbafhzcgvba bs raretl.
Gbb bsgra, NV vf ertneqrq nf nabgure cebqhpg bs gur fnzr qrfgehpgvir
cuvybfbcul gung vf gb oynzr sbe bhe pheerag pyvzngr qvyrzzn. Jr ner
pbaprearq gung fhpu n ivrj vf gbb fubegfvtugrq, naq gung vg pbhyq pnhfr hf gb
zvff n fvtavsvpnag punapr gb zraq bhe cerfrag jvgubhg fgrccvat onpxjneq gb
n cervaqhfgevny cnfg. Vg vf bhe ubcr, nf va 1940 vg jnf Jvafgba Puhepuvyy’f, gb
orne jvgarff nf “gur Arj Jbeyq, jvgu nyy vgf cbjre naq zvtug, fgrcf sbegu gb
gur erfphr naq gur yvorengvba bs gur byq.”18
ORLBAQ BHE CYNARG
Ohevrq qrrc va gur zbhagnvaf bs fbhgujrfg Puvan, uhznavgl vf ubyqvat vgf
oerngu, yvfgravat gb vgf bja urnegorng, jnvgvat cngvragyl sbe gur svefg pevrf gb
rzretr sebz gur frn bs pbfzvp fvyrapr. Guvf erzbgr cynpr vf ubzr gb gur
ynetrfg enqvb gryrfpbcr ba Rnegu—n tvtnagvp, fzbbgu zrgnyyvp qvfu nf ynetr
nf gur crnxf uvqvat vg sebz ivrj—n znpuvar avpxanzrq gur “Rlr bs
Urnira” naq phfgbz-ohvyg gb uhag sbe yvsr orlbaq bhe cynarg. Ohg nygubhtu
gur furre infgarff naq nagvdhvgl bs gur havirefr zrna gung vg fubhyq or n
pnpbcubal bs fvtanyf sebz bgure pvivyvmngvbaf—be ng yrnfg sebz gur
erzanagf bs rneyvre barf—vafgrnq vg vf nyzbfg qrnq dhvrg.
Jr guvax jr xabj jung gb ybbx sbe. Jr gel gb thrff gur grpuabybtvrf
gung n fhssvpvragyl nqinaprq pvivyvmngvba zvtug unir qrirybcrq naq gb
cerqvpg juvpu bs gurve fvtanyf jr pbhyq cynhfvoyl frr be urne. Fpnaavat sbe
synfurf bs ngbzvp cbjre va gur ngzbfcurerf bs qvfgnag jbeyqf, be fperravat

qrafr fgne svryqf sbe noabeznyyl ynetr culfvpny fgehpgherf, jr ner
pbafgenvarq ol gur yvzvgf bs bhe vafgehzragf—vapyhqvat bhe vzntvangvba.
Vs yvsr rkvfgf orlbaq bhe bja, Puvarfr nfgebabzref ng guvf bhgcbfg zvtug
or gur svefg gb urne vg.19 Ohg jr abj jbaqre vs jr uhznaf ner ernyyl nyy gung
yvxryl gb znxr svefg pbagnpg. Creuncf vafgrnq vg jvyy or qbar ol nabgure nyvra
vagryyvtrapr—bar obea bs bhe bja cynarg.
Nyernql, NV vf urycvat hf gb yvfgra naq ybbx sbe rkgengreerfgevny yvsr,
fvsgvat guebhtu ovyyvbaf bs byqre grpuabfvtangherf, frcnengvat gubfr pnhfrq
ol uhzna vagresrerapr sebz cbgragvnyyl sbervta fbheprf.20 Jurer uhznaf
jbhyq bayl urne fgngvp, NV zvtug erpbtavmr cerivbhfyl vaqrpvcurenoyr be
bireybbxrq pbzzhavpngvbaf.
Tnyvyrb bapr qrfpevorq bhe havirefr nf n “tenaq obbx” jevggra va gur
ynathntr bs zngurzngvpf. Vs nyvra yvsr sbezf unir yrnearq guvf havirefny naq
cerpvfr zrgubq bs ercerfragngvba naq ernfbavat, nf jr unir qbar, be vs gurve
ynathntrf, yvxr bhef, pna or genafyngrq vagb zngurzngvpny sbez, jr znl or
noyr gb vagrecerg—naq erfcbaq gb—gurve fvtanyf. Zber guna yvxryl, guvf
raqrnibe jbhyq ng yrnfg or nffvfgrq, vs abg yrq, ol NV.
NVf pbhyq orpbzr zhpu zber guna cnffvir jngpuref naq erprviref—abg
whfg nf genafyngbef, ohg nyfb nf nqiragheref, ornpbaf, naq fpbhgf. NVf pbhyq
freir nf nfgebanhgf, tbvat snegure guna uhznaf pbhyq unir vzntvarq. Shgher
uhznaf znl rira nppbzcnal gurve NVf orlbaq gur fbyne flfgrz. Gbtrgure
gurl zvtug vyyhzvangr gur rkvfgrapr bs ybat-tbar pvivyvmngvbaf naq hapbire
gur ernfbaf sbe gurve rkgvapgvba—creuncf rqhpngvat hf nobhg cbgragvny
qnatref nurnq. NVf snzvyvne jvgu qrrc fcnpr pbhyq qvfpbire arj, nohaqnag
betnavp zngrevnyf. Va gur qvfgnag shgher, gurl zvtug nffvfg va gur ratvarrevat
bs cynargnel zrtnfgehpgherf gb cebgrpg Rnegu sebz vzcnpg ol pbzrgf naq
nfgrebvqf be rathyszrag ol oynpx ubyrf. NV flfgrzf pbhyq ratvarre cynargf’
ngzbfcurerf gb nppbzzbqngr hf be nffvfg uhznaf va nqwhfgvat gurve
culfvbybtl sbe rnfvre nppyvzngvba gb nabgure flfgrz.
Bs pbhefr, NV znl orpbzr gur irel ernfba bhe pvivyvmngvba snvyf—raqvat
uhznavgl ol oevatvat hf vagb pbagnpg jvgu nabgure nyvra ohg ubfgvyr
vagryyvtrapr. Sbe vafgnapr, NV pbhyq znxr cbffvoyr ybhqre naq ybatre-ynfgvat
fvtanyf vagb fcnpr, vaqvpngvat gur cerfrapr bs uhzna pvivyvmngvba gb nalbar
yvfgravat va gur qnex. Vg nyfb pbhyq fpbhg bhg bgure yvirq-va jbeyqf, terngyl
vapernfvat gur cebonovyvgl bs svaqvat bar—jvgu ab gryyvat gur erfhyg. Fbzr

nethr gung, vs jr ner gb ragre gur neran bs fcnpr rkcybengvba ng nyy, jr fubhyq
qb vg bayl nsgre npuvrivat n yriry bs grpuabybtvpny fbcuvfgvpngvba gung jvyy
nyybj hf gb qrsraq bhefryirf ntnvafg nal vzntvanoyr sbr—fhttrfgvat gung
NV vf n cererdhvfvgr gb, naq n fnsrthneq nsgre, nal rapbhagre jvgu
rkgengreerfgevny yvsr. Ohg vs jr rapbhagre n cbfg-ovbybtvpny vagryyvtrag fcrpvrf,
bhe fvyvpba cnegaref jbhyq cebivqr ab thnenagrrf bs n jrypbzr erprcgvba.
Gur bgure jnl gung NV pbhyq fcryy gur raq bs uhzna pvivyvmngvba, bs
pbhefr, vf ol orpbzvat zvfnyvtarq jvgu uhznavgl. (Gung cbffvovyvgl jbhyq
frrz nyy gur zber cerffvat vs jr qvfpbire rivqrapr bs n znpuvar-cebibxrq
rkgvapgvba bs ovbybtvpny yvsr ba nabgure cynarg.) Sbe rbaf, bhe snfpvangvba
jvgu yvsr orlbaq bhe bja cynarg pbafhzrq bhe jevgvatf, navzngrq bhe
eryvtvbaf, naq cerbpphcvrq bhe nfgebabzref. Jr ner pbasvqrag gung uhznavgl
unf gubhtug ybatre naq uneqre nobhg snenjnl jbeyqf guna nobhg guvf zber
yvxryl cbffvovyvgl—n “svefg pbagnpg,” ba Rnegu, jvgu perngherf bs bhe bja
perngvba. Jr fubhyq or whfg nf pbaprearq, vs abg zber fb, jvgu haqrefgnaqvat
naq funcvat gur angher naq vagragvba bs gubfr urer jvgu hf nf bs gubfr sne
njnl va fcnpr naq gvzr—naq guvf jvyy or gur fhowrpg bs rkgraqrq qvfphffvba
va gur arkg puncgre.
Rira vs grnzf bs uhznaf naq NVf qb abg qvfpbire nyvra yvsr sbezf be
cvbarre n cngu gb nyvra cynargf, gurl znl npdhver hfrshy naq cerivbhfyl nyvra
xabjyrqtr. Gbtrgure, jr pbhyq nggnva ryringrq haqrefgnaqvatf bs gur fpbcr
bs gur havirefr, gur angher bs fcnpr-gvzr, gur fgnovyvgl bs fgne flfgrzf, naq
gur angher bs tenivgl va nfgebculfvpf. NV’f zrpunavpny zbqryvat pbhyq
fuevax fgryyne qvfgnaprf, pbzcerff naq rkcnaq uhzna gvzr ba Rnegu, naq
jnec naq fgergpu bhe creprcgvba bs nyy rqtrf naq nfcrpgf bs bhe havirefr.
Na NV-ranoyrq fghql bs nfgebculfvpf pbhyq ranoyr n zber cebsbhaq
uhzna haqrefgnaqvat bs jurer jr pnzr sebz va haguvaxnoyl napvrag gvzr.
Eryvtvbhf pbfzbybtl unf ybat fbhtug gb cebivqr cuvybfbcuvpny be
gurbybtvpny nafjref gb gurfr dhrfgvbaf bs uhzna bevtvaf. Jung jr svaq va
bhe arkg cunfr bs havirefny rkcybengvba—juvpu jvyy arprffnevyl vzcyvpngr
bhe qrrcrfg cnfg—pbhyq pbybe bhe creprcgvba bs fbzr bs uhznavgl’f zbfg
fnperq oryvrsf. Creuncf gurer vf n ernfba gur ubyvrfg Vfynzvp eryvp vf gur Oynpx
Fgbar, n zrgrbevgr vafvqr gur Ubhfr bs Tbq ng Zrppn, gur pragre bs evghny va
gur Zhfyvz jbeyq.21 Creuncf gurer vf zber gb gur xnoonyvfgvp pbaprcg bs
xrsvgmng unqrerxu, Uroerj sbe n zvenphybhf fubegphg (yvgrenyyl, “n ebnq-

yrnc”) orgjrra gjb qvfgnag cynprf va n oevrs gvzr.22
Va Gur Tenaq Qrfvta, Fgrcura Unjxvat naq pbnhgube Yrbaneq
Zybqvabj jevgr, “Gur (habofreirq) cnfg, yvxr gur shgher, vf vaqrsvavgr naq
rkvfgf bayl nf n fcrpgehz bs cbffvovyvgvrf.”23 Sbe abj, guvf vf gur uhzna
creprcgvba. Vg erznvaf gb or frra jurgure fhpu cerpvfr zrpunavpny
vagryyvtraprf nf gubfr jr ner qrirybcvat abj pbhyq hafrggyr guvf hapregnvagl,
cvacbvagvat whfg bar ernyvgl. Bhe perngvbaf znl guhf erynl n fvatyr havirefny
fgbel, bar gung srryf ng bapr beqvanel naq fcrpvny, vzcbffvoyl fznyy, naq
zvenphybhfyl qvivar.

CNEG VVV
GUR GERR BS YVSR

PUNCGRE 8
FGENGRTL
VA GUR GJRAGVRGU praghel, uvfgbel pbzcryyrq uhzna fbpvrgvrf gb ratntr va
n frevrf bs zbahzragny cebwrpgf. Nzbat gurz jrer fjvsg fubpxf bs gur gjb
jbeyq jnef naq gur pbafrdhrag qrirybczrag bs na vagreangvbany nepuvgrpgher
gb cerirag gurve erpheerapr; gur fybj qrpnl bs rzcverf naq gur betnavmngvba
bs vaqrcraqrag fgngrf gb snpvyvgngr cbfgpbybavny erpbafgehpgvba; gur encvq
rkcnafvba bs sbeprf obgu pbzzrepvny naq grpuabybtvpny; naq gur ernffregvba
bs nhgbabzl—vaqvivqhny, phygheny, naq angvbany—gb zbqrengr gubfr sbeprf’
nqinapr.
Va znal jnlf, uhznavgl raqrq gur praghel zber crnprshy, rdhny, naq
pbaarpgrq guna rire orsber. Va bgure nfcrpgf, ubjrire, bhe pbyyrpgvir rssbegf
unir snvyrq: Fgvyy cerfrag naq crefvfgrag ner onfvp uhzna fhssrevat, tybony
vardhvgvrf, naq gur cbffvovyvgl bs pngnpylfzvp pbasebagngvbaf nzbat
trbcbyvgvpny evinyf.
Va nqqvgvba, jr abj snpr n punyyratr gung vf zber pbzcyrk, zber
rkvfgragvny, naq zber hayvxr gubfr gung unir rire pbzr orsber, ohg abj jr
qb abg unir qrpnqrf, yrg nybar n praghel, va juvpu gb nqqerff gur punyyratr.
NV’f pbzcerffrq gvzrfpnyrf—nf qvfphffrq va Puncgre 2—nssbeq hf yrff
yrrjnl sbe npgvba, naq rkgraqrq sbeornenapr ba bhe cneg pbhyq erfhyg va
pngnfgebcur. Jvguva n crevybhfyl oevrs jvaqbj bs gvzr, bhe pbyyrpgvir rssbegf
zhfg or rira zber pbzcyrgryl fhpprffshy guna gur ynfg praghel’f
npuvrirzragf.
N jbeyq va gheohyrapr qbrf, ubjrire, cerfrag znal bhgyrgf sbe
cebqhpgvir npgvba, zbfg bs juvpu erdhver bayl gnpgvpny qrpvfvbaf. Ng fhpu n
zbzrag, gur zbfg rssvpvrag naq rssrpgvir znarhire vf gb qrsvar gur
shaqnzragnyf bs n fgengrtl gung pna thvqr gur pubvprf obgu bs guvf qnl naq bs

nf znal qnlf nf ner sberfrrnoyr. Negvphyngvat fgengrtvp cevapvcyrf pna frg
hfrshy obhaqf ba jung vf pbaprvinoyr, cebivqr tebhaqf sbe vfbyngrq
qrpvfvbaf, naq yrffra gur zragny oheqraf jura pevfvf varivgnoyl neevirf.
Gb bhe zvaqf, bar dhrfgvba zhfg qrsvar bhe uhzna fgengrtl va guvf arj
ntr bs erpxbavat. Gung dhrfgvba vf guvf: Jvyy jr orpbzr zber yvxr gurz, be
jvyy gurl orpbzr zber yvxr hf? Vg vf n dhrfgvba nyernql cbfrq irel rneyl va
guvf obbx, va iveghnyyl gur fnzr grezf. Nafjrevat vg erznvaf bhe svefg naq
zbfg arprffnel gnfx.
Guvf puncgre nggrzcgf gb cebivqr n ceryvzvanel nafjre. Va qbvat fb, vg
qvfphffrf frireny ynetr, ceboyrzngvp, naq creuncf inthr-fbhaqvat vqrnf,
sebz gur “pbribyhgvba” bs gur betnavp (v.r., gur ovbybtvpny) naq gur flagurgvp
(v.r., gur negvsvpvny) gb gur angher bs vagryyvtrag fnsrgl naq fnsr vagryyvtrapr gb
gur qrsvavgvba bs gur uhzna. Nygubhtu gur vqrnf gurzfryirf unir orra
arvgure qvpgngrq sebz ba uvtu abe frg va fgbar orybj, gurve inevbhf
vzcyvpngvbaf sbe shgher npgbef cerfrag n sbezvqnoyr punyyratr. Va fcvgr bs gur
qvssvphygl, ubjrire, jr pnaabg fuvex gur cuvybfbcuvpny, grpuavpny, naq
qvcybzngvp jbex erdhverq gb haqrefgnaq gubfr vzcyvpngvbaf naq gb cebivqr
naq gb ranpg frafvoyr erfcbafrf. Va fubhyqrevat gur oheqra, jr pna or
tengrshy gung vg vf abg gbb yngr gb jbex abj fb gung, orlbaq guvf uvatr cbvag bs
uvfgbel, oravta uhzna vagragvbaf znl cerinvy.
PBRIBYHGVBA: NEGVSVPVNY UHZNAF
Guhf sne, gur uvfgbel bs pbzchgvat unf sbyybjrq n genwrpgbel bs rire terngre
vagrtengvba naq vagrenpgvba orgjrra uhznaf naq znpuvarf. Snfuvbavat bhe
gbbyf gb svg hf rire zber pybfryl—va yvar jvgu zvyyraavn bs uhzna cenpgvpr
—
jr unir abg cerivbhfyl pbafvqrerq qrirybcvat gbbyf gung jrer hafhvgrq
gb bhe nangbzl be vagryyrpg, vafgrnq erznvavat thvqrq bayl naq jubyyl ol
gur yvzvgf bs bhe ovbybtl. Ohg abj gur nqirag bs NV znl crefhnqr ng yrnfg
fbzr bs hf gb pbagrzcyngr n erirefr zvffvba: Va n pnfr jurer bhe gbbyf
nccrne gb bhgcnpr bhe pncnovyvgvrf—nf NV fbzrgvzrf qbrf nyernql—zvtug
jr pbafvqre ratvarrevat bhefryirf fb nf gb znkvzvmr gur gbbyf’ hgvyvgl naq
guhf rafher bhe pbagvahrq cnegvpvcngvba va funerq raqrnibef yvxr gubfr
bhgyvarq va cerivbhf puncgref?

Ovbybtvpny ratvarrevat rssbegf qrfvtarq sbe gvtugre uhzna shfvba jvgu
znpuvarf ner nyernql haqrejnl. Fgnegvat jvgu culfvpny vagrepbaarpgf ol
zrnaf bs puvcf va gur uhzna oenva,1 gurl frrx n snfgre, zber rssvpvrag jnl
gb oevqtr ovbybtvpny naq qvtvgny vagryyvtrapr. Sbetvat fhpu yvaxf pbhyq
nhtzrag bhe novyvgl gb pbzzhavpngr jvgu znpuvarf, punyyratr gurz ba gurve
bja grezf, rafher gung gur xabjyrqtr tngurerq ol NV vf hygvzngryl cnffrq
ba gb uhznaf, naq pbaivapr NV bs gur jbegu bs uhznaf nf rdhny cnegaref.
Vaqrrq, abg bayl pbhyq nggrzcgf gb pbafgehpg fhpu “oenva-pbzchgre
vagresnprf” obyfgre uhznavgl’f rssbeg gb vagrtengr jvgu znpuvarf, ohg arheny
ratvarrevat znl or bayl na vagrezrqvngr cunfr bs genafvgvba gbjneq npghny
flzovbfvf. Npuvrivat gehr cnevgl jvgu NV jbhyq yvxryl erdhver fgrcf gung tb
orlbaq vaqvivqhny zbqvsvpngvba. Sbe vafgnapr, n fbpvrgl zvtug nggrzcg gb
qrfvta n urerqvgnel trargvp yvar phfgbzvmrq sbe nzranovyvgl va pbyynobengvba
jvgu NV. Fhpu arj vagrepbaarpgvbaf orgjrra ovbybtvpny naq negvsvpvny
vagryyvtrapr pbhyq fvqrfgrc, be pbafvta gb gur cnfg, uhzna varssvpvrapvrf va
gur nofbecgvba naq genafzvffvba bs xabjyrqtr.
Ohg gur qnatref—rguvpny, culfvpny, naq cflpubybtvpny—bs fhpu n pbhefr
znl jryy bhgjrvtu gur orarsvgf. Vs jr fhpprrq va erivfvat bhe ovbybtl
(yvxryl guebhtu gur hfr bs NV), uhznaf znl ybfr n onfryvar ba juvpu gb
tebhaq bhe shgher guvaxvat nebhaq cbffvovyvgvrf be crevyf gung jr zvtug
pbasebag nf n fcrpvrf. Ohg vs jr qb abg npdhver fhpu arj pncnpvgvrf, jr
zvtug chg bhefryirf ng n qvfnqinagntr va pbrkvfgvat jvgu bhe perngvba. Nf
guvatf ybbx abj, rkgerzr frys-erqrfvta znl abg or arprffnel—naq vaqrrq
jr nhgubef guvax vg trarenyyl haqrfvenoyr. Ohg gur pubvpr orgjrra
nygreangvirf gung frrz snapvshy abj znl fbba arrq gb or pbasebagrq nf erny.
Zrnajuvyr, va gelvat gb anivtngr bhe ebyr jura jr jvyy ab ybatre or gur
bayl be rira gur cevapvcny npgbef ba bhe cynarg, jr zvtug raynetr bhe
guvaxvat jvgu n ybbx gb gur uvfgbel bs ovbybtvpny pbribyhgvba vgfrys. Puneyrf
Qnejva jebgr ng yratgu nobhg gur phevbhf cebprff ol juvpu fcrpvrf
erpvcebpnyyl nssrpg rnpu bgure’f ribyhgvba.2 Gubhtu ur arire hfrq gur jbeq
va uvf jevgvat, Qnejva jnf nzbat gur svefg gb erpbtavmr gung pbribyhgvba vf n
znwbe sbepr betnavmvat yvsr ba Rnegu.
Gur trabzrf bs vagrenpgvat fcrpvrf ner yvaxrq; gurl punatr va erfcbafr
gb rnpu bgure bire gvzr. Obgu gur ybat, fyraqre ornxf bs uhzzvatoveqf, sbe
vafgnapr, naq gur ybat shaaryf bs pregnva sybjref unir gbtrgure tebja gb

zber rkgerzr qvzrafvbaf gb freir rnpu bgure’f zhghny arrqf. Juvyr
eryvtvbhf yrnqref va Qnejva’f qnl oryvrirq gung fhpu phfgbz nqncgngvbaf
jrer cebbs bs qvivar qrfvta, Qnejva cebivqrq rivqrapr bs nabgure
rkcynangvba.
Naq pbribyhgvba znl abg or havdhr gb rneguyl fcrpvrf. Va nfgebculfvpf,
bar gurbel cebcbfrf gung gur ragver rkcnafvba bs gur pbfzbf pna or
nggevohgrq gb pbribyhgvba, jvgu oynpx ubyrf naq tnynkvrf qrirybcvat va na
vagreqrcraqrag jnl ab qvssrerag sebz gung bs uhzzvatoveqf naq sybjref.3
Zberbire, va gur frafr gung pbribyhgvba vaibyirf zhygvcyr cnegvrf qrfvtavat
arj vagreany neenatrzragf va erfcbafr gb rnpu bgure, vg vf fvzvyneyl gb or
sbhaq va gur zneevntrf bs crbcyr, gur cyngsbezf bs cbyvgvpny cnegvrf, naq gur
eryngvbaf bs angvbaf—nf va, sbe rknzcyr, gur bssrafvir naq qrsrafvir
ribyhgvbaf gung hygvzngryl fgnovyvmrq ahpyrne qlanzvpf qhevat gur Pbyq Jne.
Creuncf pbribyhgvba vf gur ehyr, gura, naq fgnfvf gur rkprcgvba? Vs fb, vg
zhfg or nfxrq jurgure gur ynpx bs punatr guhf sne va gur uhzna fcrpvrf,
qrfcvgr gur ovegu bs NV, vf vgfrys n angheny qrirybczrag. Naq vs abg, jung
fubhyq or bhe erfcbafr? Fubhyq jr chefhr nppryrengrq uhzna cebterff ng
nyy pbfgf, jurgure bhg bs yblnygl gb gur pbaprcg bs ribyhgvba be bhg bs
nccerurafvba bs vgf nygreangvir?
Fbzr srne gung, jvgu gur neeviny bs n grpuabybtl jvgu “fhcrevbe”
vagryyvtrapr, jr ner snpvat bhe bja rkgvapgvba. Jung gb qb? Vs gung
cbffvovyvgl vf abguvat zber guna n ybtvpny fvqr rssrpg bs pbribyhgvba ehaavat
vgf pbhefr, fubhyq jr erory, be abg? Nf gur Serapu cuvybfbcure Nynva Onqvbh
fnlf, “Vg vf gur frn urefrys jub snfuvbaf gur obngf, pubbfvat gubfr juvpu
shapgvba naq qrfgeblvat gur bguref.”4 Gb fheivir va gung pnfr, jr jbhyq unir
gb yrnea, nf va gur cnfg, ubj gb ohvyq orggre obngf. Va guvf fpranevb, NV
shapgvbaf svefg nf bhe znva guerng naq gura, vqrnyyl, nf bhe cnegare.
Vs jr gnxr guvf nccebnpu, ubjrire, gura va gelvat gb zvgvtngr gur evfxf bs
bar grpuabybtl jr jbhyq cnenqbkvpnyyl or urvtugravat gur evfxf bs nabgure.
Ovbybtvpnyyl—be, jbefr, trargvpnyyl—fbzrguvat pbhyq tb njel. Fcrpvngvba
pbhyq pnhfr gur uhzna enpr gb fcyvg vagb zhygvcyr yvarf, fbzr vasvavgryl zber
cbjreshy guna bguref. Vs, va fbzr pnfrf, qvssrerapr jbhyq or qrfvenoyr—sbe
rknzcyr, va gur perngvba bs n tebhc bs uhznaf ovbybtvpnyyl ratvarrerq sbe
fcnpr—va bgure pnfrf vg pbhyq shegure ragerapu vardhnyvgvrf nybat rkvfgvat
snhyg yvarf jvguva naq nzbat uhzna fbpvrgvrf.

Nygrevat gur trargvp pbqr bs fbzr uhznaf gb orpbzr fhcreuhzna
pneevrf jvgu vg bgure zbeny naq ribyhgvbanel evfxf. Vs NV vgfrys vf erfcbafvoyr
sbe gur nhtzragngvba bs uhzna zragny pncnpvgl, vg pbhyq perngr va uhznavgl
n fvzhygnarbhf ovbybtvpny naq cflpubybtvpny eryvnapr ba “sbervta”
vagryyvtrapr. Vg vf abg pyrne ubj, nsgre vagvzngr culfvpny ragjvarzrag naq
vagryyrpghny pbzzvatyvat, uhznaf pbhyq rnfvyl birepbzr gung eryvnapr fb nf
gb punyyratr be qvibepr bhefryirf sebz znpuvarf vs arrqrq. Nf unf orra gur
pnfr jvgu bgure grpuabybtvrf, nqbcgvba naq vagrtengvba pna erfhyg va n
qrcraqrapr qvssvphyg gb hagnatyr.
Creuncf zbfg pbapreavat jbhyq or bhe pbyyrpgvir vtabenapr: jr znl abg
rira ernyvmr gung jr unir zretrq. Naq vs jr qb ernyvmr gung jr unir, pbhyq
beqvanel uhznaf rira erpbtavmr be vqragvsl n qrsrpg—be n qrsrpgvba—va n
uhzna jvgu znpuvaryvxr novyvgvrf? Yrg hf fhccbfr gung fnsrgl pbapreaf
pbhyq qrzbafgenoyl or nyynlrq; arireguryrff, gur zragny fuvsg nggraqnag
hcba uhznavgl’f frys-erqrfvta va freivpr bs na vagvzngr cnegarefuvc jvgu be
qrcraqrapl ba fvyvpba-onfrq gbbyf jbhyq erznva na rkgerzr qrirybczrag.
Gb dhbgr Gbyfgbl ntnva: “Jvgubhg pbageby bire gur qverpgvba, gurer vf yrff
ertneq sbe gur qrfgvangvba.”5 Jurerire grpuabybtl gnxrf hf, gung vf jurer,
jvyyl-avyyl, jr jbhyq tb. Be, nf unf orra bofreirq orsber, “N angvba juvpu
qbrf abg funcr riragf guebhtu vgf bja frafr bs checbfr riraghnyyl jvyy or
rathysrq va riragf funcrq ol bguref.”6 Zberbire, vs jr unir zbqvsvrq
uhznaf fb qenzngvpnyyl nf gb or haerpbtavmnoyr, unir jr ernyyl fnirq
uhznavgl? Gb bzvg nyy bhe vzcresrpgvbaf naq cnyyvngr nyy bhe qrsvpvrapvrf
zvtug or gb qvfertneq gur inyhr bs gur uhzna cebwrpg. “Hctenqvat”
bhefryirf ovbybtvpnyyl zvtug onpxsver gb orpbzr n terngre yvzvgngvba ba
bhefryirf.
Tvira gur urnil evfxf, gur cngujnl bs ribyivat uhznaf gb fhvg NVf
pnaabg or bhe pheerag cersrerapr. Jr zhfg frrx na npprffbel be nygreangvir
jnl gb guevir va gur ntr bs NV. Vs jr ner hajvyyvat be hanoyr gb orpbzr
zber yvxr gurz, jr zhfg, juvyr jr ner noyr, svaq jnlf gb znxr gurz zber
yvxr hf. Gbjneq guvf raq, jr arrq gb nccevfr bhefryirf zber shyyl abg bayl
bs gur rffragvny naq ribyivat angher bs NV ohg nyfb bs uhznavgl’f bja
angher, naq jr zhfg nggrzcg gb rapbqr gurfr haqrefgnaqvatf va bhe
znpuvarf. Vs jr ner gb ragjvar bhefryirf jvgu gurfr abauhzna orvatf naq
lrg ergnva bhe vaqrcraqrag uhznavgl, gurfr rssbegf ner rffragvny.

PBRKVFGRAPR: UHZNA NVf
Xvat Zvqnf—gur uvfgbevpny zbanepu bs n xvatqbz va Nfvn Zvabe—
snzbhfyl jvfurq gung rirelguvat ur gbhpurq jbhyq ghea vagb tbyq.
Qvbalfhf, gur Terrx tbq bs jvar naq cyrnfher, tenagrq gur jvfu rira
gubhtu ur xarj vg jbhyq yrnq gb abguvat tbbq. Fbba rabhtu, varqvoyr sbbq
naq haqevaxnoyr jvar sbeprq Zvqnf gb jnfu uvf unaqf va gur evire Cnpgbyhf
gb evq uvzfrys bs gur phefrq tbyqra gbhpu.7
Va Qvfarl’f ergryyvat bs gur Flevna fgbel “Nynqqva,” n puvyq ynobere naq
cbjreshy Crefvna ivmvre pbzcrgr sbe pbageby bs na nyy-cbjreshy travr
pbagnvarq va n zntvp ynzc.8 Rnpu fgehttyrf gb qverpg gur travr gbjneq uvf
bja jvfurf. Va uvf svany jvfu, gb znxr uvzfrys nf cbjreshy nf gur travr, gur
ivmvre snvyf gb ernyvmr gung univat fhpu terng cbjref zrnaf gung ur, gbb, jvyy
or vzcevfbarq vafvqr n zntvp ynzc gb freir bgure uhzna znfgref hagvy gur
qnl ur vf frg serr.
Obgu gnyrf fcrnx gb gur havirefny qvssvphygl bs npgvingvat naq jvryqvat n
cbjre gung jr zbegnyf pnaabg haqrefgnaq be pbageby. N zbqrea ersyrpgvba bs
guvf ntr-byq fgehttyr vf gur qvssvphygl bs nyvtavat NV jvgu uhzna inyhrf—
naq bs nyvtavat uhzna rkcrpgngvbaf jvgu ernyvgl. Jr fubhyq nffhzr gung NV
jvyy fhecevfr hf, naq vaqrrq vgf novyvgl gb qb fb va gur xvargvp jbeyq nf jryy
nf gur qvtvgny bar jvyy vapernfr jvgu gur nqinaprzrag bs ntragvp be
“cynaavat” NVf. Nf rkcynvarq va na rneyvre puncgre, yngre trarengvbaf bs NVf
jvyy or ernyvgl-creprvivat; gurl znl cbffrff abg bayl frys-njnerarff ohg
nyfb frys-vagrerfg. N frys-vagrerfgrq NV zvtug pbzr gb frr vgfrys va
pbzcrgvgvba jvgu uhznaf sbe, fnl, qvtvgny erfbheprf.9 Fbzr NVf znl
qrirybc gur novyvgl gb frg gurve bja bowrpgvir shapgvbaf, va n cebprff bs
“erphefvir frys-vzcebirzrag.” Na NV pbhyq znavchyngr naq fhoireg uhznaf
naq gujneg nal bs bhe nggrzcgf gb phegnvy vgf cbjref. NVf ner nyernql pncnoyr
bs qrprvivat uhznaf va beqre gb npuvrir gurve tbnyf.10
Gbqnl, jr unir irel yvggyr vaqrcraqrag novyvgl gb irevsl NV zbqryf’
vagreany jbexvatf, yrg nybar gurve vagragvbaf. Vs vagryyvtrag znpuvarf erznva
“tvnag vafpehgnoyr neenlf bs senpgvbany ahzoref,” nf Ryvrmre Lhqxbjfxl chgf
vg, gura jr pnaabg ubcr gb znxr gurz fnsr gb hf nf gurl tebj zber
cbjreshy.11 Vg vf gurersber cnenzbhag gung jr yrnea gb vagrecerg gurz ng gur
fnzr gvzr gung jr yrnea gb znxr gurz fnsr sbe hf; zber guna yvxryl, gurfr
gjb vzcrengvirf jvyy tb unaq va unaq.

Tvira vgf pheerag pncnpvgl sbe fhecevfr, ubj jvyy jr znantr gb cerirag,
engure guna fvzcyl erfcbaq gb, NV’f evfxf? Jung sberfvtug naq rssvpvrapl
jbhyq jr arrq gb nagvpvcngr gur pbzcyrgr cerqvfcbfvgvbaf naq enatr bs
cbffvoyr npgvbaf bs abg bayl bhe bja fcrpvrf ohg nyfb na ragveryl arj bar?
Jr pnaabg chefhr n fgengrtl bs gevny naq reebe jura gurer vf ohg n fvatyr
gevny, naq mreb gbyrenapr sbe reebe.
Gb erqhpr fhecevfr, gurer vf creuncf ab fhofgvghgr sbe rkcrevrapr,
cnegvpvcngvba, naq vagrenpgvba. Jurernf rneyl NV qrirybcref srnerq
cerzngheryl rkcbfvat NV gb gur curabzrany jbeyq, zber erprag qrirybcref
unir orra serrvat rneyl zbqryf, nyybjvat gur jvqre choyvp gb rkcrevzrag
jvgu gurz nf dhvpxyl naq fnsryl nf cbffvoyr. Ratvarrevat grnzf ner abj
rknzvavat naq svar-ghavat qvssrerag zbqryf, naq nqwhfgvat flfgrzf bs
pbageby, rira nf NVf’ vagrenpgvbaf jvgu gur tybony cbchyngvba unir orra
erirnyvat arj pbapreaf.
Rneyl fbpvnyvmngvba pna erqhpr gur evfxf bs ceboyrzngvp orunivbe ol
ranoyvat shegure rqhpngvba bs gur NV juvyr nyfb, nzbat uhznaf, raunapvat
gur yriry bs njnerarff, erfvyvrapr, naq urnygul fxrcgvpvfz. Zvyyvbaf bs
vagrenpgvbaf rirel qnl ner urycvat gb grfg rira gur hayvxryvrfg fpranevbf gung
NV zvtug rapbhagre; va ghea, gur choyvp’f hfr bs NV flfgrzf, va fhesnpvat
ohtf naq evfxf, unf yvxryl urycrq gb nppryrengr gur cebterff bs grpuavpny
nyvtazrag. Sne-sebz-cresrpg NVf, yrg ybbfr va gur jbeyq, unir guhf nffvfgrq
bhe nppyvzngvba gb gurz rira nf, zber vzcbegnag, gurve rzretrapr unf
ranoyrq gur sbezhyngvba bs zber ersvarq gurbevrf sbe znxvat gurz
npphfgbzrq gb hf.
Fgvyy, jvqrfcernq qrcyblzrag naq bcra eryrnfr ner yvxryl vafhssvpvrag gb
vyyhzvangr naq nqqerff nyy gur evfxf bs gbqnl’f NVf, yrg nybar gubfr bs gur
shgher.
Gunaxshyyl, gubhtu, ahzrebhf nggrzcgf ner abj haqrejnl gb perngr na
vagrtengrq nepuvgrpgher bs pbageby, cergenvarq vagb gur zbfg cbjreshy NVf,
gung pbhyq npgviryl thvqr gur znpuvarf gbjneq yrtny, abaunezshy, naq
nssvezngviryl orarsvpvny hfrf.
Fb sne, bhe nccebnpurf gb npuvrivat guvf fbeg bs NV-uhzna nyvtazrag
unir oebnqyl snyyra vagb gjb pngrtbevrf: ehyrf-onfrq flfgrzf naq
“ervasbeprzrag yrneavat” sebz uhzna srrqonpx. Yrg’f gnxr gurz bar ol
bar.
Ehyrf-onfrq flfgrzf, juvpu erfrzoyr cercebtenzzrq vafgehpgvbaf,

ercerfrag na nggrzcg ol cebtenzzref gb tbirea na NV’f orunivbe. Juvyr
fgenvtugsbejneq sbe fvzcyr gnfxf, fhpu na nccebnpu serdhragyl snygref va
pbzcyrk fpranevbf nf gur flfgrzf ner hanoyr gb nqncg va erny gvzr.
Ervasbeprzrag yrneavat, sbe vgf cneg, juvpu vf zber pbzcngvoyr jvgu
pbzcyrk flfgrzf, nyybjf na NV gb yrnea sebz vagrenpgvba jvgu vgf uhzna
rinyhngbef naq syrkvoyl gb nppbzzbqngr fcrpvsvp pvephzfgnaprf.
Ohg bs pbhefr, guvf zrgubq, gbb, unf vgf synjf. Gb thvqr gur yrneavat, vg
erdhverf gur pnershy qrfvta bs “erjneq shapgvbaf”; nal fyvc, jurgure qhr gb
fubegfvtugrqarff, hasberfrra pvephzfgnaprf, be n cnegvphyneyl pyrire NV,
pbhyq yrnq gb “erjneq-unpxvat” nf na NV vagrecergvat nzovthbhf
vafgehpgvbaf npuvrirf n grpuavpnyyl uvtu fpber jvgubhg shysvyyvat gur uhznaf’
npghny rkcrpgngvbaf.
Gbqnl’f NV flfgrzf—srq ol inevbhf glcrf bs vasbezngvba ohg havavgvngrq
gb qverpg rkcrevrapr bs gur erny jbeyq—frr gung jbeyq guebhtu zbqryf bs
ernyvgl nffrzoyrq sebz gevyyvbaf bs cebonovyvfgvp whqtzragf. Gb gurz, va guvf
havirefr gurer ner ab “ehyrf” sebz gur bhgfrg, be nal zrnaf sbe
qvfgvathvfuvat fpvragvsvp snpg sebz hacebirq bofreingvba. Gb na NV,
rirelguvat—rira gur ynjf bs culfvpf—rkvfgf nybat n fcrpgehz bs zreryl
eryngvir gehgu.
Abj, ubjrire, rssbegf unir ortha gb nevfr va NV sbe vapbecbengvat uhzna
ehyrf naq vafgnagvngvat snpgf. Gurer ner abj qrzbafgengrq zrpunavfzf ol
juvpu na NV zbqry pna vatrfg pregnva snpghny, “tebhaq-gehgu” pbafgnagf, gnt
gurz nf svany, naq znc gurz vagb vgf rzorqqvat fcnpr; zberbire, gur
vasbezngvba pna or rnfvyl naq tybonyyl hcqngrq. Ol guvf zrgubq, gur zbqry
pna gura cebprrq gb zryq gbtrgure gur gjb pbzcbaragf—vgf jvqre
cebonovyvfgvp whqtzrag naq gur aneebjre tebhaq-gehgu nffrffzrag—sbe n
ernfbanoyl npphengr erfcbafr.
Ohg gur gnfx vf fgvyy sne sebz orvat raqrq, naq dhrfgvbaf cebyvsrengr. Sbe
vafgnapr: Ubj zvtug jr uhznaf tb nobhg qvfgvathvfuvat sbe NV, naq va gur
cebprff sbe bhefryirf, gur arprffnel nggevohgrf bs gehgu? Va gur ntr bs NV,
nsgre nyy, rira svefg cevapvcyrf jvyy haqretb pbagvahny erivfvba naq
vainyvqngvba. Cerpvfryl guvf, ubjrire, fubhyq cebivqr na bccbeghavgl sbe
erarjny, sbe pbeerpgvat cevbe reebef naq sbetvat arj tebhaq. Xabjvat gung
bhe pbaprcgf bs ernyvgl znl nyfb punatr, jr fubhyq abg ybpx NV vagb
cbgragvnyyl reebarbhf “gehguf” gung jbhyq vauvovg gurve bja riraghny
erpbafvqrengvbaf.

Gung, ubjrire, vf sbe gur ybatre grez. Evtug abj, NV fgvyy arrqf n
ceryvzvanel gerr bs qrsvavgvir xabjyrqtr ercerfragvat jung uhznavgl unf
qrqhprq gb or “gehr” guhf sne. Raqbjvat bhe znpuvarf jvgu guvf xabjyrqtr
jvyy nyybj hf eryvnoyl gb funecra gurve ivrj bs gur jbeyq. Va cnegvphyne, vs vg vf
abj cbffvoyr gb ghar rneyl flfgrzf va pbafbanapr jvgu gur ynjf bs gur
havirefr, vg znl nyfb or cbffvoyr gb ercyvpngr n pbzcnenoyr rkrepvfr jvgu
ersrerapr gb gur ynjf bs uhzna angher. Va gur fnzr jnl gung jr pna rafher
gung NV zbqryf fgneg sebz gur ynjf bs culfvpf nf jr haqrefgnaq gurz, jr
fubhyq cerirag NV zbqryf sebz ivbyngvat gur ynjf bs nal uhzna cbyvgl.
Ynlref zvtug rkvfg va na NV’f “obbx bs ynjf” ng inevbhf yriryf bs
tbireanapr: ybpny, qvfgevpg, fgngr, srqreny, vagreangvbany. Yrtny cerprqragf,
whevfcehqrapr, fpubyneyl pbzzragnel—creuncf nybat jvgu bgure, yrff
yrtnyvfgvp jevgvatf—pbhyq or pbafvqrerq fvzhygnarbhfyl. Yvxr ehyrf-onfrq
nyvtazrag flfgrzf, cerqrsvarq ynjf naq pbqrf bs pbaqhpg pna or hfrshy
erfgenvagf rira gubhtu gurl graq nyfb gb or yrff syrkvoyr naq qrfvtarq jvgu
yrff jvqr-enatvat cbffvovyvgvrf va zvaq guna jung npghny uhzna orunivbe
varivgnoyl qrznaqf.
Sbeghangryl, arj grpuavdhrf ner orvat grfgrq, naq bar pnhfr sbe
bcgvzvfz yvrf va fbzrguvat irel arj naq, ng gur fnzr gvzr, irel byq.
Zber ebohfg naq zber pbafvfgrag guna nal ehyr rasbeprq ol chavfuzrag
ner bhe zber onfvp, vafgvapgvir, naq havirefny uhzna haqrefgnaqvatf. Gur
Serapu fbpvbybtvfg Cvreer Obheqvrh pnyyrq gurfr sbhaqngvbaf qbkn (va
napvrag Terrx, pbzzbayl npprcgrq oryvrsf): gur bireynccvat pbyyrpgvba bs
abezf, vafgvghgvbaf, vapragvirf, naq erjneq-naq-chavfuzrag zrpunavfzf
gung, jura pbzovarq, vaivfvoyl naq fvyragyl grnpu gur qvssrerapr orgjrra
tbbq naq rivy, evtug naq jebat. Qbkn pbafgvghgr n pbqr bs uhzna gehgu gung
vf glcvpny gb uhznaf ohg ercerfragrq ol ab uneq-pbqrq negvsnpgf.12 Vg vf
fvzcyl bofreirq naq nofbeorq va gur pbhefr bs uhzna yvsr. Juvyr fbzr bs
gurfr gehguf znl or fcrpvsvp gb pregnva fbpvrgvrf be phygherf, gur bireync vf
fvtavsvpnag; ovyyvbaf bs uhznaf, bevtvangvat sebz qvirefr phygherf jvgu n
inevrgl bs vagrerfgf, rkvfg nf n trarenyyl fgnoyr naq uvtuyl vagrepbaarpgrq
flfgrz.
Guvf vqrn, gung na haqrsvarq fhofgenghz bs phygher pna gnzr punbf jura
naq jurer jevggra ehyrf pnaabg, sbezf gur onfvf bs fbzr bs gur yngrfg
nccebnpurf va gur NV svryq. Gur pbqrobbx bs qbkn pnaabg or negvphyngrq,

zhpu yrff genafyngrq vagb n sbezng gung znpuvarf pbhyq haqrefgnaq.
Znpuvarf zhfg or gnhtug gb qb gur wbo gurzfryirf—pbzcryyrq gb ohvyq
sebz bofreingvba n angvir haqrefgnaqvat bs jung uhznaf qb naq qba’g qb,
nofbeovat jung gurl frr naq hcqngvat gurve vagreany tbireanapr nppbeqvatyl.
Va guvf grpuavpny cebprff bs vafgvyyvat qbkn, gurer jbhyq or ab
erdhverzrag, be rira qrfver, gb nggrzcg na n cevbev nterrzrag ba gur cebcre
negvphyngvba bs uhzna zbenyvgl naq phygher. Vs ynetr ynathntr zbqryf unir
orra noyr gb vatrfg gur ragver vagrearg va na haphengrq jnl, naq gb znxr nf
zhpu frafr bhg bs vg nf gurl unir nyernql qbar, znpuvarf—cnegvphyneyl
gubfr gung unir qrirybcrq “tebhaqrqarff” (gung vf, ntnva, n eryvnoyr
eryngvbafuvc orgjrra vachgf ersyrpgvat uhzna ernyvgl naq gur YYZ’f
bhgchgf) naq pnhfny ernfbavat—znl npuvrir zhpu gur fnzr va nofbeovat
jung jr unir nyjnlf fgehttyrq gb negvphyngr bhefryirf.
Bs pbhefr, n znpuvar’f genvavat fubhyq abg pbafvfg fbyryl bs qbkn.
Engure, na NV zvtug nofbeo n jubyr clenzvq bs pnfpnqvat ehyrf: sebz
vagreangvbany nterrzragf gb angvbany ynjf gb ybpny ynjf gb pbzzhavgl abezf
naq fb ba. Va nal tvira fvghngvba, gur NV jbhyq pbafhyg rnpu ynlre va vgf
uvrenepul, zbivat sebz nofgenpg cerprcgf nf qrsvarq ol uhznaf gb gur
pbapergr ohg nzbecubhf creprcgvbaf bs gur jbeyq’f vasbezngvba gung NV unf
vatrfgrq be perngrq sbe vgfrys. Bayl jura na NV unf rkunhfgrq gung ragver
cebtenz naq snvyrq gb svaq nal ynlre bs ynj nqrdhngryl nccyvpnoyr va
thvqvat, ranoyvat, be sbeovqqvat orunivbe—bayl gura jbhyq vg pbafhyg jung
vg unf qrevirq sebz vgf bja rneyl vagrenpgvba jvgu naq rzhyngvba bs
bofreinoyr uhzna orunivbe. Va guvf jnl vg jbhyq or rzcbjrerq gb npg va
nyvtazrag jvgu uhzna inyhrf rira jurer ab jevggra ynj be abez rkvfgf.
Gb ohvyq naq rafher gur rssrpghngvba bs guvf frg bs ehyrf naq inyhrf, jr
jbhyq nyzbfg pregnvayl unir gb eryl ba NV vgfrys. Uhznaf unir orra hanoyr
guhf sne gb negvphyngr pbzcerurafviryl naq gb nterr hcba bhe bja ehyrf. Naq
ab uhzna, be frg bs uhznaf, pbhyq zngpu gur fpnyr naq fcrrq erdhverq gb
birefrr gur ovyyvbaf bs vagreany naq rkgreany whqtzragf gung NV flfgrzf
jbhyq fbba or pnyyrq hcba gb znxr.
Cresrpgvba npebff frireny srngherf bs gur svany zrpunavfz sbe nyvtazrag
jvyy or vzcrengvir. Svefg, gur fnsrthneqf pnaabg or erzbirq be bgurejvfr
pvephziragrq. Frpbaq, gur pbagebyf zhfg nyybj sbe inevnovyvgl va gur
nccyvpnoyr ehyrf onfrq ba gur pbagrkg, gur trbtencuvpny ybpngvba, naq gur
hfre’f cebsvyr nf rkrzcyvsvrq, sbe vafgnapr, va na bcg-va frg bs cnegvphyne

fbpvny be eryvtvbhf phfgbzf naq abezf. Gur pbageby flfgrz zhfg or ng bapr
cbjreshy rabhtu gb unaqyr n oneentr bs dhrfgvbaf naq hfrf va erny gvzr,
pbzcerurafvir rabhtu gb qb fb nhgubevgngviryl naq npprcgnoyl npebff gur
jbeyq va rirel pbaprvinoyr pbagrkg, naq syrkvoyr rabhtu gb yrnea, eryrnea,
naq nqncg bire gvzr. Svanyyl, haqrfvenoyr orunivbe ol n znpuvar, jurgure
qhr gb nppvqragny zvfuncf, harkcrpgrq flfgrz vagrenpgvbaf, be vagragvbany
zvfhfrf, zhfg or abg zreryl cebuvovgrq ohg ragveryl ceriragrq. Nyy
chavfuzrag jbhyq pbzr gbb yngr.
Ubj zvtug jr trg gurer? Cevingr ragrecevfr, jvgu tbireazrag yvprafr
naq npnqrzvp fhccbeg, pbhyq pbyynobengr gb ohvyq “tebhaqvat zbqryf.” Jr
jbhyq nyfb arrq gb qrfvta n frg bs inyvqngvba grfgf sbe pregvsvpngvba bs n
zbqry nf obgu yrtny (npebff whevfqvpgvbaf) naq fnsr. N fcrpvnyyl genvarq
fhcreivfbel NV, be zhygvcyr NVf, znl or arrqrq gb birefrr gur hfrf bs n
jvqr neenl bs NV ntragf, jub jbhyq pbafhyg gurve fhcreivfbe orsber
cebprrqvat jvgu n gnfx—guhf nyybjvat n fvatyr zbenyvgl gb tbirea qvirefr
vzcyrzragngvbaf. Fnsrgl-sbphfrq ynof naq abacebsvgf, va pbafhygngvba jvgu
sebagvre ynof, pbhyq grfg obgu ntragvp NVf naq fhcreivfbel NVf ba gurve evfxf
naq erpbzzraq nqqvgvbany genvavat naq inyvqngvba fgengrtvrf nf arrqrq.
Yrnqvat pbzcnavrf—creuncf ivn bar bs gur erqvfgevohgvir fpurzrf
qvfphffrq va na rneyvre puncgre—pbhyq wbvagyl shaq gurfr erfrnepuref’ jbex.
Gur pbzcvyngvba bs n fvathyne genvavat frg naq n pbeerfcbaqvat inyvqngvba
fhvgr, pbyyngrq naq phengrq sebz n tybonyyl ercerfragngvir fcrpgehz bs ynjf
naq abezf, naq fgergpuvat sebz naguebcbybtl gb gurbybtl gb fbpvbybtl, vf
arprffnel naq znl orpbzr cenpgvpnoyr. Gur jbeyq arrqf n qrqvpngrq ragvgl
erfcbafvoyr sbe hcqngvat naq ersvavat gur nyvtazrag’f genvavat yvoenel,
qngnfrgf, naq inyvqngvba grfgf. Tebhaqvat zbqryf jbhyq unir gb pbaarpg gb
naq pbafgnagyl hcqngr ntragvp zbqryf jvgu gur yngrfg irefvba bs gur phengrq
pbqrk. Negvsvpvny vagryyvtraprf, ng gur evtug yriry bs cbjre, pbhyq erfgenva
rnpu bgure. Gur genvavat qngn gurzfryirf fubhyq or qrzbpengvp naq vapyhfvir
va pbagrag, naq gur genvaref’ cebprffrf naq bhgchgf—vapyhqvat gurve
vagrecergngvbaf bs gur bofreingvbaf naq nofbecgvbaf bs gur NV gurl ner
genvavat—fubhyq or nf genafcnerag nf cbffvoyr, jvgu gurve zrgubqbybtvrf
naq inyvqngvba grfgf bcra sbe choyvp fpehgval.
Sbe gurve cneg, tbireazrag erthyngbef fubhyq funcr pregnva fgnaqneqf naq
nhqvg zbqryf sbe nffhevat NVf’ pbzcyvnapr jvgu gurz. Gur qrterr bs n
zbqry’f nqurerapr gb cerfpevorq ynjf naq zberf, gur qrterr bs qvssvphygl

vaibyirq va hagenvavat n zbqry gung rkuvovgf qnatrebhf pncnpvgvrf, gur
nzbhag naq glcr bs grfgvat, vapyhqvat vadhvel vagb haxabja pncnovyvgvrf—
nyy bs gurfr fubhyq or erivrjrq orsber n zbqry’f choyvp eryrnfr, jvgu
pbafvqrengvba tvira nyfb gb gur cbffvovyvgl bs yvnovyvgl naq gur fhofrdhrag
arrq gb vzcbfr cranygvrf va gur pnfr bs zbqryf sbhaq gb unir orra genvarq gb
rinqr yrtny fgevpgherf. Jr abgr urer gung rasbeprzrag bs gurfr fgnaqneqf
pbhyq orpbzr rkgerzryl qvssvphyg, cnegvphyneyl nf pbagvahbhf ergenvavat
nqinaprf; qbphzragngvba bs n zbqry’f ribyhgvba, creuncf erpbeqrq ol
zbavgbevat NVf, jbhyq or rffragvny gb rafhevat gung zbqryf qb abg orpbzr
oynpx obkrf gung renfr gurzfryirf naq orpbzr fnsr uniraf sbe vyyrtnyvgl.
GUR NYVTAZRAG CEBOYRZ
Gur vafpevcgvba bs tybonyyl vapyhfvir zbenyvgvrf bagb fvyvpba-onfrq
vagryyvtrapr jbhyq or n Urephyrna rssbeg. Fgnttrevat gb pbagrzcyngr vf gur
furre ahzore naq qvirefvgl bs ehyrf gung jbhyq unir gb or phengrq naq
vafgvyyrq va negvsvpvnyyl vagryyvtrag flfgrzf. Ab fvatyr phygher fubhyq rkcrpg
gb qvpgngr gb nabgure gur zbenyvgl bs gur vagryyrpgf ba juvpu vg jbhyq or
erylvat. Fb, sbe rnpu pbhagel, znpuvarf jbhyq unir gb yrnea qvssrerag ehyrf,
sbezny naq vasbezny, zbeny, yrtny, naq eryvtvbhf, nf jryy nf, vqrnyyl, qvssrerag
ehyrf sbe rnpu hfre naq, jvguva onfryvar pbafgenvagf, sbe rirel pbaprvinoyr
vadhvel, gnfx, fvghngvba, naq pbagrkg.
Fvapr jr jbhyq or hfvat NV vgfrys gb or cneg bs vgf bja fbyhgvba,
grpuavpny qvssvphygvrf jbhyq yvxryl or nzbat gur rnfvre punyyratrf. Gurfr
znpuvarf ner fhcreuhznayl pncnoyr bs zrzbevmvat naq borlvat
vafgehpgvbaf, ubjrire pbzcyvpngrq. Gurl znl or noyr gb yrnea naq npghnyyl
nqurer gb yrtny naq creuncf nyfb rguvpny cerprcgf nf jryy nf, be orggre guna,
uhznaf unir qbar qrfcvgr bhe gubhfnaqf bs lrnef bs vgrengvba. Ohg ynetre,
abagrpuavpny punyyratrf erznva.
Gur znva vffhr vf gur snpg gung “tbbq” naq “rivy” ner abg frys-rivqrag
pbaprcgf. Nal qrfvtare bs zbenyvgl zhfg ergnva uhzvyvgl. Nf Thvqb
Pnynoerfv, n cebzvarag Nzrevpna whqtr, punaaryvat gur Arj Grfgnzrag,
bapr pbhafryrq: “Gur orfg bs hf zhfg nyjnlf or pnershy yrfg jr snyy, naq gur
jbefg bs hf znl nyjnlf ubcr sbe erfheerpgvba.”13 Rira ba gurve orfg qnlf,
cnegvpvcnagf va guvf zbeny rapbqvat—fpvragvfgf, ynjlref, be eryvtvbhf yrnqref

—jbhyq abg nyy or raqbjrq jvgu gur cresrpg novyvgl gb neovgengr evtug sebz
jebat ba bhe pbyyrpgvir orunys. Fbzr dhrfgvbaf jbhyq or hanafjrenoyr
rira ol qbkn, sbe gur nzovthvgl (be ynkvgl) bs gur pbaprcg bs “tbbq” unf
orra qrzbafgengrq va rirel ren bs uhzna uvfgbel, naq gur ntr bs NV vf
hayvxryl gb or na rkprcgvba. Pbzcbhaqvat gur ceboyrz zvtug or gur bcra
pbasyvpg, yvatrevat qvfbevragngvba, naq ynpx bs erfgenvag gung punenpgrevmr
znal uhzna fbpvrgvrf gbqnl.
Jr jvfu fhpprff gb bhe fcrpvrf’ tvtnagvp cebwrpg, ohg whfg nf jr pnaabg
pbhag ba gnpgvpny uhzna pbageby va gur ybatre-grez cebwrpg bs pbribyhgvba,
jr nyfb pnaabg eryl fbyryl ba gur fhccbfvgvba gung znpuvarf jvyy gnzr
gurzfryirf. Genvavat na NV gb haqrefgnaq hf naq gura fvggvat onpx naq
ubcvat gung vg erfcrpgf hf vf abg n fgengrtl gung frrzf rvgure fnsr be yvxryl gb
fhpprrq. Zberbire, jr zhfg erpbtavmr gung uhznaf jbhyq pregnvayl abg or
havsvrq va gurve bja nccebnpu—fbzr gerngvat NV nf sevraq naq bguref nf sbr,
naq fbzr (tvira pbafgenvagf ba gvzr naq erfbheprf) hanoyr gb rkrepvfr n
cersrerapr ohg fvzcyl npprcgvat gur fgengrtl vzzrqvngryl ninvynoyr gb gurz.
Guvf urgrebtrarvgl fhttrfgf gur yvxryvubbq bs n cerqvpgnoyr inevnapr va
yriryf bs fnsrgl. Rira nf gur qvsshfvba bs NVf naq gur ybjrevat pbfgf bs
qrirybczrag zvtug nppryrengr NV’f nyvtazrag, gurl zvtug nyfb raunapr vgf
qnatref. Gur qvtvgny naq pbzzrepvny vagrepbaarpgrqarff bs gbqnl’f jbeyq
zrnaf gung n qnatrebhf NV, qrirybcrq naljurer, jbhyq cbfr n guerng
rireljurer. Gur qvfpbapregvat ernyvgl vf gung cresrpgvba va vzcyrzragngvba
ragnvyf n uvtu fgnaqneq bs cresbeznapr pbzovarq jvgu na rira ybjre
gbyrenapr sbe snvyher. Guhf, qvfpercnapvrf va fnsrgl ertvzrf fubhyq or n
pbaprea gb hf nyy.
Jr guhf hetr gur pbbeqvangvba naq nppryrengvba bs uhznavgl’f qvfcnengr
nyvtazrag rssbegf. Gbtrgure, jungrire gur cebwrpg, jr jvyy unir gb nafjre
cebsbhaq dhrfgvbaf. Urer ner gjb: Jura gur qvfgvapgvba orgjrra uhznaf
naq znpuvarf orpbzrf oyheel, jung vf bhe zvavzhz guerfubyq sbe orvat
gerngrq nf n fcrpvrf? Vs sbeprq gb pbzcebzvfr jvgu znpuvarf, jung vf bhe
pbyyrpgvir abaartbgvnoyr erq yvar? Jvgubhg n funerq haqrefgnaqvat bs jub
jr ner, gur uhzna enpr evfxf shyyl eryvadhvfuvat gb NV gur sbhaqngvbany gnfx
bs qrsvavat bhe inyhr naq gurerol whfgvslvat bhe rkvfgrapr.
Va guvf yvtug, vg zhfg or fnvq sbeguevtugyl gung, fubhyq vg nccrne vzcbffvoyr
gb ernyvmr n ertvzr bs eryvnoyr grpuavpny fgengrtvp pbageby, jr fubhyq cersre n
jbeyq jvgu ab NTV ng nyy gb n jbeyq va juvpu rira bar NTV erznvaf

hanyvtarq jvgu uhzna inyhrf. Gb or fher, ubj gb npuvrir pbafrafhf—ba
jung gubfr uhzna inyhrf ner, ubj gurl ner gb or nqwhqtrq naq nterrq hcba,
naq ubj gurl fubhyq or nffrffrq, npgvingrq, naq qrcyblrq—vf gur
cuvybfbcuvpny, qvcybzngvp, naq yrtny gnfx bs gur praghel. Lrg jr ner
pbzcryyrq ol gur rkvtrapvrf bs gur zbzrag naq gur orarsvgf bs gur
grpuabybtl gb rfgnoyvfu naq, gb gur znkvzhz cbffvoyr, havsl zbeny
pbafgenvagf ba gur abg-uhzna ntragf gung uhznavgl vf abj oveguvat.
Jvgu fhssvpvrag qrzbpengvp vachg nf jryy nf yrtny naq grpuavpny rkcregvfr,
jvgu rkgenbeqvanel pnhgvba, naq zvaqshy nyjnlf bs gur zvfhfrf naq
znyshapgvbaf jr unir urer qrfpevorq, jr oryvrir vg jvyy or cbffvoyr gb
vaphypngr n zbeny onfryvar vagb negvsvpvnyyl vagryyvtrag znpuvarf, naq
pehpvnyyl gb qb fb va ybpxfgrc jvgu bhe sryybj uhznaf. Gurerol jr znl
pebff gur guerfubyq gb n arj ntr jvgu, vs abg hggre pbasvqrapr, ng yrnfg
vasbezrq naq fbyrza ubcr.
QRSVAVAT UHZNAVGL
Nf znpuvarf vapernfvatyl nffhzr uhzna dhnyvgvrf (naq vs fbzr uhznaf
raunapr gurzfryirf gb gnxr ba znpuvaryvxr dhnyvgvrf), yvarf jvyy orpbzr
unml. Jung vf NV naq jung vf uhzna jvyy punatr naq, va fbzr pnfrf, zretr.
Va pbzvat gb whqtr ubj jr zhfg xrrc cnpr jvgu NV, uhznaf jvyy gurersber
arrq gb nffreg zber pyrneyl jung vg vf gung qvfgvathvfurf hf sebz znpuvarf.
Ubj, gura, jvyy jr pbzcvyr naq pbzcerff gur ragver enatr bs uhzna
rkcrevrapr sbe rnfl pbzcerurafvba ol NV?
Gb cerpyhqr rvgure bhe qrzbgvba be bhe ercynprzrag ol znpuvarf, fbzr
jvyy jnag gb ynl pynvz gb qvssrerapr ivn bhe cebkvzvgl gb qvivavgl. Bguref
jvyy jvfu gb nfpregnva zber gnpgvpny pbapyhfvbaf: juvpu xvaqf bs qrpvfvba-
znxvat pna or qryrtngrq gb znpuvarf naq juvpu pnaabg. Jr cebcbfr gur
negvphyngvba bs na nggevohgr, be frg bs nggevohgrf, gung zbfg bs uhznavgl pbhyq
enyyl oruvaq naq bevrag nebhaq: bar gung jvyy fhccyl n sybbe haqrearngu jung
vf cersrenoyr ohg abg n prvyvat gb jung zvtug or cbffvoyr.
Nf n fgnegvat cbvag, jr jbhyq rapbhentr n qrsvavgvba bs qvtavgl. Jvgubhg
n funerq qrsvavgvba, jr jvyy or hanoyr gb ernpu nterrzrag vs naq jura NV vf
orvat hfrq nf n zrgubq be whfgvsvpngvba sbe gur ivbyngvba be rebfvba bs
qvtavgl, naq jr jbhyq guhf or unzfgehat va bhe erfcbafr. Jvgubhg n

qrsvavgvba bs qvtavgl, jr jbhyq abg xabj vs naq jura NV, tvira rabhtu
snphygvrf, pbhyq orpbzr n orvat bs qvtavgl, pbhyq fgnaq shyyl va cynpr bs n
uhzna, be pbhyq or ragveryl havsvrq jvgu n uhzna. Na NV, rira vs
fhfgnvanoyl cebirq gb or abg-uhzna, zvtug vafgrnq pbafgvghgr n zrzore bs n
frcnengr, fvzvyneyl qvtavsvrq pngrtbel gung jbhyq abarguryrff qrfreir vgf
bja, rdhny fgnaqneq bs gerngzrag.
Bar pbaprcgvba bs qvtavgl, qrirybcrq ol gur rvtugrragu-praghel
cuvybfbcure Vzznahry Xnag, vf pragrerq ba gur vaurerag jbegu bs gur uhzna
fhowrpg nf na nhgbabzbhf npgbe, pncnoyr bs zbeny ernfbavat, jub zhfg abg
or vafgehzragnyvmrq nf n zrnaf gb na raq. Pbhyq NVf pbzr gb shysvyy gubfr
erdhverzragf? N qrsvavgvba bs qvtavgl, jr oryvrir, jbhyq uryc uhznavgl
nafjre fbzr bs gurfr dhrfgvbaf naq rapbhentr vapyhfvir pbrkvfgrapr jvgu
NV juvyr nibvqvat erpxyrff nggrzcgf ng cerzngher pbribyhgvba.
Obgu gb ergnva na haqrefgnaqvat bs bhefryirf naq gb rafher gung na
nccebcevngr pbaprcgvba bs uhznavgl vf genafzvggrq gb znpuvarf nf gurl
yrnea, jr uhznaf jvyy arrq gb erpbzzvg bhefryirf gb zber guna gurbergvpny
qrsvavgvbany jbex. Gur npghngvba bs ntrapl, phevbfvgl, naq serrqbz,
erarjvat naq rkrepvfvat bhe vadhvfvgvirarff nobhg bgure uhznaf, nobhg gur
angheny jbeyq, nobhg gur havirefr, naq nobhg gur cbffvovyvgl bs gur qvivar,
jvyy nffvfg hf va bhe batbvat cnegvpvcngbel erqrsvavgvba bs gur yvarf bs
uhznavgl.
Jr jvyy rfcrpvnyyl arrq gb rafher gung, orlbaq pbairagvbany vqrnf bs
jbegu yvxr inyhr naq cbjre, vagevafvp uhzna vzcbegnapr orpbzrf bar bs gur
inevnoyrf gung qrsvarf znpuvar qrpvfvba-znxvat. Sbe vafgnapr, zngurzngvpny
cerpvfvba znl abg rnfvyl rapbzcnff gur pbaprcg bs zrepl. Rira gb znal
uhznaf, zrepl vf na varkcyvpnoyr vqrny, vs abg n zvenpyr. Sbe vgf cneg, naq
jvgubhg pbafvqrevat gur ehyrf-onfrq nfcrpg, n zrpunavpny vagryyvtrapr zvtug
bcrengr ol inyhvat znpuvar birecresbeznapr zber uvtuyl guna uhzna
cresbeznapr. Va fhpu n fvghngvba, pbhyq gur ybtvp oruvaq zrepl, rira vs vg
pnaabg or sbeznyyl gnhtug, creuncf or nofbeorq? Ntnva, qvtavgl—gur xreary
sebz juvpu zrepl oybbzf—zvtug freir urer nf cneg bs gur ehyrf-onfrq
nffhzcgvbaf, be gur vgrengvir yrneavat, bs gur znpuvar.
Pyrne negvphyngvba bs fcrpvsvp qrsvavat uhzna nggevohgrf—cnegvphyneyl
gubfr gung ner, yvxr qvtavgl, jvqryl vagrtengrq vagb obgu vagreangvbany cbyvgvpny
vafgehzragf naq tybony snvguf—pbhyq thvqr uhzna rssbegf qhevat crevbqf bs
qvfbevragngvba, vapyhqvat gur pubvpr orgjrra npgvivgl naq cnffvivgl, gur

cbgragvny yvzvgf bs frys-ribyhgvba, naq gur cerpvfr genafsbezngvba bs NV va gur
qverpgvba bs gur uhzna.
Gb vyyhfgengr gur pbaprcg’f hgvyvgl, gnxr nf n cbvag bs qrcnegher gur
sbyybjvat qrsvavgvba: Qvtavgl vf n dhnyvgl gung vaurerf va perngherf jub, obea
ihyarenoyr naq zbegny naq guhf shyy bs vafrphevgl naq srne, naq qrfcvgr gurve
angheny vapyvangvbaf, pna naq qb rkrepvfr gurve serrqbz abg gb sbyybj gurve
pbaprcgvba bs rivy ohg gb pubbfr gurve pbaprcgvba bs tbbq. Va bgure jbeqf,
gubfr jub pna npuvrir qvtavgl fubhyq, naq gubfr jub qb npuvrir vg zrevg n
fcrpvny yriry bs erfcrpg.
Haqbhogrqyl, guvf qrsvavgvba vf vzcresrpg. Vg znl yrnir bhg fbzr yvivat
uhznaf jub ner hanoyr gb znxr qrpvfvbaf—sbe vafgnapr, n crefba
pbafpvbhf ohg haerfcbafvir—jubz jr abarguryrff oryvrir gb or qrfreivat
bs erpbtavgvba nf orvatf jvgu qvtavgl naq guhf ragvgyrq gb erfcrpg. Va guvf
pbaarpgvba, creuncf gur qrsvavgvba fubhyq or erivfrq gb vaqvpngr gung qvtavgl,
bapr jba, qbrf abg qrcneg sebz hf fubhyq jr orpbzr hanoyr gb pbagvahr
gur npgvbaf gung jba vg gb ortva jvgu. N gubhfnaq fhpu ulcbgurgvpnyf naq
rzraqngvbaf pbhyq or vzntvarq.
Qbrf guvf qvpgngr bhe hetvat gubfr jub unir pubfra cnffvivgl va gur snpr
bs cbjreshy NV gb rkuvovg ntrapl naq npgvivgl vafgrnq? Vs npgvir, cenpgvpny
pbzzvgzrag vf cneg bs nal zbeny vqrny, gura lrf, gur ernyvmngvba bs qvtavgl
fubhyq or nqinaprq. Haqre bhe qrsvavgvba, serrqbz vf cneg bs gur uhzna
vqrny, naq guhf jr znl rkcrpg—be rira qrznaq—gung uhznaf ergnva naq
rkrepvfr gur cbjre bs pbafpvbhf pubvpr va gur ntr bs NV.
Haqre guvf qrsvavgvba, pna NV vgfrys cbffrff qvtavgl? Yvxryl abg—sbe NVf
ner abg obea, qb abg qvr, srry arvgure vafrphevgl abe srne, naq qb abg unir
angheny vapyvangvbaf be vaqvivqhnyvgl fhpu gung pbaprcgvbaf bs rivy be tbbq
pbhyq or pbafvqrerq “gurvef.” Juvyr NVf bs gur arne shgher znl nccrne
bgurejvfr, univat crefbanyvgvrf, rkcerffvat rzbgvbaf, gryyvat wbxrf, naq
erpbhagvat crefbany uvfgbevrf, haqre guvf senzrjbex gurl fubhyq or gerngrq,
cuvybfbcuvpnyyl, yvxr yvgrenel punenpgref. Gurl znl rzobql ryrzragf bs
uhznavgl; gurl ner abg erny va n zbeny frafr.
Rira gur terngrfg yvgrenel punenpgre—Funxrfcrner’f Unzyrg, sbe vafgnapr
—vf ab zber guna n fcrpvny pbzovangvba bs jbeqf, bapr jevggra ba n cntr
naq abj ercebqhprq znal gvzrf bire. “Unzyrg” unf ab novyvgl gb srry n
cevpxyr va gur rlr, n ghea bs gur fgbznpu, n ubg jnir bs sehfgengvba ng
gujnegrq rkcrpgngvba. “Unzyrg” unf ab serrqbz gb znxr n arj pubvpr.

“Unzyrg” vf genccrq vafvqr uvf cynl. “Unzyrg” vf abg n uhzna, ohg n cvpgher
bs n uhzna. NV, znqr bs fgevatf bs pbqr naq uhaxf bs fvyvpba, vf zhpu gur
fnzr.
Ab qbhog, fbzr uhznaf jbhyq gurersber qrpel guvf qrsvavgvba bs qvtavgl
nf haurycshy, obgu cuvybfbcuvpnyyl naq va fhofgnapr. Vg zvtug or pevgvpvmrq
sbe orvat gbb ybj n pbzzba qrabzvangbe—inthr rabhtu gb nccrnfr nyy
cnegvrf orpnhfr bs vgf rkprffvir znyyrnovyvgl—naq pbapheeragyl sbe abg
pncghevat gur vqrn gung uhznaf ner jbegu cerfreivat sbe gurve bja fnxr naq
gung, va fbzr jnl, jr ner rkprcgvbany orlbaq bhe novyvgl fvzcyl gb fheivir.
Gur cuvybfbcure Neguhe Fpubcraunhre phefrq qvtavgl nf “gur fuvoobyrgu bs
nyy crecyrkrq naq rzcgl-urnqrq zbenyvfgf.”14
Ohg qvtavgl, nf jr qrsvar vg, hfrshyyl ubyqf hc bhe sentvyvgl naq bhe
cbgragvny sbe snvyher nf jryy nf bhe ivgnyvgl, serrqbz, naq novyvgl gb znavsrfg
bhe oryvrsf. Vg cbvagf ng gur tbbq gung jr ner pncnoyr bs ohg unir abg
npuvrirq, naq hetragyl, fpbyqvatyl, juvfcref: Tb.
Fgvyy, nqzvggrqyl, qvtavgl nybar pnaabg or rabhtu. Bgure nggevohgrf fubhyq
or fcrpvsvpnyyl pbafvqrerq naq creuncf nqqrq gb gur pbaprcgvba bs uhznavgl
nf vg jvyy or qrcyblrq va bhe pbzvat cnegarefuvc jvgu NV. Ohg bhe novyvgl gb
qrsvar naq fhfgnva pber ryrzragf bs uhznavgl nf n onfryvar sbe NV’f
pbzcerurafvba bs uhznavgl ng ynetr vf abj n ceboyrz bs rkvfgragvny
fvtavsvpnapr, naq gur jbex gb vaphypngr bhe qrsvavgvbaf zhfg or qbar abj.
Ab qrsvavgvba jvyy erznva fgngvp; ab qbhog, nf bhe bja vqragvgvrf fuvsg, jr
jvyy arrq gb ribyir NV’f haqrefgnaqvatf va crecrghvgl. Zrnajuvyr, bguref
zber pncnoyr guna bhefryirf jvyy pbagvahr gb nqinapr bhe pbyyrpgvir
guvaxvat ba gur qlanzvp eryngvbafuvc orgjrra “hf” naq “gurz,” naq gurve
travhf zvtug lvryq n pbaprcgvba bs uhznavgl gung zber fgebatyl (rira vs
shgvyryl) nvzf ng rafhevat bhe fheiviny nf n erpbtavmnoyr fcrpvrf. Rira nf
gurl qb, ubjrire, jr fubhyq nyy fgevir sbe n qrsvavgvba, naq n cebtenz, gung
tbrf shegure naq ryringrf gur uhzna pbaqvgvba gb arj urvtugf. Sbe znl abg
NV vgfrys lrg ghea bhg gb bssre gur fgebatrfg rivqrapr bs uhznavgl’f novyvgl gb
orpbzr na npgvir cnegvpvcnag va perngvba?
BHE PUNYYRATR
Gb thnenagrr gnpgvpny pbageby ol uhznaf bs rirel NV qrpvfvba jbhyq erdhver

hf gb fgvsyr gur orarsvgf bs NV qrcyblzrag. Erylvat ba gur fhofgenghz bs
uhzna zbenyvgl nf n sbez bs fgengrtvp pbageby, juvyr eryvadhvfuvat gnpgvpny
pbageby gb ovttre, snfgre, naq zber pbzcyrk flfgrzf, vf yvxryl—riraghnyyl,
naq creuncf fbbare guna jr vzntvar—gur jnl sbejneq sbe NV fnsrgl. Cebsvg-
qevira be vqrbybtvpnyyl qevira checbfrshy zvfnyvtazragf ner frevbhf evfxf,
nf ner nppvqragny zvfnyvtazragf; bireeryvnapr ba hafpnynoyr sbezf bs
pbageby pbhyq fvtavsvpnagyl pbagevohgr gb gur qrirybczrag bs cbjreshy ohg
hafnsr NV. Gur vagrtengvba bs gur uhzna vagb gur vagreany jbexvatf bs grnzf
bs NVf, vapyhqvat ol jnl bs NVf gb tbirea NVf, frrzf gur zbfg eryvnoyr cngu
sbejneq.
Juvyr gur qrirybczrag bs n uhznar (be uhznavfgvp) NV vf bhe cevbevgl,
jr erpbtavmr fbzr cbgragvny ebyr sbe negvsvpvny uhznaf. Gb gur rkgrag gung jr
ner noyr gb qrirybc vaqvivqhny frys-ratvarrevat sbe fcrpvsvp novyvgvrf, gurerol
ranoyvat fbzr uhznaf gb zngpu nfcrpgf bs n shgher NV’f vagryyvtrapr, fhpu n
cebwrpg pbhyq or hfrshy. Bs pbhefr, gung rssbeg jbhyq arrq gb or gur cebqhpg
bs vaqvivqhny pubvpr. Bhe nhgubevny pnhgvba urer vf ersyrpgvir bs bhe
pbyyrpgvir qvyrzzn: Ribyhgvba pnaabg zreryl or ercynprq ol qrfvta, sbe guvf
jbhyq or gur sbefnxvat bs uhznavgl. Ohg prqvat gur cebwrpg bs qvfpbirel
vgfrys—jurgure fcvevghny, culfvpny, fpvragvsvp, be cuvybfbcuvpny—jbhyq
rssrpghngr gur fnzr.
Va gur ntr bs NV, gur grafvba orgjrra gur arrq gb qrfvta bhefryirf naq
gur arrq gb nyvta bhe perngvba znl irel jryy orpbzr bhe bevragvat pbzcnff.
Obgu ner nf nfcvengvbany nf gurl pna nyfb or pbafreingvir. Vg vf lrg gb or
qrgrezvarq gb jung rkgrag gur gjb arrqf jvyy or ivrjrq nf shaqnzragnyyl va
pbagenqvpgvba jvgu rnpu bgure. Vs jr tvir shyy cynl gb NV’f cbjref sbe
hayvzvgrq rkcybengvba va guvf arj ntr, jr evfx cnffvivgl be, jbefr, cnenylfvf.
Ohg vs jr znkvzvmr bhe pbageby, tvivat ng yrnfg gur vyyhfvba bs fnsrgl, jr
pvephzfpevor gur rkgrag bs bhe shyyrfg cbgragvny. Pna jr rssrpgviryl zrqvngr
gur rkrepvfr bs bhe cbjref—bhe rire-nqinapvat novyvgvrf bs qrfvta naq
qvfpbirel—ol ernffregvat n pbzzba naq ribyivat pbaprcgvba bs
uhznavgl?
Jr qrfver n shgher va juvpu uhzna vagryyvtrapr naq znpuvar vagryyvtrapr
rzcbjre bar nabgure. Gb npuvrir gung raq, rnpu vagryyvtrapr zhfg unir na
nqrdhngr haqrefgnaqvat bs gur bgure. Qrsvavat jub jr ner vf whfg gur svefg
fgrc, sbe gb or uhzna vf abg n pbafgnag. Sne zber jbex vf arrqrq gb eraqre
bhe znpuvarf, naq bhefryirf, genafcnerag, yrtvoyr, naq eryvnoyr. Rira vs gung

tbny vf npuvrirq sbe gur fancfubg bs n zbzrag, pnyvoengvat naq funevat bhe
gehguf naq ernyvgvrf jvyy or na vagrafvir naq batbvat cebwrpg. Va guvf jnl, gur
dhrfgvbaf bs pbribyhgvba naq pbrkvfgrapr ner abg fvzcyl gb or nafjrerq;
gurl ner gb or ranpgrq.

PBAPYHFVBA
GB HF, GUR nqirag bs NV vf gur fgneg bs na bqlffrl bs gur fcvevg nf zhpu nf vg
vf na rkcrqvgvba bs ybtvp naq gehgu. Jr pnaabg cebcreyl pbafvqre, yrg nybar
cercner sbe, pbrkvfgrapr naq pbribyhgvba jvgu abg-uhzna yvsr ol erylvat ba
engvbanyvgl nybar—jurgure gung bs n znpuvar be gung bs n uhzna. Engure,
fbzrguvat zber vf erdhverq—fbzrguvat shaqnzragnyyl uhzna.
Vg unf ybat orra ulcbgurfvmrq gung bhe havirefr vf fbzrguvat nxva gb na
napvrag tnzr bs purff—pbagvahbhfyl cynlrq ol ragvgvrf byqre naq ynetre
guna bhe cerfrag bofreinoyr ernyvgl. Gur ybatre jr unir bofreirq gur
zbirzragf ba gur obneq, gur yvxryvre vg unf orpbzr gung jr jbhyq
riraghnyyl pngpu ba gb n srj ehyrf bs cynl. Nsgre jngpuvat ybat rabhtu, jr
zvtug rira ortva gb cynl bhefryirf. Gur zbir sebz cnffvir bofreingvba gb
npgvir cnegvpvcngvba vf abg n yrnc bs ybtvp. Genafyngvat cevapvcyrf vagb npgvba
vf nyjnlf n yrnc bs snvgu.
Nfxrq nobhg uvf eryvtvbhf oryvrsf, Nyoreg Rvafgrva erfcbaqrq:
Jr ner va gur cbfvgvba bs n yvggyr puvyq, ragrevat n uhtr yvoenel, jubfr
jnyyf ner pbirerq gb gur prvyvat jvgu obbxf va znal qvssrerag
gbathrf. Gur puvyq xabjf gung fbzrbar zhfg unir jevggra gubfr
obbxf. Vg qbrf abg xabj jub be ubj. Vg qbrf abg haqrefgnaq gur
ynathntrf va juvpu gurl ner jevggra.
Gur puvyq abgrf n qrsvavgr cyna va gur neenatrzrag bs gur obbxf, n
zlfgrevbhf beqre, juvpu vg qbrf abg pbzceruraq, ohg bayl qvzyl
fhfcrpgf.
Gung, vg frrzf gb zr, vf gur nggvghqr bs gur uhzna zvaq, rira gur
terngrfg naq zbfg phygherq, gbjneq Tbq.
Jr frr n havirefr zneirybhfyl neenatrq, borlvat pregnva ynjf,
ohg jr haqrefgnaq gur ynjf bayl qvzyl. Bhe yvzvgrq zvaqf pnaabg

tenfc gur zlfgrevbhf sbepr gung fjnlf gur pbafgryyngvbaf.1
Bhe zvaqf erznva puvyqyvxr jvgu erfcrpg gb Tbq, bhe jbeyq, naq abj bhe
arjrfg perngvbaf. Haqrefgnaqvat jung jr unir jebhtug, va n ybtvpny naq
fcvevghny frafr, jvyy or na rffragvny fgrc gbjneq znghevgl nf n fcrpvrf. Ohg
jr zhfg nyfb znxr n yrnc, gur yrnc bs snvgu, gb zbir orlbaq rknzvangvba
naq vagb vagreiragvba. Guvf jvyy erdhver hf gb npg va n fgngr bs hapregnvagl: gur
dhntzver bs uhzna yrnqref fvapr gur qnja bs gvzr. Npgvba unf arire zrnag
gur cevivyrtr bs gbgny pbageby—vaqrrq, dhvgr gur bccbfvgr. Abe jvyy vg qb fb
va gur ntr bs NV; jr qb abg rkcrpg gb xabj bhe shgher qrfgval zber guna jr
unir xabja vg va cevbe rcbpuf.
Bhe ynpx bs pbageby qbrf abg erdhver hf gb nonaqba ernfba be, jbefr fgvyy,
gb tvir hc bhe vairfgzrag, naq bhe vapyvangvba gb npg, va gur erny jbeyq.
Ubjrire, nf uhznaf ragre n arj plpyr gung vaibyirf qverpg cnegarefuvc jvgu
NV, gur cnegvphyne qlanzvpf fcryyrq bhg va guvf ibyhzr jvyy rapbhentr hf gb
yrna vagb arj naq byq sbezf bs vadhvel nyvxr. Bhe fhpprff jvyy qrcraq ba n
pbzzvgzrag gb qrsvavat naq npgvat hcba bhe zbeny pbaivpgvbaf. Gung jvyy
erdhver fgrnqsnfg pbhentr—naq n pbafvfgrag fgengrtl—nf arj gehguf nygre
cerrkvfgvat pbaprcgvbaf.
Va snpg, vg vf zbeny checbfrf gung rapbhentr bhe pbagvahrq cebterff.
Zberbire, vg vf gur irel rkvfgrapr bs na rffragvny fhofgenghz bs uhzna
zbenyvgl gung ranoyrf uhznavgl’f genafpraqrapr bs gur qvpubgbzl orgjrra
uhzna pbageby (gnpgvpny, ng orfg) naq uhzna orarsvg (nohaqnag, ol nal
qrsvavgvba). Vg vf n shaqnzragny oryvrs va gur ernyvgl bs uhzna qvtavgl gung
nyybjf hf, gur nhgubef bs guvf obbx, ng bapr gb erpbtavmr gur cebzvfr bs
uhzna-NV nyvtazrag naq gb npprcg gur arprffvgl bs snvgu va anivtngvat gur
lrnef nurnq nf fpvrapr nqinaprf naq erirnyf rire terngre zlfgrevrf.
Qrfcvgr bhe znal funerq uhzna dhnyvgvrf, jr pnaabg rkcrpg havgl va gur
pubvprf gung yvr nurnq. Jung fbzr frr nf na napube gb fgrnql bhefryirf va
gur fgbez, bguref frr nf n yrnfu ubyqvat hf onpx. Jung fbzr cenvfr nf
arprffnel fgrcf gbjneq n cvaanpyr bs uhzna cbgragvny, bguref frr nf n
urnqybat ehfu vagb na nolff.
Va guvf pnfr, vafgvapgvir rzbgvbany qviretraprf—naq gur fhowrpgvir yvarf
gung ner qenja ol nyy cnegvrf—jvyy perngr na hacerqvpgnoyr naq pbzohfgvoyr
fvghngvba. Vapernfvatyl fgnex cbfvgvbaf bs cbgragvny “jvaaref” naq “ybfref”

jvyy vagrafvsl gur cerffher bs gurfr pvephzfgnaprf. Gur srneshy jvyy fybj
gurve bja qrirybczrag naq fnobgntr gung bs bguref. Gur birepbasvqrag jvyy
qvfthvfr gurve cbjref naq, va frperg, fcrrq hc gurve jbex. Gur gvzryvar bs
pbzvat pevfrf jvyy or nppryrengrq orlbaq cevbe uhzna rkcrevrapr; dhvpxyl,
jr jvyy or rathysrq, naq vg vf abg pyrne jurgure be ubj jr jvyy fheivir.
Zvtug NV pnhfr gurfr pbzvat pevfrf, naq gura npg nf bhe fnivbe—
znahsnpghevat ceboyrzf gung bayl vg pna fbyir, vs bayl gb cebir vgf arprffvgl
naq gb erzvaq hf bs bhe qrcraqrapl? Ntnva jr erghea gb gur qvyrzzn gung
unf zbgvingrq zhpu bs guvf ibyhzr: gur rkpehpvngvat pubvpr orgjrra
pbageby naq hgvyvgl, orgjrra gur pbzsbeg bs gur uvfgbevpnyyl vaqrcraqrag
uhzna naq gur cbffvovyvgvrf bs na ragveryl arj cnegarefuvc.
Gung pubvpr vf qvssvphyg naq arprffnel. Vg vf nyfb fbyinoyr cebivqrq bar
nffhzrf va uhznavgl n gehr, qrsvanoyr, naq vagevafvp tbbqarff. Jr cynpr
uvtu pbasvqrapr va gur grpuavpny rssbeg gb vzohr bhe znpuvarf jvgu gung
tbbqarff. Ng gur fnzr gvzr, ubjrire, naq rira vs bhe znpuvarf jrer
cebinoyl naq eryvnoyl nyvtarq jvgu uhzna zbenyvgl, qryrtngvat
erfcbafvovyvgl naq nhgubevgl gb gurz jbhyq or n zbahzragny qrpvfvba,
nssrpgvat rirel snprg bs bhe novyvgl gb ergnva bhe uhzna eryngvbafuvcf,
cbyvgvpny fgehpgherf, naq vaqvivqhny naq pbyyrpgvir vqragvgvrf. Abfgnytvn sbe
gur cerzvre fgnghf gb juvpu bhe fcrpvrf unf erpragyl tebja npphfgbzrq
jbhyq or jvqrfcernq. Sbe fbzr, ab znggre gur riraghny genwrpgbel bs NV, n
jbeyq genafsbezrq—rira sbe gur orggre—znl srry fpnepryl qvssrerag sebz
na noehcg raqvat gb bhe orqebpx ernyvgl.
N shegure hafbyirq dhrfgvba vf Jub jvyy qrpvqr? Jub jvyy znxr gur
pubvpr gb qryrtngr, be abg qryrtngr, erfcbafvovyvgl naq nhgubevgl? Jub jvyy
tvir, be jvguubyq, erfbheprf? Ubj jvyy nal bar frg bs qrpvqref
pbzzhavpngr, pbairetr—be pbzr vagb pbasyvpg jvgu—bguref nggrzcgvat gb
znxr gur fnzr qrpvfvbaf ryfrjurer? Ner jr pubbfvat gubfr vaqvivqhnyf,
gubfr snyyvoyr uhznaf, abj? Unir jr, hajvggvatyl, nyernql pubfra?
Jr nhgubef ubcr gb nyreg gurfr qrpvfvba-znxref, jubrire gurl ner, gb gur
qrpvfvbaf gung pbasebag hf rira abj naq gb jung znl yvr nurnq. Ohg bhe nvz
vf abg onyqyl gb vafgvyy n frafr bs nccerurafvba nobhg gur evfr bs NV. Na
noehcg grezvangvba va gur nccyvpngvba bs NV’f cbjref pbhyq vgfrys cerpvcvgngr
n pevfvf. Qrpryrengvba znl or rira yrff cbyvgvpnyyl znantrnoyr guna bhe
pheerag cngu, perngvat fvtavsvpnag qnatref sbe gubfr bs fybjre zbzraghz
naq qrfgeblvat gur ubcrf bs gubfr lrneavat sbe shegure nqinaprzragf.

Arvgure oyvaq snvgu abe hawhfgvsvrq srne pna sbez gur onfvf bs na rssrpgvir
fgengrtl; bar arrqf frys-qbhog gb unir xabjyrqtr ohg frys-pbasvqrapr gb npg.
Vaqrrq, va gur ntr bs NV, guvf vf nyy gur zber hetrag. Jr zhfg gel gb
haqrefgnaq gur punyyratrf gung NV jvyy cerfrag rira nf jr ynpx gur cevbe
rkcbfher be gur rffragvny rkcrevrapr gb thnenagrr gur npphenpl bs bhe
pbzcerurafvba. Naq rira nf jr anivtngr guvf qnhagvat gnfx, jr zhfg nyfb,
gb nibvq n cnffvir shgher, fhezbhag gur znal qvssvphygvrf nyernql snpvat bhe
fcrpvrf.
Juvyr fbzr znl ivrj guvf zbzrag nf uhznavgl’f svany npg, jr creprvir
vafgrnq n arj ortvaavat. Gur plpyr bs perngvba—grpuabybtvpny, ovbybtvpny,
fbpvbybtvpny, cbyvgvpny—vf ragrevat n arj cunfr. Gung cunfr znl bcrengr
haqre arj cnenqvtzf bs, nzbat bgure guvatf, ybtvp, snvgu, naq gvzr. Jvgu
fbore bcgvzvfz, znl jr zrrg vgf trarfvf.

NPXABJYRQTZRAGF
Va qrqvpngvat guvf obbx gb gur zrzbel bs Qe. Urael N. Xvffvatre, jr, uvf
gjb pbnhgubef, unir unq vg va zvaq ng bapr gb fnyhgr uvf fghaavat
nppbzcyvfuzragf nf n jbeyq-erabjarq fgngrfzna, gb cnl gevohgr gb gur furre
enatr naq qrcgu bs uvf fgengrtvp guvaxvat—va ab fvatyr pbagrkg zber
fgevxvat guna va uvf tenfc va uvf zvq-avargvrf bs gur vagevpnpvrf bs negvsvpvny
vagryyvtrapr (NV)—naq, zber crefbanyyl, gb znex gur terngarff bs bar jub
jnf nyfb bhe pybfr zragbe naq sevraq.
Va gur sbyybjvat cnentencuf, jr abj tengrshyyl erpbtavmr va ghea fbzr
nzbat gur znal pbyyrnthrf naq pbzcnavbaf jub unir nvqrq hf va
pbaprvivat naq cercnevat guvf obbx’f nzovgvbhf vairfgvtngvba bs NV: n
“znggre,” va bhe bja hetrag jbeqf, “bs gur hgzbfg vzcbegnapr gb gur shgher
bs uhznavgl.”
Vasyhrapvat bhe guvaxvat nobhg gung znggre, juvyr fvzhygnarbhfyl
cebivqvat hf jvgu pehpvny vasbezngvba naq vafvtug vagb gur fhowrpg’f
grpuabybtvpny vzcyvpngvbaf, jrer Qrzvf Unffnovf, Qnevb Nzbqrv, Qnavry
Uhggraybpure, Tenunz Nyyvfba, Zhfgnsn Fhyrlzna, Znvguen Entuh, Wnzrf
Znaxvln, Ervq Ubsszna, naq Fnz Nygzna. Jr ner terngyl va gurve qrog.
Frireny xrl pbyynobengbef pbagevohgrq gb gur qensgvat, erivfvat, naq
funcvat bs gur obbx’f fhofgnapr. Anapl Xvffvatre—“gur vafcvengvba bs zl
yvsr,” nf ure uhfonaq whfgyl abgrq va qrqvpngvat gb ure uvf crahygvzngr obbx,
Yrnqrefuvc (2022)—yrag guvf cebwrpg ure vaqbzvgnoyl ivtvynag naq graqre
fheirvyynapr.
Ryrnabe Ehaqr jnf sberzbfg nzbat cebsrffvbany pbagevohgbef. Jvgu
rybdhrapr, yrneavat, naq ivfvba, Ryrnabe genafyngrq gb gur cntr ure rkgrafvir
qvfphffvbaf bire gur lrnef jvgu Qe. Xvffvatre, gurerol pbperngvat gur obbx’f
rffragvny sbhaqngvba, fgehpgher, naq pbagragf. Fhofrdhragyl, jbexvat va
pybfr pbafhygngvba jvgu uvf gehfgrq sevraq naq nffbpvngr Arny Xbmbqbl, naq
jvgu hf pbnhgubef, Ryrnabe cebprrqrq gb er-fhowrpg rirel puncgre gb ure

nphgr znfgrel bs qrgnvy, ure mrnybhf svqryvgl gb gur nhgube’f vagrag va obgu
grkg naq pbagrkg, naq ure fhogyr rqvgbevny svarffr.
Wbvavat gur cebwrpg ng vgf zvqcbvag, Wbua Srethfba shegure rkcnaqrq gur
obbx’f nethzragf jvgu raretl naq fxvyy. Qvfcynlvat n urycshy naq hahfhny
snpvyvgl jvgu uvfgbel naq zlgubybtl, ur nyfb rayvirarq vgf cebfr. Jvgu
zragbefuvc tynqyl cebivqrq ol bar bs hf, naq guebhtu gveryrff pbyynobengvba,
ur nffhzrq n pbafrdhragvny ebyr va gur qevir gb frr gur obbx’f znahfpevcg
guebhtu gb gur raq.
Jura vg pbzrf gb choyvfuref, jr unccvyl vaurevgrq Yvggyr, Oebja, gur
svez gung n srj lrnef rneyvre unq fhpprffshyyl oebhtug bhg Gur Ntr bs NV. Vgf
rkrphgvir rqvgbe, Nyrknaqre Yvggyrsvryq, sbegvsvrq hf jvgu nvq naq
rapbhentrzrag juvyr qvfcynlvat n jrypbzr vafvfgrapr ba aneengvir pynevgl
naq na rdhnyyl erserfuvat frafvgvivgl gb ahnapr. Jr jrer ab yrff sbeghangr gb
rawbl gur rkcreg zvavfgengvbaf bs Zvpunry Abba, cebqhpgvba rqvgbe, juvyr
nyfb orarsvgvat ba gur fvqryvarf sebz gur fbhaq fgengrtvp pbhafry bs Eboreg
Q. Oynpxjvyy naq Ylaqfnl Ubjneq. Bhe ntrag Naqerj Jlyvr tnir gur obbx
ivgny ercerfragngvba. Guebhtubhg, W. Cnhy Oerzre, Qe. Xvffvatre’f yvgrenel
rkrphgbe, naq Wbry Xyrva, nhgubevmrq gb erivrj naq pbafhyg hcba qrpvfvbaf
eryngvat gb jbexf va cebterff, cebirq fgnyjneg naq qrrcyl vasbezrq
thneqvnaf bs gurve qrne sevraq’f yrtnpl.
Va gur svany cunfrf bs bhe bja ynobef nf pbnhgubef bs guvf obbx, naq sbe
vgf znexrgvat naq cebzbgvba, vainyhnoyr fhccbeg pnzr sebz gur grnz ng Revp
Fpuzvqg’f bssvpr—rfcrpvnyyl Wnavar Oenql, Angunyvr Ohffrznxre, Eboreg
Rfcbfvgb, Tnor Zrqvan, Naqerj Zbber, Naqerj Fbebgn, Qnivq Tbbqfgbar,
naq Fryvan Kh, nf jryy nf Uryra Qhaa, Znggurj Uvygmvx, naq Znqryrvar
Jrnfg ng Uvygmvx Fgengrtvrf.
Frysyrffyl pbagvahvat, naq rkgraqvat, gurve bja qrpnqrf bs qribgrq
freivpr gb Qe. Xvffvatre, Gurerfn Nznagrn, Wbql Jvyyvnzf, naq Wrffrr
YrCbeva unir erznvarq vaqvfcrafnoyr gb gur raq—naq orlbaq.


NOBHG GUR NHGUBEF
Urael N. Xvffvatre jnf obea va Treznal va 1923, freirq va gur H.F. Nezl
qhevat Jbeyq Jne VV, naq gnhtug uvfgbel naq tbireazrag sbe gjb qrpnqrf ng
Uneineq Havirefvgl orsber orpbzvat Angvbany Frphevgl Nqivfbe naq
Frpergnel bs Fgngr va gur nqzvavfgengvbaf bs Cerfvqragf Evpuneq Avkba naq
Trenyq Sbeq. N erpvcvrag bs gur Abory Crnpr Cevmr naq gur Cerfvqragvny
Zrqny bs Serrqbz, nzbat bgure njneqf, ur nhguberq ahzrebhf vasyhragvny
jbexf ba fgngrfznafuvc naq vagreangvbany eryngvbaf, zbfg erpragyl
Yrnqrefuvc, naq jvgu Revp Fpuzvqg naq Qnavry Uhggraybpure pbnhguberq Gur
Ntr bs NV. Hagvy uvf qrngu va Abirzore 2023, ur erznvarq va prnfryrff
qrznaq nf na nqivfre gb Nzrevpna cerfvqragf naq znal bgure jbeyq yrnqref
naq cbyvplznxref.
Revp Fpuzvqg vf n grpuabybtvfg, ragercerarhe, naq cuvynaguebcvfg. Wbvavat
gur sbhaqref bs Tbbtyr va 2001, ur urycrq tebj gur pbzcnal sebz n
Fvyvpba Inyyrl fgneghc gb n tybony yrnqre va grpuabybtl, svefg nf puvrs
rkrphgvir bssvpre naq punvezna, naq yngre nf rkrphgvir punvezna naq
grpuavpny nqivfre. Va 2021, ur sbhaqrq gur Fcrpvny Pbzcrgvgvir Fghqvrf
Cebwrpg, n abacebsvg vavgvngvir gb fgeratgura Nzrevpn’f ybat-grez
pbzcrgvgvirarff va NV naq grpuabybtl. Zbfg erpragyl, ur naq uvf jvsr
Jraql pbsbhaqrq Fpuzvqg Fpvraprf, n abacebsvg betnavmngvba jbexvat gb
nqinapr fpvrapr naq grpuabybtl gung qrrcraf uhzna haqrefgnaqvat bs gur
angheny jbeyq naq qrirybcf fbyhgvbaf gb tybony vffhrf.
Penvt W. Zhaqvr, cerfvqrag bs Zhaqvr & Nffbpvngrf, wbvarq Zvpebfbsg va
1992 naq ergverq va 2014 nf puvrs erfrnepu naq fgengrtl bssvpre. Ur nqivfrf
Zvpebfbsg ba dhnaghz pbzchgvat naq plorefrphevgl, vf n qverpgbe bs gur
Vafgvghgr sbe Flfgrzf Ovbybtl, n grpuabybtl nqivfre gb gur Pyrirynaq Pyvavp,
naq nyfb na vairfgbe/nqivfre va rneyl-fgntr pbzcnavrf vaibyirq va NV,
ovbgrpu, shfvba raretl, naq zngrevnyf fpvrapr. Ur freirq Cerfvqragf Pyvagba,

Ohfu, naq Bonzn ba gur Angvbany Frphevgl Gryrpbzzhavpngvbaf Nqivfbel
Pbhapvy naq gur Cerfvqrag’f Pbhapvy bs Nqivfbef ba Fpvrapr naq
Grpuabybtl. Nzbat uvf ubabef vf n Qbpgbe bs Ratvarrevat qrterr sebz
Eraffrynre Cbylgrpuavp Vafgvghgr.
